<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk</link><title>Fun Pro UK</title><description>All the latest news from the Experts in bringing the Fun to your Events! Check out the latest items and news with the Fun Pro UK team. On this page you will find short stories about venues and we..</description><language>en-gb</language><ttl>60</ttl><lastBuildDate>Mon, 24 Nov 2025 00:00:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news-feed.ashx" title="Fun Pro UK" rel="self" /><item><title>Creative Team Building Activities to Do in Birmingham</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-11-21/creative-team-building-activities-to-do-in-birmingham</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-11-21/creative-team-building-activities-to-do-in-birmingham</guid><pubDate>Fri, 21 Nov 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/team-building-event.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Planning a &lt;a href="/pages/conference-and-event-hire-birmingham"&gt;corporate event&lt;/a&gt; in Birmingham gives you access to the UK's second-largest city with its excellent transport links, diverse venues, and comprehensive range of activities. Whether you're organising a half-day energiser for your Birmingham-based team or bringing colleagues together from across the country for a full away day, understanding your options helps you create an event that genuinely strengthens your team whilst achieving your specific objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The challenge lies not in finding activities, but in choosing the right ones for your particular team dynamics, budget, and goals. This guide walks you through the practical considerations that matter when planning your event in Birmingham, from understanding what different &lt;a href="/pages/team-building-ideas"&gt;team building activities&lt;/a&gt; are most suitable for your event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Why Birmingham Is Perfect for Team Building Events&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/birmingham-city.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Birmingham's central UK location makes it remarkably accessible for teams travelling from across the country. With direct train connections from London (1 hour 20 minutes), Manchester (1 hour 30 minutes), and excellent motorway links via the M6, M5, and M42, it's often easier to bring a national team to Birmingham than to struggle with London's complexity and costs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The city's infrastructure supports corporate events exceptionally well. You'll find modern conference facilities like the &lt;a href="/pages/nec-birmingham"&gt;NEC&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href="/pages/game-hire-icc-birmingham"&gt;ICC&lt;/a&gt; alongside unique historical venues, from canal-side locations in Brindleyplace to the creative industrial spaces of Digbeth. This variety means you can match your venue to your team's personality and your event's objectives, whether that's a polished corporate environment or something more relaxed and characterful.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Birmingham's hospitality sector has developed to serve its substantial business community, which translates into competitive pricing, professional service, and venues accustomed to corporate requirements. For event planners, this means straightforward logistics when it comes to arranging things like hotels, restaurants, and activity providers who understand what you need and deliver it reliably.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Understanding Your Team Building Objectives&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/people-playing-during-team-building.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Before exploring specific activities, it's worth considering what you're actually trying to achieve. &lt;a href="/pages/team-building-ideas"&gt;Team building events&lt;/a&gt; succeed when they match their format to genuine objectives rather than simply booking something that sounds fun.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Are you bringing together a newly formed team that barely knows each other? Your priority might be creating relaxed opportunities for natural conversation. Perhaps you're addressing communication challenges within an established team, which suggests activities requiring collaboration and clear information sharing. If you're celebrating success or thanking your team for a demanding period, the focus shifts towards enjoyment and recognition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Team dynamics matter significantly when choosing activities. A group of twenty-five year-olds in marketing might thrive on competitive, high-energy challenges, whilst a finance team spanning ages twenty-five to sixty with varying fitness levels needs something more universally accessible. Neither approach is better; they're simply different tools for different situations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Timing considerations affect your options considerably. Summer months open up outdoor possibilities around Birmingham, though you'll need longer booking lead times as these popular slots fill quickly. &lt;a href="/pages/indoor-game-hire-for-corporate-events-across-uk"&gt;Indoor activities&lt;/a&gt; provide year-round reliability, particularly valuable for corporate schedules that can't accommodate weather-related rescheduling. Half-day activities (typically 2-3 hours) work well for teams based in Birmingham or as part of a wider &lt;a href="/pages/conference-and-event-hire-birmingham"&gt;conference&lt;/a&gt; programme, whilst full away days suit bringing together regional teams or marking significant occasions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Interactive Entertainment for Corporate Events in Birmingham&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/fun-pro-batak-interactive-game.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional interactive entertainment has become increasingly popular for corporate team building because it addresses several challenges simultaneously. Unlike activities requiring specific skills or fitness levels, well-designed &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; create immediate engagement across diverse groups.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;Racing simulators&lt;/a&gt; bring out everyone's competitive spirit whilst remaining genuinely accessible; you don't need driving skills to enjoy the experience, and the thrill of competition creates natural team dynamics and plenty of laughter. Similarly, reaction games like &lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/43/batak-pro"&gt;Batak Pro&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/61/batak-lite"&gt;Batak Lite&lt;/a&gt; test coordination and quick thinking in ways that don't penalise people less comfortable with physical activities. What matters is that the experience creates energy, encourages team support, and gives colleagues a chance to see each other in a completely different light from their usual office interactions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;Interactive entertainment&lt;/a&gt; works particularly well when you've got mixed groups of different ages, varying physical capabilities, or teams combining introverts who find forced icebreakers awkward with extroverts who thrive on them. Professional-grade equipment and proper &lt;a href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;delivery&lt;/a&gt; make the difference between an activity that feels slightly embarrassing and one that generates genuine excitement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For Birmingham-based events, interactive games can be set up in hotel function rooms, office spaces, or dedicated venues across the city centre, which provides flexibility for combining team building with meetings or conferences. The professional delivery aspect matters here; you need providers who arrive punctually, set up efficiently, and run activities that maintain momentum throughout your allocated time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Creative and Hands-On Experiences&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/bartenders-having-fun.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Chocolate making workshops&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These provide a structured activity that keeps hands busy whilst creating natural opportunities for conversation. You're working together on something tangible, learning new skills, and ending up with something to take home, all without the pressure of winners and losers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Pottery workshops&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These offer similar benefits with a different creative outlet. There's something genuinely relaxing about working with clay, and the focus required creates a comfortable atmosphere for quieter team members who might struggle in more boisterous activities. Birmingham has several pottery studios that cater to corporate groups, typically offering 2-3 hour sessions where everyone creates their own piece.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Cocktail masterclasses &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These have become popular for Birmingham corporate events, particularly when combined with evening socialising. Learning to mix drinks provides a surprisingly effective icebreaker; there's technique to learn, creativity to express, and the social element of sharing your creations. Venues like Dirty Martini in the city centre offer structured classes with professional bartenders, providing the right balance between learning and enjoyment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Pizza making workshops &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These take a similar approach with food rather than drinks. You'll typically spend time learning to prepare dough, select toppings, and use traditional pizza ovens, all whilst chatting with colleagues in an informal setting. It's particularly effective for teams who want something interactive but not competitive, and the shared meal afterwards extends the team building naturally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Active and Outdoor Team Building in Birmingham&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/outdoor-game-during-team-building.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When the weather permits and your team's fitness levels allow, outdoor activities in Birmingham provide memorable experiences. Retro sports day events tap into nostalgia whilst creating plenty of laughter; there's something delightfully levelling about watching senior managers attempt egg-and-spoon races or sack races. These activities work because they're familiar enough that nobody feels intimidated, yet unusual enough in a corporate context to feel special.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Treasure hunts around Birmingham city centre combine problem-solving with exploring the city. Teams follow clues around landmarks like Centenary Square, the Bullring, and the Jewellery Quarter, completing challenges and answering questions. It's particularly effective for bringing together people from different offices or departments who benefit from working together on neutral ground.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For teams seeking more adrenaline, Birmingham offers go-karting at TeamSport's Birmingham venue (which claims the longest track in the UK), quad biking experiences in the surrounding countryside, and climbing at venues like Rock Up in the city centre. These activities suit younger teams or those with established dynamics where competition enhances rather than complicates relationships.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It's worth considering that active outdoor activities require more careful planning. You'll need to communicate clearly about physical requirements, provide options for team members with different capabilities, and have backup plans for weather-dependent activities. NPF Bassetts Pole in Sutton Coldfield offers a comprehensive outdoor centre with multiple activities and indoor facilities, which provides useful flexibility.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Problem-Solving and Challenge-Based Activities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/escape-room.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Escape rooms &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These have become remarkably popular for &lt;a href="/pages/team-building-ideas"&gt;corporate team building&lt;/a&gt; because they require genuine collaboration under time pressure. Birmingham offers numerous options, from themed rooms in the city centre to mobile escape room providers who bring the experience to your venue. The challenge forces teams to communicate clearly, delegate effectively, and work together, all whilst being genuinely entertaining.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Crystal Maze-style challenges &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Teams rotate through physical, mental, skill, and mystery challenges, earning crystals (or points) before a final challenge. This format works well because it showcases different strengths; your quietest team member might excel at the puzzle round, whilst the most physically capable person shines elsewhere.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Murder mystery events &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These provide problem-solving in a more theatrical format. Professional actors guide teams through investigating a fictional crime, interviewing suspects, and piecing together clues. It's particularly effective for evening events or when combined with dinner, as the activity develops throughout the meal.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These challenge-based activities suit teams working on communication or decision-making skills, though they're less successful when team dynamics are already strained; pressure can amplify tensions rather than resolve them. They work best for reasonably cohesive teams looking to strengthen existing relationships.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Relaxation and Wellbeing Activities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/group-of-people-performing-yoga.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Not every team building event needs to be high-energy or competitive. Wellbeing activities have gained prominence as organisations recognise the value of supporting team mental health and providing genuine stress relief.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Yoga and pilates classes &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These can be arranged at your Birmingham office or venue, offering a completely different team experience. There's vulnerability in trying something new together, particularly something that requires focus and calm rather than performance. Many teams find this shared experience creates unexpected connections.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Sound bath sessions &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These use gongs, singing bowls, and other instruments to create an immersive relaxation experience. Whilst less common than yoga, they're increasingly available in Birmingham and suit teams who want to try something genuinely different whilst prioritising wellbeing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Life drawing classes &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These offer creative expression without requiring artistic skill. The focus and concentration required create a meditative quality, whilst the shared slightly-awkward-but-interesting experience becomes a talking point. It's particularly effective for teams who find forced fun activities uncomfortable but still want time together outside normal work contexts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These activities work best when positioned honestly; they're not about high energy or competition but about giving your team space to breathe, reset, and connect in a gentler way. They suit teams dealing with stressful periods or organisations genuinely committed to wellbeing rather than simply ticking boxes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Birmingham Venues and Locations for Team Building&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/beautiful-city-of-birmingham.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Understanding Birmingham's geography helps you plan logistics effectively. The city centre offers several distinct areas, each with its own character and practical considerations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Brindleyplace&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Sitting along the canal network, this area provides attractive surroundings with numerous bars and restaurants. It's easily accessible from Birmingham New Street station and has good parking, making it practical for both local and travelling teams. The area suits activities that benefit from attractive surroundings or can be combined with casual dining.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Colmore Row and the broader business district &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This area offers convenience for Birmingham-based teams, particularly those whose offices are already in this area. It's the most corporate part of the city, which feels appropriate for some events but might lack character for teams seeking something more memorable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Digbeth &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Recently this area has emerged as Birmingham's creative quarter, with industrial venues offering character and space. It's slightly further from the main transport hubs, which means it works best when you're arranging transport or your team is comfortable navigating independently. The area suits activities emphasising creativity or teams who appreciate less polished, more authentic settings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;The Jewellery Quarter &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Providing historic charm with boutique venues, it's walkable from the city centre and offers character without being too far from amenities. This area works well for &lt;a href="/news/2024-11-29/team-building-activities-for-small-groups"&gt;smaller teams&lt;/a&gt; or activities like creative workshops where the venue's atmosphere contributes to the experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Broad Street &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This is Birmingham's main nightlife area, which makes it excellent for evening team building or activities you're combining with drinks and socialising. Venues here understand group bookings and late finishes, though daytime activities might feel slightly incongruous in spaces designed for evening entertainment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Outside the city centre, venues like NPF Bassetts Pole offer dedicated outdoor activity centres with professional facilities, whilst various country estates and conference centres in the surrounding countryside provide options for teams wanting to escape the urban environment entirely.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Choosing the Right Activity for Your Team&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/team-building-activity.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Matching activities to your specific team requires considering several factors simultaneously. Team size affects what's practical; activities that work brilliantly for twelve people might feel chaotic or impersonal with fifty. Interactive entertainment and sports-style activities typically scale well, whilst creative workshops often work better with smaller groups where everyone receives individual attention.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Physical capabilities matter more than many people initially consider. It's easy to assume everyone can participate in moderately active challenges, but teams include people with varying fitness levels, mobility considerations, and comfort zones. Choosing activities that don't penalise less physically capable people ensures everyone feels included rather than embarrassed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The personality mix within your team influences what succeeds. Teams with many introverted members might find aggressive icebreakers uncomfortable, whilst groups of extroverts might feel underwhelmed by quieter creative activities. The goal isn't to exclude either group but to find activities where both can engage comfortably.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Budget considerations extend beyond the activity cost itself. Factor in transport (particularly if you're bringing teams from different locations), catering, any accommodation requirements, and contingency funds. Birmingham's competitive market means you can usually find good value, but rushing into the cheapest option often means compromising on quality or suitability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When speaking with activity providers, ask about their experience with corporate events, what they provide versus what you need to arrange, how they handle different group sizes, and what happens if circumstances change. Professional providers in Birmingham are accustomed to these questions and should answer them clearly and confidently.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What are the most popular team building activities in Birmingham?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Interactive games, escape rooms, creative workshops, and outdoor treasure hunts consistently rank among the most popular activities. This popularity stems from their inclusivity; they work across different ages, abilities, and personalities without requiring specific skills. Professional delivery matters significantly; activities succeed when providers understand corporate requirements and handle logistics smoothly, leaving you to focus on your team rather than worrying about organisation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How much should I budget for team building in Birmingham?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Budget expectations vary considerably based on activity type. Creative workshops and relaxed activities typically cost &amp;pound;20-40 per person, interactive entertainment and problem-solving challenges range from &amp;pound;30-60 per person, whilst outdoor adventure activities and full-day experiences often reach &amp;pound;40-80+ per person. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These costs usually include basic delivery but may not cover venue hire, catering, or transport. Birmingham's competitive market means you can find quality at various price points, though unusually cheap options often compromise on equipment quality or professional facilitation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How far in advance should I book team building activities in Birmingham?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Summer months and the Christmas period require the longest lead times; ideally 8-12 weeks for popular activities and venues. Spring and autumn offer more flexibility, with quality providers typically available at 4-6 weeks notice. Indoor activities generally have better availability than outdoor options or venues with limited capacity. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Booking early provides better choice and rates, though Birmingham's comprehensive market means last-minute options usually exist if circumstances demand them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What team building activities work for large groups in Birmingham?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Interactive games, treasure hunts, sports day events, and challenge-based activities scale effectively to large groups because they maintain engagement without requiring everyone to focus on a single facilitator simultaneously. Venue capacity becomes the primary constraint; you'll need spaces that accommodate your numbers comfortably. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional facilitation matters more with larger groups; experienced providers manage logistics, maintain momentum, and ensure everyone participates rather than some people drifting to the periphery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Are there team building activities suitable for mixed abilities in Birmingham?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Creative workshops, problem-solving challenges, and professional interactive entertainment cater well to mixed abilities because they don't require specific physical capabilities or penalise people with mobility considerations. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When evaluating activities, consider whether success depends on particular physical abilities or if people can contribute in different ways. The best providers ask about your team composition and adapt accordingly, which demonstrates their experience with diverse groups.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can I combine team building with a conference in Birmingham?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Birmingham's strong conference infrastructure makes this remarkably straightforward. Many venues offer both conference facilities and space for team building activities, or they're located near activity providers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt; Half-day activities (typically 2-3 hours) work particularly well for conference programmes, either as energisers between sessions or as afternoon activities following morning meetings. Interactive entertainment, creative workshops, and problem-solving challenges suit this format because they deliver impact within limited timeframes whilst complementing rather than overwhelming conference content.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Small Conference vs. Large Conference</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-11-03/small-conference-vs-large-conference</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-11-03/small-conference-vs-large-conference</guid><pubDate>Mon, 03 Nov 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2&gt;Small Conference vs. Large Conference: How to Choose the Right Interactive Entertainment&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/group-of-professional-people-celebrating.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Are you planning a &lt;a href="/pages/conference-idea"&gt;conference&lt;/a&gt;? One of the most important decisions you'll make is selecting the right entertainment to keep your attendees engaged, energised, and talking long after the event ends. However, what works brilliantly for an intimate gathering of 30 colleagues might fall flat at a large-scale conference with 300 attendees, and vice versa.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Interactive games and entertainment aren't one-size-fits-all. The size of your conference fundamentally changes how you approach entertainment hire, from the types of games you select to how many you need, where you place them, and how your attendees will interact with them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;With over 15 years of experience as &lt;a href="/pages/about-corporate-entertainment-hire"&gt;corporate event specialists&lt;/a&gt;, we've helped event planners &lt;a href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;across the UK&lt;/a&gt; navigate these decisions for conferences of every size. In this guide, we'll walk you through the key considerations for choosing &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive entertainment&lt;/a&gt; based on your conference size, so you can create an engaging experience that achieves your event goals whilst staying within budget.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Understanding the Key Differences Between Small and Large Conferences&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Before we explore specific entertainment choices, it's worth considering what actually defines a small versus large conference, and why size matters so much.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For the purposes of interactive entertainment planning, we typically consider a small &lt;a href="/pages/conference-idea"&gt;conference&lt;/a&gt; to be anything from 20 to 100 attendees. These events often take place in hotel meeting rooms, small conference centres, or dedicated corporate training facilities. They're usually focused on specific topics, &lt;a href="/pages/team-building-ideas"&gt;team building&lt;/a&gt;, or departmental gatherings where attendees generally know each other or share a common purpose.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;A large conference, on the other hand, typically involves 100 to 500+ attendees. These events take place in convention centres, large hotels, or purpose-built conference venues. They often feature multiple sessions, keynote speakers, and attendees from different departments, companies, or even industries who may be meeting for the first time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Why does this distinction matter for &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive entertainment&lt;/a&gt;? Because conference size affects everything: the space you have available, how attendees engage with activities, the logistics of &lt;a href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;delivery&lt;/a&gt; and setup, and ultimately which games will create the most impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Space and Venue Considerations for Conference Game Hire&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;One of the first practical considerations when hiring &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; for your conference is space. It's not just about whether games will physically fit; it's about creating an environment where entertainment enhances the flow of your event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Space Requirements for Small Conferences&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Small conference venues present unique space challenges. You're often working with breakout rooms, smaller conference halls, or sectioned areas within larger spaces. Every square metre counts, and you need to be thoughtful about how interactive games fit into the overall layout.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Most compact interactive games require approximately 2 to 3 square metres of floor space. Reaction-based games like &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/63/danger-zone-strike-a-light-game-hire"&gt;Strike a Light&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="/category/batak"&gt;Batak&lt;/a&gt; walls tend to have smaller footprints, making them ideal for tighter spaces. You'll also need to consider the "playing radius" which refers to the space around the game where people stand to play, wait their turn, or watch others compete.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;In smaller venues, we typically recommend positioning 2 to 4 games maximum. This provides variety without overwhelming the space or making the room feel cluttered. Think about room flow: you don't want games blocking natural walkways or preventing attendees from accessing refreshments, presentations, or other key areas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Space Requirements for Large Conferences&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Large conference venues offer completely different opportunities. With more space comes the ability to create multiple entertainment zones, but you'll need to think strategically about placement to ensure games are discovered and used throughout the event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;At larger conferences, we often recommend 6 to 10+ interactive games, depending on attendee numbers and event duration. The key is distributing them thoughtfully across the venue. Consider creating distinct zones: a high-energy area with &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;racing simulators&lt;/a&gt; and competitive games, a more relaxed zone with accessible challenges, and perhaps games positioned near networking spaces to serve as natural conversation starters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Larger equipment like racing simulators requires approximately 3 to 4 square metres each, plus additional space for spectators. Games positioned near main thoroughfares, registration areas, or refreshment stations naturally attract higher participation. Strategic distribution ensures attendees encounter different activities as they move through the venue, maintaining energy throughout the day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Attendee Engagement: How Conference Size Changes the Game&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/team-building.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Understanding how conference size affects attendee behaviour is crucial when selecting interactive entertainment. The dynamics of participation shift dramatically based on group size.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Engagement Dynamics at Small Conferences&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;At smaller conferences, social dynamics work in your favour. There's less anonymity, which means attendees often feel more comfortable, or sometimes more obligated; to participate. When 40 people are in a room and a few start playing an interactive game, others naturally gravitate towards the activity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You'll typically see higher participation rates at small conferences. It's not unusual for 70-80% of attendees to try at least one interactive game during the event. This happens partly because there's social visibility, people notice who's joining in, and partly because the smaller scale makes activities feel more accessible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;However, this intimacy cuts both ways. Some attendees, particularly those who are naturally shy, may feel more exposed at small conferences. This is why we emphasise offering games with different participation levels. Not everyone needs to be the star player; some people are perfectly happy keeping score or watching.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The beauty of interactive entertainment at small conferences is that games become natural conversation starters. Two colleagues who've just competed on &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/63/danger-zone-strike-a-light-game-hire"&gt;Strike a Light&lt;/a&gt; now have a shared experience to discuss. That's the foundation of genuine connection, which is often exactly what organisers hope to achieve.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Engagement Dynamics at Large Conferences&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Large conferences present a different engagement picture. Whilst you'll have lower participation rates percentage-wise with perhaps 30-40% of attendees directly playing games, the absolute numbers are still significant. At a conference of 300 people, that's 90 to 120 participants actively engaging with your entertainment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;At this scale, creating what we call "spectator appeal" becomes important. Games need to attract attention from across large spaces and draw people in through visual interest and energy. A racing simulator with multiple screens or a &lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/3/cash-grabber-machine-hire"&gt;Cash Grabber&lt;/a&gt; with swirling branded notes creates a focal point that attendees notice as they move through the venue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Queue management becomes a consideration at large conferences. With more people competing for the same activities, you'll want enough variety to prevent frustration. This is where having 6 to 10 games makes sense as it distributes attendees across multiple activities and keeps wait times manageable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Large conferences benefit from what we call "permission through observation." When attendees see others enjoying interactive games, it gives them permission to join in themselves. This cascading effect means positioning games in high-visibility areas significantly impacts participation rates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Selecting the Right Interactive Games for Your Conference Size&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/speed-test-competition-interactive-games.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Now we come to the practical question: which games should you actually hire? The answer depends heavily on your conference size, as different games excel in different settings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Best Interactive Games for Small Conferences (20-100 attendees)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For smaller conferences, focus on games that encourage high participation, spark conversation, and don't require extensive space. Reaction-based challenges work particularly well because they're quick to play, easy to understand, and create instant moments of friendly competition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Games like Batak reaction walls and Strike a Light are excellent choices for small conferences. They have compact footprints, can accommodate a steady stream of players without creating long queues, and appeal to a wide range of ages and abilities. The beauty of these skill-based challenges is that everyone can participate regardless of physical ability; you're simply testing your reflexes against the clock.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider games that work as conversation starters. Giant&lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire/9/giant-buzz-wire"&gt; buzzwire&lt;/a&gt; challenges, car simulators, or precision-based activities give people something to discuss beyond the standard opening questions. They create shared experiences that break down social barriers naturally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For small conferences, we typically recommend 2 to 4 games maximum. This provides variety without fragmenting your group too much. Think about the mix of skills your games test. One reaction-based game, one precision challenge, and perhaps one fun &lt;a href="/category/company-award-ceremonies/11/classic-photo-booths"&gt;photo booth&lt;/a&gt; to create a balanced selection that appeals to different personalities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Best Interactive Games for Large Conferences (100-500+ attendees)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Large conferences allow you to think bigger, literally. This is where high-impact entertainment comes into its own, with games that create visual spectacle and draw attendees from across the venue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Racing simulators work brilliantly at large conferences. They have strong spectator appeal, with screens visible from a distance and the competitive element creating natural crowds of supporters. Multiple simulators positioned together create a focal point that becomes a destination within the conference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Cash Grabbers and similar high-energy games create moments that attendees photograph and share on social media. At large conferences where you're potentially trying to create buzz or strengthen brand awareness, these visually striking activities contribute to the overall impact of your event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;However, don't overlook more accessible options. Large conferences benefit from a strategic mix: some high-octane activities for the competitive attendees, alongside more approachable challenges for those who prefer lower-pressure participation. Dance machines, photo booth experiences, or precision challenges provide this balance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For conferences of 100 to 200 attendees, consider 6 to 8 games. For 200 to 500 attendees, 8 to 12 games ensures variety and prevents bottlenecks. The exact number depends on your event duration&amp;mdash;a 2-hour evening reception needs fewer options than a full-day conference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Budget Considerations: Getting the Most from Your Conference Entertainment Hire&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Let's address the practical reality of budgets. Event planning always involves balancing what you'd ideally like against what's financially feasible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Small conferences often work with tighter per-person budgets. When you're planning for 40 attendees, the cost of interactive game hire represents a more significant portion of your overall budget. Our recommendation for small conferences is to focus on 2 to 3 high-quality games rather than spreading your budget across numerous options. Two excellent interactive games that suit your audience will create far more engagement than five mediocre activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Large conferences can leverage economies of scale. Whilst your absolute entertainment budget is higher, the per-person cost often becomes more manageable as attendee numbers increase. This allows you to create the variety and impact that large conferences demand without the per-person costs becoming prohibitive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When planning your budget, consider what's included in the hire cost. With &lt;a href="/pages/about-corporate-entertainment-hire"&gt;Fun Pro&lt;/a&gt;, delivery, professional setup, and collection* are included as part of our &lt;a href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;nationwide service&lt;/a&gt;. There are no surprise costs for installation or equipment testing. This comprehensive approach helps you budget accurately.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It's worth thinking about entertainment as an investment rather than simply a cost. Interactive games serve multiple purposes: they're ice-breakers, networking facilitators, energy boosters, and memory makers. When attendees leave your conference talking about their experiences, when they've made genuine connections with colleagues; that's the return on your entertainment investment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Early booking often provides advantages. Planning ahead gives you the best selection of games for your dates and allows time to discuss your specific requirements with our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;* Delivery, setup and collection may incur additional costs depending on your location and the final cost will always be shared with you when providing a quote.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Logistics and Setup: What Event Planners Need to Know&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Behind every successful conference is meticulous planning of logistics. Understanding what's involved in delivering and setting up interactive entertainment helps you coordinate smoothly with your venue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Delivery and Setup for Small Conference Venues&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Small venue logistics are generally simpler, but space constraints require careful planning. We'll coordinate with you on access times, delivery schedules, and any venue-specific requirements well before your event date.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Setup time for 2 to 4 games typically takes 1 to 2 hours. We schedule this to ensure everything's ready before your attendees arrive, testing each game to confirm proper operation. It's helpful to share your floor plan with us during the planning stage so we can advise on optimal game placement and identify any potential space issues before event day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Power requirements for small conference setups are usually straightforward. Most venues have adequate power points, though we'll always confirm electrical needs when discussing your specific game selection. Collection happens after your event concludes, coordinated around your venue access times.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Delivery and Setup for Large Conference Venues&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Large conference logistics require more extensive coordination, particularly at major venues like convention centres. These locations often have specific protocols for deliveries, loading bay access, and equipment installation that we navigate regularly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Setup for large conferences typically requires extended time&amp;mdash;often 3 to 4 hours for 6 to 10+ games, and sometimes day-before installation for very large events. This ensures everything's positioned correctly, tested thoroughly, and ready to create the impact you need.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Detailed floor plans become crucial at this scale. We'll work with you to map out exact game positions, considering factors like power distribution, natural attendee flow, and sightlines. This planning stage helps avoid last-minute surprises.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We're experienced working at major UK venues and understand the coordination required with other suppliers. Whether it's ensuring our setup doesn't interfere with AV installation, catering preparation, or registration desk arrangement, we've navigated these logistics countless times at events across the UK.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Making Your Choice: A Practical Framework&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;With all this information in mind, here's a practical framework to guide your decision-making process when hiring interactive entertainment for your conference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Start by knowing your numbers. Your attendee count is the foundation of every other decision. Are you planning for 35 people, 150, or 400? This immediately narrows your options and helps determine how many games you'll need.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Understand your space. What's your venue like? Do you have a single large hall, multiple breakout rooms, or a mix of both? How much floor space can reasonably be dedicated to interactive entertainment? If possible, share floor plans or venue details when discussing options with suppliers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Define your primary goal. What are you hoping to achieve with interactive entertainment? Is networking your top priority? Are you focused on team building? Perhaps you're launching a product and want to create memorable brand moments? Your goal should guide which games you select.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider your audience mix. Think about who's attending. What's the age range? Are there varying physical abilities to consider? Will you have a mix of outgoing personalities and quieter attendees? The best entertainment selections consider everyone.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Set a realistic budget. Be honest about what you can invest in interactive entertainment. It's better to have this conversation early and receive recommendations that genuinely fit your financial parameters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This is where expert advice makes a real difference. With 15 years of experience delivering interactive entertainment to conferences across the UK, we've seen what works in countless situations. We understand the practical realities of different venues and how to create engaging experiences within different budget constraints.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Early planning gives you the best outcomes. Reach out 4 to 8 weeks before your conference to discuss your requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How many interactive games should I hire for a conference of 150 people?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For a conference of 150 attendees, we typically recommend 4 to 6 interactive games. This provides variety without overcrowding your venue and ensures attendees don't face long waits. The exact number depends on your event duration; a 2-hour networking session needs fewer games than a full-day conference with multiple breaks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What's the minimum space requirement for conference game hire?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Space requirements vary by game type. Compact games like reaction walls need approximately 2m x 2m, whilst racing simulators require around 3m x 3m including space for players and spectators. For small conferences, you can create excellent engagement with as little as 20 square metres dedicated to interactive entertainment. We always recommend sharing your floor plan with us so we can advise on the best layout.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Do you deliver and set up equipment for conferences across the UK?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, Fun Pro provides &lt;a href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;nationwide delivery&lt;/a&gt;, professional setup, and collection across the UK. With over 15 years of experience as corporate event specialists, we handle everything from our Coventry base to venues throughout England, Wales, and Scotland. Setup times are coordinated with your venue to ensure everything's ready before your attendees arrive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are interactive games suitable for formal corporate conferences?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Absolutely. Interactive games work brilliantly at formal conferences by providing natural ice-breakers and networking opportunities. They help colleagues see each other in a different light and create memorable moments that people discuss long after the event. We understand how to provide professional entertainment that enhances rather than detracts from your conference objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How far in advance should I book conference entertainment?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For the best choice of games and guaranteed availability, we recommend booking 4 to 8 weeks before your conference. However, we can often accommodate bookings with shorter notice. Early planning gives you time to discuss your specific requirements with our team and ensures we can recommend the perfect mix of games for your conference size and goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Can you cater for attendees with different abilities at conferences?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, inclusive entertainment is one of our core values. We consider diverse needs when recommending games, ensuring there are options suitable for different ages, abilities, and comfort levels. Many of our games can be adjusted for accessibility, and we'll always discuss your attendee mix to ensure everyone can participate and enjoy themselves.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Ready to Plan Your Conference Entertainment?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Choosing the right&lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt; interactive entertainment&lt;/a&gt; for your conference doesn't need to be complicated. Whether you're planning an intimate gathering of 30 colleagues or a large-scale conference with 300+ attendees, the key is understanding how size affects every aspect of your entertainment strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;With over 15 years of experience as corporate event specialists, we've helped event planners across the UK create engaging conference experiences that achieve their goals. From intimate team-building sessions to large-scale conferences at major venues, we understand the unique considerations each type of event presents.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Our consultative approach means we take the time to understand your specific requirements; your attendee numbers, venue constraints, conference goals, and audience mix. We'll recommend the right combination of interactive games to create genuine &lt;a href="/news/2024-12-17/exhibition-stand-ideas-8-ways-to-attract-attention-and-boost-engagement"&gt;engagement&lt;/a&gt; whilst working within your budget.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Get in touch&lt;/a&gt; with our friendly team to discuss your conference requirements. We'll guide you through the options, answer your questions, and help you create an event that attendees remember for all the right reasons.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>The Complete Guide to Choosing the Right Venue for Your Corporate Event</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-09-26/the-complete-guide-to-choosing-the-right-venue-for-your-corporate-event</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-09-26/the-complete-guide-to-choosing-the-right-venue-for-your-corporate-event</guid><pubDate>Fri, 26 Sep 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/fun-pro-corporate-event.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Planning a &lt;a href="/pages/office-and-corporate-entertainment"&gt;corporate event&lt;/a&gt; can feel overwhelming, and perhaps no decision carries more weight than selecting the right venue. With over 15 years of experience as corporate event specialists, we understand the pressure you face when choosing a space that needs to impress clients, engage employees, and reflect your company's professionalism. The venue you select will influence everything from attendance rates to the overall success of your event, making this choice one that deserves careful consideration and expert guidance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Whether you're organising a &lt;a href="/pages/team-building-ideas"&gt;team-building day&lt;/a&gt;, client entertainment event, or company &lt;a href="/pages/conference-idea"&gt;conference&lt;/a&gt;, the right venue creates the foundation for memorable experiences that bring people together. Let's explore the essential factors that will help you make this crucial decision with confidence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Venue Selection Can Make or Break Your Event&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The venue you choose does far more than simply provide four walls and a roof. It sets the entire tone for your event and directly impacts how attendees perceive both the occasion and your organisation. A well-chosen venue enhances engagement, supports your event objectives, and creates an atmosphere where genuine connections can flourish.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider the ripple effects of venue selection: the right space can boost attendance by being easily accessible, whilst poor accessibility might lead to disappointing turnout. A venue with adequate capacity and proper layout ensures comfortable networking and effective presentations, whereas cramped conditions can leave attendees feeling frustrated and disengaged.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;From our experience working with companies like &lt;a href="/pages/rolls-royce-christmas-fun"&gt;Rolls-Royce&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="/pages/putting-kpmg-in-the-picture"&gt;KPMG&lt;/a&gt;, we've seen how venue choice affects everything from the effectiveness of &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive entertainment&lt;/a&gt; to the overall professional impression your event creates. Corporate events, in particular, require venues that can accommodate the specific needs of business audiences whilst maintaining the flexibility to support various activities and presentations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The financial implications are equally significant. Choosing the wrong venue can lead to unexpected costs, from additional equipment hire to last-minute accessibility solutions. More importantly, a poorly chosen venue can undermine months of planning and investment in other aspects of your event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Essential Venue Selection Criteria for Corporate Events&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/london-eye.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Location and Accessibility&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The location of your venue plays a crucial role in determining who can attend your event and how they'll feel about the experience from the moment they receive the invitation. For corporate events where you're expecting attendees from across the UK, consider venues with excellent transport links to major cities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Transport Links and Geographic Considerations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Look for venues near major motorway junctions, particularly the M25, M40, M6, and M1 for events drawing attendees from different regions. Railway connections are equally important &amp;ndash; venues within walking distance of main line stations significantly reduce travel stress for your guests. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For international attendees or those travelling from Scotland and Northern Ireland, proximity to major airports like Heathrow, Manchester, or Birmingham can make the difference between guests attending and having to decline the invitation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Parking and Local Transport&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Adequate parking remains essential for many corporate events. Ensure the venue offers sufficient spaces for your expected attendance, and check whether parking charges apply &amp;ndash; these can add unexpected costs to your attendees' experience. For venues in city centres where parking is limited, excellent public transport links become even more critical.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Inclusive Accessibility&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider the diverse needs of your attendees from the outset. This means ensuring step-free access, accessible toilets, hearing loop systems where appropriate, and clear signage throughout the venue. Many modern corporate attendees expect venues to accommodate different mobility requirements, and planning for this demonstrates your organisation's inclusive values.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Capacity and Space Planning&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Getting the capacity right requires more than simply counting heads. You'll need to consider different space requirements for various parts of your event and plan for a comfortable experience that encourages the interactions you're hoping to achieve.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Estimating Attendance Accurately&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Start with your target attendee list, but apply realistic expectations about actual turnout. For internal corporate events, you might expect 80-90% attendance, whilst external client events often see 60-70% of invited guests attending. However, always plan venue capacity for your full invitation list &amp;ndash; it's far better to have extra space than to turn away attendees.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Space Requirements for Different Activities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/office-and-corporate-entertainment"&gt;Corporate events&lt;/a&gt; rarely involve just one type of activity. You might need theatre-style seating for presentations, small group spaces for breakout sessions, and open areas for networking or interactive entertainment. Consider whether your chosen activities require additional ceiling height &amp;ndash; this is particularly important if you're planning to include &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; or technology demonstrations that enhance engagement and team building.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Layout Flexibility&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Look for venues that offer configurable spaces rather than fixed layouts. The ability to adjust room configurations throughout the day allows you to create different atmospheres for different segments of your event. This flexibility becomes invaluable when you're incorporating various elements like presentations, networking, and interactive activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Technical Infrastructure and Equipment&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Today's corporate events rely heavily on technology, and venue limitations can significantly impact your event's effectiveness. Don't assume that all venues offer the same level of technical support &amp;ndash; there can be substantial differences in quality and reliability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Audio-Visual Requirements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional-grade AV equipment is non-negotiable for most corporate events. Ensure the venue provides reliable sound systems, high-quality projectors or LED screens, and proper lighting controls. Test everything during your site visit &amp;ndash; poor audio quality can undermine even the most engaging presentations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Connectivity and Power&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Reliable WiFi isn't just helpful; it's essential for modern corporate events. Verify that the venue's internet capacity can handle your expected number of users simultaneously. Don't forget about power requirements, particularly if you're incorporating interactive technology or entertainment that requires additional electrical supply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Integration with External Suppliers&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Many venues have restrictions on external equipment or preferred supplier lists. If you're planning to include interactive entertainment or specialised technology, confirm early in the selection process that your chosen suppliers can work effectively within the venue's constraints. Some venues charge additional fees for external equipment, whilst others may have safety requirements that affect setup times and logistics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Catering and Hospitality Options&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Food and hospitality standards can significantly influence how attendees remember your event. The quality of catering often becomes a talking point that extends well beyond the event itself, making this an area where investment in quality pays dividends.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Service Standards and Flexibility&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Look for venues that can accommodate various dietary requirements without making special requests feel burdensome. Professional catering teams should handle allergies, religious dietary needs, and lifestyle choices seamlessly. The service style &amp;ndash; whether buffet, served meals, or casual refreshments &amp;ndash; should align with your event's tone and timing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Break-out Spaces and Flow&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider how catering areas integrate with your overall event flow. Separate spaces for registration refreshments, lunch, and networking drinks help create natural transitions between different parts of your programme. This is particularly important for events that include interactive elements where you want to maintain energy and engagement throughout the day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Hidden Venue Costs to Budget For&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Venue hire costs can extend well beyond the basic room rental, and unexpected charges have derailed many event budgets. Understanding potential additional costs helps you make informed decisions and avoid unpleasant surprises.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Common Additional Charges&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Most venues charge extra for services like cleaning, security, and equipment that you might assume are included. Cleaning fees often apply regardless of how tidy you leave the space, whilst security requirements may be mandatory for evening events or when alcohol is served. Equipment hire &amp;ndash; from basic items like coat rails to essential AV gear &amp;ndash; can add substantial costs to your budget.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Time-Related Costs&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Pay close attention to the venue's standard hire hours and overtime charges. Many venues charge premium rates for early morning access or late evening use, which can be essential for setup and breakdown of interactive entertainment or elaborate decorations. Some venues also charge for rehearsal time or technical testing, particularly important if your event includes presentations or demonstrations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;VAT and Invoice Structures&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Always confirm whether quoted prices include VAT, as this 20% addition can significantly impact budgets. Some venues structure their pricing to include certain services in the base cost, whilst others itemise everything separately. Request detailed breakdowns that show exactly what's included and what will incur additional charges.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Insurance and Liability Requirements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Many venues require event organisers to provide public liability insurance, typically &amp;pound;2-5 million coverage. This might be included in your company's existing business insurance, but it's worth confirming coverage levels and obtaining certificates well in advance. Some activities or entertainment options may require additional insurance considerations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Questions to Ask Potential Venues&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The right questions during your initial venue enquiries can save considerable time and prevent mismatched expectations. Here's what to ask before you even arrange a site visit:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Initial Enquiry Essentials&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;What are your standard hire hours, and what are the overtime rates?&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Do you have exclusive use of hired spaces, or might there be other events running simultaneously?&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;What's included in the base hire fee, and what services incur additional charges?&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Can you provide a detailed breakdown of all potential costs?&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;What are your payment terms and cancellation policies?&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Do you have restrictions on external suppliers or preferred vendor lists?&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Site Visit Priorities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;During your venue visit, focus on practical considerations that affect your attendees' experience. Check the registration and reception areas for smooth arrival processes. Test the acoustics in presentation spaces by speaking from different positions. Examine the flow between different areas, particularly important if your event includes various activities or entertainment elements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Contract and Policy Clarifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Understanding venue policies prevents problems later in your planning process. Ask about their approach to setup and breakdown times, particularly if you're incorporating interactive entertainment that requires professional installation. Clarify policies around decorations, signage, and any restrictions that might affect your branding or theming plans.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Venue Types for Different Corporate Event Goals&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Different corporate events require different venue characteristics, and understanding these requirements helps you focus your search on appropriate options.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Team Building and Interactive Events&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Events focused on team building and colleague interaction need venues that support participation and engagement. Look for spaces with flexible layouts that can accommodate group activities and interactive entertainment. Consider ceiling height requirements for certain activities, and ensure there's adequate space for people to move around comfortably.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The venue's atmosphere plays a crucial role in encouraging participation. Spaces that feel too formal might inhibit the relaxed interaction you're hoping to create, whilst overly casual venues might not reflect the professional standards appropriate for corporate events. Natural light and good ventilation help maintain energy levels throughout active team-building sessions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When planning &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive entertainment&lt;/a&gt;, consider practical requirements like floor surfaces suitable for activities, adequate power supply for technology-based games, and acoustics that allow multiple activities to run simultaneously without interference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Conferences and Presentations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Conference venues require excellent sightlines, professional lighting, and acoustics that ensure every attendee can engage fully with presentations. Theatre-style seating works well for keynote sessions, but consider whether you'll need breakout spaces for smaller group discussions or workshops.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Registration and welcome areas set the tone for &lt;a href="/pages/conference-idea"&gt;professional conferences&lt;/a&gt;, so look for venues with impressive entrance spaces that reflect the calibre of your event. Technical infrastructure becomes particularly important for conferences, including reliable internet for live streaming or social media engagement, and professional-grade AV equipment for clear presentations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Client Entertainment and Networking&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Client entertainment events require venues that create impressive first impressions whilst facilitating comfortable networking. The atmosphere should reflect your company's brand and values whilst feeling welcoming and engaging for guests who may not know each other well.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider how the venue layout supports natural networking flow. Spaces that are too large can feel empty and make networking difficult, whilst cramped conditions prevent comfortable conversation. Look for venues with interesting features or talking points that provide natural conversation starters and help break down social barriers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Common Venue Selection Mistakes (and How to Avoid Them)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Learning from common pitfalls can help you avoid the frustration and additional costs that come with venue selection mistakes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Booking Too Late&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Popular venues, particularly those in convenient locations with good facilities, book up months in advance. Starting your venue search at least six months before your event date gives you better options and often better pricing. Last-minute bookings frequently result in compromises on location, quality, or cost.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Underestimating Space Requirements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Many event organisers focus primarily on seated capacity without considering space needed for registration, catering, networking, and interactive activities. Plan for the total experience your attendees will have, including arrival and departure logistics. It's generally better to choose a slightly larger venue than to discover you're cramped for space.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Ignoring Backup Plans&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Weather contingencies aren't just important for outdoor venues &amp;ndash; consider what happens if transport links are disrupted, if technical systems fail, or if attendance significantly exceeds expectations. Venues with flexible spaces and good backup facilities provide peace of mind and professional alternatives when circumstances change.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Failing to Test Everything&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Never assume that equipment works perfectly or that room layouts will function as you imagine. During your site visit, test microphones, check internet speeds, and walk through your entire event timeline. This is particularly important if you're incorporating interactive entertainment or technology demonstrations that require reliable technical support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Not Considering the Complete Attendee Journey&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Think beyond the event itself to the complete experience your attendees will have. This includes everything from finding parking to locating facilities, from registration processes to departure logistics. Small frustrations in any of these areas can significantly impact how attendees remember your event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How far in advance should I book a corporate event venue?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For the best selection and pricing, start your venue search 6-8 months before your event date. Popular venues and peak times (spring and autumn for many corporate events) require even longer lead times. However, don't worry if you're working with shorter timescales &amp;ndash; many venues have cancellations or quieter periods that can work in your favour.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What's the most important factor when choosing an event venue?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Whilst all factors matter, location and accessibility often have the greatest impact on attendance and attendee satisfaction. The best venue facilities won't compensate for poor accessibility that prevents people from attending or creates stress about getting there.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do I calculate the right venue capacity for my event?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Plan for your full invitation list rather than expected attendance, but consider different space requirements for different activities. Allow approximately 6-8 square feet per person for reception-style networking, 10-12 square feet for seated dining, and additional space for interactive activities or entertainment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What questions should I ask during a venue site visit?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Focus on practical considerations: test the acoustics, check the flow between spaces, verify technical capabilities, and understand all cost implications. Ask about setup and breakdown procedures, particularly if you're incorporating entertainment or activities that require professional installation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How can I ensure my venue choice supports interactive entertainment?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider ceiling height, floor surfaces, power requirements, and acoustics when planning interactive elements. Discuss your entertainment plans with venue staff during your visit to identify any restrictions or additional requirements. Some venues have experience with interactive corporate entertainment and can provide valuable insights.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What are typical venue hire costs for corporate events in the UK?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Costs vary significantly based on location, facilities, and time of year. London venues typically range from &amp;pound;500-&amp;pound;5,000+ per day, whilst regional venues might start from &amp;pound;200-&amp;pound;2,000 per day. Remember to budget for additional costs like catering, equipment, and any extra services that aren't included in the base hire fee.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Do I need public liability insurance for my corporate event?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Most venues require event organisers to have public liability insurance, typically &amp;pound;2-5 million coverage. This might be included in your company's business insurance, but check coverage levels and obtain certificates in advance. Some interactive entertainment or activities may require additional insurance considerations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 30px; color: inherit;"&gt;Ready to start planning your next corporate event? &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Our experienced team understands the challenges of event planning and can help you create engaging experiences that achieve your objectives whilst taking the stress out of the process. &lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Contact us&lt;/a&gt; today for a detailed quote.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Why Manchester is the Perfect City for Brand Activation Events</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-09-12/why-manchester-is-the-perfect-city-for-brand-activation-events</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-09-12/why-manchester-is-the-perfect-city-for-brand-activation-events</guid><pubDate>Fri, 12 Sep 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/manchester.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When you're planning a &lt;a href="/pages/brand-activation-games-manchester"&gt;brand activation event&lt;/a&gt; that needs to deliver real impact, the choice of location can make or break your campaign's success. Whilst London might seem like the obvious choice, savvy event planners are increasingly discovering that Manchester offers everything you need for memorable brand experiences - often with better value, more authentic engagement, and genuine Northern warmth that helps brands connect with audiences in meaningful ways.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Planning brand activation events can be challenging enough without worrying about whether your chosen city will support your goals. That's why understanding what makes Manchester uniquely suited for experiential marketing campaigns can take the guesswork out of your location decision and help ensure your brand activation delivers the engagement and results you're working towards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Manchester's Unique Business Advantages for Brand Activations&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/brand-activation-game.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Manchester represents the largest city region economy outside London, with a gross value added of &amp;pound;78.7 billion. This economic strength translates into practical advantages for your brand activation event hire needs. The city attracts major corporations across finance, technology, manufacturing, and creative industries, creating natural networking opportunities when your activation brings together diverse professional audiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The central location offers excellent transport links that make Manchester accessible for attendees travelling from across the UK. With direct rail connections to London, Birmingham, Liverpool, and Leeds, plus Manchester Airport providing international connectivity, you can draw audiences from a much wider geographical area than many other regional cities. This accessibility is particularly valuable when you're planning activations that need to demonstrate national reach or bring together geographically dispersed teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Many Brands Choose Manchester for Brand Activation Events&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;From a practical standpoint, Manchester offers significantly better value than London whilst maintaining the professional standards that corporate clients expect. Venue costs, accommodation, and local suppliers typically offer 20-30% better value, allowing you to allocate more of your budget towards the interactive entertainment and production elements that directly impact your activation's success. This cost efficiency doesn't mean compromising on quality - Manchester's established business infrastructure supports complex event logistics with the same precision you'd expect from larger cities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The diverse economic base means your brand activation can tap into audiences from different sectors naturally. Whether you're targeting financial services professionals in the city centre, tech innovators in the digital quarter, or manufacturing executives visiting from the wider region, Manchester provides authentic access to these communities rather than requiring you to artificially assemble them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;The Creative Energy That Powers Memorable Brand Experiences&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Manchester's creative heritage runs much deeper than nostalgia - it actively supports modern brand activation campaigns that need to cut through the noise and create genuine emotional connections. The city's music legacy, from The Smiths to Oasis, has evolved into a thriving contemporary scene that includes innovative digital agencies, experiential marketing specialists, and creative talent who understand how to craft authentic brand experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The Northern Quarter perfectly embodies this creative energy, offering a vibrant backdrop for &lt;a href="/pages/brand-activation-games-manchester"&gt;brand activations&lt;/a&gt; that want to feel genuine rather than corporate. The area's street art, independent venues, and creative businesses provide natural authenticity that helps brands connect with younger demographics and creative professionals. When your activation needs to demonstrate innovation or creative thinking, Manchester's environment supports your messaging through the very spaces where you're hosting it.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This creative ecosystem means you have access to local suppliers and talent who specialise in experiential marketing Manchester campaigns. From video production teams who understand how to capture authentic moments to &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive entertainment&lt;/a&gt; specialists who can adapt quickly to your brand requirements, the city's creative infrastructure supports sophisticated activations without the premium pricing of London-based agencies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The cultural landmarks throughout Manchester provide unique backdrop opportunities that can enhance your brand storytelling. Whether you're using industrial heritage spaces that speak to innovation and progress, or contemporary venues that reflect modern business success, the city offers diverse visual narratives that can reinforce your brand messaging naturally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Diverse Venues to Match Any Brand Activation Goal&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/manchester-city.png" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Manchester's venue landscape offers remarkable flexibility for different types of brand activation events, allowing you to match your space precisely to your campaign objectives and audience expectations. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;The city centre business district &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This key area provides modern conference facilities and corporate spaces that work perfectly for professional brand activations focused on B2B networking, product launches for business audiences, or &lt;a href="/pages/team-building-ideas"&gt;team-building&lt;/a&gt; experiences that need to maintain a corporate feel whilst introducing interactive entertainment elements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For brands seeking more creative and memorable environments, &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;The Northern Quarter &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Delivering unique venues that help activations stand out from typical corporate events. Converted warehouses, independent bars with character, and gallery spaces provide the kind of authentic backdrop that encourages social sharing and creates talking points that extend your activation's reach beyond the event itself. These spaces work particularly well for brands targeting creative industries, younger demographics, or campaigns that want to demonstrate innovation and forward thinking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;City centre locations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Outdoor brand activations benefit from Manchester's excellent including busy pedestrian areas perfect for sampling campaigns, park spaces that work for larger experiential installations, and transport hubs that provide high footfall for awareness-building activations. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The city centre's compact layout means outdoor activations can capture diverse audiences as people move between shopping areas, business districts, and entertainment venues throughout their day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For campaigns requiring hybrid approaches that combine physical and digital experiences, Manchester offers venues equipped with the latest technology infrastructure alongside flexible spaces that can accommodate interactive entertainment elements. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Modern hotels and purpose-built event spaces provide the technical capabilities needed for live streaming, app-based interactions, or virtual reality experiences, whilst maintaining the personal touch that makes physical brand activations effective.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Venue Selection by Campaign Type&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When you're planning &lt;a href="/pages/brand-activation-games-manchester"&gt;product launches&lt;/a&gt;, Manchester's premium hotels and modern event spaces provide the professional environment that builds confidence in new offerings, whilst allowing scope for interactive demonstrations and hands-on experiences that help audiences understand product benefits practically. These venues typically offer excellent catering options and breakout spaces that encourage networking and extended engagement with your brand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Team-building brand activations work exceptionally well in the Northern Quarter's more relaxed venues, where the informal atmosphere helps colleagues connect naturally, whilst interactive entertainment creates shared experiences that strengthen working relationships. The area's bars and creative spaces feel less corporate, making it easier for people to step outside their usual professional roles and engage authentically with team-building activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consumer sampling campaigns achieve excellent results in Manchester's shopping centres and busy pedestrian areas, where diverse footfall ensures broad demographic reach, whilst the city's friendly culture encourages people to stop and engage with brand representatives. The compact city centre means you can capture both shoppers and professionals during lunch breaks, maximising your activation's exposure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For B2B networking activations, professional venues with flexible breakout spaces work best, allowing you to combine formal presentations with interactive entertainment elements that encourage conversation and relationship building between different companies and industries represented in Manchester's diverse business community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Manchester's Engaged and Diverse Audiences&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Manchester's population offers exceptional opportunities for brand activations because of its unique combination of professional diversity, cultural engagement, and genuine enthusiasm for new experiences. The city's large student population creates a young, digitally-savvy demographic that's eager to engage with innovative brands and quick to share experiences across social media platforms, amplifying your activation's reach organically.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The professional workforce spans multiple industries, from financial services and legal firms to technology companies and creative agencies. This diversity means your brand activation can connect with different professional communities simultaneously, creating networking opportunities whilst demonstrating your brand's relevance across various sectors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Cultural diversity throughout Manchester supports inclusive brand messaging and helps ensure your activation resonates with different communities. The city's strong tradition of social consciousness means audiences appreciate brands that demonstrate an authentic commitment to inclusion and community engagement rather than superficial diversity initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Local pride runs deep in Manchester, and brands that demonstrate genuine understanding of and commitment to the city often receive a warmer reception than those that treat it as simply another tour stop. This local engagement can significantly enhance your activation's impact, particularly when you incorporate elements that celebrate Manchester's heritage or support local communities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Social media engagement rates tend to be higher in Manchester than in many other cities, partly because of the strong sense of community and partly because people are more likely to share experiences that feel authentic and locally relevant. This organic amplification can extend your activation's reach far beyond the immediate participants.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Practical Considerations for Your Manchester Brand Activation&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Transportation &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Logistics work in your favour when choosing Manchester for brand activation events. Excellent rail connections mean attendees can travel from London, Birmingham, Liverpool, Leeds, and other major cities easily, often arriving more relaxed than they would after fighting London traffic or navigating complex underground systems. Manchester Airport provides direct international connections for global companies, whilst the city's compact layout means most venues are within walking distance of transport hubs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Accommodation &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Options range from budget-friendly hotels perfect for larger team events to luxury properties that work for executive activations or client entertainment. The concentration of hotels near the city centre means you can often negotiate group rates that include easy access to your venue, reducing logistical complexity whilst controlling costs effectively.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;The local supplier network &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This has developed specifically to support corporate events and experiential marketing campaigns. Established relationships between venues, caterers, audio-visual specialists, and interactive entertainment providers mean you can coordinate complex activations through suppliers who work together regularly, reducing the risk of communication gaps or compatibility issues that can derail events.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Weather considerations &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;In the unpredictable UK climate, considering the weather is important for outdoor activations, but Manchester's excellent indoor venue options mean you can plan effective contingencies without compromising your campaign's impact. Many venues offer flexible indoor-outdoor spaces that allow you to adapt to conditions whilst maintaining your activation's core objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Permits and regulations &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For outdoor brand activations, it&amp;rsquo;s important to follow streamlined processes determined by Manchester City Council, particularly for established locations where previous activations have proven successful. The local authority's experience with corporate events means they understand business needs whilst maintaining appropriate oversight, creating predictable approval processes that support planning timelines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Success Stories: Brands That Have Activated in Manchester&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Major international brands consistently choose Manchester for significant &lt;a href="/pages/brand-activation-games-manchester"&gt;activation campaigns&lt;/a&gt;, demonstrating the city's proven ability to deliver measurable results. Technology companies frequently use Manchester for product launches that need to reach both business and consumer audiences, benefiting from the city's diverse demographics and strong digital engagement rates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Financial services firms have found Manchester particularly effective for B2B activations, where the professional audience appreciates quality interactive entertainment that facilitates networking whilst the costs remain reasonable enough to invite larger groups than would be practical in London. These campaigns often report higher engagement rates and stronger follow-up conversion than similar activations in other cities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Retail brands targeting younger demographics achieve excellent results through Northern Quarter activations that feel authentic to the area's creative culture. The organic social sharing that results from genuinely engaging experiences in characterful venues often exceeds expectations, providing valuable user-generated content that extends campaign reach.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Manufacturing and engineering companies use Manchester's industrial heritage venues for activations that celebrate innovation and progress, finding that the authentic industrial backdrop reinforces their brand messaging whilst interactive entertainment helps technical products feel accessible to broader audiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Seasonal timing can significantly impact activation success, with spring and early autumn generally providing the best conditions for outdoor elements whilst avoiding conflicts with major local events. Summer activations benefit from extended daylight and outdoor venue options, whilst winter campaigns can create memorable contrast by bringing warmth and energy to the season when people most appreciate engaging experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Planning Your Manchester Brand Activation Event&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/manchester-brand-activation-event.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When you're ready to explore Manchester as your brand activation location, it's worth considering how interactive entertainment can enhance your campaign's impact whilst ensuring all attendees can participate meaningfully. Professional-grade &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; and activities create natural conversation starters, encourage networking between different groups, and provide memorable shared experiences that reinforce your brand messaging long after the event concludes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The key to successful brand activation event hire lies in matching your entertainment choices to your specific audience and objectives whilst considering the unique opportunities that Manchester's venues and culture provide. Interactive entertainment works particularly well in Manchester because the local culture encourages participation and engagement, making it easier to break down social barriers and create the authentic connections that drive brand loyalty.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Whether you're planning team-building activations that need to work for diverse personality types, consumer experiences that must appeal to different age groups, or B2B networking events that bring together various industries, the right interactive entertainment can ensure everyone feels included whilst supporting your broader campaign goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What makes Manchester better than London for brand activation events?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Manchester offers better value whilst maintaining professional standards, with venue costs typically 20-30% lower than London. The city's compact layout makes logistics simpler, whilst the local culture tends to be more approachable and engaging, leading to better participant interaction. Transport links remain excellent for national reach, but without London's complexity and costs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How far in advance should we book venues for Manchester activations?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For most corporate brand activations, booking 8-12 weeks in advance provides good venue selection whilst allowing time for proper planning. Popular venues during business &lt;a href="/pages/conference-idea"&gt;conference&lt;/a&gt; season (September-November, March-May) may require longer lead times, whilst summer months often offer more flexibility for both indoor and outdoor options.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What's the best area of Manchester for corporate brand activation events?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The city centre business district works well for professional audiences and formal activations, whilst the Northern Quarter provides creative energy for innovative campaigns targeting younger demographics. Many successful activations combine both areas, using professional venues for formal elements and creative spaces for networking or entertainment portions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Are there restrictions on outdoor brand activations in Manchester city centre?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Manchester City Council operates clear processes for outdoor events, with established guidelines for different types of campaigns. Most restrictions focus on safety, traffic flow, and environmental impact rather than prohibiting activities. Working with experienced local suppliers helps navigate requirements efficiently whilst ensuring compliance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What's the typical cost difference between Manchester and other major UK cities?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Manchester typically offers 20-30% savings compared to London across venues, accommodation, and suppliers, whilst costs remain competitive with other major regional cities like Birmingham or Leeds. The savings often allow for enhanced interactive entertainment or production values that directly improve activation impact and attendee experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Ready to discover how Manchester can enhance your next brand activation campaign?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Our experienced team understands both the opportunities Manchester provides and how interactive entertainment can maximise your campaign's impact. &lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Contact our friendly team&lt;/a&gt; to discuss your requirements and explore how we can help create memorable &lt;a href="/pages/brand-activation-games-manchester"&gt;brand experiences&lt;/a&gt; that deliver real results for your business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Top 10 Interactive Games to Break the Ice at Freshers Week Events</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-09-05/top-10-interactive-games-to-break-the-ice-at-freshers-week-events</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-09-05/top-10-interactive-games-to-break-the-ice-at-freshers-week-events</guid><pubDate>Fri, 05 Sep 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/fresher-week-event.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/freshers-entertainment-ideas"&gt;Freshers week&lt;/a&gt; can feel overwhelming for new university students - and equally challenging for the event organisers tasked with creating memorable experiences that help thousands of strangers become friends. If you're planning freshers activities, you'll know the pressure to get it right. Students arrive with high expectations, diverse backgrounds, and varying comfort levels with social situations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The good news? &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;Interactive games&lt;/a&gt; are one of the most effective ways to break down barriers naturally, create genuine connections, and ensure your freshers events are talked about for all the right reasons. With over 15 years of experience as corporate event specialists, we've seen firsthand how the right mix of interactive entertainment can transform nervous freshers into confident, connected students.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Interactive Games Are Essential for Successful Freshers Week Events&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/people-playing-interactive-game.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Freshers week presents unique challenges that traditional event formats simply can't address. You're bringing together students from different countries, cultures, and backgrounds - many of whom have never lived away from home before. The pressure to make friends quickly can be intense, and not everyone thrives in unstructured social situations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Interactive games provide a natural solution to these challenges. They give students a shared focus that takes the pressure off forced conversations, whilst creating opportunities for genuine connections to develop. Rather than expecting students to network in abstract ways, games provide concrete activities that reveal personality, encourage teamwork, and generate the kind of shared experiences that form the foundation of lasting friendships.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;What's more, well-chosen games can accommodate different personality types within the same activity. Whilst some students jump at the chance to be centre stage, others prefer supporting roles or simply watching and cheering. Interactive games allow for this natural variation in participation levels, ensuring everyone can engage in ways that feel comfortable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For event organisers, games also provide structure and energy that keeps events moving smoothly. Rather than worrying about awkward silences or students standing around unsure what to do, interactive activities create natural flow and engagement that makes your job considerably easier.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;10 Interactive Games Perfect for Freshers Week Ice Breaking&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/fun-pro-whack-a-mole.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;High-Energy Games for Large Groups&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;1. Human Knot Challenge&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This classic team-building game works brilliantly for freshers events because it requires cooperation, communication, and a good sense of humour. Students form a circle, reach across to hold two different people's hands, then work together to untangle themselves without letting go.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The beauty of the human knot is that it breaks down physical barriers quickly - students have to work closely together and laugh at the inevitable confusion. It's particularly effective for international students, as it requires minimal verbal communication whilst encouraging plenty of interaction.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;What you'll need: Just space and willing participants &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Group size: 8-15 people per circle &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Time required: 10-15 minutes per round&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;2. Speed Networking with Props&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Transform traditional speed networking by adding interactive elements. Set up stations with different props - unusual objects, conversation starter cards, or quick challenges that pairs complete together before moving on.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This format works well because it gives students something to focus on besides themselves, making conversations flow more naturally. The props serve as excellent ice breakers, and the timed rotation ensures everyone meets multiple people without lengthy awkward pauses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;What you'll need: Timer, variety of props or conversation starters &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Group size: Any even number &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Time required: 30-45 minutes&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;3. Interactive Quiz Competition&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Create teams randomly and run a quiz that mixes general knowledge with fun facts about your university, local area, and student life. The key is balancing questions so international students aren't disadvantaged whilst ensuring local students don't dominate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Quiz competitions naturally encourage teamwork and reveal different strengths within groups. They're also excellent for creating talking points that continue long after the game ends.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;What you'll need: Quiz questions, scoring system, small prizes &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Group size: Teams of 4-6 people &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Time required: 45-60 minutes&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Tech-Enhanced Interactive Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;4. Digital Reaction Games&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional-grade reaction games like &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/63/danger-zone-strike-a-light-game-hire"&gt;Strike a Light&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="/category/batak"&gt;Batak&lt;/a&gt; walls create instant excitement and draw crowds. These high-tech games test reflexes and coordination whilst providing clear, measurable challenges that students can rally around.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The competitive element naturally creates cheering sections and conversations, whilst the quick rounds mean lots of students can participate without long waits. These games are particularly effective as centrepiece attractions at freshers fairs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;What you'll need: Professional game hire (requires power supply) &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Group size: Individual play with audience engagement &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Time required: Ongoing attraction&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;5. Virtual Reality Experiences&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;VR stations create natural gathering points where students take turns experiencing virtual worlds whilst others watch and react. The technology itself is a conversation starter, and the shared experience of watching reactions creates bonding opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Choose experiences that are accessible to beginners and likely to generate entertaining reactions - virtual rollercoasters or simple games work better than complex scenarios requiring gaming experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;What you'll need: VR headsets, suitable content, supervision &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Group size: 1 player with 5-10 observers &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Time required: 3-5 minutes per person&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;6. Interactive Gaming Stations&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Set up familiar multiplayer games like &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;racing simulators&lt;/a&gt; or motion-controlled sports games. These work particularly well because students often know the games already, reducing barriers to participation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Gaming stations appeal to students who might find traditional ice breakers uncomfortable whilst still encouraging social interaction through shared play and friendly competition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;What you'll need: Gaming consoles, multiplayer games, screens &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Group size: 2-4 players with observers &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Time required: Ongoing entertainment&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Creative and Collaborative Activities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;7. Collaborative Art Projects&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Provide large canvases and art supplies for groups to create collaborative pieces - perhaps themed around hopes for university life or representations of their diverse backgrounds. The key rule is that participants must talk to others whilst contributing to the artwork.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This activity works well for students who prefer creative expression to competitive games. It's also excellent for creating lasting displays that remind students of their freshers week experience throughout the year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;What you'll need: Large canvases, art supplies, protective coverings &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Group size: 10-20 people per canvas &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Time required: 45-60 minutes&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;8. Photo Scavenger Hunt&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Create lists of campus locations, objects, or scenarios that teams must photograph. Include items that encourage creativity - "your team pretending to be a famous painting" or "finding something that represents your course."&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Scavenger hunts get students exploring campus whilst working together and being creative. The photo element creates shareable memories and social media content that extends the impact beyond the event itself.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;What you'll need: Task lists, smartphones, designated areas &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Group size: Teams of 3-5 people &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Time required: 60-90 minutes&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;9. Talent Showcase Mixer&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Instead of a traditional talent show, create rotating stations where small groups share skills or interesting facts about themselves - anything from showing dance moves to explaining unusual hobbies or demonstrating party tricks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This format is less intimidating than performing for large audiences whilst still allowing students to show their personalities and discover shared interests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;What you'll need: Designated areas, possibly microphone for larger groups &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Group size: Circles of 8-12 people &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Time required: 30-45 minutes&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Classic Games with Fresh Twists&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;10. Giant Jenga with Questions&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Use professionally-made &lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/44/giant-jenga-hire"&gt;giant Jenga&lt;/a&gt; blocks, but write questions or challenges on each piece. When students remove blocks, they answer the question or complete the challenge before placing it on top.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This combines the familiar satisfaction of Jenga with structured conversation starters. The physical element keeps things engaging whilst the questions help students learn about each other naturally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;What you'll need: Giant Jenga set, prepared questions &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Group size: 6-10 people per game &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Time required: 20-30 minutes per round&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Choosing the Right Games for Your Freshers Event&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/people-watching-interactive-game.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Selecting appropriate games requires careful consideration of your specific circumstances. Start by evaluating your venue constraints - indoor spaces limit high-energy physical games, whilst outdoor events need weather backup plans. Consider your expected attendance numbers and whether you're planning multiple simultaneous activities or single large-group events.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Think about your student demographic carefully. Universities with large international populations benefit from games requiring minimal verbal communication, whilst established local student communities might enjoy more culturally-specific activities. Mixed groups often work best with activities that reveal diverse backgrounds as strengths rather than barriers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It's worth considering the timing within your broader freshers programme. High-energy games work well early in events when energy is high, whilst more relaxed activities suit later periods when students might be getting tired. Always plan more activities than you think you'll need - successful events often run over time, and having backup options prevents awkward gaps.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Budget considerations vary significantly depending on whether you're hiring professional equipment or organising DIY activities. Professional-grade interactive games create impressive focal points and handle heavy usage well, whilst simpler activities can be highly effective with proper facilitation and preparation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Practical Tips for Running Successful Ice Breaker Games&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/two-man-playing-interactive-game.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The success of &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; often depends more on facilitation than the activities themselves. Ensure you have enthusiastic staff members who can explain rules clearly, encourage participation without pressuring reluctant students, and keep energy levels high throughout events.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Plan for different participation levels from the start. Not every student will want to be actively involved in every game, and that's perfectly fine. Create natural observer roles - scorekeeping, cheering, photography - that keep less active students engaged without forcing uncomfortable participation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Have weather contingencies ready for outdoor events. British weather can be unpredictable, and nothing kills event energy faster than scrambling for indoor alternatives when rain arrives. Either choose games that work in light rain or have clear backup plans that transition smoothly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider the practical logistics carefully. Games requiring equipment setup need adequate time buffers, especially if you're running multiple activities simultaneously. Ensure you have enough staff to supervise different areas and manage transitions between activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Create natural conversation opportunities during and after games. Build in brief discussion periods where teams can celebrate successes, compare strategies, or simply chat whilst transitioning to new activities. These informal moments often produce the most meaningful connections.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Making Your Freshers Games Inclusive and Accessible&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Inclusive game selection ensures all students can participate meaningfully in your &lt;a href="/pages/freshers-entertainment-ideas"&gt;freshers events&lt;/a&gt;. Consider physical accessibility from the planning stage - many traditional games can be adapted for students with mobility differences without compromising the core experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For international students, choose games that don't rely heavily on cultural knowledge or rapid language processing. Visual games, physical challenges, and activities with clear demonstrated rules work better than word-based games or those requiring cultural references.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Be mindful that introverted students might find large group activities overwhelming. Offer smaller group alternatives or observation roles that still provide social connection without demanding centre-stage participation. Many successful freshers events run multiple activities simultaneously, allowing natural self-selection based on comfort levels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider cultural sensitivity in competitive activities. What feels like friendly rivalry to some students might feel uncomfortably aggressive to others. Focus on collaborative challenges and personal improvement rather than elimination-style competitions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Remember that freshers week can be emotionally intense for many students. Build in quiet spaces and gentler activities alongside high-energy games, ensuring students who need breaks can step back without missing out entirely.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 30px; color: inherit;"&gt;Hire Interactive Games for Freshers Week Today&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Planning memorable &lt;a href="/pages/freshers-entertainment-ideas"&gt;freshers week events&lt;/a&gt; takes considerable thought and preparation, but interactive games provide proven solutions for creating connections and positive experiences. Whether you're organising intimate welcome sessions or large-scale freshers fairs, the right mix of activities can transform nervous new students into confident university community members.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If you're looking for professional-grade &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive entertainment&lt;/a&gt; for your freshers events, our experienced team understands the unique challenges of university welcome weeks. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;With over 15 years of experience helping institutions create memorable experiences, we can help you choose the perfect mix of games and activities for your specific event needs. &lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Get in touch&lt;/a&gt; to discuss how interactive entertainment can make your freshers week unforgettable for all the right reasons.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How long should ice breaker games run during freshers events? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Most ice breaker games work best in 15-30 minute segments, with natural break points for students to chat and move around. Longer activities risk losing attention, whilst shorter ones don't allow enough time for meaningful interaction. Plan for 2-3 games per hour with transition time between activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What's the ideal group size for freshers week interactive games? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This depends heavily on the specific game, but most work well with 8-15 participants. Smaller groups can feel exclusive, whilst larger ones make individual participation difficult. For bigger events, run multiple versions of the same game simultaneously rather than trying to accommodate everyone in single activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do you encourage shy students to participate in freshers games? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Start with low-pressure activities that don't require individual performance, and always provide observer roles that still involve engagement. Pair shy students with more outgoing partners rather than putting them in groups where they might get overwhelmed. Most importantly, never force participation - gentle encouragement works much better than pressure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What equipment do you need for successful freshers week ice breakers? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This varies enormously depending on your chosen activities. Simple games might need nothing more than paper and pens, whilst tech-enhanced options require professional equipment and power supplies. Always have backup supplies and simple alternatives that don't need equipment in case of technical issues.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can interactive games work for both indoor and outdoor freshers events? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Absolutely, though you'll need different approaches for each setting. Outdoor games can be more physical and handle larger groups, whilst indoor activities focus more on conversation and creativity. Many games adapt well to both settings with minor modifications to suit the space available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do you adapt ice breaker games for different cultural backgrounds? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Focus on universal human experiences rather than cultural-specific knowledge. Physical games, visual challenges, and activities based on personal preferences work well across cultures. Avoid games requiring rapid language processing or cultural references, and always explain rules clearly with demonstrations rather than just verbal instructions.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Ultimate Freshers Week Party Game Ideas: Make Your University Welcome Week Unforgettable</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-08-29/ultimate-freshers-week-party-game-ideas-make-your-university-welcome-week-unforgettable</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-08-29/ultimate-freshers-week-party-game-ideas-make-your-university-welcome-week-unforgettable</guid><pubDate>Fri, 29 Aug 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/coconut-shy.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Freshers week represents one of the most critical periods in any student's university journey. Those first few days set the tone for friendships, experiences, and memories that will last throughout their academic years. As someone responsible for planning these pivotal welcome events, you understand the immense pressure to create something truly special &amp;ndash; an experience that helps nervous first-years feel welcomed whilst ensuring your event stands out amongst the packed freshers week schedule.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The right &lt;a href="/pages/freshers-entertainment-ideas"&gt;freshers entertainment hire&lt;/a&gt; can transform a standard university gathering into an unforgettable celebration that students will talk about for years to come. But with so many options available and countless practical considerations to navigate, how do you choose entertainment that genuinely works for your diverse student population?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Drawing from over 15 years of experience as corporate event specialists, we've seen how the right interactive entertainment can break down barriers, create genuine connections, and turn anxious freshers into confident university students ready to embrace their new adventure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Interactive Entertainment is Essential for Successful Freshers Events&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Planning Freshers Week entertainment involves much more than simply booking a few games and hoping for the best. You're creating the foundation for your students' entire university experience, and that responsibility deserves thoughtful consideration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Breaking Down Social Barriers Between New Students&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Think about the challenge facing your first-year students. They've arrived in an unfamiliar city, living with strangers, surrounded by thousands of people they've never met. Traditional "networking" approaches often fall flat because they feel forced and artificial. &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;Interactive games&lt;/a&gt;, however, create natural conversation starters that feel organic and fun.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When students are focused on beating their friends at &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;racing simulators&lt;/a&gt; or working together on team challenges, they're not consciously trying to make friends &amp;ndash; it just happens naturally. The shared experience of attempting a tricky &lt;a href="/category/fun-fair-stalls"&gt;fairground game&lt;/a&gt; or cheering each other on during competitions creates instant bonds that formal introductions simply cannot replicate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Creating Memorable First Impressions That Set the Tone&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Your freshers week events are many students' first real taste of university life. A poorly organised event with limited activities can leave new students feeling disappointed and questioning their university choice. Conversely, professional-grade &lt;a href="/pages/freshers-entertainment-ideas"&gt;freshers games&lt;/a&gt; that create energy, laughter, and genuine excitement establish your institution as somewhere that truly cares about student experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We've worked with universities that've told us that years later, alumni still mention specific games from their freshers week as highlights of their university experience. That's the power of getting your entertainment choices right.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Ensuring Inclusive Participation Across Different Backgrounds&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Every freshers week welcomes students from vastly different backgrounds &amp;ndash; from confident extroverts to anxious introverts, international students navigating cultural differences to local students excited about independence. Your entertainment choices need to work for all of them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The best freshers entertainment hire provides multiple participation levels. Some students will dive straight into competitive challenges, whilst others prefer observing before gradually joining in. Having a mix of high-energy games alongside gentler activities ensures everyone finds their comfort zone whilst still being part of the collective experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Top Interactive Game Categories for Freshers Week Success&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/cornhole-game.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Understanding which types of games work best for student events requires considering both the practical realities of university venues and the diverse preferences of your audience. Here's how to choose entertainment that delivers maximum impact for your freshers week programme.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Racing Simulators and Action Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Racing simulators consistently rank among the most popular freshers games, and for good reason. They provide immediate excitement, are easy to understand regardless of language barriers, and create natural tournament opportunities that build energy throughout your event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Racing Games Work Brilliantly for Mixed Groups&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;Car simulators&lt;/a&gt; offer the perfect balance of individual challenge and group entertainment. Participants get the thrill of competition whilst spectators enjoy cheering on their new friends. The games are self-explanatory &amp;ndash; everyone understands the concept of driving fast and finishing first &amp;ndash; making them accessible to students from any background.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;What's more, racing simulators accommodate different skill levels naturally. Experienced gamers can show off their talents whilst complete beginners can have just as much fun, often surprising themselves with unexpected victories that create memorable moments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Creating Tournament-Style Competitions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider organising mini-tournaments throughout your event rather than just offering open play. This approach maintains energy levels and gives students reasons to return throughout the evening. You might run qualifying rounds early in the event, building towards finals later when crowds are at their peak.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Simple prizes &amp;ndash; perhaps branded university merchandise or local restaurant vouchers &amp;ndash; add an extra incentive without requiring significant budget increases. The key is creating talking points that extend beyond the immediate game experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Classic Fairground and Carnival Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Traditional carnival games and &lt;a href="/category/fun-fair-stalls"&gt;fun fair stalls&lt;/a&gt; bring a sense of nostalgic fun that appeals across age groups whilst creating an authentic festival atmosphere on your campus. These games work particularly well for students who might find high-tech alternatives intimidating.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Traditional Stall Games That Appeal to All Ages&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Games like&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/6/electronic-basket-ball-hire"&gt; Basketball Shootout&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/48/high-striker"&gt;High Striker&lt;/a&gt; provide familiar challenges that don't require explanation. Students can participate individually or in groups, making them perfect for mixed social situations where friend groups are still forming.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These games also photograph beautifully, creating shareable moments for social media that extend your event's reach. When students post pictures of themselves attempting carnival challenges, they're naturally promoting your event to their networks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Creating a Festival Atmosphere on Campus&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Multiple fairground stalls arranged together transform any venue into an exciting festival environment. This approach works particularly well for outdoor events or large indoor spaces where you can create distinct activity zones that encourage natural movement and exploration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Team-Building Interactive Challenges&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Some of the most effective freshers entertainment hire focuses on collaborative rather than competitive experiences. These games naturally bring strangers together whilst building the cooperation skills students will need throughout their university years.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Games That Naturally Form Mixed Groups&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Look for activities that require multiple participants but don't rely on existing friendships. Games that randomly assign teams or encourage students to form groups based on interests rather than prior connections help break down social barriers more effectively than purely individual competitions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Interactive challenges that require different skills &amp;ndash; perhaps combining physical coordination, problem-solving, and creativity &amp;ndash; ensure every team member can contribute something valuable, building confidence and mutual respect from the very start.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Planning Considerations for Freshers Week Entertainment&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Successful freshers entertainment hire requires careful consideration of practical factors that can make or break your event. Having worked with corporate clients for over 15 years, we understand how proper planning transforms good ideas into exceptional experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Timing Your Entertainment Within the Busy Welcome Week Schedule&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/freshers-entertainment-ideas"&gt;Freshers week &lt;/a&gt;schedules are notoriously packed, with mandatory registration sessions, academic introductions, accommodation meetings, and social events competing for students' attention. Your entertainment needs to fit seamlessly into this complex timetable rather than adding stress to an already overwhelming period.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider positioning interactive games during natural downtime &amp;ndash; perhaps between formal sessions when students need energy breaks, or during early evening periods before organised nightlife begins. This timing captures students when they're most receptive to new experiences whilst avoiding direct competition with essential activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Budget-Friendly Solutions That Still Deliver Maximum Impact&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/college-and-university-entertainment"&gt;University event&lt;/a&gt; budgets require careful management, but this doesn't mean compromising on quality or safety standards. Professional freshers games hire often provides better value than attempting to source multiple smaller providers, as you benefit from comprehensive service, proper insurance coverage, and experienced setup teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Think strategically about which games will create the most lasting impact. A smaller number of high-quality, professionally managed activities often generates more positive feedback than numerous cheaper alternatives that may break down or require constant supervision.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Venue Requirements and Space Planning&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;University venues present unique challenges &amp;ndash; from historic buildings with access restrictions to modern facilities with specific health and safety requirements. Professional entertainment providers should conduct thorough site surveys, providing detailed space plans that ensure optimal game placement whilst meeting all venue requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider power requirements, floor protection, and accessibility needs early in your planning process. Games that require significant setup time or specialised equipment need coordination with venue management well in advance of your event date.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Creating Inclusive Freshers Events That Work for Everyone&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Modern freshers week planning must acknowledge the diverse needs and preferences of contemporary students. Creating truly inclusive events requires thoughtful consideration of different backgrounds, abilities, and comfort levels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Accommodating Students Who Prefer Quieter Activities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Not every first-year student thrives in high-energy party environments. Some may come from cultural backgrounds where large social gatherings feel unfamiliar, whilst others simply prefer smaller-scale interactions. Your entertainment mix should provide options for these students without making them feel excluded from the main event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider incorporating games that work well with smaller groups or individual participation. Activities that allow students to drop in and out naturally &amp;ndash; perhaps skill-based challenges where they can attempt personal bests rather than competing directly with others &amp;ndash; ensure everyone can participate at their comfort level.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Ensuring Accessibility for Students with Different Abilities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Inclusive freshers entertainment hire means considering how students with various physical abilities can participate meaningfully in your activities. This goes beyond legal compliance to genuine inclusion that makes every student feel valued and welcome.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional entertainment providers should offer games with multiple interaction methods. For example, racing simulators with adjustable controls, team challenges that utilise different skills, and activities that can be enjoyed through participation or enthusiastic spectating all contribute to truly accessible events.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Balancing High-Energy Activities with Calmer Alternatives&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Successful freshers week events maintain energy whilst providing natural breathing spaces where students can process new experiences and form conversations. This balance is particularly important for international students who may need time to adjust to new social norms, or those who find large group activities overwhelming.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Consider creating distinct zones within your event space &amp;ndash; perhaps high-energy competitive areas alongside quieter skill-based games where students can focus on personal challenges whilst still being part of the collective experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Professional Setup and Safety Standards for Student Events&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Universities require entertainment providers who understand the professional standards expected in educational environments. This means going far beyond basic game rental to provide comprehensive, safety-conscious service that supports your event's success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Importance of Proper Insurance and Safety Certifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Student events demand the highest safety standards, not just for legal compliance but for peace of mind.&lt;a href="/pages/freshers-entertainment-ideas"&gt; Professional freshers entertainment&lt;/a&gt; hire should include comprehensive public liability insurance, full risk assessments for each activity, and PAT testing certificates for all electrical equipment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Your chosen provider should work collaboratively with your venue's health and safety teams, providing detailed documentation well in advance and remaining flexible if venue requirements change. This professional approach removes stress from your planning process whilst ensuring student safety remains the top priority.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Professional Installation and Breakdown Services&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Freshers week schedules leave little room for equipment problems or setup delays. Professional entertainment providers should arrive with sufficient time for thorough setup, testing all equipment before students arrive whilst remaining available throughout your event to address any technical issues immediately.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Equally important is efficient breakdown and removal that doesn't interfere with subsequent events or normal university operations. This attention to logistical details reflects the professional standards your institution expects from all service providers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Experience with Corporate Events Matters&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Entertainment providers with extensive corporate experience understand the professional standards universities require. They're accustomed to working within complex organisational structures, meeting strict safety requirements, and delivering consistent quality that reflects well on their clients' reputations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This background proves invaluable when managing the unique pressures of freshers week &amp;ndash; from accommodating last-minute schedule changes to ensuring games remain engaging throughout extended event periods.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Making Your Freshers Entertainment Instagram-Worthy&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Today's students document their experiences extensively through social media, making shareable moments a crucial consideration for successful freshers week planning. The right entertainment choices create natural photo opportunities that extend your event's impact far beyond the immediate participants.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Games That Create Natural Photo Opportunities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Visual impact matters enormously for social media success. Interactive games that look exciting from multiple angles &amp;ndash; racing simulators with dramatic setups, colorful carnival games, or team challenges that create action shots &amp;ndash; provide the backdrop students want for their university memories.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider how different games photograph and film. Activities that create clear "winning moments" or dramatic action provide the shareable content that helps promote your event organically through students' personal networks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Encouraging Social Media Sharing with Event Hashtags&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Provide clear, memorable hashtags that students can use when posting about their freshers week experiences. These create searchable archives of your event whilst helping new students connect with others who attended the same activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider creating visual displays with your hashtags positioned near the most photogenic games, making it easy for students to remember and use your preferred tags when sharing their experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Creating Memorable Moments Students Will Talk About All Year&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The most successful freshers week entertainment creates stories students will share throughout their university years. This might be the unexpected victory in a racing tournament, the group effort required to master a team challenge, or simply the laughter shared whilst attempting carnival games with new friends.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These memorable moments become part of your university's culture, creating traditions that returning students eagerly share with each new cohort of freshers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Freshers Entertainment Hire FAQs&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How far in advance should we book Freshers Week entertainment?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Early booking is essential for Freshers Week, as September represents peak demand for student entertainment across the UK. We recommend securing your entertainment at least 8-12 weeks in advance, particularly if you have specific date requirements or need popular games like racing simulators. Early booking also allows time for proper venue surveys and coordination with your facilities team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What's the typical budget range for interactive games at university events?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Freshers entertainment hire costs vary based on your specific requirements, event duration, and number of activities. As corporate event specialists, we work with universities to create packages that deliver maximum impact within available budgets. We'd be &lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;happy to discuss &lt;/a&gt;your specific needs and provide a detailed quote that includes all delivery, setup, and collection costs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can you provide entertainment for both indoor and outdoor Freshers events?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Absolutely. Our extensive range includes games specifically designed for outdoor use as well as indoor alternatives that work in everything from historic halls to modern student centres. We conduct detailed venue surveys to recommend the most suitable options for your specific location and weather contingency planning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do you ensure games are suitable for students with different abilities?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Inclusive design is fundamental to our approach. We offer games with multiple participation methods, adjustable difficulty levels, and options for both active participation and enthusiastic spectating. Our team works with you to understand your student population's specific needs and recommend entertainment that ensures everyone can participate meaningfully.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What safety measures are in place for Freshers Week game hire?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Safety is our absolute priority. All equipment comes with comprehensive public liability insurance, current PAT testing certificates, and detailed risk assessments. Our experienced teams conduct thorough setup and testing procedures whilst remaining on-site to monitor equipment throughout your event. We work closely with university health and safety teams to ensure full compliance with all venue requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Do you provide staff to run the games during our event?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, professional supervision can be included with our freshers entertainment hire upon request. Our friendly, experienced team members understand how to encourage participation, maintain energy levels, and ensure games run smoothly throughout your event. They're trained to work with diverse student populations and can adapt their approach based on your event's specific atmosphere and requirements. If you&amp;rsquo;d like to have staff attend your event, you can request this when booking and we will provide you with a detailed quote.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 30px; color: inherit;"&gt;Plan Your Unforgettable Freshers Week with Fun Pro&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Planning exceptional freshers week entertainment requires balancing numerous considerations &amp;ndash; from creating inclusive experiences that work for diverse student populations to ensuring professional standards that reflect well on your institution. The right&lt;a href="/pages/freshers-entertainment-ideas"&gt; freshers games&lt;/a&gt; can transform nervous first-years into confident university students ready to embrace everything their new adventure offers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;With over 15 years of experience providing professional-grade interactive entertainment, we understand the unique challenges facing university event planners. Our comprehensive service that includes &lt;a href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;nationwide delivery&lt;/a&gt;, professional setup, and full collection, takes the stress out of freshers entertainment hire whilst ensuring your students enjoy unforgettable welcome week experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Ready to start planning your ultimate Freshers Week entertainment? &lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Contact our friendly team&lt;/a&gt; to discuss your specific requirements and discover how we can help create the memorable, inclusive celebration your new students deserve.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>How to Choose The Right Entertainment for Your Company Christmas Party</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-08-08/how-to-choose-the-right-entertainment-for-your-company-christmas-party</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-08-08/how-to-choose-the-right-entertainment-for-your-company-christmas-party</guid><pubDate>Fri, 08 Aug 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/whack-an-elf.jpg"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Planning your company Christmas party can feel overwhelming, especially when it comes to selecting the right entertainment. With so many options available, how do you choose activities that will engage everyone from the newest intern to the managing director? The key is understanding your team, your venue, and your objectives to create a celebration that brings people together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/christmas-entertainment-game-hire"&gt;Christmas game hire&lt;/a&gt; takes the guesswork out of party planning, providing professional equipment and expert guidance to ensure your festive celebration is memorable for all the right reasons. The right &lt;a href="/category/christmas-games"&gt;games&lt;/a&gt; and entertainment can transform a standard office gathering into an event your colleagues will talk about well into the new year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;The Role of Entertainment in Corporate Christmas Celebrations&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;A successful company Christmas party does more than just mark the end of another year. It's an opportunity to strengthen relationships, boost morale, and show appreciation for your team's hard work. However, without proper entertainment, even the best-intentioned celebrations can fall flat.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Entertainment serves as a social catalyst, breaking down the invisible barriers that exist in workplace hierarchies. When the finance director is laughing alongside a junior assistant whilst playing &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt;, it creates connections that extend far beyond the party itself. These shared experiences help build stronger working relationships and improve team dynamics throughout the year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The right entertainment also ensures your party has energy and momentum from start to finish. Rather than relying solely on conversation and background music, interactive games and activities give people something to do, somewhere to go, and reasons to mingle with colleagues they might not usually spend time with.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Assessing Your Company's Entertainment Needs&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Before selecting any &lt;a href="/pages/christmas-entertainment-game-hire"&gt;Christmas entertainment&lt;/a&gt;, take time to consider who'll be attending your party. A tech startup with predominantly young employees will have different preferences compared to a traditional firm with a broad age range and diverse backgrounds.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Think about your company culture. Is your workplace formal and traditional, or relaxed and innovative? Are your employees naturally outgoing, or do they tend to be more reserved? These characteristics should influence your entertainment choices significantly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider whether partners, families, or children will be invited. Family-friendly entertainment requires different planning compared to adults-only events. Similarly, after-hours parties allow for different entertainment options than lunchtime celebrations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Don't forget about accessibility requirements. Ensure your chosen entertainment can accommodate colleagues with mobility issues, visual or hearing impairments, or other accessibility needs. Inclusive entertainment ensures everyone feels valued and can participate fully in your celebration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Popular Christmas Entertainment Options for Corporate Events&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/popular-christmas-game.jpg"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;High-Tech Interactive Experiences&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Modern interactive entertainment brings excitement and novelty to your Christmas party. &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;Racing car simulators&lt;/a&gt; allow colleagues to compete in friendly motorsport competitions, whilst &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/39/dance-machine"&gt;dance machines&lt;/a&gt; get people moving and create plenty of laughter. These high-tech options often become conversation pieces that people remember long after the party ends.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/christmas-game-hire/66/roll-and-bowl-reindeer-racing-game-hire"&gt;Reindeer Roll n Bowl &lt;/a&gt;combines technology with Christmas theming, creating engaging competitions that don't require long time commitments. Guests can participate as they feel comfortable, making these options perfect for mixed groups with varying confidence levels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Classic Holiday Entertainment&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Classic Christmas entertainment brings nostalgic charm to your office celebration. Traditional fairground games with festive theming like &lt;a href="/category/christmas-game-hire/79/whack-an-elf"&gt;Whack an Elf &lt;/a&gt;are easy to understand and don't require special skills or knowledge. These activities work particularly well for creating inclusive entertainment that welcomes all ages and abilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Collaborative Group Activities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If your company values collaboration, team-based Christmas entertainment can reinforce these principles whilst celebrating the season. Group challenges and festive team activities encourage colleagues to work together in a relaxed, fun environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These activities are particularly effective for larger companies where departments might not interact regularly. Mixed teams create opportunities for cross-departmental relationship building that can benefit your business throughout the coming year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Low-Key Entertainment Solutions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Not every moment of your Christmas party needs high-energy activities. Quieter entertainment options provide alternatives for colleagues who prefer smaller group interactions or need breaks from more intensive activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These gentler options also serve as excellent backup entertainment when other activities are busy, ensuring there's always something engaging available throughout your celebration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Essential Planning Considerations for Christmas Entertainment&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Venue Analysis and Space Planning&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Your venue significantly impacts your entertainment choices. Measure available space carefully, considering not just the footprint of equipment but also the room needed for people to move around safely and comfortably.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Indoor venues offer more control over conditions but may have restrictions on ceiling height, power availability, or noise levels. Outdoor venues provide more space but require weather contingency planning, especially for December events in the UK.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider the layout of your venue. Entertainment should be positioned where it's visible and accessible but won't block important areas like bars, buffets, or emergency exits. Good placement can enhance the flow of your party and encourage participation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Investment and Cost Management&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Christmas entertainment comes at various price points, so establish your budget early in the planning process. Remember that professional hire typically includes delivery, setup, operation, and collection, which represents significant value compared to managing entertainment yourself.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider the cost per person when evaluating options. More expensive entertainment might actually provide better value if it engages more people for longer periods. Similarly, having multiple entertainment options can justify higher costs by ensuring everyone finds something they enjoy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Many entertainment hire companies offer package deals that can help stretch your budget whilst providing greater variety for your guests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Event Flow and Scheduling&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Think carefully about when entertainment will be most effective during your party. Many successful events start with interactive entertainment to help people settle in and mix, then transition to other activities like speeches or awards presentations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider whether you want entertainment running throughout the entire event or concentrated during specific periods. Some companies prefer active entertainment during earlier, more casual phases, then quieter background options during dinner or more formal segments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Allow flexibility in your schedule. Popular entertainment might need longer time slots, whilst some activities work better in shorter bursts throughout the evening.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Integrating Entertainment with Your Corporate Culture&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Fostering Natural Participation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The best Christmas entertainment feels optional rather than mandatory. Some colleagues will naturally gravitate towards interactive activities, whilst others prefer to observe or participate more quietly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider appointing enthusiastic team members as informal "entertainment ambassadors" who can demonstrate activities and encourage others without creating pressure. Their enthusiasm often proves contagious and helps more reserved colleagues feel comfortable joining in.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Avoid making entertainment feel competitive to the point where people feel stressed or excluded. The goal is celebration and connection, not creating winners and losers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Ensuring Universal Appeal&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Ensure your entertainment choices welcome all members of your team. This means considering physical abilities, cultural backgrounds, and personal comfort levels when selecting activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Provide multiple entertainment options so people can choose what appeals to them. Having quiet alternatives alongside more active entertainment ensures everyone finds something they enjoy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider the social dynamics of your workplace. If certain departments or seniority levels tend to cluster together, choose entertainment that naturally encourages mixing and interaction across these groups.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Optimising Entertainment Impact at Your Christmas Event&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Leveraging Visual and Social Elements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Modern Christmas parties often extend beyond the event itself through social media sharing. Position entertainment in visually appealing settings and ensure good lighting for photos and videos.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider providing props, &lt;a href="/pages/branded-game-hire"&gt;branded games&lt;/a&gt; and backdrops, or themed decorations that encourage people to take pictures. These visual elements can enhance your company's social media presence whilst creating lasting memories for employees.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Encourage sharing with company hashtags, but keep it optional. Not everyone wants their party photos on social media, so respect personal preferences whilst providing opportunities for those who enjoy sharing their experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Maintaining Event Momentum&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Plan your entertainment to maintain energy levels throughout your celebration. Start with activities that help people arrive and settle in, build to more engaging interactive entertainment, then provide gentler options for later in the evening.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider how entertainment transitions work with other party elements like food service, speeches, or presentations. Smooth transitions keep energy levels consistent and prevent awkward lulls in your celebration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Have backup entertainment ready in case popular activities become too busy or if technical issues arise. Flexibility ensures your party continues smoothly regardless of unexpected challenges.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Booking Your Christmas Party Entertainment&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Timing Your Booking&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/christmas-entertainment-game-hire"&gt;Christmas entertainment&lt;/a&gt; gets booked quickly, especially for popular December dates. Start your planning process early, ideally in September or October, to ensure you get your preferred dates and entertainment options.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Weekend dates in December are particularly popular, so book these well in advance. Consider whether mid-week celebrations might offer better availability and pricing whilst still providing excellent entertainment value.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Popular entertainment options get reserved first, so prioritise booking your most important activities early in your planning process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Choosing the Right Entertainment Provider&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Look for entertainment hire companies with specific experience in corporate Christmas events. Check reviews from other businesses and ask for references from similar companies or events.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Understand exactly what's included in your hire package. Professional services should include delivery, setup, operation support, and collection. Clarify what happens if equipment develops problems during your event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;At Fun Pro UK, we provide &lt;a href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;nationwide delivery&lt;/a&gt; coverage including London, Manchester, Birmingham, and across the UK. Our experienced team handles everything from consultation to cleanup, ensuring your Christmas party entertainment runs smoothly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider companies that offer &lt;a href="/pages/branded-game-hire"&gt;custom branding&lt;/a&gt; options for their entertainment. Branded games and activities can enhance your company's visibility whilst providing professional-looking entertainment that reflects well on your organisation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Ready to Book Your Perfect Christmas Party Entertainment?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Choosing the right entertainment for your company Christmas party doesn't have to be complicated. By understanding your team, your venue, and your objectives, you can select activities that bring people together and create lasting positive memories.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The best Christmas parties combine different types of entertainment to cater for varying preferences and energy levels throughout the event. Professional entertainment hire ensures you have quality equipment, expert support, and the peace of mind that comes from working with experienced providers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Remember that Christmas party entertainment is an investment in your team's morale and relationships. The connections made and memories created during your celebration can have positive effects on workplace culture throughout the coming year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional Christmas entertainment hire takes the stress out of party planning whilst ensuring your celebration achieves its goals. From interactive games that break down barriers to traditional activities that welcome everyone, the right entertainment mix can transform your company Christmas party into an event people genuinely look forward to.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Contact our friendly team&lt;/a&gt; at Fun Pro UK to discuss your Christmas party entertainment requirements. With years of experience in corporate events and a comprehensive range of entertainment options, we'll help you choose the perfect activities for your team and venue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Start planning your memorable Christmas celebration today; your colleagues will thank you for creating an event that brings everyone together in the festive spirit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do I know what type of entertainment will suit my team? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider your company culture, employee demographics, and typical social dynamics. A consultation with entertainment professionals can help match activities to your specific team characteristics and party objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can Christmas entertainment be branded with our company logo? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, many entertainment options can be customised with your company branding, including custom graphics, logos, and colour schemes that reinforce your corporate identity throughout the celebration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How far in advance should I book Christmas party entertainment? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We recommend booking 6-8 weeks in advance, especially for December dates. Popular entertainment and peak weekend slots get reserved quickly during the Christmas season.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What happens if entertainment equipment breaks down during our party? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional hire companies provide backup equipment and rapid response support. Our experienced team can quickly resolve technical issues to ensure your celebration continues smoothly. You can contact us on 024 7 -722 -0701 or email &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.com"&gt;info@funprouk.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Is Christmas entertainment suitable for mixed-age groups? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, we offer entertainment options designed for diverse age groups and abilities. During consultation, we'll recommend activities that ensure everyone can participate and enjoy your celebration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Do you provide entertainment for venues outside major cities? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We offer nationwide coverage throughout the UK, including London, Manchester, Birmingham, and beyond. Delivery charges may apply for locations outside our standard service areas.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Christmas Party Games That Are Perfect for Office Teams</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-07-25/christmas-party-games-that-are-perfect-for-office-teams</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-07-25/christmas-party-games-that-are-perfect-for-office-teams</guid><pubDate>Fri, 25 Jul 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/christmas-party-game-hire.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Christmas party season is fast approaching, and if you're tasked with organising your company's festive get together, you're probably wondering how to create an event that people will enjoy. While traditional office Christmas parties often revolve around dinner and drinks, adding interactive &lt;a href="/category/christmas-games" style="background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;Christmas party games&lt;/a&gt; can transform your gathering from polite small talk into genuine fun and connection.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/christmas-entertainment-game-hire"&gt;Christmas game hire&lt;/a&gt; offers a practical solution for busy event planners who want to create memorable experiences without the stress of sourcing and managing entertainment equipment themselves. Professional game hire ensures you have quality activities that actually work, whilst giving you one less thing to worry about during your Christmas party planning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Christmas Party Games Are Essential for Office Teams&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/news/2025-06-27/planning-a-company-christmas-party-heres-how-games-can-break-the-ice"&gt;Christmas parties&lt;/a&gt; can be tricky social events. You've got colleagues from different departments who barely interact during the working day, plus partners and family members who might not know anyone else there. Traditional party formats often leave people standing around in small groups, struggling to find common ground.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Games naturally break down these barriers. They give people a shared activity to focus on, create opportunities for laughter and conversation, and help colleagues see each other in a completely different light. The marketing manager who's usually all business might turn out to be brilliantly competitive at table football, whilst the quiet finance assistant could be a wizard at quiz games.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Interactive entertainment also helps with the awkward timing that many Christmas parties suffer from. Rather than everyone arriving at different times and wondering what to do, games provide an immediate focal point that draws people in as soon as they walk through the door.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Understanding Your Office Team Dynamic&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Before you hire games for Christmas parties, think about who'll be attending. A tech startup with twenty-something employees will have very different preferences compared to a family business where three generations work together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider the mix of ages, interests, and personalities in your workplace. If you've got a physically active team who love a challenge, competitive games like &lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/88/scalextric-slot-car-racing"&gt;Scalextric car racing&lt;/a&gt; might be perfect. For a more reserved group, gentler activities like &lt;a href="/category/pub-games/16/casino-table-hire"&gt;casino tables&lt;/a&gt; that encourage conversation might work better.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Don't forget about partners and children if they're invited. Family-friendly options like &lt;a href="/category/christmas-game-hire/100/christmas-prize-crane"&gt;Christmas prize crane&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="/category/christmas-game-hire/89/candy-cane-snatch-it"&gt;candy cane snatch-it&lt;/a&gt; games ensure everyone can participate, whilst adult-only games might be better suited to after-hours events. Understanding your team dynamic helps you choose Christmas party game hire options that everyone will enjoy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Top Christmas Party Games for Office Teams&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/fun-pro-uk-candy-cane-snatch.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Interactive Christmas Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Modern interactive games are particularly popular at Christmas parties because they feel fresh and exciting. &lt;a href="/category/christmas-game-hire/66/roll-and-bowl-reindeer-racing-game-hire"&gt;Racing simulators&lt;/a&gt; let colleagues compete in virtual motorsport, whilst &lt;a href="/category/christmas-game-hire/12/christmas-photo-booths"&gt;photo booths&lt;/a&gt; get people interacting and laughing together. These high-tech options often become the talking point of the entire evening.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Christmas Reaction Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Reaction games like &lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/61/batak-lite"&gt;Batak Lite&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/43/batak-pro"&gt;Batak Pro&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href="/category/christmas-game-hire/66/roll-and-bowl-reindeer-racing-game-hire"&gt;Reindeer Roll n Bowl&lt;/a&gt; are brilliant for creating short, sharp competitions that don't require long commitments. People can jump in and out as they please, making them perfect for parties where mingling is important.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 30px; font-family: inherit; color: inherit;"&gt;Practical Planning Tips for Your Christmas Party&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Space and Venue Requirements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Before committing to any Christmas party game hire, carefully measure your venue space. Games need room not just for the equipment itself, but for people to move around safely and comfortably.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Indoor venues often work best for Christmas parties, but make sure you have adequate ceiling height for particularly tall games. Also consider power requirements for electronic games and whether you'll need extension leads.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Timing and Flow&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Think about when during your party the games will be most useful. Many organisers find that having games available from the start helps people settle in and mix, rather than saving them for later in the evening.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider whether you want games running throughout the entire event or just during specific periods. Some companies prefer to have games during the earlier, more casual part of the evening, then move to more traditional party activities later.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Budget Planning&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Christmas party game hire comes at various price points, so establish your entertainment budget early in your planning process. Remember that professional hire often includes delivery, setup, and collection, which can represent significant value compared to buying equipment outright.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Many hire companies offer package deals for multiple games, which can help stretch your budget further whilst providing more variety for your guests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Making Christmas Games Work for Your Office Culture&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Setup and Presentation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional game hire companies typically handle setup, but it's worth discussing placement in advance. Games should be positioned where they'll be noticed but won't block important areas like bars, buffets, or emergency exits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Good lighting around game areas is important for both safety and atmosphere. If your venue has adjustable lighting, make sure game areas are well-lit whilst maintaining the festive ambiance elsewhere.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Encouraging Participation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Some people need encouragement to try new activities. Consider having a few enthusiastic colleagues act as "game ambassadors" to get things started and show others how much fun they can have.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Avoid making games feel mandatory or competitive to the point where people feel pressured. The goal is to create opportunities for fun and &lt;a href="/news/2025-03-18/boost-team-spirit-with-these-ideas-for-your-next-work-social-event"&gt;boost team morale&lt;/a&gt;, not to stress people out.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Maximising Engagement and Participation at Your Christmas Party&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Creating Shareable Moments&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;People love to share fun experiences. Set up your space so it's easy to take photos and videos. This could be through photo booths, branded backdrops, or digital scoreboards that show off high scores and winners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The more visually appealing your setup is, the more likely people are to snap a picture and post it online. Bright colours, &lt;a href="/pages/branded-game-hire"&gt;clever branding&lt;/a&gt;, or even themed props can go a long way in encouraging content creation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Safety Considerations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional game hire companies should provide equipment that meets safety standards, but it's worth checking insurance coverage and any specific requirements for your venue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Make sure there's adequate space around games for safe movement, and consider whether you need any additional safety measures for your specific group or venue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Booking Your Christmas Party&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Timing Your Booking&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Christmas is the busiest time of year for party entertainment, so book your games well in advance. Many companies start their Christmas party planning in September or October to ensure they get their preferred dates and equipment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Popular games and peak dates (especially December weekends) get booked up quickly, so don't leave it until the last minute.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Choosing the Right Supplier&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Look for game hire companies with experience in corporate events and good reviews from other businesses. Check what's included in their service, whether setup and collection are part of the package, and what happens if equipment develops problems during your event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;At Fun Pro UK, we provide &lt;a href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;nationwide delivery&lt;/a&gt; coverage to major cities, including London, Manchester, Birmingham, and across the UK. Our experienced team handles everything from delivery to setup, ensuring your Christmas party runs smoothly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Ready to Plan Your Perfect Christmas Party?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The best Christmas parties are the ones people are still talking about months later. By choosing the right mix of games and activities, you can create an event that brings your team together in a completely new way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Games provide natural conversation starters, shared experiences, and opportunities for colleagues to see different sides of each other. They can help break down workplace hierarchies and build stronger relationships that last well beyond the Christmas season.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Christmas party planning doesn't have to be stressful. With the &lt;a href="/category/christmas-games"&gt;right games&lt;/a&gt; and activities, you can create an event that brings your team together and gives everyone something to enjoy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional &lt;a href="/pages/christmas-entertainment-game-hire"&gt;Christmas party game hire&lt;/a&gt; takes the guesswork out of entertainment planning, ensuring you have quality equipment and support when you need it most. From interactive high-tech games to classic fairground activities, there are options to suit every group and budget.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Contact our friendly team&lt;/a&gt; at Fun Pro UK to discuss your Christmas party requirements. With years of experience in corporate events and a wide range of game options, we'll help you create a Christmas celebration that your colleagues will remember for all the right reasons.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;FAQs&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How much space do Christmas games require? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Space requirements vary depending on the games you choose. Most games need a minimum of 3x3 metres including player space, but we can recommend suitable options for any venue size during your consultation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can Christmas games be customised with our company branding? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, many of our games can be &lt;a href="/pages/branded-game-hire"&gt;customised&lt;/a&gt; with your company branding, including custom graphics, logos, and colour schemes to match your corporate identity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What's included in your Christmas game hire service? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Our hire service includes delivery, professional setup, full instructions, and collection after your event. We also provide backup equipment and on-site support if needed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How far in advance should I book Christmas party games? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We recommend booking at least 6-8 weeks in advance, especially for December dates. Popular games and peak weekend slots get booked quickly during the Christmas season.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Are the games suitable for all ages and abilities? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We offer a wide range of games suitable for different age groups and abilities. During consultation, we'll recommend the best mix based on your guest list and requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What happens if a game breaks down during our event? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We provide backup equipment and rapid response support. Our experienced team can quickly resolve any technical issues to ensure your party continues smoothly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Do you provide games for venues outside major cities? &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, we offer nationwide coverage &lt;a href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;throughout the UK&lt;/a&gt;. Delivery charges may apply for locations outside our standard service areas, which we'll discuss during booking.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Planning a Company Christmas Party? Here's How Games Can Break the Ice</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-06-27/planning-a-company-christmas-party-heres-how-games-can-break-the-ice</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-06-27/planning-a-company-christmas-party-heres-how-games-can-break-the-ice</guid><pubDate>Fri, 27 Jun 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/catch-us-if-you-can-games.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The Christmas party season is fast approaching, and if you're tasked with organising your company's festive celebration, you're probably wondering how to create an event that brings everyone together. While traditional Christmas parties often revolve around dinner and drinks, adding interactive &lt;a href="/pages/christmas-entertainment-game-hire"&gt;Christmas games&lt;/a&gt; can transform your gathering from polite small talk into genuine fun and connection. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/christmas-entertainment-game-hire"&gt;Christmas game hire&lt;/a&gt; offers a practical solution for busy event planners who want to create memorable experiences without the stress of sourcing and managing entertainment equipment themselves. Professional game hire ensures you have quality activities that actually work, whilst giving you one less thing to worry about during your Christmas party planning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Games Work So Well at Christmas Parties&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Christmas parties can be tricky social events. You've got colleagues from different departments who barely interact during the working day, plus partners and family members who might not know anyone else there. Traditional party formats often leave people standing around in small groups, struggling to find common ground.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Games naturally break down these barriers. They give people a shared activity to focus on, create opportunities for laughter and conversation, and help colleagues see each other in a completely different light. The marketing manager who's usually all business might turn out to be brilliantly competitive at table football, whilst the quiet finance assistant could be a wizard at quiz games.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Interactive entertainment also helps with the awkward timing that many Christmas parties suffer from. Rather than everyone arriving at different times and wondering what to do, games provide an immediate focal point that draws people in as soon as they walk through the door.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Understanding Your Audience When Planning Games&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Before you hire games for your Christmas party, think about who'll be attending. A tech startup with twenty-something employees will have very different preferences compared to a family business where three generations work together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider the mix of ages, interests, and personalities in your workplace. If you've got a physically active team who love a challenge, competitive games might be perfect. For a more reserved group, gentler activities that encourage conversation might work better.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Don't forget about partners and children if they're invited. Family-friendly options ensure everyone can participate, whilst adult-only games might be better suited to after-hours events.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Popular Christmas Party Game Options&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Interactive Games &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/reindeer-roll-n-bowl.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Modern interactive games are particularly popular at Christmas parties because they feel fresh and exciting. Racing simulators let colleagues compete in virtual motorsport, whilst dance machines get people moving and laughing together. These high-tech options often become the talking point of the entire evening.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Reaction games like &lt;a href="/category/christmas-game-hire/66/roll-and-bowl-reindeer-racing-game-hire"&gt;Reindeer Roll n Bowl&lt;/a&gt; are brilliant for creating short, sharp competitions that don't require long commitments. People can jump in and out as they please, making them perfect for parties where mingling is important. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Classic Fairground Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Traditional &lt;a href="/category/fun-fair-stalls"&gt;fairground stalls and games&lt;/a&gt; bring a sense of nostalgia that works perfectly with Christmas celebrations. Hook a duck, coconut shy, and similar games are easy to understand and don't require any special skills or knowledge. They're also great conversation starters, with people often sharing memories of childhood visits to fairgrounds.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These games work particularly well for mixed-age groups because everyone can participate regardless of their gaming experience or physical abilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Team-Based Activities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If your workplace thrives on collaboration, team-based games can be an excellent choice. &lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/44/giant-jenga-hire"&gt;Giant Jenga&lt;/a&gt;, oversized Connect Four, or team quiz machines encourage groups to work together and support each other.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These activities are particularly effective for larger companies where people might not know everyone. Teams can be mixed across departments, creating opportunities for colleagues to interact who might never usually work together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Quieter Options&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Not everyone wants to be the centre of attention at the Christmas party. Quieter games like table football, pool tables, or retro arcade games provide entertainment options for people who prefer smaller group interactions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These games also serve as great backup options for when the main entertainment is busy, ensuring there's always something for people to do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Practical Christmas Party Planning Considerations&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Space and Venue Requirements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Before committing to any Christmas party game hire, carefully measure your venue space. Games need room not just for the equipment itself, but for people to move around safely and comfortably.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Indoor venues often work best for Christmas parties, but make sure you have adequate ceiling height for activities like basketball hoops or throwing games. Also consider power requirements for electronic games and whether you'll need extension leads.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Timing and Flow&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Think about when during your party the games will be most useful. Many organisers find that having games available from the start helps people settle in and mix, rather than saving them for later in the evening.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider whether you want games running throughout the entire event or just during specific periods. Some companies prefer to have games during the earlier, more casual part of the evening, then move to more traditional party activities later.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Budget Planning&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Christmas party game hire comes at various price points, so establish your entertainment budget early in your planning process. Remember that professional hire often includes delivery, setup, and collection, which can represent significant value compared to buying equipment outright.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Many hire companies offer package deals for multiple games, which can help stretch your budget further whilst providing more variety for your guests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Making the Most of Your Christmas Game Hire&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Setup and Presentation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional game hire companies typically handle setup, but it's worth discussing placement in advance. Games should be positioned where they'll be noticed but won't block important areas like bars, buffets, or emergency exits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Good lighting around game areas is important for both safety and atmosphere. If your venue has adjustable lighting, make sure game areas are well-lit whilst maintaining the festive ambiance elsewhere.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Encouraging Participation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Some people need encouragement to try new activities. Consider having a few enthusiastic colleagues act as "game ambassadors" to get things started and show others how much fun they can have.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Avoid making games feel mandatory or competitive to the point where people feel pressured. The goal is to create opportunities for fun, not to stress people out.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Safety Considerations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional game hire companies should provide equipment that meets safety standards, but it's worth checking insurance coverage and any specific requirements for your venue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Make sure there's adequate space around games for safe movement, and consider whether you need any additional safety measures for your specific group or venue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Booking Your Christmas Party Games&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Timing Your Booking&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Christmas is the busiest time of year for party entertainment, so book your games well in advance. Many companies start their Christmas party planning in September or October to ensure they get their preferred dates and equipment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Popular games and peak dates (especially December weekends) get booked up quickly, so don't leave it until the last minute.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Choosing the Right Supplier&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Look for game hire companies with experience in corporate events and good reviews from other businesses. Check what's included in their service, whether setup and collection are part of the package, and what happens if equipment develops problems during your event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Ask about their cancellation policy and whether they offer any guarantees on equipment functionality.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Creating Lasting Memories&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The best Christmas parties are the ones people are still talking about months later. By choosing the right mix of games and activities, you can create an event that brings your team together in a completely new way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Games provide natural conversation starters, shared experiences, and opportunities for colleagues to see different sides of each other. They can help break down workplace hierarchies and build stronger relationships that last well beyond the Christmas season.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Ready to Plan Your Perfect Christmas Party?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Christmas party planning doesn't have to be stressful. With the right games and activities, you can create an event that brings your team together and gives everyone something to enjoy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional Christmas party game hire takes the guesswork out of entertainment planning, ensuring you have quality equipment and support when you need it most. From interactive high-tech games to classic fairground activities, there are options to suit every group and budget.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Contact our friendly team&lt;/a&gt; at Fun Pro UK to discuss your Christmas party requirements. With years of experience in corporate events and a wide range of game options, we'll help you create a Christmas celebration that your colleagues will remember for all the right reasons.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Start planning your perfect Christmas party today; your team will thank you for it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>How to Increase Engagement at Your Brand Activation Event</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-05-30/how-to-increase-engagement-at-your-brand-activation-event</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-05-30/how-to-increase-engagement-at-your-brand-activation-event</guid><pubDate>Fri, 30 May 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/fun-pro-uvex.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If you're planning a &lt;a href="/pages/promotional-event-games"&gt;brand activation event&lt;/a&gt;, your biggest goal is to grab attention and get people talking. Whether you're launching a product, building awareness, or driving footfall at a trade show, keeping your audience engaged is key to making it a success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;From eye-catching visuals to interactive experiences, here are some simple, proven ways to increase engagement at your next brand activation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Engagement Matters at Brand Activations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;A brand activation isn't just about turning up and showing off your logo. It&amp;rsquo;s about making real connections with your audience. When people interact with your brand in a fun and memorable way, they&amp;rsquo;re more likely to remember you, talk about you, and buy from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;That&amp;rsquo;s why engagement should be at the heart of any brand activation event plan. If your setup is static or uninviting, people will simply walk past. On the other hand, if there&amp;rsquo;s something exciting or playful going on, you&amp;rsquo;ll attract attention and create natural opportunities to start conversations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Engaged visitors are also more likely to stick around, share their experience online and become brand advocates. It&amp;rsquo;s not just about making noise, it&amp;rsquo;s about building lasting impressions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Use Games for Your Brand Activation Event&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/baylis-and-harding-game.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;One of the most effective ways to boost engagement is by using interactive games. Games create energy, spark conversations, and give people a reason to spend more time at your stand or space.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Popular options include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/3/cash-grabber-machine-hire"&gt;Cash Grabbers&lt;/a&gt; &amp;ndash; quick, fun and perfect for competitions or giveaways&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/batak"&gt;Batak Reaction Games&lt;/a&gt; &amp;ndash; great for testing speed and reflexes&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/prize-games/49/prize-wheel"&gt;Prize Wheels&lt;/a&gt; &amp;ndash; simple to set up and always a crowd-puller&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These games don&amp;rsquo;t just fill space, they turn your stand into an attraction. People passing by will want to know what&amp;rsquo;s going on, which naturally increases footfall. And once people are there, you&amp;rsquo;ve got the perfect opportunity to tell your brand story and get them involved in a more meaningful way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When you hire games for a brand activation, you're not just entertaining your visitors, you're creating a moment they&amp;rsquo;ll associate with your brand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Make It Easy to Join In&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The more effortless the experience, the more likely people are to take part. Keep instructions short and friendly. Use staff or brand ambassadors who are outgoing, approachable and ready to help people get involved without pressure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;A complex game or unclear setup can put people off, especially at busy events where time and attention spans are limited. Keep things simple, intuitive and open to all ages and abilities. The easier it is to join in, the more traffic and engagement you&amp;rsquo;ll see.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It also helps to have small prizes or incentives. Even something as simple as branded merchandise, discount codes or social media shoutouts can encourage participation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These little touches can make all the difference. People love a challenge, but they also love a reward &amp;ndash; even if it&amp;rsquo;s just for fun.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Create Shareable Moments&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;People love to share fun experiences. Set up your space so it&amp;rsquo;s easy to take photos and videos. This could be through photo booths, branded backdrops, or digital scoreboards that show off high scores and winners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The more visually appealing your setup is, the more likely people are to snap a picture and post it online. Bright colours, clever branding, or even themed props can go a long way in encouraging content creation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You can even add a branded hashtag and encourage visitors to tag your company on social media. This turns your event into a source of user-generated content that works for you long after the day is over.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s also a good idea to have someone on your team capturing photos and videos throughout the day. These can be used to promote future events or shared as part of your post-event marketing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Collect Data (Without Being Pushy)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Games and competitions are a great way to collect leads without putting people off. Offer a prize draw in exchange for basic contact details, or allow people to enter using a QR code that links to a form or landing page.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Data collection is a key part of any brand activation, but it&amp;rsquo;s important to do it right. No one wants to feel like they&amp;rsquo;re being sold to. Instead, offer something of value in return, whether it&amp;rsquo;s a prize, a discount, or exclusive content.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Just make sure you&amp;rsquo;re clear about how their data will be used, and always follow GDPR guidelines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The right approach can help you build a solid list of warm leads who&amp;rsquo;ve already had a positive experience with your brand &amp;ndash; making them more likely to convert down the line.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Hire Games for a Brand Activation With Impact&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Hiring the right games for your event can completely change how people respond to your brand. At Fun Pro UK, we specialise in brand activation event hire with a wide range of interactive games designed to boost engagement, drive traffic and create memorable experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;From small pop-ups to large-scale exhibitions, we&amp;rsquo;ve got options for every type of activation. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re planning something indoor or outdoor, one day or several, we can recommend the best mix of games and equipment to help you stand out.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We also handle delivery throughout the UK*, setup and breakdown &amp;ndash; so you can focus on making the most of your event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;*Delivery may incur an additional charge.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Ready to Plan Your Brand Activation?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If you want your brand to stand out and connect with your audience in a fun and memorable way, our team at Fun Pro UK is here to help. &lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Get in touch today&lt;/a&gt; to hire games for a brand activation that gets people talking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>How to Find The Best Games for Your College Or School Summer Party</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-05-12/how-to-find-the-best-games-for-your-college-or-school-summer-party</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-05-12/how-to-find-the-best-games-for-your-college-or-school-summer-party</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 May 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/mega-wire-game.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;With summer fast approaching, many schools and colleges are starting to think about different ways to mark the occasion, especially for those who are in their final year.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The end of the academicl year is a great time for everyone to come together, celebrate all the hard work from the previous year, and show some appreciation for all of those involved in the running of the school to make it a place where children enjoy coming, teachers enjoy their job, and parents feel good about sending their children there.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
What better way to do that than with a school summer party filled with fun activities, games, and entertainment that everyone can enjoy?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;At Fun Pro, we&amp;rsquo;re here to help you create a truly memorable experience for your staff, the children and their families, and in this post, we&amp;rsquo;re going to share with you some of our top tips for finding the very best games to hire for your school&amp;rsquo;s summer party.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Hire Games for Your College Or School Summer Party&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;School and college summer parties mark an important transition, whether it's moving up a year, saying goodbye to primary school, or celebrating exam completion. The right games create a fun and memorable atmosphere that brings pupils, teachers, and sometimes even parents together and allows for a day where everyone can just let their hair down, be themselves and not worry about learning or sticking to timetables.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Quality college and school party games can:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Create lasting memories for pupils of all ages&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Promote inclusivity by offering something for everyone&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Provide structured entertainment that keeps the event running smoothly&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Give children a positive end to their school year&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Allow pupils to interact with classmates and teachers in a relaxed setting&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Planning Your School Summer Party: Key Considerations&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Before diving into specific game options, consider these important factors when planning your event:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Age-Appropriate School Summer Party Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Different age groups have varying preferences and abilities. What works brilliantly for reception classes might fall flat with Year 6 pupils, whilst secondary school students will probably appreciate more challenging activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;For younger children (Reception-Year 2):&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Simple, easy-to-understand games with clear rules&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Activities that don't require extended focus or complex skills&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Colourful, visually engaging equipment&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Games that involve movement but minimal competition&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;For middle years (Year 3-6):&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Team-based activities that encourage cooperation&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Games that balance skill and chance&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Activities with mild competitive elements&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Games that accommodate different physical abilities&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;For secondary school pupils:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;More challenging competitions that test skills&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Activities with a 'cool factor'&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Games that allow for socialising whilst playing&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Options that respect their growing independence&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Indoor vs Outdoor Game Options&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;With the British summer weather being so notoriously unpredictable, having contingency plans for both indoor and outdoor settings is essential:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Outdoor game options:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/twin-axe-throwing.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/21/inflatable-assault-courses#BodyContent"&gt;Inflatable obstacle courses&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/23/large-bouncy-castles"&gt;bouncy castles&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/freshers-fair-games/98/twin-axe-throwing"&gt;Twin Axe Throwing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/branded-exhibition-games/64/mega-wire-branded-game-hire-stand-alone"&gt;Mega Wire&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Sports day-style competitions&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Indoor alternatives:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games"&gt;Arcade Games&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/batak"&gt;Reaction Games&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Table-based challenges (&lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/27/football-tables"&gt;football tables&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/60/air-hockey-table-hire"&gt;air hockey&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Top Game Hire for College and School Summer Party Success&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional game hire from Fun Pro offers significant advantages over DIY options. When you hire games for your school summer party, you benefit from:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Professional-grade equipment that's built to last&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Properly maintained and safety-tested games&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Delivery, setup and collection services*&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Expert advice on game selection&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Games that have proven popular at similar events&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;*Delivery may incur additional charges.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Here are some of our post popular games hired by category:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Interactive Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Digital natives respond brilliantly to technology-enhanced games:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;Racing simulators&lt;/a&gt; that let pupils experience the thrill of motorsport&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/39/dance-machine"&gt;Dance machines&lt;/a&gt; that get everyone moving to popular tunes&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/batak"&gt;Batak &lt;/a&gt;reaction games that test speed and coordination&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These modern options are particularly effective for secondary school leavers' events, where pupils expect something more challenging and energetic than traditional party games.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Classic Inflatables and Obstacle Courses&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/inflatable-game.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Nothing says 'summer party' quite like bouncy castles and inflatable challenges:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Age-appropriate bouncy castles for different year groups&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Inflatable obstacle courses for energetic competition&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/fun-days/33/bungee-run"&gt;Bungee run&lt;/a&gt; challenges for older pupils&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The visual impact of colourful inflatables instantly transforms any school field or sports hall into a festival atmosphere.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Traditional Fairground Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Time-tested fairground classics never go out of style:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/fun-fair-stalls/96/coconut-shy-stall-hire"&gt;Coconut shy&lt;/a&gt; challenges&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/fun-fair-stalls/95/target-ring-toss-hire"&gt;Target ring toss&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These games have the advantage of being familiar to teachers, parents, and pupils alike, making them easy to explain and quick to enjoy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;How to Hire Games for Your College Or School Summer Party&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Finding and securing the right entertainment requires advance planning:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Start early: Book popular items at least 2-3 months in advance, especially for June/July events when demand peaks&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Consider your budget: Quality game hire comes at various price points&amp;mdash;establish your spending limit before contacting suppliers&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Think about space: Measure your available indoor and outdoor areas to ensure games will fit comfortably&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Check logistics: Confirm access routes, power requirements, and whether staff supervision is included&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Verify safety credentials: Ensure suppliers have proper insurance and safety certifications for school events&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Maximising Value When You Hire Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Make your budget stretch further with these practical tips:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Book multiple games from a single supplier for potential package discounts&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Consider half-day hire for shorter events&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Share costs with other local schools or parent committees for consecutive day bookings&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Balance premium attractions with more affordable options&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Ask about term-time weekday discounts (often available outside peak weekend demand)&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Creating Themed Zones for Different Interests&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Rather than distributing games randomly, consider creating themed activity zones that cater to different interests:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Active Zone:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Inflatables and physical challenges&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Sports-based competitions&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Dance and movement games&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Skill Zone:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Target games requiring precision&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Problem-solving challenges&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Reaction testing games&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Chill-Out Zone:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Less intensive activities&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Games suitable for quiet participation&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Options for those needing sensory breaks&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This approach ensures pupils can find activities that match their energy levels and preferences throughout the event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;College and School Summer Party Games: Inclusivity Considerations&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Ensuring all pupils can participate regardless of ability is essential:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Select games that can be enjoyed by children with different physical capabilities&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Include options that don't rely solely on speed or strength&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Consider noise levels for pupils with sensory sensitivities&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Ensure adequate shaded areas for outdoor events&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Provide seating near activities for those who need rest periods&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Making Memories with the Perfect College and School Party Games&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The end of the school year represents a significant milestone for pupils of all ages. By carefully selecting the right mix of school summer party games, you create not just a fun day out, but a celebration that recognises achievements and builds school community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Professional game hire removes the stress from event planning, ensuring high-quality equipment and proper safety measures. Whether you're organising a small key stage celebration or a whole-school extravaganza, investing in quality entertainment ensures pupils end their school year on a high note.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Ready to start planning your school summer celebration? &lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Contact our friendly team&lt;/a&gt; at Fun Pro UK for expert advice on selecting the perfect games for your specific requirements. With nationwide delivery and years of experience in educational settings, we'll help make your school summer party truly unforgettable!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>The Ultimate Guide To A Successful Exhibition Plan: Using Interactive Games To Stand Out</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-05-02/the-ultimate-guide-to-a-successful-exhibition-plan-using-interactive-games-to-stand-out</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-05-02/the-ultimate-guide-to-a-successful-exhibition-plan-using-interactive-games-to-stand-out</guid><pubDate>Fri, 02 May 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/whack-a-mole.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;In today's competitive business landscape, creating a memorable&lt;a href="/pages/exhibition-game-hire"&gt; exhibition event&lt;/a&gt; stand that draws visitors in is crucial for generating leads and building brand awareness. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Businesses and individuals all over the country have trusted us here at Fun Pro for over 15 years to help them create memorable experiences, whether it&amp;rsquo;s generating buzz at a &lt;a href="/pages/promotional-event-games"&gt;brand activation&lt;/a&gt; event, boosting team morale at &lt;a href="/news/2025-02-10/use-fun-staff-party-games-to-help-build-a-happier-more-productive-team"&gt;staff parties&lt;/a&gt;, or simply just providing fun activities at &lt;a href="/pages/wedding-entertainment"&gt;weddings&lt;/a&gt; and community events.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
In this guide, we&amp;rsquo;re going to share with you why our interactive games for hire like &lt;a href="/category/batak"&gt;Batak&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/category/prize-games"&gt;Prize Crane&lt;/a&gt; games, and &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;Car Simulators&lt;/a&gt; can make all the difference to your next event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Interactive Games Are Essential For Exhibitions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Corporate events like exhibitions are highly competitive environments where dozens, sometimes hundreds, of companies are competing for attention, and it&amp;rsquo;s more important than ever to stand out in unique and interesting ways. &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Traditional static displays often fail to create meaningful connections with potential clients, which is where things like &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; come in. Using things like games has been shown to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Create a natural, low-pressure environment for conversations&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Boost stand visibility and foot traffic by up to 35%&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Provide a memorable experience that keeps your brand top-of-mind&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Generate valuable lead data through game participation&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Offers unique branding opportunities that reinforce your marketing message&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;According to recent industry research, exhibition stands with interactive elements experience 65% more engagement than those without. This translates directly to a higher return on your exhibition investment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Creating Your Exhibition Game Plan: Things to Consider&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Before choosing what kind of interactive elements you&amp;rsquo;d like, consider these crucial factors:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Exhibition Goals: Define what success looks like for you. Is it lead generation, brand awareness, product demonstration, or relationship building?&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Available Space: Understand your stand dimensions and layout to choose appropriate games that will fit&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Target Audience: Select games that resonate with your demographic and industry&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Branding Integration: Plan how your visual identity will be incorporated into the games&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Staff Requirements: Determine how many team members you'll need to operate games and engage visitors&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Budget Considerations: Balance impact with investment for maximum ROI&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Early planning is essential - we recommend booking your entertainment and hiring games at least 8-12 weeks before major exhibitions to ensure availability and allow for any custom branding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Prize Crane Machines: The Ultimate Lead Generation Tool&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/prize-crane-machines.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Our premium Prize Crane machines are consistently among our most popular exhibition offerings, and for good reason. These eye-catching units combine nostalgic appeal with powerful marketing capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How Prize Cranes Transform Exhibition Stands&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Irresistible Appeal: The classic arcade experience draws visitors of all ages&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Extended Engagement: Average interaction time of 2-3 minutes provides ample opportunity for staff conversations&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Custom Branding: Full vinyl wrapping options transform the entire unit into a brand showcase&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Strategic Prize Selection: Incorporate branded merchandise, product samples, or high-value incentives&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Lead Capture: Optional digital integration allows for contact information collection&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Pro Tip: Fill your Prize Crane with a combination of branded merchandise and higher-value "special prizes" to generate excitement. Branded USB drives, power banks, and premium desk accessories provide lasting value while keeping your brand visible long after the exhibition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Batak Reaction Games: Competitive Engagement for High-Energy Results&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/batak-reactions-game.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For exhibitions where you want to create excitement and draw crowds, our Batak reaction games deliver exceptional results. These high-energy games tap into visitors' competitive nature while providing valuable brand exposure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Maximising Batak Impact at Your Exhibition&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Competition Element: Create leaderboards and daily prizes to encourage repeat visits&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Social Media Integration: Encourage participants to share their scores online&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Industry Relevance: Link game performance to industry metrics or company values&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Space Efficiency: Compact footprint works well even in limited exhibition spaces&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Cross-Generational Appeal: Simple concept with broad demographic appeal&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Car Simulators: Creating an Immersive Brand Experience&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/fun-pro-car-simulators.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When you need to make a substantial impression, our professional-grade Car Simulators deliver an immersive experience that guarantees exhibition impact. These premium units combine cutting-edge technology with exceptional branding opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Car Simulators Dominate Exhibition Floors&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Crowd-Drawing Power: Creates visible excitement that attracts attendees from across the venue&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Extended Engagement: Average session time of 5+ minutes provides deep brand interaction&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Premium Perception: Associates your brand with high-quality, innovative experiences&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Demographic Versatility: Appeals to diverse age ranges and professional backgrounds&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Implementation Strategy: Position the simulator at the front corner of your stand to maximise visibility while creating a natural flow into your main display area. Staff should use the waiting time to qualify visitors and introduce key marketing messages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Integrating Games Into Your Broader Exhibition Strategy&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Interactive games deliver maximum value when seamlessly integrated into your overall exhibition strategy. Here's how to ensure cohesion:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Pre-Event Marketing: Promote your interactive stand features in pre-exhibition communications&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Data Capture Planning: Design a smooth process for collecting lead information from game participants&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Staff Training: Ensure your team knows how to use game interactions to initiate meaningful conversations&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Follow-Up Strategy: Plan personalised follow-ups that reference the exhibition experience&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Performance Metrics: Define clear KPIs to measure game effectiveness (leads, conversations, social mentions)&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;By thoughtfully integrating games into your broader strategy, you transform them from simple entertainment into powerful marketing tools.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Can the games be branded to match our company's visual identity? &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, absolutely. You can choose from various customisation options when hiring games from Fun Pro so that you can display your company or product branding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;How far in advance should we book for a major exhibition? We recommend securing your exhibition entertainment 8-12 weeks in advance, particularly for popular dates and custom branding requirements. For major industry exhibitions, earlier booking is advisable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Do you provide staff to operate the games? Yes, we offer professional game attendants as an optional service. Many clients prefer this option to free up their team for valuable sales conversations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Are these games suitable for all types of exhibitions? While our games have proven successful across diverse industries, we'll help you select the most appropriate options for your specific audience, objectives and exhibition environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Nationwide Exhibition Game Hire: Coverage Across the UK&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Fun Pro UK provides comprehensive exhibition game hire services throughout the United Kingdom. Our experienced teams regularly service major exhibition venues in:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;London (ExCeL, Olympia, Business Design Centre)&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Birmingham (NEC, ICC)&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Manchester (Manchester Central, EventCity)&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Liverpool (ACC Liverpool)&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Glasgow (SEC)&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Cardiff (Motorpoint Arena)&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Coventry (Ricoh Arena)&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Our logistics team ensures smooth delivery,* professional installation, and prompt collection, allowing you to focus entirely on engaging with exhibition visitors.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
*Delivery and collection may incur additional charges.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Getting Started: Planning Your Exhibition Game Strategy&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Ready to transform your next exhibition stand? The process is simple:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Consultation: Discuss your exhibition goals, space constraints, and target audience with our events team&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Customisation: Explore branding options and game selection based on your specific requirements&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Confirmation: Secure your booking with clear delivery and collection scheduling&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Preparation: Receive comprehensive guidelines to maximise your exhibition game investment&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Execution: Enjoy professional delivery, installation and technical support throughout your event&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Ready to Stand Out at Your Next Exhibition?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Contact&lt;/a&gt; our exhibition specialists today to discuss how our interactive games can transform your next exhibition experience. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Boost Team Spirit With These Ideas For Your Next Work Social Event</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-03-18/boost-team-spirit-with-these-ideas-for-your-next-work-social-event</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-03-18/boost-team-spirit-with-these-ideas-for-your-next-work-social-event</guid><pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Organising a work social event is a great way to strengthen team bonds, improve morale, and create a positive workplace culture. But with so many options available, how do you choose the perfect activities? Whether you're planning a small &lt;a href="/news/2025-02-10/use-fun-staff-party-games-to-help-build-a-happier-more-productive-team"&gt;staff party&lt;/a&gt; or a large-scale &lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;corporate event&lt;/a&gt;, incorporating things like&lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt; interactive games&lt;/a&gt; can make all the difference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;The Importance Of a Well Planned Work Social Event&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Team-building activities provide an opportunity for employees to connect outside of the usual office setting. These events help improve communication, collaboration, and overall job satisfaction. By choosing engaging and entertaining activities, you ensure everyone has a memorable experience that translates into a&lt;a href="https://www.helpscout.com/blog/increase-team-productivity/"&gt; more productive team&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Work Social Event Ideas &amp;amp; Activities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;1. Arcade Game Challenge&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games"&gt;Arcade games&lt;/a&gt; bring a sense of nostalgia and fun, making them a perfect choice for a work social event. Renting a selection of arcade games allows employees to compete, bond, and enjoy a light-hearted break from work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;Fun Pro Recommends: Prize Crane Arcade Grabber&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/prize-crane-arcade-grabber.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/47/prize-crane-arcade-grabber"&gt;prize crane arcade grabber&lt;/a&gt; is an exciting addition to any work event, offering a mix of luck and skill. Employees can compete to grab prizes, making it a great conversation starter and a fun way to boost engagement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;2. High-Speed Thrills with Racing Car Simulators&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For teams that enjoy a bit of competition, &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;racing car simulators&lt;/a&gt; are a thrilling option. These simulators provide an adrenaline-pumping experience that allows participants to race against their colleagues in a fun and friendly environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;Fun Pro Recommends: Racing Car Simulators&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/fun-pro-racing-car-simulators.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;With immersive visuals and realistic driving experiences, racing car simulators create an exciting atmosphere where employees can challenge each other for the fastest lap times. This activity is perfect for fostering a sense of &lt;a href="https://www.atlassian.com/blog/teamwork/the-importance-of-teamwork"&gt;teamwork&lt;/a&gt; and healthy competition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;3. Reaction Speed Games for Team Bonding&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Testing reaction speeds can be a great way to encourage quick thinking and friendly competition. Games that require fast reflexes can be both entertaining and beneficial for &lt;a href="https://www.health.harvard.edu/mind-and-mood/train-your-brain"&gt;sharpening cognitive skills&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 dir="ltr"&gt;Fun Pro Recommends: Batak Games&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/fun-pro-batak-games.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The &lt;a href="/category/batak"&gt;Batak&lt;/a&gt; reaction game is an excellent choice for a work social event. It challenges participants to hit randomly lit targets as quickly as possible, improving their reflexes while having fun. It&amp;rsquo;s a great icebreaker and ideal for creating a lively and interactive environment. Choose between &lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/43/batak-pro"&gt;Batak Pro&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/61/batak-lite"&gt;Batak Lite&lt;/a&gt; to suit your needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;4. Retro Gaming Night&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Why not take a trip down memory lane with a retro gaming night? Set up classic arcade machines and gaming consoles to let employees unwind with their favourite childhood games. This event is perfect for fostering friendly competition and nostalgia.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;5. Interactive Team Quiz with Mini Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Combine the excitement of a pub-style quiz with interactive mini-games. Each round can feature a different challenge, from racing games to reaction tests, keeping employees entertained throughout the event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do I choose the best activity for my team?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider the interests and preferences of your team members. If they enjoy competition, racing simulators or reaction speed games might be ideal. For a more relaxed experience, arcade games or a retro gaming night could be a great fit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How much space do I need for these activities?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The space required depends on the activity. Arcade machines and racing simulators need a dedicated area, while a quiz night or &lt;a href="/category/pub-games"&gt;pub games&lt;/a&gt; can usually be set up in a conference room or open office space.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can I mix different activities in one event?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Absolutely. Combining multiple activities, such as racing simulators and a quiz night, can create a diverse and engaging experience for all employees and help everyone feel included by choosing an activity that they enjoy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How can I ensure everyone gets involved?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Offering a variety of activities and forming teams can help encourage participation. Creating a friendly competition with small prizes can also motivate employees to engage. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;However, it&amp;rsquo;s also important to keep in mind that some people are more introverted than others or simply may not feel comfortable joining in, so this should never be forced or made into an issue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Plan Your Work Social Event with Fun Pro UK&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Choosing the right work social event can make a significant impact on team dynamics and morale. By incorporating engaging activities like arcade games, racing simulators, and reaction-based challenges, you create an unforgettable experience that employees will talk about long after the event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;At Fun Pro UK, we provide a range of interactive and exciting games to take your corporate event to the next level. From arcade machines to high-tech simulators, our selection ensures a fun-filled and memorable experience for your team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/all-products"&gt;Explore our range of entertainment options&lt;/a&gt; today and start planning your next successful work social event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Use Fun Staff Party Games to Help Build a Happier, More Productive Team</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-02-10/use-fun-staff-party-games-to-help-build-a-happier-more-productive-team</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-02-10/use-fun-staff-party-games-to-help-build-a-happier-more-productive-team</guid><pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Staff parties are a great way to encourage &lt;a href="/news/2024-12-05/the-best-ideas-for-team-bonding-activities-in-the-workplace" style="background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;team bonding&lt;/a&gt; and make everyone feel included, and build stronger relationships at work. The type of parties you throw at your company say a lot about the culture you&amp;rsquo;ve created or are trying to create, so it&amp;rsquo;s important to think about this when planning the activities you&amp;rsquo;d like to include. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Whether it&amp;rsquo;s fun staff party games that allow everyone to show their competitive side, or something a bit more formal where your team can mingle and get to know each other outside of work, the key to a good staff party lies in the planning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;In this post, we&amp;rsquo;re going to share our top tips for throwing an unforgettable staff party to show your team that you appreciate them and what they do, and in turn, build a happier, more fulfilled and productive team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;The Benefits of Staff Party Games:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Staff party games are a lot of fun and offer the perfect way to bring your team together outside of work and show their fun side. Here are some of the things that make staff party games so popular among employees:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;They encourage team bonding&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Just because people work together, doesn&amp;rsquo;t necessarily mean they have gotten to know each other other than to say hello when passing by in the corridor or in the occasional team meeting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="https://hbr.org/2020/07/true-friends-at-work"&gt;This 2022 study&lt;/a&gt; by the Harvard Business Review found that genuine work-based friendships not only benefit employees, but can have a positive impact on the business itself due to increased productivity and morale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You may even have experienced this yourself; having people at work that you can chat to each day, go for lunch, and have a laugh makes going to work more enjoyable and less tedious, so it&amp;rsquo;s the same for your staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When at work each day, people are mostly kept within their own teams, making it difficult to form friendships outside their team or department. Staff parties, and especially those that include interactive activities like staff party games are great ways to get people mixing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.stylist.co.uk/life/careers/work-best-friend-research/917923"&gt;Another study found&lt;/a&gt; that more than half of UK workers directly credit their current or previous jobs with meeting some of their most important friends. Of course, we can&amp;rsquo;t say that staff parties are the main reason they met and formed a friendship, but it&amp;rsquo;s certainly clear that certain aspects of company culture make it easier for employees to connect and bond with each other.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;They&amp;rsquo;re inclusive&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;With so many options to choose from and with something for everyone, staff party games are designed to be inclusive and take into consideration things like physical ability, whether someone is extroverted or introverted, and many can even help with managing things like language barriers which is especially important when you&amp;rsquo;re leading a multicultural team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;They boost staff morale&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s just a fact of life that we all have to work, but with over &lt;a href="https://www.gettysburg.edu/news/stories?id=79db7b34-630c-4f49-ad32-4ab9ea48e72b"&gt;one third of our lives&lt;/a&gt; spent working, the profession we choose should be something that is enjoyable, or at the very least, not something that we hate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Many companies will throw the traditional annual Christmas party, but from the perspective of the staff, it can often feel like nothing more than a tick box exercise with very little thought or effort put in.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When you truly care about building a strong and positive company culture and take the time to think about fun staff party ideas your team will genuinely enjoy and want to participate in, then your employees will feel more appreciated at work, staff retention rates will be higher, and morale will be better overall.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;They improve communication&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;One of the most challenging aspects of managing a team is navigating the different personalities and communication styles in a way that everyone feels supported and heard.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Group activities like staff party games require teamwork and communication which will then filter through into helping them communicate more effectively in the workplace.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Exciting Staff Party Game Ideas:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Whether this is your first time organising a staff party or you&amp;rsquo;re something of an expert, we have a range of party games for you to choose from that are guaranteed to make your next staff party the one that everyone talks about for years to come. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Here are some of the staff party games available to hire from Fun Pro:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Prize Crane games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXc97BGF5hyiVSErKIYApaJvohLmOPLldUssmdpbAZhgxTHermNaUUSHnFX52aAHIQSs4QfOL61JSdyGxj7pWfuTKqSQgdmMuLo0lSo_4WWrQaOWFOhqtwttSxFb36BEXSddqAwXHQ?key=KExXpscMQ0sVnSHnZPw7R9RA" width="602" height="1289" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/47/prize-crane-arcade-grabber"&gt;Prize Crane games&lt;/a&gt; make a great addition to staff parties of all sizes and a great way to break the ice and get everyone involved. If you remember going to an arcade as a child, the thrill of wondering whether you&amp;rsquo;d win that teddy was half the fun. With our Prize Crane arcade games, your team can have hours of fun just with these alone. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The machines themselves come in a range of themes and colours and they don&amp;rsquo;t require any coins; simply fill them with your chosen prizes and see who&amp;rsquo;s lucky enough to win.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Prices start at just &amp;pound;495+ VAT.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Racing Car simulators&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXeUzUVWxEyKzJSb-wOi-OHRFVrBX6g8HaQqZQKQ7uzbcwJ2Ok5CQcnRgfBaS2JZeqfeBWTh9KkE7pnyQU5VgnbpBXUK5uVEkNyyXJOillYpfMF6o8ZzmyYPgfYRJ50EyLVnMurw?key=KExXpscMQ0sVnSHnZPw7R9RA" width="602" height="799" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For the more competitive employees in your team, what better way to encourage some healthy rivalry and team spirit than with &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;racing car simulators&lt;/a&gt;? &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These car simulators are perfect for staff parties and will really help bring the team together as they race against each other.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Prices for our racing car simulators start at &amp;pound;475+ VAT for 1 car.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Football tables&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXcYoss85CC33LxdcGHlnKKXr8eaFoHTFexyMSmCprph5kKazJCbdVKUCfvrtykpqMjV_scX6pbbo4TDfhC2kuF1vIp0ASpII9CA_QnHVttw-MqVXX2Gpwec7qQsbT_DjTQ42XT5iA?key=KExXpscMQ0sVnSHnZPw7R9RA" width="602" height="796" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/27/football-tables"&gt;Football tables&lt;/a&gt; and other team games are a great way to bring people together and break the ice at staff parties since they encourage teamwork, and lighthearted competition among colleagues. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;With prices starting at &amp;pound;295+ VAT, Fun Pro football tables are an affordable way to throw a great staff party that everyone can enjoy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Crazy golf&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXcDP_n55c2YLhJJovraclyrH4c6UKy8Pf0UniTsL-ZYRCN68P9oc2O19_9eUcVZbEQPz4QE9Lkc24G6KIEIwnxjFE_-q4965ROu4Y_Jxdm767kWLAkdXxIB4ptzngKCisxk2fwktQ?key=KExXpscMQ0sVnSHnZPw7R9RA" width="602" height="804" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Crazy golf, also known as mini-golf, is a fantastic way to get employees interacting in a relaxed and enjoyable setting. With creative obstacles and engaging courses, crazy golf promotes teamwork, patience, and a bit of friendly competition. It&amp;rsquo;s a perfect option for indoor or outdoor staff parties and caters to all skill levels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Our &lt;a href="/category/fun-days/81/crazy-golf"&gt;crazy golf&lt;/a&gt; hire starts at &amp;pound;495 +VAT.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Batak games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXdcC9AEk16l2797BBtrlCkW5lAV_ki9ouPjVdnQiEutYgaaFUFYYjp24Dd1HBQCjqKMa6d93-HrRZgQpsn15uX-YxGJwS1876Zq4HjjQzbQ0SO2ulV1znhAPb-Up7tQavVwkrE3aQ?key=KExXpscMQ0sVnSHnZPw7R9RA" width="602" height="752" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/search.aspx?q=batak"&gt;Batak reaction games&lt;/a&gt; are always a hit at staff parties and events, especially when people are playing in groups. These high-energy games involve pressing illuminated buttons as quickly as possible, making them ideal for those in your team who enjoy a fast-paced challenge. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The prices for our &lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/61/batak-lite"&gt;Batak Lite&lt;/a&gt; games start at &amp;pound;445 + VAT and &amp;pound;495 + VAT for&lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/43/batak-pro"&gt; Batak Pro.&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Tips For Organising Your Next Staff Party:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Planning a staff party that people enjoy takes a good level of planning and organising to make sure that it goes smoothly and that your employees are talking about it for all the right reasons.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Here are some of our top staff party planning tips:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Set a budget&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The first step is to think about how much you can afford for things like the venue, games, food, and other essentials.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s also a good idea to shop around so that you can balance cost-effectiveness with quality to get the best value for your money.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Choose a suitable venue&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When looking for a location for your staff party, you should look for one that can comfortably accommodate the amount of people in your team, as well as space for any planned activities like party games, stalls, or photo booths. You should also consider the time of year and if you plan to have any outdoor activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Decide on themes and entertainment&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Staff parties with a specific theme like a &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/4/retro-arcade-games"&gt;retro arcade&lt;/a&gt; night, carnival or a decade-specific theme is a great way to get people involved in the activities and show their personalities outside of work. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Once you&amp;rsquo;ve chosen your theme, you can pick things to bring it to life like music, lighting, activities, and decor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Consider different needs and preferences&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When planning something like a staff party or event, it&amp;rsquo;s important to think about the fact that your team consists of people with a variety of needs and preferences. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For example, if you have staff members who are neurodivergent, or have a physical difficulty, then choosing activities that could be overwhelming for them, or a venue that doesn&amp;rsquo;t have wheelchair access is probably going to exclude some of your team from attending. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You should also consider that some people are more introverted or extroverted than others, and while you can&amp;rsquo;t accommodate 100% of everyone&amp;rsquo;s needs and preferences, aiming to make your staff party as inclusive as possible will make it easier for people to attend and also make them feel that the company really cares about them and appreciates the work they do, in turn leading to increased morale and higher productivity&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Source Games and Equipment&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Now that you&amp;rsquo;ve figured out the finer details of your staff party, it&amp;rsquo;s time to start getting everything you need in place to make it happen. If you know that you&amp;rsquo;re going to be having things like staff party games, then start contacting suppliers like Fun Pro to check prices and order the games and equipment you need. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s always a good idea to speak with a variety of suppliers for things like catering and decorations to see what deals they&amp;rsquo;re offering so that you can have a great staff party without spending more than you have to.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Find Staff Party Games With Fun Pro:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;At Fun Pro UK, we understand the importance of creating memorable and fun events. Our wide variety of staff party games and equipment means there&amp;rsquo;s always something for everyone, no matter your team size or budget.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Choose Fun Pro UK?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expert Support&lt;/strong&gt;: We&amp;rsquo;re here to help you choose the best games and activities so that you can plan a truly unforgettable staff party or event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;End-to-end Service&lt;/strong&gt;: We don&amp;rsquo;t just supply you with equipment and leave you to it; we will deliver, install and collect everything once you&amp;rsquo;re done.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Something For Everyone&lt;/strong&gt;: From interactive game hire to arcade machines, we offer a range of options to make sure your next staff party has something that everyone can enjoy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Custom Branding&lt;/strong&gt;: We can apply your custom branding or company logo to any games or machines you hire and will remove them once you&amp;rsquo;re finished with them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reliability&lt;/strong&gt;: Our top-notch equipment and seamless service mean you can focus on enjoying the party while we handle the logistics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Take a look through our &lt;a href="/category/all-products"&gt;range of staff party games&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk#FooterContact"&gt;get in touch with us&lt;/a&gt; for a free quote.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do staff party games improve team morale and productivity?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Staff party games are a great way to get people interacting outside of work in a fun and lighthearted way so they&amp;rsquo;re more likely to get to know other people in the team they may not have met before. These relationships overflow into their work which makes coming to work more enjoyable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How can I ensure all employees&amp;mdash;introverts included, enjoy the event?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Although you&amp;rsquo;ll never be able to accommodate every single need and preference when planning an event, a good rule of thumb is to make sure that you&amp;rsquo;re planning a range of activities that most people can enjoy. Introverts may be more likely to enjoy things that only require one or a few people to play. Whereas extroverts will be more likely to enjoy games and activities that are more team-focused.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What types of games are most effective for large corporate gatherings?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The types of games and activities you hire for your event will depend on the company culture you have, the event you&amp;rsquo;re planning. If you&amp;rsquo;re hosting a more formal, corporate event or staff party, then activities like &lt;a href="/category/christmas-game-hire/16/casino-table-hire"&gt;casino tables&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/category/company-award-ceremonies/11/classic-photo-booths"&gt;photo booths&lt;/a&gt;, or even &lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/44/giant-jenga-hire"&gt;giant Jenga&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Should I hire a professional organiser or DIY the staff party planning?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Although there are certainly some aspects of planning a staff party or team event that are easy enough to do yourself, others will be much easier if you partner with a professional event hire company like Fun Pro, especially if you&amp;rsquo;re looking to have things like branded party games.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do I choose a suitable venue or space for group games?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When choosing a venue for your event or staff party, you should consider things like how many people will be attending, what kind of activities you would like to have for people, and whether or not the venue is accessible for anyone who might require this.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s the best way to encourage participation and enthusiasm among employees?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This is never something that should be forced. If you already have a good company culture where your staff feel valued and appreciated, and they can see that the events you put on are trying to be inclusive, then most people will want to attend and will happily participate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can we incorporate company branding or themes into the games?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes. All of our games and machines can be branded with your company or event logo and promotional images. These are especially popular for things like conferences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do I measure the success of hosting staff party games?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The best way to measure the success of any party or event where you&amp;rsquo;re including things like games and activities is to see how many people are participating. You&amp;rsquo;ll also likely get feedback from people after the event as they&amp;rsquo;ll happily tell you how much they enjoyed themselves.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>How to Choose the Perfect Photo Booth for Your Event</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-01-28/how-to-choose-the-perfect-photo-booth-for-your-event</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-01-28/how-to-choose-the-perfect-photo-booth-for-your-event</guid><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When you're hosting a fun and unique event, there needs to be a fine balance between meticulous planning and delivering an experience that guests would find memorable. Attendees should be able to cherish memories of the event for years and years to come.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;No wonder photo booths have become a staple at events. These beloved booths offer an exciting way to capture memories while keeping guests entertained. Whether it&amp;rsquo;s a &lt;a href="/pages/wedding-entertainment"&gt;wedding&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/pages/office-and-corporate-entertainment"&gt;corporate event&lt;/a&gt;, birthday party, or community gathering, a &lt;a href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;photo booth hire&lt;/a&gt; adds an extra layer of fun.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If you&amp;rsquo;re considering a photo booth for your event, knowing how to choose the perfect one can make all the difference. Let&amp;rsquo;s explore the best options and essential tips for finding the ideal booth for your needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Find the Best Photo Booth Hire for Your Next Event&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Photo booths come in many types. Depending on the style, you can find one that fits your specific event just right. Some photo booths can even be customised to suit your preferences and or your brand. Here&amp;rsquo;s a quick look at popular options:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;1. Classic Photo Booths&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfrP6fMC8vSJ51RNRFp5im6OQyl7gjXgdgDK3qOkfWPdeeoNCvXNrWdVEk1xSXzObGmtMBwdsWVLfYWC5jjGcWGjbf06MCt5g7WuqYy1sTIcc11N_corPyrRz1_0InqKPOUnDm7Og?key=GMLM4MbQteSQewAOhBOopIPG" width="624" height="416.2559993913531" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The traditional photo booth is an all time favourite for many events. You can also add a unique flair to them to make them more personal and memorable for the attendees.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These &lt;a href="/category/company-award-ceremonies/11/classic-photo-booths"&gt;classic photo booths&lt;/a&gt; can come with customisable backdrops and props; everything from glamorous red carpets to vibrant cityscapes and even whimsical fairytale landscapes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It can also come with customisable print designs that complement event themes or personal style. These prints can also include personalised messages or &lt;a href="/pages/promotional-event-games"&gt;branding elements&lt;/a&gt; that your guests would love.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;2. Interactive Photo Booths&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXd0k_EpxLb_NBfeE4dfOeX7ksO22zhIwBIQFsc_5YQDEX1sMssecBNQjNgTNnrLRjUCYpjI5PBIFxt9nwwznyVrwHx_rZ-3adFgL3cOU9HpML6fxcWQaWoYb_xrCKOZb3XqgsYqXQ?key=GMLM4MbQteSQewAOhBOopIPG" width="624" height="349" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Interactive photo booths combine technology with entertainment, like our &lt;a href="/category/christmas-game-hire/12/christmas-photo-booths"&gt;Christmas-themed photo booths&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;magic mirrors&lt;/a&gt;. These types of photo booths have increased in popularity because they deliver engaging and immersive experiences to users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Some interactive photo booths can also include augmented reality (AR) experiences, slow motion capture, and even 360 degree &lt;a href="/news/2018-01-30/saturday-night-selfies-at-milton-keynes"&gt;selfie booths&lt;/a&gt; that capture pictures from every angle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;3. Bespoke Photo Booths&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXe5oh2Z3RDjAxwm8bdweqgQUNugJpvV6aZ6gi4HnivLlf0BEIcTmD760HOE1yq_HpD2Nap7rkI0DO-BlzO1FjQRawMToZOqaR7NSk8OYdL-yAzEBY3N9C-t7VeVNQPSz3W8XzM0hQ?key=GMLM4MbQteSQewAOhBOopIPG" width="624" height="627" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;To deliver a completely customised experience, &lt;a href="/category/branded-exhibition-games/24/bespoke-photo-booth-hire"&gt;bespoke photo booths&lt;/a&gt; are the way to go. Photo booths like this can be tailored to match an event&amp;rsquo;s specific requirements, incorporating elements like branded backdrops, props, and interactive features that reflect your theme or corporate identity. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;They're ideal for product launches, marketing campaigns, and unique celebrations. Bespoke booths can also include personalised animations, augmented reality effects, and themed designs. Their flexibility is unmatched and makes sure that your event stands out while giving guests a one of a kind experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;4. Green Screen Photo Booths&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXc0EXV4RkG_ja_oF3zr4rQk8Q8TIsFob3U9GKWzWoljDpiBb-wXD_VuiorTY950kohsi_shk-35atTtz2i63vB-KjiNBAJvwgNeIoLsIiiTXfJh_QPNc_a-TssaOlszkSpmqQuisw?key=GMLM4MbQteSQewAOhBOopIPG" width="624" height="472" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;Green screen photo booths&lt;/a&gt; give you limitless backgrounds to choose from, and your guests can pick from high quality effects. With a green screen photo booth, the only limit is your creativity. Combined with the right themed props and scene transitions, a green screen photo booth can deliver an immersive experience that keeps all the guests entertained.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Key features to look for when hiring a photo booth, include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Instant photo printing for guests who love taking home prints as souvenirs.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Digital sharing options that let attendees upload their photos directly to social media.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Customisable backdrops and props for the corporate photo booth hire that match the theme of the event.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Fun filters and overlays that add a creative touch to photos.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;How to Choose the Best Photo Booth to Hire&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;There are a few things you need to consider when hiring a photobooth for your event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt; 1. Space Availability&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Check how much room the photo booth needs. Open air photo booths and compact selfie stations are good for locations with limited room, because you can set them up anywhere.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;However, larger installations, such as 360 photo booths or classic photo booths, will need more space. There needs to be enough space so guests can queue up for photos without disrupting the flow of the event. Be sure to plan the layout to avoid crowding and maintain smooth traffic flow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;2. Event Style and Theme&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Think of the style and theme of your event. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;For instance, for weddings and corporate galas, mirror photo booths or classic photo booths are a great choice. And if you&amp;rsquo;re hosting a casual party or an outdoor event, the event would benefit from an open air booth with themed backdrops and props. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Matching the booth&amp;rsquo;s style to your event&amp;rsquo;s tone enhances the overall experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;3. Budget&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Budget is another critical factor. Photo booths for parties come in a range of prices, so compare prices and hiring periods to find one that suits your budget.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Look for value added features such as unlimited photo prints, digital sharing capabilities, and a big prop selection. Inclusions like this can significantly improve the guest experience without stretching your budget.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;4. Guest Demographics&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider the age range of your guests as well. Family friendly events often call for photo booths equipped with fun props, colourful themes, and interactive features that entertain guests of all ages. For corporate events, options that offer custom branding, sleek aesthetics, and professional grade photos are perfect for leaving a lasting impression.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How far in advance should I hire a photo booth for my party?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We recommend booking 4 to 6 weeks in advance to secure the photo booth you want, especially during peak seasons.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can I customise the photo booth backdrop and print designs?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes! We offer custom backdrops and branded prints to match your event theme or corporate identity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Are props included when hiring a photobooth?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Absolutely. Our photobooth hire comes with a variety of props to add fun and creativity to your photos.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How much space is needed to set up the photo booth hire in London, UK?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The space required depends on the type of photo booth rental. Open-air setups need a minimum of 8x8 feet, while enclosed booths may require more room.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Does the hire include unlimited photo prints or digital copies?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, it does. It includes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Unlimited visits and 2 prints per visit in colour or black and white&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Optional video messaging from your guests&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Fun filled prop box&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;A direct download link to your photos sent after your event&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Your company messages or logos on every print&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Do you offer digital sharing options for social media?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes. Our booths are equipped with features that allow guests to share photos instantly via email or social media.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Do I need to provide a power source for the photo booth?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, a standard power outlet is required. We&amp;rsquo;ll advise you on setup requirements beforehand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What happens if there are technical issues during the event?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If you require onsite assistance during the event, our team is one call away to resolve any issues promptly and deliver a smooth experience for your guests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can the photo booth be branded for corporate or promotional events?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Absolutely! We provide custom branding options for backdrops, props, and photo prints to align with your event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Book Fun Pro UK&amp;rsquo;s Photo Booth Rental for Corporate Events and Birthdays&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We specialise in providing high quality photo booth rentals for any event. We have different photo booth rentals to choose from, so you can always find the perfect match for your event&amp;rsquo;s needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/"&gt;Fun Pro UK&lt;/a&gt; handles the delivery, setup, and breakdown, so you can focus on enjoying your event. You can also add your logo or event theme to backdrops and print designs for a personalised touch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Let us help you create unforgettable memories with our high quality photo booths.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Fun Employee Appreciation Day Ideas that Your Team Will Love</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-01-24/fun-employee-appreciation-day-ideas-that-your-team-will-love</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-01-24/fun-employee-appreciation-day-ideas-that-your-team-will-love</guid><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The world celebrates Employee Appreciation Day in March every year! Your team works hard, and they deserve a day that's dedicated to celebrating their efforts. Taking time to show appreciation creates a moment for connection and celebration; it&amp;rsquo;s a reminder that every contribution matters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Many companies want to show appreciation to their staff, but might be working with a smaller budget. The good news is that you don&amp;rsquo;t need to spend a lot of money to make your team feel appreciated. A little creativity and thoughtfulness goes a long way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;A well planned celebration can make a big impact. It can boost employee morale, increase loyalty, and help build a stronger, more motivated workforce.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;In this post, we will be covering some fun and exciting ideas you can use to celebrate your team and show them just how much you appreciate what they do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Employee Appreciation Day Ideas to Motivate Your Team&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Your employees deserve to feel valued for all the hard work they do. Here are some popular employee appreciation ideas that will make the day truly memorable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;1. Team Building Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXegQSIkDw6DtHiBmfi0HID0rjuPSi9RVvayV2pYDtD0E04LNJfdndUpJhsOz5e2tESx8CdNv3SW49ghdpxIoO0-gXVCJkST7w_zWm-rgE23H-F6NKHoqtANiBw48IKci8HX63-u4w?key=3QGxajlrJekofxv54zo3rIjy" width="624" height="312" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/news/2024-12-05/the-best-ideas-for-team-bonding-activities-in-the-workplace"&gt;These activities help employees bond&lt;/a&gt; and get to know each other outside of work, letting them unwind and have fun together, while also being a way to encourage collaboration and friendly competition. &lt;a href="/pages/team-building-ideas"&gt;Team building games&lt;/a&gt; range from simple trivia competitions to scavenger hunts around the office to complicated relays on an inflatable obstacle course run.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We have a wide variety of interactive games that would be perfect for Employee Appreciation Day. Our top picks include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/43/batak-pro"&gt;Batak Pro&lt;/a&gt;: The perfect game to challenge your team's reaction times, coordination, and stamina. It's a high energy game that sparks competitive spirits in a fun and engaging way.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/36/ballnado-grabber"&gt;Ballnado Ball Grabber&lt;/a&gt;: A thrilling game where participants work together to grab flying balls and win exciting prizes.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;Racing Car Simulators&lt;/a&gt;: The game that immerses all players in exciting races and a realistic and dynamic driving experience, complete with a choice of tracks and off road tests.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/4/retro-arcade-games"&gt;Retro Arcade Games&lt;/a&gt;: The ultimate crowd favourite! It has two player options and a library of up to 60 beloved games including Pac Man, Space Invaders, Frogger, 1944, Pinball, Galaxian, and Donkey Kong.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/20/total-wipe-out"&gt;Total Wipe Out&lt;/a&gt;: This gets everyone involved in the fun. It's a swinging arm game inspired by the likes of TV shows like 'It's a Knockout' and 'Total Wipeout.'&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/21/inflatable-assault-courses"&gt;Inflatable Assault Courses&lt;/a&gt;: Split your staff into different teams, pit department against department, or arrange relay races. It encourages friendly rivalry and bonding that lets the team cheerfully encourage each other.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Fun Pro also has sports inspired interactive games, like &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/6/electronic-basket-ball-hire"&gt;Electronic Basketball&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/60/air-hockey-table-hire"&gt;Air Hockey&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/category/all-products/87/shuffleboard-hire"&gt;Shuffle Board&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/80/table-tennis-hire"&gt;Table Tennis&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/27/football-tables"&gt;Football Tables&lt;/a&gt;, and more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;2. Personalised Notes or Gifts&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXemF28K4rCG86w6Jij5Vg42dwMFbl8q0LVSsCx8SgAoUSGjJJCJjlvXs3FGU8pWPQtoYMs178ImZLxN4M2GhKbaoM2k9btlsjzcnpFu_iAoG4RT1GORQH2LTdLXnGFGkW2FFeGCAw?key=3QGxajlrJekofxv54zo3rIjy" width="624" height="351" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Personalisation goes a long way. If words of affirmation are your way of showing appreciation, a personalised note or gifts are a good option. A lot of thought goes into handwriting notes and this naturally has a stronger effect on everyone. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Personalised notes or postcards are one of the best ways to show employees genuine gratitude and effort.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;And when it comes to personalised gifts, employees appreciate something unique, something they want and appreciate. To up the ante and make things more interesting, you can encourage the whole team to give gifts to each other (even if it's not Christmas).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;3. Office Makeovers&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXewXYEX-rFLET7RRzraYXAboWb9FdD4oa_LVTId7z42QQn5PLD8soPPrmZZgBK3nsAzQhJ9_C2OhrgVM2MaCYmz0R8-T0iNRmc5gQoZedneypW9oD0M42uAp2L9eYTPuVqW59bp2g?key=3QGxajlrJekofxv54zo3rIjy" width="624" height="416" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Surprise your team with a workplace makeover. Refresh the office environment by introducing new d&amp;eacute;cor, arranging comfortable break areas, or even adding fun elements like a photo booth or a snack bar.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;A makeover will show your employees that you care about their work environment, and it makes them feel appreciated when they come to work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;4. Wellness Activities and Retreats&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfjsYvDGnoviXe_c4CP5rMHAKDD7Lqunj7NQlKq_OYJFvGcI9uhz8UtjWNVUwGM_VcJiDg2MfDFJn6bGh5D7OSSx2n2OSct-zH_3okZ5o3ygZkBm1s4fg-hT5KsWKNwJ8-vLp_R?key=3QGxajlrJekofxv54zo3rIjy" width="624" height="417" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;To increase job satisfaction and retention, employee wellbeing is important. Providing wellness activities on Employee Appreciation Day can show your team that you value their health and wellbeing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Activities like yoga, meditation, a spa package, or even a healthy snack station can boost morale and help reduce workplace stress. But if your employees work remotely or live far from each other, you can buy packages that are close to their places or provide an allowance for a relaxing spa day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;5. Employee Recognition and Awards Programmes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXeEcWdev1N5ee9e02OYVQP6fC9wjy64nVKVh-Mb4sAE9nKqZuu6JxyNlEJDvNFig5iu4yB-MVstX40lh9TTbck1EQM2RtOAb7VQCW6biGgA0VuRXDMKNRkFWNJcNPcHycJKQ5mVoA?key=3QGxajlrJekofxv54zo3rIjy" width="624" height="416" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You can boost employee morale with a consistent programme for &lt;a href="/category/company-award-ceremonies"&gt;rewards and recognition&lt;/a&gt;. Of course, one day a year of appreciation is not enough to keep employee morale high, but it can help increase employee loyalty. You can create custom programmes using spreadsheets and gift card vendors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Employee recognition platforms also exist where your team can do peer to peer recognitions, get rewards, and point gifting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;6. Shoutouts on Employee Collaboration Platforms&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Public appreciation should not be understated. Employee collaboration platforms like Skype, Microsoft Teams, Slack, etc can let you do this. Simply choose employees that you want to appreciate and write something for everyone to see. It might not take a lot of time, effort, or thought for you, but receiving public recognition can mean a lot for your team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Workers Appreciation Day Matters&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If you're running a company and have a team of people working together with you, you have to remember that you're managing people. And you know what people need other than the basic resources? They need recognition, appreciation, and validation!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Recognising your employees on Employee Appreciation Day isn't just about one day of celebration, it's about creating a culture of appreciation that should be upheld all year round. When employees feel that their hard work is valued, it results in numerous benefits for both individuals and the company as a whole:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Increased Job Satisfaction: Regular recognition helps employees feel more satisfied in their roles, which leads to a more motivated and committed team.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Reduced Burnout: Recognising achievements and showing gratitude helps employees avoid burnout by reminding them of the value of their work.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Healthier Workplace Culture: Appreciation creates a positive, inclusive workplace culture where employees feel supported and motivated to do their best.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Higher Employee Retention: The happier your employees are, the more they would stay in their existing job and appreciate their own efforts at the company.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Strong Culture: Employee Appreciation Day is also a great way to promote a healthier work culture in your business. It makes everyone feel included and appreciated.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Better Productivity: If you appreciate employees, they will be motivated to perform well and some will even want to outdo their past achievements. Appreciation feels good and it inspires everyone to always be better.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;When is the best time to celebrate Employee Appreciation Day?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Employee Appreciation Day typically falls on the first Friday in March, but you can choose any day that works best for your team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How can I recognise employees with limited resources?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You don&amp;rsquo;t need a big budget to show appreciation. Simple, thoughtful gestures like handwritten notes, public recognition, company fun and games, or team lunches can make a big impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What types of team-building games work for large groups?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Fun Pro UK offers games that are crowd favourites and cater to large groups. Take your pick from interactive or corporate game hires like Batak Pro and &lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/61/batak-lite"&gt;Batak Lite&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/category/branded-exhibition-games/64/mega-wire-branded-game-hire-stand-alone"&gt;Mega Wire&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/2/lights-out-game"&gt;Lights Out Game&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/3/cash-grabber-machine-hire"&gt;Cash Grabber Machines&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/category/exhibition-games/77/virtual-pinball"&gt;Virtual Pinball&lt;/a&gt;, and more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can these ideas be adapted for remote or hybrid work environments?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, many employee appreciation ideas, such as virtual trivia, online wellness challenges, and remote team building games, can be adapted to fit a remote or hybrid workforce.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do I ensure activities are inclusive and accessible for all staff?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s important to consider the different needs of your employees. Make sure that games and activities can be enjoyed by everyone, regardless of physical ability, and that there&amp;rsquo;s a range of options to suit various interests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can Fun Pro UK handle event logistics and setup?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, Fun Pro UK offers full event support, including logistics, setup, and coordination. Our team ensures a smooth and hassle-free experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do I measure the success of our Employee Appreciation Day?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You can measure success through employee feedback, engagement levels during activities, and follow up surveys to gauge the lasting impact of the event on morale and job satisfaction.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;How Fun Pro UK Can Help You Host the Perfect Event&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/"&gt;Fun Pro UK&lt;/a&gt; specialises in creating interactive, memorable experiences that can transform any Employee Appreciation Day into an event your team will remember for years to come. We offer a wide range of engaging games and event equipment designed to cater to different company cultures and budgets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;From giant games to &lt;a href="/news/2024-05-03/the-secret-to-team-building-interactive-games"&gt;interactive team building challenges&lt;/a&gt;, we have options that can accommodate both small teams and large corporate events. Our team works with you to make sure that the event runs smoothly from start to finish. We will also provide you with all the support needed for a successful celebration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;With our experience and extensive equipment options, Fun Pro UK makes it easy for you to create a celebration that resonates with your team, boosts morale, and fosters lasting loyalty.&lt;/p&gt;
Let us help you host an unforgettable Employee Appreciation Day. &lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Contact us today&lt;/a&gt; and start planning the perfect event for your team.</description></item><item><title>Fun Group Activities for Events in 2025</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-01-21/fun-group-activities-for-events-in-2025</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2025-01-21/fun-group-activities-for-events-in-2025</guid><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Finding fun group activities that everyone will enjoy is challenging. How do you keep a large group of guests (sometimes of different ages) with different interests entertained? No one wants to attend a boring event!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It's true that only a few group activities will satisfy everyone, but finding the right group bonding activities can transform boring gatherings into memorable experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Fun group activities encourage social interaction, build team spirit, and keep everyone entertained in community gatherings, &lt;a href="/pages/office-and-corporate-entertainment"&gt;corporate events&lt;/a&gt;, festivals, and more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Fun Pro UK offers a wide variety of &lt;a href="/pages/party-games-hire"&gt;group party games for hire&lt;/a&gt;, suitable for any occasion. Our collection includes speed reaction games, interactive challenges, classic arcade games, and activities designed to encourage friendly competition and ensure everyone has an enjoyable experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Read on for our best group bonding activities that anyone can enjoy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Fun Group Activities that Bring Everyone Together&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s a look at some of the best group activity options that Fun Pro UK has to offer:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;1. Scalextric Slot Car Racing&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXc7IjSXZtAE7Ar30qdL2kQf6eZUETgkvT2bP37x-HvtuuP7KD6pnV1xGoMz3_ZpTQtr8HpoLjZf_lrp0Ygv6e5MSVdFjoukaQ-vrLDhGTCEZzSezqe3cbDBzgMJggZOBCxaJfsu0w?key=rMF-jzrAipDieRgEKpKJiNU1" width="624" height="312" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/all-products/88/scalextric-slot-car-racing"&gt;Scalextric Slot Car Racing&lt;/a&gt; brings the excitement of high speed motorsport to your event. It delivers a nostalgic yet exhilarating activity for guests of all ages. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Enjoy a classic racing game with detailed tracks and intricately designed miniature cars that race along twisting turns and straights. Perfect for sparking friendly competition and endless entertainment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;2. Racing Car Simulators&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXdTSefBFJus95Vz1k3mQA8UDv6tb_fv0GoWbSh0VZd9LQMiVjWAF8rIGmXMIgcTF5lmdych53hl634h_ubEB6ginFD5sU6VXP8HCKinAxsKT13jcAwunoPgQJvjPU_nX4PqGW4QGA?key=rMF-jzrAipDieRgEKpKJiNU1" width="624" height="312" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If you&amp;rsquo;re looking for an immersive experience that puts your guests in the driver&amp;rsquo;s seat of a realistic racing setup, play with &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;Racing Car Simulators&lt;/a&gt;. Entertain your guests with state of the art graphics, authentic controls, and high-speed action. This way, attendees can enjoy the adrenaline-pumping thrill of professional motorsport without ever leaving the venue. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt; 3. Shuffle Board &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXdk83uLDWRmx02WeUcLH8RYzAX90tFN1fPYaXVuR6qzSrjygyDE6qadXYtjeIbn3kr2XkF60pgcp35A0W-b00xEKkSHvKUIjezK8ZD_3JCRIZQ9ryjlgUWVTmIy25FoX_P4n_gy-g?key=rMF-jzrAipDieRgEKpKJiNU1" width="561" height="438" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The &lt;a href="/category/all-products/87/shuffleboard-hire"&gt;Shuffle Board hire&lt;/a&gt; brings competitive fun to your event! It's a classic game perfect for guests of all ages and skill levels, guaranteeing hours of engaging entertainment. Players slide pucks down the smooth board and score points by landing them in the scoring zones. It's a game of strategy, skill, and precision that&amp;rsquo;s easy to learn but hard to master.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;4. Roll and Bowl&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXenOw6L4QUVJxKolh4Vi2nldv5rHBI6Hrh4t_SICLFmGsej2-uGUhVNDSBo7qisMUnMNft2xiDuLi_4a5foZZNQRwlexHNzv6Ny749IYZ6HgQyMi_5yiFggdHjm7ApvEGPEerNULA?key=rMF-jzrAipDieRgEKpKJiNU1" width="624" height="312" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Bring the race day experience to your next event with the &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/51/roll-and-bowl-game-hire"&gt;Roll and Bowl Derby Game Hire&lt;/a&gt;! It's an interactive, four-player, fairground-style horse racing game.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Simply choose your horse&amp;rsquo;s colour, roll and bowl your ball, and race your way to the finish line. The more points you score by landing your ball in the scoring holes, the faster your horse will race towards victory. But be careful because accuracy is key! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The game features a built-in PA system with full running commentary, vibrant sound effects, and LED lighting to create an atmosphere that feels like the real thing. Draw in a crowd, give away prizes, and keep everyone cheering on their favourite jockeys.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;The Benefits of Fun Group Activities for Your Event&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These activity ideas and huge group games aren't just sources of amusement, they shape the overall experience at a gathering, encourage participation, and create stronger connections between guests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Whether it's a corporate retreat or a community festival, fun group activities up the engagement and creates a positive atmosphere. Here's why incorporating fun group activities during events is a must.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;1. It brings people together&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Ice breakers and &lt;a href="/news/2024-12-05/the-best-ideas-for-team-bonding-activities-in-the-workplace"&gt;bonding activities&lt;/a&gt; bring people of different backgrounds, departments, or communities together. It encourages everyone to interact in a fun and relaxed environment. Competitive yet light hearted games provide common ground, spark conversations, and inspire collaboration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This is particularly effective in corporate settings, where games can dissolve barriers and promote teamwork, as well as in family or community events, where guests may not know each other well.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;2. It can be inclusive entertainment for all ages and abilities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Fun group activities like this cater to diverse audiences as they have varying difficulty levels and game types. Anyone can participate regardless of their age, fitness level, or physical ability. With this level of inclusivity, no guest feels left out. The event must be enjoyable for all.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;3. It creates memorable events&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Events are defined by the memories they create. Unique, engaging, and fun group activities help forge unforgettable moments that encourage laughter, competition, and teamwork. When guests work together to complete a task or go head to head in a challenge, it fosters camaraderie that lingers long after the event ends.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Massive group games and interactive experiences create the kinds of moments that guests will discuss for days or even weeks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What types of group activities does Fun Pro UK offer for hire?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Fun Pro UK offers a diverse selection of interactive games and attractions designed to suit events of all sizes and types. Our catalogue includes competitive team games, &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games"&gt;arcade games&lt;/a&gt;, fun fair games, &lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/21/inflatable-assault-courses"&gt;inflatable challenges&lt;/a&gt;, prize stalls, and more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Our games cater to corporate team building, festivals, community fairs, school events, and private celebrations. If you're unsure which options best suit your event, our team is happy to recommend games based on your audience and goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can I customise the games to match my event theme?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Absolutely! We understand that personalisation adds a unique touch to your event. Many of our &lt;a href="/pages/branded-game-hire"&gt;games can be custom branded&lt;/a&gt; with specific colours, personal designs, themed decorations, and logo placements to align with your event&amp;rsquo;s theme, corporate identity, or branding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt; How far in advance should I book to secure the equipment I want?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;To avoid disappointment, we recommend booking at least 4 to 6 weeks in advance, particularly during peak seasons such as &lt;a href="/pages/summer-entertainment"&gt;summer festivals&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/news/2024-08-23/christmas-events-and-party-ideas"&gt;Christmas parties&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href="/pages/team-building-ideas"&gt;corporate team building&lt;/a&gt; periods.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If your event is approaching quickly, contact Fun Pro UK as soon as possible. We will do our best to accommodate late requests based on availability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Does Fun Pro UK provide setup and staffing for the event?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, we offer full service support to make sure your event runs smoothly. This includes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Delivery, setup, and breakdown of all hired equipment by our experienced team.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;On site staff (upon request) can operate the games, manage queues, explain rules, and oversee safety.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Are the games suitable for both indoor and outdoor events?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, our equipment is designed for flexible use in both indoor and outdoor environments. We can recommend specific games based on your venue&amp;rsquo;s size and surface type. We also consider weather conditions and provide outdoor friendly, durable setups or rain covers where necessary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Is there a minimum or maximum hire period?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Our hire periods vary between &lt;a href="/"&gt;game hires&lt;/a&gt;. They are also flexible to accommodate various event schedules. If you require the equipment for an extended period, just let us know. We&amp;rsquo;re happy to customise the hire duration based on your needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can you accommodate last minute changes or additional requests?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If your guest list grows, or you decide to add more activities, we will do our best to adjust bookings or provide extra equipment. While availability may vary, we encourage you to contact us with any last minute changes, and we&amp;rsquo;ll help you find a solution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do I ensure the equipment is delivered safely and on time?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Our logistics team manages safe, punctual delivery to make sure everything arrives well in advance of your event. We coordinate directly with your venue or event planners to ensure smooth access and timely setup.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;All equipment is thoroughly inspected and sanitised before delivery. And on the day of the event, our team will handle installation and safety checks to guarantee everything is secure and ready for use.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Book Your Fun Group Activities with Fun Pro UK&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You can elevate your next event! Booking with Fun Pro UK is simple, and our team is dedicated to making sure your experience is stress free, from setup to takedown.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We invite you to explore our full range of activities and discover our corporate entertainment options. &lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Contact us today&lt;/a&gt; to ensure you get the best selection for your event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Exhibition Stand Ideas: 8 Ways to Attract Attention and Boost Engagement</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-12-17/exhibition-stand-ideas-8-ways-to-attract-attention-and-boost-engagement</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-12-17/exhibition-stand-ideas-8-ways-to-attract-attention-and-boost-engagement</guid><pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Have you ever visited an exhibition stand? If yes, think about what attracted you to the stand. Was it the products or services? Was it the level of engagement and entertainment they offered? Was it the unique design?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Whatever your answer may be, it all boils down to an unforgettable experience at that particular exhibition stand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;A good exhibition stand design is more than just a physical space; it&amp;rsquo;s the perfect stage for your brand to captivate, connect, and convert. Strategic planning of your exhibition stand effectively communicates your brand identity on top of creating meaningful engagement with your audience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;In a conference or trade show where there's so much competition around, you only have a couple of seconds to snag your target audience's attention and convert them into paying customers and lasting clientele.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Needless to say, it's a race to see who wins over the audience first.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;In this guide, we&amp;rsquo;ll help bring your vision to life while making your stand the highlight of any event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;8 Exhibition Stand Ideas That Will Leave an Impression&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Engaging and inviting attractions are sure to bring more potential leads to your stand. Attendees at expos and business conferences like to get involved and interact with something, and the more engaging it is, the more people will remember you and your brand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;1. Host Live Demos&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Live demonstrations showcase your products or services in action. Stands with live demos get more footfalls than stands that just have products lined up on the shelves. Live demos can give all attendees a nice break from walking around and stopping from one stand to the next. The right host for your live demo can inject some enthusiasm and interest in your audience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;A dynamic and interactive experience captivates attendees and clearly communicates the value of what your business offers. For example, if you&amp;rsquo;re a tech company, you can demonstrate the latest features of a particular software, and a food brand can prepare and offer tastings onsite.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Here are some additional tips to consider:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Schedule demos at regular intervals to keep your booth buzzing with activity.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Incorporate audience participation to make the demo more engaging.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Use visual aids, like screens or printed materials, to complement the live demonstrations.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;2. Create a Lounge or Caf&amp;eacute; Space&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;During a business event, it gets tiring to walk from one exhibition stand to the next and look at everything they have to offer. So having a lounge space is definitely a great way to attract customers and gather potential leads for your business by requiring an email address or contact details as the price of admission.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Comfortable seating and a relaxed atmosphere encourages visitors to linger. On top of getting their contact details, it also gives you more time to connect with them. You can also add branded cushions, tables, or coffee cups to subtly reinforce your brand identity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Keep the space tidy and professional to maintain a polished image, set up charging stations, offer free wifi, and provide branded takeaway items, such as reusable water bottles or coffee cups, as souvenirs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;3. Provide Free Refreshments&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Coming off of the idea of creating a lounge space, free refreshments, such as bottled water, bags of popcorn, protein bars, and canned drinks, can make your booth a hotspot. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Offering complimentary snacks or drinks can make your booth a hotspot. It&amp;rsquo;s a simple yet effective way to attract foot traffic and create positive associations with your brand. Branded cups, napkins, or bottles can also add an extra touch of professionalism.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Be sure to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Choose refreshments that are easy to serve and consume.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Be mindful of dietary restrictions and offer a variety of options.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Position refreshments strategically in your expo stand design to encourage exploration.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;4. Offer Product Samples&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Giving away free samples is a classic. It&amp;rsquo;s a tried and true method to drum up intrigue in audiences and it&amp;rsquo;s also potentially risk free for them. Sampling is a very effective marketing tactic to attract visitors to your stands.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;After all, who doesn&amp;rsquo;t love trying out products firsthand?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Make sure the samples align with your target audience and highlight your key offerings. You can also give people takeaway bags or small containers with your logo to keep your brand top of mind.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;And before visitors leave the stand, encourage attendees to share their feedback so that you can gather valuable insights for your team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;5. Create a Product Wall&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Product walls combine branding, decorating, and innovative hustling in one feature. A visually striking product wall serves as both a display and a conversation starter. You can arrange your products in a creative, eye catching way to make them irresistible to passersby.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;However, if you&amp;rsquo;re a service based business, consider using visuals, such as infographics or testimonials, to communicate your offerings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Use clever lighting to highlight specific features or products, use QR codes to provide additional information, and regularly refresh the wall to keep the wall looking pristine and relevant.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;6. Interactive Game Entertainment&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If there&amp;rsquo;s one trick that draws crowds every single time and sparks excitement at the same time, it&amp;rsquo;s &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;An interactive exhibition and the right games can create a lively atmosphere and give attendees a reason to stay longer at your stand. Anything from a simple challenge or a high tech setup can provide fun and memorable interactions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Some interactive game hires to consider include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/branded-exhibition-games/64/mega-wire-branded-game-hire-stand-alone"&gt;Mega Wire&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire/9/giant-buzz-wire"&gt;Buzz Wire&lt;/a&gt; tests attendees&amp;rsquo; precision and patience. It challenges players by requiring a steady hand to navigate a wire loop without touching it.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/batak/43/batak-pro"&gt;Batak Pro&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="/category/batak/61/batak-lite"&gt;Batak Lite&lt;/a&gt; are perfect for competitive visitors. Batak has multiple levels that are suitable for players of all skill levels. They're reflex games that test players' reaction times.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="https://funprouk.co.uk/category/arcade-games/63/danger-zone-strike-a-light-game-hire"&gt;Strike A Light&lt;/a&gt; adds a fast paced, thrilling element to your stand design. It&amp;rsquo;s a reaction based game that sees how fast you can hit the button as they light up.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/67/whack-a-mole-game-hire"&gt;Whack A Mole&lt;/a&gt; is a nostalgic and engaging crowd favourite. You can set up a friendly competition to see who can hit the most moles the fastest.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/47/prize-crane-arcade-grabber"&gt;Prize Claw Grabbing Machines&lt;/a&gt; offer exciting rewards and are great crowd pleasers. Let attendees try their luck at grabbing branded prizes from the machine. It's a fun and interactive way to engage with potential customers.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/grab-a-grand/3/cash-grabber-machine-hire"&gt;Cash Grabbers&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="/category/grab-a-grand/36/ballnado-grabber"&gt;Ballnado Grabbers&lt;/a&gt; literally create a whirlwind of fun. It's a game that challenges players to grab as much as possible while inside a wind vortex.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/prize-games/49/prize-wheel"&gt;Prize Wheels&lt;/a&gt; are a great option for exhibitions and trade shows. Players can spin the wheel to win prizes or discounts on your products or services. Prize wheel can also be customised to fit your specific requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;7. Deliver a VR/AR Experience&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Virtual reality (VR) and augmented reality (AR) technologies are the ultimate head turners at exhibitions. You can offer a virtual tour of your facilities or an augmented look at your product lineup.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These technologies create a buzz and can also develop a sense of curiosity among the attendees. It can help you spread your brand message in a fun and exciting way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Some additional tips to consider:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Create an accessible and user friendly experience for all attendees.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Keep your VR/AR setup aligned with your brand message and goals.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Use a staff member to guide participants and explain the technology.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;8. Host a Photo Booth&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Who doesn't want a memorable photo of any event? &lt;a href="/category/company-award-ceremonies/11/classic-photo-booths"&gt;Photo booths&lt;/a&gt; can be customised to have branded backdrops and decor. You can also put your business' name on photo booth printouts and provide props and accessories that represent your brand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It engages attendees, &lt;a href="/news/2024-02-25/elevate-your-brand"&gt;spreads brand awareness&lt;/a&gt;, and offers digital sharing options that amplify your reach beyond the exhibition floor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Advantages of an Engaging Exhibition Stand Design&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Designing an exhibition that&amp;rsquo;s impactful also offers numerous benefits like:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Increased foot traffic&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Better brand recognition&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Stronger customer relationships&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Higher ROI&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do I attract customers to my stall?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Focus on eye catching visuals and other interactive activities. Incorporate vibrant colours, clear signage, and displays that tell your brand story. Be welcoming, knowledgeable, and ready to initiate conversations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do you make an exhibition layout?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Plan a layout that maximises space and incorporates interactive zones. The layout must also align with your branding. Consider these additional tips to help your exhibition stand stick out:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Consider the flow of foot traffic and accessibility for all attendees.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Place key attractions like interactive games or live demos at high visibility points.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Use lighting, partitions, and creative structures to differentiate areas.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do I choose an exhibition stand?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider your budget, goals, and audience when thinking of expo stand ideas and exhibition stand games. Prioritise functionality, and make sure the design accommodates your planned activities. It's worth working with experienced designers and expert event planners like &lt;a href="/"&gt;Fun Pro&lt;/a&gt; to balance creativity and practicality.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do I set up a small exhibition?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Focus on impactful visuals, strategic planning, and targeted activities. Do the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Use banners, backdrops, and props that highlight your key messages.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Create a cohesive theme.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Keep your setup clean and uncluttered.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Plan the exhibition stand design in advance to make sure all equipment, signage, and promotional materials are in place.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Final Thoughts: Explore Unique Exhibition Ideas&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;To create a unique exhibition stand design, you need the right tools to captivate, connect, and convert. If you&amp;rsquo;re unsure of how to go about it, Fun Pro can take the stress out of designing an engaging exhibition stand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We have a range of &lt;a href="/category/branded-exhibition-games"&gt;interactive games and custom branding options&lt;/a&gt; that will help your stand attract attention in any venue.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Trade Show Marketing Ideas That Will Make You Stand Out</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-12-16/trade-show-marketing-ideas-that-will-make-you-stand-out</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-12-16/trade-show-marketing-ideas-that-will-make-you-stand-out</guid><pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Trade shows draw hundreds of people to a single event centre every year. It brings businesses in the same industry together, and it's the perfect place for your brand to show off its products and services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;To capitalise on this opportunity, you need to develop a trade show marketing strategy that amplifies your brand's visibility, generates quality leads, and creates memorable impressions. And when trade show and event marketing is done right, it can give your business a big boost.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Let's explore some trade show marketing ideas that will help make this venture a success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Pre Trade Show Marketing Ideas That Build Excitement&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;One of the keys to any successful event is to build anticipation before it happens. Pre-show marketing drives booth traffic and captures attendees' attention. Marketing strategy for trade shows will help you make a strong first impression.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Announce Your Attendance Early&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Promote your participation in the trade show weeks or months in advance. Announce your participation through various channels. Whether it&amp;rsquo;s through your website, social media, email newsletters, and even press releases, there is no shortage of ways to get the word of your participation out there.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Create a dedicated landing page or blog post and include key event details like your booth number, event schedule, and highlights of what visitors can expect.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s also a good idea to give attendees a compelling reason to stop by. Sweeten the deal. Offer exclusive product launches, live demonstrations, or give your attendees the opportunity to meet with experts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You can also use countdown timers on your website or social posts to build urgency as the event date approaches.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Drum Up Interest with Email Campaigns&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;As prevalent as social media is, nothing still beats email when it comes to promoting information. Email campaigns are a direct way to communicate with your target audience and spark interest in your booth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Create a series of emails leading up to the event. Each email must have a unique focus. For instance:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Email 1 would be an announcement of your attendance. This serves as the teaser of what to expect.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Email 2 could be a preview of featured products, services, or activities. You can also show off interactive games that would be at your trade show stand or new product releases.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Email 3 could be an invitation to book one-on-one meetings or reserve spots for exclusive presentations during the trade show.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Include clear CTAs and links to pre-register for events, sign up for contests, or download resources. For extra engagement, segment your list to tailor messages to specific audience interests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Partner with Influencers or Industry Leaders&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Working with industry influencers can boost your trade show stand&amp;rsquo;s visibility. Reach out to bloggers, vloggers, or thought leaders, who align with your brand and appeal to the trade show audience. Engage them to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Promote your booth on their platforms through posts, stories, or live streams.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Participate in panels, Q&amp;amp;A sessions, or product demonstrations at your booth.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Create co branded content, like a webinar or guide, to distribute pre show and during the event.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Leverage Social Media Advertising&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When you&amp;rsquo;re doing social media advertising, create a mix of organic posts and paid ads to engage potential attendees. Some ideas could include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Using carousel ads to show off multiple products or activities at your booth.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Sharing behind the scenes content, such as booth setups or product sneak peeks.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Run video ads that highlight what makes your booth unique and impossible to miss. The &amp;lsquo;it&amp;rsquo; factor could be a prize draw, unique demos, free consultations, or a chance to win rare product giveaways.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Don&amp;rsquo;t forget to use event hashtags and tag the trade show&amp;rsquo;s official accounts to expand visibility.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Offer Pre-show Incentives&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Entice attendees with exclusive incentives they can redeem at your booth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You can promote limited edition items or branded merchandise for the first visitors to your stand, offer special deals that are only redeemable at the trade show to encourage foot traffic, or launch a social media competition where winners can collect their prizes at your booth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These are examples of great methods to attract attention and boost foot traffic. You can also offer exclusive content. Share free downloadable resources that attendees can access by visiting your stand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Communicate these incentives clearly in your marketing materials. Up their value and make sure they align with your audience&amp;rsquo;s interests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Trade Show Stand Ideas to Keep Visitors Engaged During the Event&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We've established that trade shows are all about attracting and converting new, potential customers. The more attendees you can attract to your exhibit, the more leads you can follow up with when the trade show is over.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Here are some successful trade show marketing strategies on the day of the event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;1. Invest in Eye-catching Branding&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Attendees should be able to identify who you are immediately. Your booth design should align with your brand&amp;rsquo;s identity. Make sure to use consistent colours, logos, and other visuals that show off your company&amp;rsquo;s personality.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You can also make use of high-quality banners and digital displays to make your stand visually striking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;2. Hire Interactive Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The last thing you want are bored attendees. It&amp;rsquo;s important to keep everyone engaged and entertained with interactive games that encourage participation. They create a lively atmosphere around your stand, plus it makes your brand so much more memorable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Popular &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; at trade shows include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Racing Car Simulators&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Organise competitive yet fun racing games between your guests. See who wins the race or who has the fastest lap. Grab the attention of attendees with an immersive virtual race while showing off a dynamic booth environment.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/branded-exhibition-games/64/mega-wire-branded-game-hire-stand-alone"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mega Wire&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt; or &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire/9/giant-buzz-wire"&gt;Giant Buzz Wire&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: Simple yet challenging. A test of precision and skill. It's a great conversation starter that ignites players' competitive nature by encouraging them to try again and again. Set up a fun competition and offer up prizes to anyone who can successfully guide the handheld loop along a giant wire without touching it.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/47/prize-crane-arcade-grabber"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prize Crane Machines&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: These machines have nostalgic charm. Fill the box with branded prizes and let attendees leave your booth with a tangible reminder of your brand.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/67/whack-a-mole-game-hire"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Whack A Mole&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: A fast-paced classic arcade game that is as highly interactive as it is physically engaging. It's one of those games that are perfect for breaking the ice and injecting some energy into your trade show stand.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/batak/43/batak-pro"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Batak Pro&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt; or &lt;a href="/category/batak/61/batak-lite"&gt;Batak Lite&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: The visually engaging setup and the quick rounds of this game keep attendees entertained and curious to try it for themselves. The goal is to score as many hits as possible within a set time. It's a fun game that tests speed, agility, and reflexes.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;&lt;a href="/category/prize-games/49/prize-wheel"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prize Wheels&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Invite visitors to spin the wheel and see what rewards they will get. It's simple, it draws a crowd, and it lets brands showcase giveaways creatively while engaging everyone in a lively manner.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Aside from interactive games, you can also add other entertaining elements that will make your booth memorable. You can try adding live music or performances or hiring brand ambassadors and mascots.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;3. Use Creative Displays to Highlight Products and Services&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Creativity is integral to trade show marketing. How you present your products and services is what will set them apart.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;And thanks to today&amp;rsquo;s technology, there is no shortage of creative trade show marketing ideas. Use touchscreens, lightbox displays, rotating platforms, a unique stand design, a well-designed product wall, or dynamic lighting effects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;To help your products or services stand out, you can use coloured LED lights, spotlights, or motion-activated lighting to draw attention and create a modern, inviting atmosphere.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;4. Host Live Demonstrations, Mini Workshops, or Q&amp;amp;A Sessions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;A live demonstration of how your products or how your services work are one of the best ways to captivate an audience. It lets attendees see the value of your offerings firsthand and ask questions in real-time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You can also educate your audience through short, interactive sessions. These sessions can focus on industry trends, how-to guides, or innovative uses of your products. Positioning yourself as an expert builds trust and builds long-term connections.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Let visitors try your products for themselves. Interactive displays or sample stations engage attendees directly and it creates a more memorable experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;5. Include Refreshment Stations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Depending on the size of the event, visitors are likely going to spend a lot of time walking around a trade show.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s a great idea to offer free refreshments. Who doesn&amp;rsquo;t love a coffee, water, or snack break? Refreshments give visitors a reason to linger longer at your stand. It&amp;rsquo;s a simple yet effective way to attract foot traffic.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Is a trade show a sales promotion?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;They can be. &lt;a href="/news/2019-03-01/the-benefits-of-exhibiting-at-trade-shows-and-exhibitions"&gt;Trade shows&lt;/a&gt; are an excellent sales promotion tool. They give your business a chance to showcase products, connect with potential customers, and generate leads in a targeted environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What characteristics of a trade show booth are likely to attract customers?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;A successful trade show stand is visually appealing, interactive, and inviting. Key elements include creative designs, engaging activities, knowledgeable staff, and clear messaging.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Are there budget-friendly trade show marketing ideas?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Absolutely! Social media promotions, branded giveaways, and simple yet impactful booth designs are cost-effective strategies. &lt;a href="/category/branded-exhibition-games"&gt;Branded interactive games&lt;/a&gt; like the &lt;a href="/category/branded-exhibition-games/64/mega-wire-branded-game-hire-stand-alone"&gt;Mega Wire&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/47/prize-crane-arcade-grabber"&gt;Prize Crane&lt;/a&gt;, or &lt;a href="/category/prize-games/49/prize-wheel"&gt;Prize Wheels&lt;/a&gt; are also affordable options.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How can trade show marketing improve lead generation?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Trade show marketing attracts a targeted audience. It opens up opportunities to engage with potential clients, collect contact information, and build meaningful connections. Interactive activities and live demos further enhance lead generation by drawing in interested attendees.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Final Thoughts: From Vision to Execution&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Creating a successful trade show experience requires a combination of strategic planning and creative execution. At Fun Pro, we specialise in providing interactive games, customisable rentals, and onsite support to make your stand a success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Let us help you create a trade show presence that drives engagement, amplifies your brand, and leaves a lasting impression.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>3 Reasons Why Games are the Key to Successful Corporate Events</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-12-11/3-reasons-why-games-are-the-key-to-successful-corporate-events</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-12-11/3-reasons-why-games-are-the-key-to-successful-corporate-events</guid><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Back in the day, corporate events were known for being uneventful; just a room with hosts, speakers, and uninterested listeners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;But in recent years, corporate events are no longer just a hotbed for information exchange or networking; it&amp;rsquo;s also a time for fostering client and employee engagement, collaboration, and team building.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The ideal corporate event should be productive, engaging, and fun.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;And this is where game hires come in.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Game hires have emerged as a popular way to address the need to be fun during a corporate event. As a business owner, building meaningful connections with employees and clientele alike is important. And meaningful connections grow from positive interactions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You wouldn&amp;rsquo;t want to bore your event attendees, would you?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This article will explore some reasons why games for corporate events are a must for your next company gathering.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;The Appeal of Games for Corporate Events&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;From &lt;a href="/category/prize-games/49/prize-wheel"&gt;prize wheels&lt;/a&gt; to air hockey tables and &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;racing car simulators&lt;/a&gt;, it&amp;rsquo;s clear that games are quite popular at any type of event, and it&amp;rsquo;s easy to see why. Games are appealing to adults just as they are to children.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Plus, who doesn&amp;rsquo;t love a bit of nostalgic joy that playing games can spark?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Here are the reasons why &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games"&gt;hiring arcade games&lt;/a&gt;, simulator games, interactive games, etc. for your next event is a great idea.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;1. Games encourage team building and collaboration&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Team building events are corporate events that are meant to bring colleagues together and have them work towards a common goal. The main purpose, of course, is to build a strong team by forming bonds and connections.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;And the good news is that there are plenty of games that encourage collaboration, camaraderie, and teamwork. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Our interactive entertainment options bring a fun and relaxed twist to corporate events. Popular activities like Batak Pro, &lt;a href="/category/all-products/88/scalextric-slot-car-racing"&gt;Scalextric Slot Car Racing&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href="/category/branded-exhibition-games/64/mega-wire-branded-game-hire-stand-alone"&gt;Mega Wire&lt;/a&gt; are just a few examples of games that create friendly competition. There&amp;rsquo;s nothing quite like the sound of each team cheering on their players as they work together to reach high scores and celebrate victories.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These activities create natural opportunities for colleagues to step outside their usual workplace dynamics and connect on a different level. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When teams engage in friendly competition, they naturally strengthen their communication, develop trust, and discover new ways to collaborate - skills that transfer seamlessly back to the workplace.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;2. Games bring stress relief during events&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;In corporate events like trade shows and expos where long presentations can sometimes lead to information overload and stress, games are the much-needed break everyone needs. They provide a quick mental reset.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You don&amp;rsquo;t want a room or a venue full of disinterested, bored, or zoned-out attendees. Everyone deserves to have a fun and relaxing time. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The importance of a light-hearted atmosphere is never more important than in a tradeshow or an expo. Hiring games for the event mixes business with enjoyment and it benefits everyone.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It keeps your guests from being bored, and it creates opportunities for positive engagement with potential business partners and clientele. Positive engagement makes your event and your brand memorable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;3. Games create lasting memories for all attendees&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;One of the main reasons why games are the popular entertainment choice for event planners and companies is their ability to create memorable experiences. Plus, people always want unique outside-of-the-box experiences, and the right games for corporate events can certainly do that.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/office-and-corporate-entertainment"&gt;Hired games for corporate events&lt;/a&gt; are more than just diversions. They&amp;rsquo;re a great way to get people excited and leave lasting positive impressions on event attendees.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Guests can walk away from the event with the thrill of winning at shuffleboard, the skill it took to conquer the Giant Buzz Wire, the pure fun of playing on the &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/39/dance-machine"&gt;Dance Machine&lt;/a&gt;, or the Race Car Simulators they enjoyed as kids.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The fun and laughter shared over these activities create memories that last well beyond the event itself. These become great conversation starters back at the office, helping build stronger relationships between colleagues.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These shared experiences bring your team closer together while creating real connections between your brand and clients - making your corporate event one to remember.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What types of games are available for corporate events?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Fun Pro has different types of games for corporate events. You can invite your guests to play a game of &lt;a href="/category/batak/43/batak-pro"&gt;Batak Pro&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="/category/batak/61/batak-lite"&gt;Batak Lite&lt;/a&gt;, set up competitive team plays with the &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/6/electronic-basket-ball-hire"&gt;electronic basketball hire&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/60/air-hockey-table-hire"&gt;air hockey table&lt;/a&gt;, or see who can grab the most prizes in the Ballnado Grabber. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can the games be customised for our company&amp;rsquo;s event theme?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, they can be customised to suit the event! Our team can help you enhance each game with custom graphics, including your company colours and logos. We want to make sure that your brand stays in people's minds long after the event is over.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Can the games be used both indoors and outdoors?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes, our games can be used both indoors and outdoors. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Games like &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/48/high-striker"&gt;High Striker&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire/9/giant-buzz-wire"&gt;Giant Buzz Wire&lt;/a&gt; can be set up outdoors to create that exciting, carnival-like atmosphere in open spaces. Meanwhile, retro arcade machines and race car simulators are perfect if you want to create immersive game zones in conference halls, exhibition centres, or indoor team building venues.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How far in advance should we book games for corporate events?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;We would recommend booking as early as possible to ensure availability. Booking a few weeks in advance should be good. Reach out to Fun Pro if you have last-minute enquiries, and we'll see what we can do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Final Thoughts&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Games for corporate events create a better attendee experience. It promotes engagement and fosters long-lasting bonds.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;As experts in &lt;a href="/"&gt;game hires for events&lt;/a&gt; and creating fun experiences ourselves, Fun Pro is passionate about helping you deliver memorable moments that thrill and engage your attendees. Our team can help you select the perfect games for your company event, and even assist you in customising hired games to suit your event theme or your brand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If you&amp;rsquo;re ready to take your event to the next level, talk to us and our team will help you plan an event and choose games that your guests will remember.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>The Best Ideas For Team Bonding Activities In The Workplace</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-12-05/the-best-ideas-for-team-bonding-activities-in-the-workplace</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-12-05/the-best-ideas-for-team-bonding-activities-in-the-workplace</guid><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When you think about how stressful daily work can get, it's not difficult to understand why a team bonding activity is more essential than ever in the modern workplace.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Team bonding activities build camaraderie, boost employee morale, and encourage person-to-person interactions among colleagues.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;But you might wonder, is there a difference between a &lt;a href="/news/2019-02-15/tips-for-running-a-successful-team-building-day"&gt;team building event&lt;/a&gt; and a team bonding activity?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Team building activities focus on developing skills like problem-solving and communication through structured exercises, while team bonding is all about creating genuine connections in a relaxed environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Where team building is skill-focused and often tied to achieving workplace goals, team bonding prioritises relationships and shared experiences that create a more enjoyable workplace. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;What do team bonding activities do?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Helps employees get to know each other better.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Build trust and encourage a sense of belonging in the team.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Improve soft skills such as empathy, leadership, and creativity.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Team bonding activities help strengthen employee connections and even reduce turnover rates. It lays the emotional foundation that makes teamwork thrive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;The Benefits of Team Bonding Activities for Work&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Having team bonding activities in your workplace has many advantages that go beyond fun and games. Activities like this help build stronger relationships among team members and improve the overall work culture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Better communication and collaboration. Team bonding activities open communication and encourage collaboration. When colleagues know each other better, they&amp;rsquo;re more likely to be comfortable sharing ideas with each other and work cohesively.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Stress reduction. Company team bonding activities provide a welcome break from routine. In the midst of a usually monotonous nine to five, it helps employees recharge and reduce stress levels. This contributes to a healthier, more motivated workforce.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Boosted morale and motivation. Games create shared experiences and fun yet casual challenges create excitement and boost morale. This leads to stronger motivation and better job satisfaction.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Improved productivity. A connected team is a more productive team. Stronger interpersonal relationships often translate into smoother workflows and fewer misunderstandings.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Creates a positive work environment. Team bonding cultivates a friendly and supportive workplace culture. It can help make everyone feel valued and appreciated.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Best Team Bonding Activities for Different Settings&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Corporate team bonding activities include everything from weekly staff lunches, to company movie nights, a company trip, scheduled coffee breaks, and more. Furthermore, team bonding activities can be tailored to suit various settings, group sizes, and workplace dynamics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;But aside from the relaxing activities that we just mentioned, team bonding can also be as simple as playing games together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Whether you're planning to have outdoor or indoor team bonding activities, there are plenty of game options to consider.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;1. Table Football&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfjTsuxT3rXsPuNFUrvpxsdnmr1SrSqrEe_82r0RLP5mDLOsIKQBrLxcBGfVU6_-4Av0lfmMddaUR0uoIslrwI9IWN9_wkk7h9mVsbzsHtJWcLOnxk0bGciFbHMO1FuFYPQz6GhSg?key=_SWbeNN363WhiAq53iB4LARQ" width="561" height="419" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The classic and perfect way to have in-office fun. It can transform any ordinary workday into moments of fun and friendly rivalry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Table football is a fast-paced game that encourages friendly competition and teamwork, plus it&amp;rsquo;s also a good game to have in the office. When your employees want a break from work, they can step away from their desks and head over to the &lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/27/football-tables"&gt;table football game&lt;/a&gt; to get their dose of fun.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Players can team up or go head-to-head. It takes strategic skill, precision,l and fast reaction times to manoeuvre the handles and score goals. But aside from its entertainment value, table football can also help everyone practise good communication and fast reflexes; not to mention, it builds camaraderie between colleagues.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Most table footballs come in a compact size. It can be an excellent addition to your office break rooms. Every player also gets a chance to showcase their skills and cheer each other on.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;2. Retro Arcade Machines&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfbS3EJ3xKtjcek9KCJNVo4TV1h4O2pScv2rGL0xYAWJRo9WBAB5zPrfOkQW7aEHeP-NZJuW0rHBjRzZASTFE-ZKYwEdYVesdtwxE9U5ldFfpil16AcJycQ8O6mHBx8LFo6KL8x?key=_SWbeNN363WhiAq53iB4LARQ" width="624" height="312" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;One of the best team bonding activities for work are &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/4/retro-arcade-games"&gt;retro arcade machines&lt;/a&gt;. These classic arcade games bring nostalgia into the workplace. It&amp;rsquo;s great for quick breaks or casual tournaments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Lots of retro arcade machines come with classic games from the golden era of gaming. We&amp;rsquo;re talking Space Invaders, Pac-Man, Street Fighter - all the good old games.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These machines are perfect for sparking excitement and creating a relaxed, fun atmosphere. Plus, the variety of games available means there&amp;rsquo;s something for everyone. This way, the team can bond over shared childhood memories while indulging in some lighthearted competition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Retro arcade machines are a great way to bring timeless fun into your workplace and it&amp;rsquo;s great to see everyone smile.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;3. Dance Machine&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXe4vhc3xWPJwLX17Fke-4r_KYfLqfzvZzX8ZjyHTfiDuX-738V6sPZJzwQQW3q2OO1NHD62Q7kNnsKy6-FRVxTF94P0nsXFRLCrwWg69-Vk3NZg2GHJf5Hs_WQGrWQZABjXGGPOEQ?key=_SWbeNN363WhiAq53iB4LARQ" width="592" height="439" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Unless your office operates under a no-sitting rule, it&amp;rsquo;s always a good idea to get everyone up and moving once in a while. Encourage movement and laughter with a dance-off!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/39/dance-machine"&gt;dance machine&lt;/a&gt; is an excellent icebreaker for both large and small teams. It&amp;rsquo;s an open invitation for everyone to step on the light-up buttons and compete in rhythm-based challenges. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;There are a lot of pulsating beats to choose from and colourful graphics to go along with it. Your team can do lighthearted showdowns or do collaborative dance-offs. The dance machine is one of those games that just bring energy and excitement to any event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Just make sure the office has enough space to accommodate this machine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;4. Racing Car Simulators&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfrHYPaaZW73uyRx9hnCt42-1_a8Ose7Ef3UQYBguPzPX_uMyb3YJoNkBxS4Nj8hgSAQr21MnfLm92XQStR8YL-jOhLjV2Y3vCbaJxu0stUo38lQAR15kOJsSr65d_JZ4lUrOieIQ?key=_SWbeNN363WhiAq53iB4LARQ" width="624" height="299" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If your team prefers high-energy games, &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;racing car simulators&lt;/a&gt; let your team channel their inner speed demons. These high-tech setups immerse players in thrilling virtual races, complete with realistic graphics and sound effects. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Colleagues can compete for the fastest lap time, cheer each other on, and enjoy a dose of healthy competition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Racing car simulators add an electrifying touch for the players. It&amp;rsquo;s perfect as in-office entertainment or at large-scale corporate gatherings. Wherever you put them, they&amp;rsquo;re crowd-pleasers that create excitement and fun.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;5. Giant Jenga&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXcRo90ZIqV5TnF1h8PEnDKktPYpEJVJFD54MaPKNrCJ5wwf4JAbDrmLS45ksAS9vpWW3-G-vPWT9VzQAmg04k_fpGFxHxlIXOKfMo31E-tAeuvtcp0uhlYJU4RTjuF3mbzl8hiB?key=_SWbeNN363WhiAq53iB4LARQ" width="624" height="348" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Regular jenga is a crowd favourite, so can you imagine the fun and excitement around a giant jenga? &lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/44/giant-jenga-hire"&gt;Giant Jenga&lt;/a&gt; just takes the classic block-stacking game to a whole new level.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This oversized version challenges players to carefully remove and balance blocks without toppling the tower. It&amp;rsquo;s a crowd favourite game that requires strategic thinking, steady hands, and teamwork. It&amp;rsquo;s one of the best games to play during break time, plus it&amp;rsquo;s great for fostering collaboration too.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s an easy game to play and set up. Plus, watching the tower wobble and fall always gets a laugh out of everyone. It&amp;rsquo;s an attention-grabbing and memorable addition to any workplace or event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;6. Giant Connect 4&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXcUcp02wwoyfe-1xFQ_y8TGDSVMF1giGxaRDiP81qseCuC8S5H76Yjs8kLTuNRLXRQo_LRB5NRyGz-gNOhY_YcNZ3ecVaveGm5skmItUA2YGFuaw0t0Xmx9G3Dfj8EnsELwaywSlg?key=_SWbeNN363WhiAq53iB4LARQ" width="546" height="544" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Take playing board games like chess and checkers to the next level! What&amp;rsquo;s better than sitting down to a four-sided board and testing the limits of your strategic thinking? A life-sized one of course! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Bring out the playful side of your team through a &lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/45/giant-connect-4-game-hire"&gt;Giant Connect 4&lt;/a&gt;. This larger-than-life version of the classic game encourages everyone to think strategically and make quick decisions. Players compete to align four discs in a row while blocking their opponent&amp;rsquo;s moves.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Giant Connect 4 is a simple yet entertaining way to spark friendly competition and strengthen team bonds.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;7. Prize Crane Arcade Grabber&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfBsLJFjRFEifApM4-CR__pWAJVQ-BAAu_qFzmRiulfgRUpTe-cBP1QZ0xwz6uPzm6J1z4c61hSqC4rIEzl77N9fHAXPuf86ZkS-4A2sW8NeoIvLJhbn7Fv0DN1In2hJjwzP5gTGQ?key=_SWbeNN363WhiAq53iB4LARQ" width="624" height="312" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/47/prize-crane-arcade-grabber"&gt;Prize Crane Arcade Grabber&lt;/a&gt; adds a touch of nostalgia and excitement in the office. This classic arcade game lets team members test their precision and patience as they try to snag prizes using the grabber claw.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s a &lt;a href="/news/2024-05-03/the-secret-to-team-building-interactive-games"&gt;fun, interactive way to engage employees&lt;/a&gt; and create lighthearted moments. You can fill the machine with small prizes, branded goodies, or even snacks. Drop a few intriguing prizes into the box and let your team test their skill at picking up objects with the mechanical claw arm. Anything they can successfully take is theirs of course.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;8. Batak Pro and Batak Lite&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfV0mCL-sEvM0Y3ZR_gW8lnkc2Fqoncr8aZeV35EO-xTag4IzLzBfYUEYEGDSlL8cbrnkKMzqe8Be2_kdq7sZpjwmRwkZTjo7zh1jNjSh6OatCCnpfUnCh71NpRIwNlmvIe7PIesw?key=_SWbeNN363WhiAq53iB4LARQ" width="624" height="465" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The &lt;a href="/category/batak/61/batak-lite"&gt;Batak Lite&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="/category/batak/43/batak-pro"&gt;Batak Pro&lt;/a&gt; is the perfect game if you want to see how fast your own reaction speed or agility is. Reaction games like these challenge players to hit randomly lit targets as quickly as possible, encouraging focus and quick reflexes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;These are one of the best games for fostering friendly competition. It's highly engaging and adaptable for all group sizes. Batak Lite and Pro bring out the best in everyone&amp;rsquo;s competitive spirit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;9. Whack A Mole&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXcfSNQsFUxPicYJxBMMwLoHuVPOChMbEvFxcFxuNYdaUzqdgW3GoTZ_zw3-ru5HCii_2ku9-PWEJOrYpPiciOn9BmUjqgULVyN3edVxFuuBfB1ZLDhAAR02Ip_dlGCEq-Mm6EfcgQ?key=_SWbeNN363WhiAq53iB4LARQ" width="624" height="677" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;The best thing about &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/67/whack-a-mole-game-hire"&gt;Whack A Mole&lt;/a&gt; is that it brings laughter and energy to the workplace and to any gathering! This beloved classic arcade-style game is a hit for all ages. Put together a game to see which one of you or your colleagues can hit as many moles as possible as the moles pop up from their holes. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;It's fast-paced and entertaining - perfect for sharpening reflexes and encouraging friendly competition between everyone. Whack A Mole is an excellent choice for getting everyone involved. The simple gameplay makes it accessible for every team member and it lets everyone have a blast.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How can I encourage all employees to participate in team bonding activities?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Choose activities that appeal to different interests and personalities. Emphasise inclusivity and highlight the fun aspects to encourage participation. Before opting for &lt;a href="/"&gt;game hires&lt;/a&gt; or deciding on a team bonding activity, ask your team what games they&amp;rsquo;d like to play in the office or what they want to do with their colleagues outside of office hours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What are some team bonding ideas for remote or hybrid teams?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Virtual trivia, online escape rooms, or remote-friendly versions of games like charades work well for remote teams. Hybrid teams can always enjoy a mix of virtual and in-person activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How can good team bonding activities help improve team communication?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Activities like these create opportunities for colleagues to interact in a relaxed setting. More than making time for fun, it encourages open dialogue and stronger interpersonal connections.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;Are there team bonding activities that can suit introverted employees?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes! Activities like puzzle-solving, virtual book clubs, or collaborative brainstorming let introverts engage in ways that suit their comfort levels. Playing solo games in a &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games"&gt;hired arcade machine&lt;/a&gt; is also a great idea.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;How do team bonding activities contribute to employee retention?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;A positive work environment where employees feel connected and valued can reduce turnover rates. Done right, it increases job satisfaction and loyalty.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;What are some cost-effective team bonding activities for limited budgets?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If hiring big games aren&amp;rsquo;t part of the budget for now, team bonding activities can be something as simple as potluck lunches, office trivia games, or outdoor picnics. Activities like this require minimal expenses but still encourage interaction and fun.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Final Thoughts&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Fun activities for team bonding aren&amp;rsquo;t just an optional perk - they&amp;rsquo;re a necessity for building a cohesive, motivated, and satisfied workforce. Whether it&amp;rsquo;s through engaging games, casual events, or shared experiences, team bonding builds trust and camaraderie that every workplace needs to thrive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Fun Pro UK specialises in providing high-quality games and activities that bring people together. Our game hires are designed to create memorable, fun, and exciting experiences for you and your team members.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Team Building Activities for Small Groups</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-11-29/team-building-activities-for-small-groups</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-11-29/team-building-activities-for-small-groups</guid><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;You've heard of &amp;lsquo;teamwork makes the dream work,&amp;rsquo; and that quote holds true for every business. &lt;a href="/pages/team-building-ideas" style="background-color: #ffffff;"&gt;Team building games&lt;/a&gt; are a way for businesses to build relationships and collaboration within the workplace. They encourage trust and communication, but they can also be lots of fun too. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;However, there is the matter of finding the right team building games on top of planning the whole thing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Fortunately, team building activities for small groups do not require resorting to outdated and awkward ice breakers from primary school. Additionally, organizing these gatherings can be much less stressful than anticipated.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;In this brief guide, we&amp;rsquo;ll walk you through the types of fun activities to have in team building, why team building is important for company success, a few planning tips for team building activities for small groups, and some &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; to try during the event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Why Team Building is Important for Small Groups&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Team building games are not just activities to help pass the time. They play an important role in developing relationships and collaboration between small groups.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Better communication. For any company to succeed, effective communication is key. Playing team building games for adults can help break down barriers in communication, encourage open dialogue, and make sure that everyone&amp;rsquo;s voice is heard.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Build stronger trust. You&amp;rsquo;ve heard people say how trust is the foundation of any high -performing team. When members of a small group join in on collaborative activities, they learn to rely on each other&amp;rsquo;s skills and expertise. This builds mutual respect and trust, and better performance in the workplace.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Efficient problem-solving. Small teams often tackle challenges that require quick thinking and innovation. Team building activities like problem -solving games and creative brainstorming sessions give team members the chance to practice and develop their critical thinking skills.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li dir="ltr" aria-level="1"&gt;
 &lt;p dir="ltr" role="presentation"&gt;Better morale. Team building activities provide a much- needed break from the usual work routine. It gives every employee a chance to relax and bond. Plus, fun team building activities also help boost morale and promote a sense of accomplishment when goals are achieved.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Fun and Interactive Games for Small Group Team Building&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When planning team building activities for small groups, you need to select activities that encourage collaboration, communication, problem- solving, and creativity. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;And since it&amp;rsquo;s for a small group, the team dynamic and chemistry is something you need to think about too. After all, no one&amp;rsquo;s having fun in an awkward event. That&amp;rsquo;s why the right types of team games can make all the difference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;You want your team to stay engaged, and this is where fun and interactive games come into play. Here are some fun team games to try and how they work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;1. &lt;a href="/category/batak/43/batak-pro"&gt;Batak Pro&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="/category/batak/61/batak-lite"&gt;Batak Lite&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfZ9m509k-dma6TKPj_-qJfaTkhnPePF7ulZ99gW7xhsNTtAS66WvUZFfJZSEi4CGqiJQLnfmg_6xF_3CmJafm2UEDTd5tDn1ArakKAUtq6VnYj1oK2i8rx6ifmly1giikz1m7FOA?key=y5J9ZASbi-bZ7cTWicehlzLg" width="581" height="290" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This game challenges your team&amp;rsquo;s reflexes and coordination. Players need to hit illuminated targets as they light up. It&amp;rsquo;s a test of speed and focus in a competitive environment. It&amp;rsquo;s a great way to promote teamwork and concentration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;2. &lt;a href="/category/grab-a-grand/36/ballnado-grabber"&gt;Ballnado Grabbe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="/category/grab-a-grand/36/ballnado-grabber"&gt;r&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="/category/grab-a-grand/3/cash-grabber-machine-hire"&gt;Cash Grabber&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXcMpqpYtad0KJ7oGW1dCXG-iQQbjsH3y0BULzq-V2jhfjbhCC0vhiTuoxY2zAb8JzmSNq6lUW7tP_QWVjdF9mPL5-knsV3jZ-dFhT49J2gGki5yc_oJxDsr8bdt_-Bs-ohqjsJxhw?key=y5J9ZASbi-bZ7cTWicehlzLg" width="572" height="286" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;A thrilling and dynamic game where one or two people enter a clear wind- filled capsule. From that point on, it&amp;rsquo;s a race against the clock to collect as many balls or as much cash as possible. It&amp;rsquo;s a very high -energy activity that encourages quick thinking and teamwork.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;3. &lt;a href="/category/all-products/87/shuffle-board-hire"&gt;Shuffle Board&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXea0gn-4NftqSFklUv8xa5Yyh_vV2BywBtpFClUmRd1dv3Oz6tqMgeceYP7kSjx5wrI7pSra13kmk8wCsiBfHzA81jlHPGuZkKM6GW1otoWO6LUlh07TZ8GjqwGuFug0N_8cPxNSg?key=y5J9ZASbi-bZ7cTWicehlzLg" width="515" height="406" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s a classic game that&amp;rsquo;s perfect for smaller teams. Players slide pucks down a long, smooth surface with the goal of landing them in specific scoring zones. It&amp;rsquo;s a fantastic way to engage in friendly competition while fostering collaboration and strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;4. &lt;a href="/category/all-products/88/scalextric-slot-car-racing"&gt;Scalextric Slot Car Racing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXd1ZJNLBYnRIr2iU4ThkEN1AJV4JXFTlJvpoeDZ-cyEYbA91VfNzQtw6UwfIXN0-YXUz5ZIzeoWCUvM0RpTCkNZUWSIcb96mUHWXecPqdiUA-6Da-duusfnuMq-29YGHXTBq6z6bQ?key=y5J9ZASbi-bZ7cTWicehlzLg" width="624" height="312" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;If your team loves a bit of speed and competition, Scalextric Slot Car Racing is an exciting game where participants race model cars around a track. It&amp;rsquo;s an excellent choice for fostering teamwork and coordination.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;5.&lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/60/air-hockey-table-hire"&gt; Air Hockey Tables&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXf1S_-ANyEmrJ_X8__3_JynDKe3djvvByShADO8PQUApY9zF8Ve3DBRUb2C4Xcdn3toDwej4k7_W-HlprfxyisfyZmil5_19Cj0au4zybDCMZETz0ldvJGiRTdWVGGqeQ8gqj0JBQ?key=y5J9ZASbi-bZ7cTWicehlzLg" width="624" height="280" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Air hockey is fast- paced and perfect for small group interactions. In this game, players work in pairs or teams to score goals by hitting a puck into the opponent&amp;rsquo;s goal. It&amp;rsquo;s a fun, interactive way to enhance communication and strategic thinking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;6. &lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/27/football-tables"&gt;Football Tables&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfDBaLgQZb0LFKClFGIewqGdZw7SSFZdOLN_RpRD1NYlPyebO7ngTCQt7rm7D_g1ipxF0-b43YxgNEF1DdyxAJkMLZ0wlbfQbJttPLPxt9TuT55_RlWTDieR6vhBCfCtaVWY97dEg?key=y5J9ZASbi-bZ7cTWicehlzLg" width="624" height="467" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Also known as foosball, football tables are a popular choice for team building. Let your teams compete in a simulated soccer game. It&amp;rsquo;s a game that requires coordination, teamwork, and quick reflexes if you want to score goals and win.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;7. &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/82/snatch-it"&gt;Snatch It&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfuwjOoKihx_kRQDU7-djEP2KdlAdPmbD8rhindwA6_KMH8za4xVUPTNKZKQZWyVK6qxjvhvDAiFXFaf_12ovRyE4-ZaE62ORaH5ZTtqPG-4m5zRgtjAtfr_qyPhyslmBwA1cIg4g?key=y5J9ZASbi-bZ7cTWicehlzLg" width="624" height="463" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;This interactive, competitive game challenges players to grab light-up cylinders as quickly as possible when they light up. It&amp;rsquo;s a simple yet exciting way to engage small teams in friendly competition. It also has the added plus of boosting team spirit and communication.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;4 Important Tips for Planning a Successful Small Group Team Building Event&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Now let's face it, planning anything, even something as seemingly simple as a small -group team building event can be stressful. But here are some helpful and important tips that you need to remember to make your event effective and enjoyable for everyone.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;1. Set Clear Goals&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Before organising team building activities, define the aim and objectives of the event. Do you want to improve communication, solve a specific workplace problem, or simply foster better relationships? Clear goals will help you choose the best activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;2. Consider Team Interests&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Choose activities that fit your team&amp;rsquo;s interests and energy levels. If your group enjoys outdoor adventures, an outdoor team-building exercise may be ideal. On the other hand, if your team prefers something more relaxing, maybe a chill cooking class, creative brainstorming sessions, or competitive indoor and interactive games might be better suited.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;3. Inclusivity and Accessibility&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Make sure that the activities are inclusive and accessible to every team member. Consider any team member&amp;rsquo;s physical limitations and preferences. Activities should be designed to include everyone, regardless of their background or ability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;4. Keep it Fun and Lighthearted&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;While team building should have a goal, it&amp;rsquo;s also important to make sure the activities are enjoyable. &lt;a href="/news/2019-02-15/tips-for-running-a-successful-team-building-day"&gt;Fun team building activities&lt;/a&gt; create lasting memories and foster positive feelings toward collaboration, making future work interactions smoother and more productive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;1. Can team building activities improve communication in small groups?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Absolutely! Team building activities for small groups encourage open dialogue. Depending on the activities or games you choose, each member of the groups gets the chance to practice and improve their communication skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;2. What are some low-cost team building activities for small groups?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Simple activities like trivia quizzes, ice- breaker games, or problem-solving challenges can be both engaging and low-cost.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;3. Are there team building activities that can be done in an office setting?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Yes! Activities like brainstorming sessions or team trivia can be done easily within an office space. Hiring arcade games or other interactive games are also a great idea if you want to hold the activity indoors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;4. How do you choose the right team building activity for a small group?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Consider the goals of the event and the team&amp;rsquo;s interests. Think about the type of activity too, and if a physical, mental, or creative activity would be more beneficial. Make sure to match the activity to your team&amp;rsquo;s strengths and preferences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;5. How long should a team building activity last for a small team?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Small group team building activities typically last between 30 minutes to 2 hours, but it depends on the type of activity and the group&amp;rsquo;s attention span as a whole.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 dir="ltr"&gt;6. How do team building activities help build trust in small teams?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;When teams work together in fun and challenging activities, they build trust. Certain games or activities rely on each person&amp;rsquo;s abilities and their ability to communicate openly and support one another.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir="ltr"&gt;Final Thoughts&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;With the right games, strengthening camaraderie within the team and creating a positive and productive work environment is more than possible. But above all, it&amp;rsquo;s important to enjoy the event and have a blast!&lt;/p&gt;
If you&amp;rsquo;re looking to take your team -building event to the next level, consider adding Fun Pro UK&amp;rsquo;s &lt;a href="/"&gt;game hires&lt;/a&gt; to the mix. Our team building games for work are perfect for small groups &amp;mdash; promoting trust, creativity, and teamwork in an interactive and enjoyable way.</description></item><item><title>Best Office Christmas Party Games</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-09-04/best-office-christmas-party-games</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-09-04/best-office-christmas-party-games</guid><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="7132c6ee-d9a5-4147-9747-f1895047cd72" dir="auto"&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Planning an event and want to ensure your guests have an amazing experience? Game rentals are a fantastic way to add fun and interactive elements to any gathering, whether it&amp;rsquo;s a corporate event, birthday party, convention, or community gathering. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But there are few corporate events more important than office Christmas parties, and incorporating our game hire ideas can make a big difference to the big day. So create memorable and engaging events for employees with these &lt;a title="Office &amp;amp; Corporate Game Entertainment" href="/pages/office-and-corporate-entertainment"&gt;office and corporate event hire ideas&lt;/a&gt;! We have it all at Fun Pro UK, including the Christmas party games and adult party games you need - all you need to do is make a booking. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Get Ready for September Exhibitions with Fun Pro UK</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-07-31/get-ready-for-september-exhibitions-with-fun-pro-uk</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-07-31/get-ready-for-september-exhibitions-with-fun-pro-uk</guid><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;As we approach the end of July, businesses across sectors are gearing up for a bustling exhibition season. Wherever you are in the country, Fun Pro UK is here to ensure your exhibition stand is the highlight of any event. With our extensive range of quality exhibition hire products, we are dedicated to enhancing your event presence throughout September 2024 and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Maximise Your Exhibition Impact with Fun Pro UK&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Make a lasting impression with our &lt;a title="Branded Exhibition Games " href="/category/branded-exhibition-games"&gt;Branded Exhibition Games&lt;/a&gt;. These games are a powerful engagement tool that can be customised with your brand&amp;rsquo;s logo and key messaging. Options like the &lt;a title="Whack A Mole game hire" href="/category/arcade-games/67/whack-a-mole-game-hire"&gt;Whack A Mole&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="The Vault" href="/category/arcade-games/50/the-vault"&gt;The Vault&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a title="Mega Wire - Branded Game Hire (stand alone)" href="/category/branded-exhibition-games/64/mega-wire-branded-game-hire-stand-alone"&gt;Mega Wire&lt;/a&gt; provide interactive fun that draws attendees to your booth and keeps them there longer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enhance your company&amp;rsquo;s visibility and attendee engagement with our &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;Corporate Entertainment&lt;/a&gt; options. From high-energy &lt;a title="Batak Pro" href="/category/exhibition-games/43/batak-pro"&gt;Batak Pro&lt;/a&gt; to the competitive Roll &amp;amp; Bowl, these activities are perfect for creating a dynamic environment that promotes networking and interaction.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No matter the size of your stand or the nature of your exhibit, our &lt;a title="Exhibition Games " href="/category/exhibition-games"&gt;Exhibition Games&lt;/a&gt; are designed to fit seamlessly into your space. Whether it&amp;rsquo;s the compact &lt;a title="ELECTRONIC BASKET BALL HIRE" href="/category/arcade-games/6/electronic-basket-ball-hire"&gt;Electronic Basketball Hire&lt;/a&gt; for sports enthusiasts or the ever-popular &lt;a title="Prize Wheel" href="/category/prize-games/49/prize-wheel"&gt;Prize Wheel&lt;/a&gt;, which offers visitors a chance to win instant prizes, our games cater to diverse audiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;For Exhibition Game Hire UK-Wide&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our strategic locations near major exhibition centres like &lt;a title="NEC Birmingham" href="/pages/nec-birmingham"&gt;NEC Birmingham&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="Millennium Point" href="/pages/millennium-point"&gt;Millennium Point&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="Telford International Centre" href="/pages/telford-international-centre"&gt;Telford International Centre&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a title="Excel London" href="/pages/excel-london"&gt;Excel London&lt;/a&gt; allow us to offer timely and efficient service. This means you can expect seamless delivery, setup, and removal of games, ensuring your focus remains on connecting with potential clients and partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customisation&lt;/strong&gt;: Tailor our games to reinforce your branding and message.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Variety&lt;/strong&gt;: A wide range of games that cater to different interests and event themes.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Convenience&lt;/strong&gt;: Proximity to major exhibition centres for prompt and reliable service.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expertise&lt;/strong&gt;: Years of experience in enhancing exhibition stands that guarantee to attract and engage visitors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As September 2024 approaches, it's crucial to plan how you'll stand out in the busy exhibition season. With Fun Pro UK, you&amp;rsquo;re choosing a partner who understands the importance of engagement, brand visibility, and creating memorable experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you ready to make your exhibition stand the most visited and talked about? &lt;a title="Contact Fun Pro UK" href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Contact Fun Pro UK&lt;/a&gt; today to discuss your needs and how our interactive games can elevate your exhibition presence.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Working in Birmingham with Custom-Branded Interactive Games</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-06-25/working-in-birmingham-with-custom-branded-interactive-games</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-06-25/working-in-birmingham-with-custom-branded-interactive-games</guid><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;At Fun Pro UK, we recently had the exciting opportunity to showcase our expertise in enhancing trade shows by installing seven custom-branded &lt;a title="Interactive Game Hire " href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; for our clients at the Installer show held at the&lt;a title="NEC Birmingham" href="/pages/nec-birmingham"&gt; NEC Birmingham&lt;/a&gt;. Our close proximity in Wolston allowed us to offer complimentary delivery, ensuring that each setup was convenient and cost-effective for our clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Each of the games provided was carefully branded with the client's logo and key messaging, turning each unit into a pivotal marketing tool that complemented the exhibitors' stands beautifully. Our in-house design team meticulously ensured that the branding was spot-on, enhancing visual appeal and brand presence on the show floor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The variety of games we set up for the event included:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a title="The Vault" href="/category/arcade-games/50/the-vault"&gt;The Vault - Honeywell&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: Engaged visitors with a high-stakes challenge of cracking the code against the clock.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a title="Ballnado Grabber" href="/category/exhibition-games/36/ballnado-grabber"&gt;Ballnado - Spirotech UK &amp;amp; Anton by Crowcon&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: Drew crowds with an energetic and visually engaging game where participants scrambled to grab flying balls.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a title="Mega Wire - Branded Game Hire (stand alone)" href="/category/branded-exhibition-games/64/mega-wire-branded-game-hire-stand-alone"&gt;Mega Wire - @A-Gas&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: Offered a steady hand challenge as attendees navigated a wand along a twisting wire.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a title="Whack A Mole game hire" href="/category/arcade-games/67/whack-a-mole-game-hire"&gt;Whack a Mole - @LG Electronics and VIVA Sanitary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: Provided fast-paced fun as participants tried to whack as many 'moles' as possible.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a title="Beat The Buzzer" href="/category/exhibition-games/62/beat-the-buzzer"&gt;Beat the Buzzer - Correla&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;: Tested participants' precision and steadiness in a tense buzzer game.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the Installer show running over several days, we are excited to see how our &lt;a title="Exhibition Games " href="/category/exhibition-games"&gt;exhibition stand games&lt;/a&gt; enhance the experience for our clients' stands, hoping to boost footfall and engagement significantly. Our aim is for these &lt;a title="Branded Exhibition Games " href="/category/branded-exhibition-games"&gt;bespoke branded games&lt;/a&gt; to attract attendees and turn visitors into profit. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you're planning an event and looking for ways to increase engagement and visibility, consider hiring interactive games from Fun Pro UK. Our ability to customise games to fit your branding needs makes us an ideal choice for your next corporate event, exhibition, or private party.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let Fun Pro UK help you make your next event a resounding success with our engaging, interactive, and custom-branded games. We're here to bring your event to life with fun and flair that will be remembered for years to come.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;📞 Call the Fun Pro UK team at 02476 7220 701 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;📧 Email us at &lt;a&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt; 🌐&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>A Busy May for the Fun Pro UK Team</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-06-04/a-busy-may-for-the-fun-pro-uk-team</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-06-04/a-busy-may-for-the-fun-pro-uk-team</guid><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;May 2024 has been a bustling month for Fun Pro UK, filled with thrilling installations, vibrant branding, and unforgettable events. Our team has been all over the map, from the &lt;a title="NEC Birmingham" href="/pages/nec-birmingham"&gt;NEC in Birmingham&lt;/a&gt; to the heart of London, bringing fun and engagement through our uniquely branded &lt;a title="Interactive Game Hire " href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt;. Here&amp;rsquo;s a roundup of what we&amp;rsquo;ve been up to this month!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One of the highlights of the month was our participation in the Dentistry Shows at the NEC, Birmingham. Our &lt;a title="Whack A Mole game hire" href="/category/arcade-games/67/whack-a-mole-game-hire"&gt;Whack A Mole&lt;/a&gt; game, cleverly rebranded as &amp;lsquo;Whack A Molar&amp;rsquo; for our client Humm Group, was a standout attraction. The game&amp;rsquo;s vibrant custom branding, matching the distinctive colours of Humm Group, drew visitors and sparked conversations among present, past, and potential customers. This event was a fantastic showcase of how tailored branding on interactive games like Whack A Mole and the &lt;a title="LEADER BOARD" href="/category/interactive-game-hire/30/leader-board"&gt;Leaderboard &lt;/a&gt;can enhance corporate presence at industry events.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We were also thrilled to be a part of the Scientific Laboratory Supplies Ltd&amp;rsquo;s annual show and conference, where we supplied five engaging games, including &lt;a title="Batak Pro" href="/category/exhibition-games/43/batak-pro"&gt;Batak Pro&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="Danger-zone-strike-a-light-game-hire" href="/category/arcade-games/63/danger-zone-strike-a-light-game-hire"&gt;Strike a Light / Danger Zone&lt;/a&gt;, Roll &amp;amp; Bowl, Whack a Mole, and a &lt;a title="ELECTRONIC BASKET BALL HIRE" href="/category/arcade-games/6/electronic-basket-ball-hire"&gt;Basketball&lt;/a&gt; game. Our in-house print team excelled in applying &lt;a title="Branded Exhibition Games " href="/category/branded-exhibition-games"&gt;bespoke branding&lt;/a&gt; to four of these games, creating a fully immersive experience for the brand. Visitors had the chance to win a &amp;pound;250 Amazon voucher!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team had a whirlwind day with multiple installs across the UK. At the Utility Week Live show at the NEC Birmingham, we delivered a custom-branded &lt;a title="FOOTBALL TABLES" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/27/football-tables"&gt;Table Football&lt;/a&gt; game for our client Fusion Utilities. The precision in branding was crucial, and our team ensured every detail was perfect.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Further, we brought fun to the ICC Wales for the ISBA2024 event with a Whack a Mole game and a Leaderboard, both featuring bespoke branding that beautifully represented the event&amp;rsquo;s theme. In London, we installed a branded &lt;a title="Pix N Mix Hire" href="/category/fun-foods/42/pix-n-mix-hire"&gt;Pick n Mix sweet stand&lt;/a&gt; and a &lt;a title="Ballnado Grabber" href="/category/exhibition-games/36/ballnado-grabber"&gt;Ballnado game&lt;/a&gt;, enhancing a showroom activation with a playful and engaging setup.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lastly, the &lt;a title="Crack The Code safe cracker" href="/category/exhibition-games/37/crack-the-code-safe-cracker"&gt;Crack the Code safe cracker game&lt;/a&gt; installation at the CWS Summit featured customised branding, making it a powerful promotional tool for our client.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;If you like what you see and want to add uniquely engaging and branded games to your next event, don&amp;rsquo;t hesitate to speak with our team. Whether it's installing interactive games that reflect your brand or designing a fun space that captivates your audience, we are here to make your event a resounding success.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;May 2024 was a testament to the creativity, dedication, and hard work of our team at Fun Pro UK. We look forward to bringing more fun and engagement to events nationwide, proving that when it comes to enhancing your event with interactive entertainment, Fun Pro UK is your go-to expert.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>The Secret to Team Building: Interactive Games</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-05-03/the-secret-to-team-building-interactive-games</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-05-03/the-secret-to-team-building-interactive-games</guid><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Interactive games have become a cornerstone of successful team-building strategies. Engaging, fun, and inherently collaborative, games like &lt;a title="Batak " href="/category/batak"&gt;Batak&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="Roll &amp;amp; Bowl " href="/category/roll-and-bowl"&gt;Roll &amp;amp; Bowl&lt;/a&gt;, and other &lt;a title="Interactive Game Hire " href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;Interactive Challenges&lt;/a&gt; offer more than just entertainment. They are powerful tools that foster teamwork, enhance communication, and bolster problem-solving skills among employees. Let&amp;rsquo;s delve into how these interactive games can transform your team-building events.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Fostering Teamwork Through Fun: The essence of team building is to strengthen the bonds between team members, and interactive games are particularly effective at this. Games like &lt;a title="Batak " href="/category/batak"&gt;Batak&lt;/a&gt; challenge teams to work together under time pressure, promoting a spirit of cooperation and collective effort. By engaging in these activities, employees learn to support each other&amp;rsquo;s strengths and compensate for weaknesses, which is crucial for a harmonious workplace environment.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Enhancing Communication in a Dynamic Setting: Communication is the lifeline of effective teamwork. Interactive games create a dynamic environment where team members must communicate clearly and effectively to succeed. For instance, &lt;a title="Roll &amp;amp; Bowl " href="/category/roll-and-bowl"&gt;Roll &amp;amp; Bowl&lt;/a&gt; requires teams to strategise and make decisions quickly, demanding concise and direct communication. These games provide a low-stakes platform for practising communication skills that are transferable to the workplace.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Sharpening Problem-Solving Skills: Problem-solving is another critical aspect of team building that interactive games can significantly enhance. Challenging scenarios that require quick thinking and strategic planning push teams to think outside the box and find innovative solutions. Whether it&amp;rsquo;s figuring out how to score higher in &lt;a title="Batak " href="/category/batak"&gt;Batak&lt;/a&gt; or developing a winning strategy in &lt;a title="Roll &amp;amp; Bowl " href="/category/roll-and-bowl"&gt;Roll &amp;amp; Bowl&lt;/a&gt;, the skills developed during these games can be invaluable back at the office.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Building Morale and Boosting Engagement: Beyond the skills development aspect, interactive games are incredibly effective at boosting morale and engagement. Participating in enjoyable and challenging activities can rejuvenate teams and leave employees feeling motivated and appreciated. This not only enhances their engagement at the event itself but can also lead to increased enthusiasm and productivity in their work.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Customising the Experience: One of the great advantages of using interactive games for team building is the ability to tailor them to specific team dynamics and company goals. Many interactive games offer options for customisation and branding, allowing companies to integrate their corporate values and objectives into the game experience. This personalisation makes the team-building activity not only a fun and engaging experience but also an extension of the company culture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interactive games are more than just play; they are a strategic tool for building stronger, more effective teams. By incorporating games like &lt;a title="Batak " href="/category/batak"&gt;Batak&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a title="Roll &amp;amp; Bowl " href="/category/roll-and-bowl"&gt;Roll &amp;amp; Bowl&lt;/a&gt; into your team-building events, you're investing in your team&amp;rsquo;s development in a way that is enjoyable, memorable, and highly beneficial.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ready to transform your team-building approach with interactive games? Explore how Fun Pro UK can help by visiting our website today. Discover the power of play for developing a cohesive and high-performing team.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>End of the Financial Year! Now is an ideal time to have a wellbeing event.</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-04-04/end-of-the-financial-year-now-is-an-ideal-time-to-have-a-wellbeing-event</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-04-04/end-of-the-financial-year-now-is-an-ideal-time-to-have-a-wellbeing-event</guid><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;End of the Financial Year! Now is an ideal time to have a wellbeing event.&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;The end of the Financial Year &lt;strong&gt;5 April, &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;t&lt;/strong&gt;he financial year comes to an end, paving the way for the next tax year and the cycle begins once again. How are you going to engage your team to start all over again and keep them motivated and engaged for that long 12 month journey? &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;With budget constraints, the offsite wellbeing events can become cost prohibitive, but why not bring interactive games and activities to the office. Interactive games are a way to bring teams together and enhance the &lt;strong&gt;team building&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;strategic thinking&lt;/strong&gt;, it is very much all about fun and games, with experiences that will make your team laugh and smile for unforgettable memories. And we all know that laughter is good for helping reduce stress and promote team interaction.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;The weekly project update meeting could turn into a driving sensation with &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire/5/racing-car-simulators#BodyContent"&gt;Racing Car Simulator&lt;/a&gt;. It&amp;rsquo;s not just about speed and positioning, interactive games encourages innovative thinking and creativity. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;A &lt;a href="/category/arcade-games/49/prize-wheel#BodyContent"&gt;Prize Wheel&lt;/a&gt;, also known as Wheel of Fortune can give everyone the opportunity to be a winner. All segments having a wellbeing themed reward, from a piece of fruit to a months free gym membership, the choice of prizes is yours. &lt;br&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Introduce a competitive edge, with hand and eye coordination being key with the &lt;a href="/search.aspx?q=batak#BodyContent"&gt;BATAK&lt;/a&gt; reaction game. Set up an internal competition, the person who strikes the most lights in 30 seconds wins.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;The in-office games on a Wellbeing Day (or any Corporate Event) certainly bring a break from the norm, it&amp;rsquo;s a superb way to encourage camaraderie, promote team building, keep the morale high and focus for the next financial year. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Whether it be breakout areas and sessions, let the interactive games bring a sense of wellbeing to the office with, fun, laughter, and excitement to the working environment. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;And if you are going off site, interactive games can still be part of your entertainment activities. Fun Pro UK will travel to your event both locally and nationally across the UK.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Give the Fun Pro UK events team a call to help your plan and deliver the best wellbeing event of 2024.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Free quotes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Email : &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Telephone : 0247 7220 701&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Batak, Grab a Grand, Roll &amp; Bowl and More!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-04-03/batak-grab-a-grand-roll-and-bowl-and-more</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-04-03/batak-grab-a-grand-roll-and-bowl-and-more</guid><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Spice up your events with Fun Pro UK's exciting range of &lt;a title="Interactive Game Hire " href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt;! Whether you're planning a corporate team-building day, a trade show, or a fun-filled private party, our diverse selection of games promises plenty of entertainment and endless competitive fun. You could even use them for &lt;a title="Exhibition Games " href="/category/exhibition-games"&gt;exhibition stand entertainment&lt;/a&gt;! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Just some of our cool suggestions include: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="Batak " href="/category/batak"&gt;Batak&lt;/a&gt; is a challenge that tests your speed, agility, and reaction time. With both Batak Lite and Batak Pro available, we have something suited for venues and events of all sizes. Perfect for encouraging a bit of friendly competition among guests, Batak is an excellent way to break the ice and get everyone involved. The game's vibrant lights and dynamic gameplay make it an eye-catching addition to any event, ensuring participants and onlookers alike are drawn to the action.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="Grab A Grand " href="/category/grab-a-grand"&gt;Grab A Grand&lt;/a&gt; sees participants stepping into a whirlwind filled with flying notes, all up for grabs. This game evokes the final round on the Crystal Maze, and is a crowd-pleaser that offers participants a unique and thrilling challenge. It's a visually spectacular way to engage attendees, making it a perfect choice for exhibitions and promotional events. With a &lt;a title="Christmas Game Hire " href="/category/christmas-game-hire"&gt;Christmas game&lt;/a&gt; also available, it's a versatile option that can be tailored to any event theme.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="Roll &amp;amp; Bowl " href="/category/roll-and-bowl"&gt;Roll &amp;amp; Bowl&lt;/a&gt; : Roll and Bowl arcade games bring the timeless fun of bowling into a more compact and versatile format. From the Donkey Derby to the festive Reindeer Racing, these games are designed to entertain guests of all ages. They offer a blend of skill, strategy, and luck, making them the perfect addition to family fun days, corporate events, and more. The joy of Roll &amp;amp; Bowl lies in its simplicity and the shared excitement it generates among participants.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interactive games and &lt;a title="Arcade Games " href="/category/arcade-games"&gt;arcade games&lt;/a&gt; from Fun Pro UK offer you the opportunity to bring people together. Whether it's the competitive thrill of Batak, the exhilarating rush of Grab a Grand, or the shared fun of Roll &amp;amp; Bowl, these games are sure to keep your guests happy. Plus, with options for &lt;a title="Branded Game Hire" href="/pages/branded-game-hire"&gt;custom branding&lt;/a&gt;, you can turn these games into unique promotional tools, enhancing your brand visibility and engagement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Based in the West Midlands but with a reach that spans the entire UK, Fun Pro UK is committed to bringing the fun to you, wherever you are. From London to Glasgow, Manchester to Leeds, our team ensures a seamless experience from delivery and setup to collection, allowing you to focus on enjoying your event. Add plenty of fun an excitement to your event - find the perfect fit for your event with Fun Pro UK.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;For more information, to explore our full range of games, look through our website!&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Prize Games - Perfect Competitive Fun!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-03-08/prize-games-perfect-competitive-fun</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2024-03-08/prize-games-perfect-competitive-fun</guid><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Planning an event this year? Whether it's a&lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt; corporate event&lt;/a&gt;, a trade show, or a private party, creating an atmosphere of fun and competition can significantly enhance the guest experience. This is where our range &lt;a title="Prize Games " href="/category/prize-games"&gt;prize games&lt;/a&gt; come into their own, offering entertainment alongside the thrill of competition and the joy of winning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prize games are the heart and soul of interactive entertainment, bringing people together through the universal language of play. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Some of our most popular prize games for hire include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="CASH GRABBER MACHINE HIRE" href="/category/exhibition-games/3/cash-grabber-machine-hire"&gt;Cash Grabber - Grab a Grand&lt;/a&gt;: Step into the whirlwind where skill and luck meet. Perfect for &lt;a title="Exhibition Games " href="/category/exhibition-games"&gt;exhibition stands&lt;/a&gt; and similar events, it's a visually spectacular way to engage participants, offering them the chance to 'grab' branded vouchers or prizes&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="Beat The Buzzer" href="/category/exhibition-games/62/beat-the-buzzer"&gt;Beat The Buzzer&lt;/a&gt;: A test of steadiness and nerve, Beat The Buzzer and the &lt;a title="GIANT BUZZ WIRE" href="/category/interactive-game-hire/9/giant-buzz-wire"&gt;Giant Buzz Wire&lt;/a&gt; challenge players to move a wand along a charged wire without touching it. If anyone can make it to the end, a prize is well-deserved!&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="High Striker" href="/category/arcade-games/48/high-striker"&gt;High Striker&lt;/a&gt;: Bring the funfair to your event with the classic High Striker. A hit at outdoor events and fun days, it allows everyone to test their strength in the most traditional of ways &amp;ndash; with the reward of ringing that bell at the top.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="Plinko Game Hire" href="/category/arcade-games/68/plinko-game-hire"&gt;Plinko Game Hire&lt;/a&gt;: Inspired by the iconic game show, Plinko is a game of chance that's always a crowd-pleaser. Participants drop chips down a pegged board, eagerly anticipating where they will land. It's perfect for injecting a bit of luck into your event, with various prizes up for grabs.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="Prize Wheel" href="/category/prize-games/49/prize-wheel"&gt;Prize Wheel&lt;/a&gt;: Spin the wheel and let fate decide! The Prize Wheel is a versatile game that can be custom-branded and used to distribute a wide range of prizes. It's an engaging way to draw attendees to your stand or add excitement to your party.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What sets these games apart is the opportunity for customisation. With &lt;a title="Branded Exhibition Games " href="/category/branded-exhibition-games"&gt;branded exhibition games&lt;/a&gt;, you can transform any of the above into a powerful promotional tool. Incorporating your company's branding into the game design will boost its visual appeal and improve brand recognition and recall, making your event a strategic marketing opportunity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;At Fun Pro UK, we understand the power of competitive fun. Our wide range of prize games is designed to deliver excitement and engagement to your guests, all while seamlessly integrating into your event's theme and objectives. Based in the West Midlands and operating nationwide, our team is ready to bring the fun directly to you, whether you're in London, Manchester, Leeds, Glasgow, or anywhere in between.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;For more information, to make an enquiry, or to book, don't hesitate to &lt;a title="Contact Fun Pro UK" href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;contact us&lt;/a&gt;. With Fun Pro UK, competitive fun is just the beginning.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Celebrate Christmas and the New Year in Style!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-11-30/celebrate-christmas-and-the-new-year-in-style</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-11-30/celebrate-christmas-and-the-new-year-in-style</guid><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;As the festive season twinkles on the horizon, it's time to think about how to bid a grand farewell to this year and usher in the new one with pomp and splendor. Whether you're planning an office Christmas party or a dazzling New Year's Eve bash, Fun Pro UK is here to take your celebrations to an extraordinary level with &lt;a title="Christmas Game Hire " href="/category/christmas-game-hire"&gt;Christmas games&lt;/a&gt; and event supplies that you'll love. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Mobile Casino: Glamour and Thrills&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Imagine the excitement of Las Vegas at your festive event with our &lt;a title="CASINO TABLE HIRE" href="/category/pub-games/16/casino-table-hire"&gt;Mobile Casino&lt;/a&gt;. This will create an atmosphere brimming with elegance and excitement. Let your guests indulge in a night of blackjack, roulette, and more, adding a sophisticated flair to your Christmas or New Year&amp;rsquo;s Eve celebration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Lights Out Game: An Electrifying Countdown&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the clock ticks down to the New Year, what better way to celebrate than with our interactive Lights Out game? This &lt;a title="Interactive Game Hire " href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive game &lt;/a&gt;symbolises bidding adieu to the old year and welcoming the new with a burst of energy and fun. It's an engaging, playful way to count down those final moments of the year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Climbing Wall: Scaling New Heights&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;New Year&amp;rsquo;s is synonymous with new challenges and aspirations. Our &lt;a title="Climbing Wall" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/76/climbing-wall"&gt;Climbing Wall&lt;/a&gt; embodies this spirit, offering a fun, exhilarating challenge to your guests. It&amp;rsquo;s a metaphor for climbing to new peaks, making it an ideal feature for a New Year&amp;rsquo;s party that&amp;rsquo;s all about embracing what lies ahead.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Red Carpet Hire: Star-Studded Entrances&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Give your guests a VIP experience right from the start with our &lt;a title="RED CARPET &amp;amp; 4 GOLD STANCHIONS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/31/red-carpet-and-4-gold-stanchions"&gt;Red Carpet Hire&lt;/a&gt;. There's something truly special about walking down a red carpet; it sets the tone for an exclusive, glamorous event. It's perfect for adding a touch of elegance to any festive party.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Tailored to Your Theme&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Every event is unique, and we pride ourselves on offering customisable options that align with your party theme. Whether it&amp;rsquo;s a winter wonderland or a glitzy gala, we tailor the experience to ensure it resonates with your vision.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our unique entertainment options are designed not just to amuse but to add meaning and excitement to your celebrations. With Fun Pro UK, the focus is on fun, not fretting over details. We manage everything from setup to operation, ensuring you can enjoy the party as much as your guests do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em style="color: inherit; ;"&gt;As the year draws to a close, it's time to make those final celebrations count. With Fun Pro UK, you&amp;rsquo;re not just planning a party; you&amp;rsquo;re crafting an experience that will be remembered long after the decorations come down. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em style="color: inherit; ;"&gt;Ready to make your Christmas and New Year's parties the highlight of the year? &lt;a title="Contact Fun Pro UK" href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Contact us today&lt;/a&gt; and let's bring some festive magic to your event!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Christmas is Coming - Arrange Party Hire!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-11-26/christmas-is-coming-arrange-party-hire</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-11-26/christmas-is-coming-arrange-party-hire</guid><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;As the twinkling lights go up and the holiday season draws near, it&amp;rsquo;s time to think about your upcoming&lt;a title="Christmas Entertainment Game Hire" href="/pages/christmas-entertainment-game-hire"&gt; Christmas parties&lt;/a&gt;. At Fun Pro UK, we specialise in turning holiday celebrations into magical, memorable events with our unique range of&lt;a title="Christmas Game Hire " href="/category/christmas-game-hire"&gt; Christmas games&lt;/a&gt; and attractions. Here&amp;rsquo;s how you can add that extra sparkle to your festivities this year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Christmas Magic Mirror&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Imagine stepping into a Christmas wonderland every time you take a photo! Our &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Christmas Magic Mirror&lt;/a&gt; does just that, offering an interactive experience complete with festive and seasonal backdrops. &lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;Photo booth hire&lt;/a&gt; is not just about capturing moments; it's about creating memories wrapped in the magic of Christmas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt; Rudolph Nosenado&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Get ready for a hilariously chaotic game where the goal is to catch as many of Rudolph's noses as possible. The &lt;a title="Reindeer Nosenado (Christmas Ballnado Hire )" href="/category/christmas-game-hire/65/reindeer-nosenado-christmas-ballnado-hire"&gt;Rudolph Nosenado&lt;/a&gt; is a unique, fast-paced game that will have everyone laughing and competing in a festive frenzy. This spin off on the &lt;a title="CASH GRABBER MACHINE HIRE" href="/category/exhibition-games/3/cash-grabber-machine-hire"&gt;Cash Grabber&lt;/a&gt; is an ideal way to bring energy and excitement to your party.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt; Whack an Elf&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;a title="Whack an Elf" href="/category/christmas-game-hire/79/whack-an-elf"&gt;Whack an Elf game&lt;/a&gt; is a Christmas twist on the classic &lt;a title="Arcade Games " href="/category/arcade-games"&gt;arcade machine&lt;/a&gt; favourite. Armed with a soft hammer, guests of all ages can enjoy whacking mischievous elves as they pop up on this &lt;a title="Whack A Mole game hire" href="/category/arcade-games/67/whack-a-mole-game-hire"&gt;Whack a Mole game&lt;/a&gt;. This is an elfin adventure that brings out the childlike joy and competitive spirit in everyone.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Santa&amp;rsquo;s Grotto&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Transform a corner of your party into the North Pole with &lt;a title="Christmas Grotto Hire " href="/category/christmas-grotto-hire"&gt;Santa&amp;rsquo;s Grotto&lt;/a&gt;. It's a festive haven where guests can bask in the holiday spirit, take photos with Father Christmas himself, and even exchange gifts. The Christmas Grotto creates a magical atmosphere that&amp;rsquo;s essential for any kid-friendly Christmas celebration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Reindeer Roll &amp;amp; Bowl&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Adding to our repertoire of Christmas fun is the &lt;a title="Roll And Bowl Reindeer Racing Game Hire" href="/category/christmas-game-hire/66/roll-and-bowl-reindeer-racing-game-hire"&gt;Reindeer Roll &amp;amp; Bowl&lt;/a&gt;. This game combines the joy of bowling with the charm of the festive season, featuring reindeer-themed pins and a snowy lane. This is a spin-off of the &lt;a title="Roll And Bowl Game Hire" href="/category/arcade-games/51/roll-and-bowl-game-hire"&gt;Roll and Bowl racing game&lt;/a&gt;, and is perfect for team-building, friendly competition, or just a roll-down memory lane.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Why Fun Pro UK is Your Go-To for Christmas Party Fun&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Fun Pro UK, we&amp;rsquo;re about more than just providing games. We create immersive experiences that resonate with the festive season. Our team ensures a hassle-free experience, handling setup, management, and breakdown, so you can focus on enjoying the party.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This Christmas, go beyond the traditional and step into a world of interactive, joyful, and magical fun with Fun Pro UK. Book online now to begin! &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Keep Conferences Fun with Fun Pro UK</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-10-17/keep-conferences-fun-with-fun-pro-uk</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-10-17/keep-conferences-fun-with-fun-pro-uk</guid><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;When planning a conference, you're creating an experience&amp;mdash;a blend of knowledge exchange, networking, and brand projection. But in today's competitive landscape, how can you ensure your conference stands out, offering attendees something genuinely memorable and fun? &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With Fun Pro UK, we have a wide range of &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;corporate event ideas&lt;/a&gt; that are ideal for conferences. &lt;a title="Conference Game Hire" href="/pages/conference-game-hire"&gt;Conference game hire&lt;/a&gt; brings a lot of advantages, ensuring that people can enjoy themselves in breaks and take advantage of everything these events have to offer. Check out some of the most popular reasons for conference entertainment hire and find out how Fun Pro UK can keep spirits high during these occasions. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Blend of Business and Fun:&lt;/strong&gt; Conferences needn't be a monotonous stream of lectures and panels. With our range of &lt;a title="Interactive Game Hire " href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; and activities, we introduce a dynamic element, ensuring attendees stay energised and engaged throughout.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Networking Made Easy:&lt;/strong&gt; Networking can sometimes be a tad awkward. Our games, from&lt;a title="Arcade Games " href="/category/arcade-games"&gt; arcade games&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a title="CASINO TABLE HIRE" href="/category/pub-games/16/casino-table-hire"&gt;casino tables&lt;/a&gt;, foster natural interactions and collaborations. This means more genuine connections and fewer forced conversations.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tailored Experiences: &lt;/strong&gt;Every conference has its unique theme and audience. Fun Pro UK understands this, offering a bespoke range of games and activities tailored to your event's needs. &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enhancing Brand Recall:&lt;/strong&gt; Conferences are as much about the brand as they are about the content. Our games and activities can be customised to reflect your branding, ensuring a consistent and memorable brand experience for all attendees.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stress-Free Logistics: &lt;/strong&gt;Organising a conference is no small feat. With Fun Pro UK, you have one less thing to worry about. Our experienced team ensures seamless setup, management, and wrap-up of all game-related activities, letting you focus on the bigger picture.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Proven Track Record: &lt;/strong&gt;Our clientele speaks volumes about our commitment to excellence. Having collaborated with numerous brands for their conferences, Fun Pro UK has the expertise, experience, and testimonials to ensure your event is nothing short of spectacular.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Value for Money: &lt;/strong&gt;While our offerings add significant value to your conference, we ensure it doesn't break the bank. Our packages are competitively priced, ensuring you get maximum ROI for every penny spent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A conference is more than just sessions and speeches. It's about creating an environment where attendees learn, network, and most importantly, enjoy themselves. With Fun Pro UK, you're not just adding a fun element; you're elevating the entire conference experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thinking of giving your conference the Fun Pro UK touch? Reach out to us through our&lt;a title="Contact Fun Pro UK" href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt; contact page&lt;/a&gt; or make a booking online. We're looking forwards to finding out more about your upcoming events. &lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Improve Staff Retention with Company Fun Days</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-09-27/improve-staff-retention-with-company-fun-days</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-09-27/improve-staff-retention-with-company-fun-days</guid><pubDate>Wed, 27 Sep 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Employee retention is a topic that often keeps business leaders awake at night. Amidst the myriad strategies to keep talent onboard, there's one that's gaining momentum: the power of play. With company fun days, Fun Pro UK can help you revamp the workplace ethos and significantly boost staff retention.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Modern professionals seek more than just a paycheque. They look for work environments that offer bonding, respect, opportunities for growth, and hopefully even a bit of fun. A relaxed, enjoyable workplace atmosphere not only boosts morale but also fosters loyalty.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So if you'd like to host one of these&lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt; corporate events&lt;/a&gt; for yourself, choose Fun Pro UK! Check out some of our popular options below, and make an order online!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Company Fun Day Rental Ideas&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="Pix N Mix Hire" href="/category/fun-foods/42/pix-n-mix-hire"&gt;Pick and Mix Stand&lt;/a&gt;: Sometimes, a simple pleasure, like reminiscing over childhood sweets, can bridge the gap between colleagues. The Pick and Mix Stand isn't a treat station that has something for everyone! Ask your staff what their favourites are and get them stocked up. &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="PLUCK A DUCK RACING" href="/category/arcade-games/8/pluck-a-duck-racing"&gt;Pluck a Duck&lt;/a&gt;: Race against the clock to see who can pluck the most ducks in the allotted time! It's a ferocious and fun race to the finish line that will definitely see colleagues laughing together. &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="Dance Machine" href="/category/arcade-games/39/dance-machine"&gt;Dance Machine&lt;/a&gt;: Put the arguments about the radio station on pause for a day - our Dance Machine is an invitation to shed inhibitions, celebrate diversity, and bond over music. Such light-hearted activities can often be the ice-breaker new teams need.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="FOOTBALL TABLES" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/27/football-tables"&gt;Table Football&lt;/a&gt;: Beyond the game's inherent fun, table football fosters collaboration and teamwork. It's always popular at all kinds of venues, and we know your workplace will be no different. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;The Benefits of Office Fun and Games Days&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When employees feel valued, acknowledged, and engaged, they're less likely to seek opportunities elsewhere. Company fun days promote work-life balance, showing staff that the company values their well-being and relaxation. They also improve your team's dynamics and boost overall morale. You should see improved staff retention if you realign your focus to making your workplace fun! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the quest to retain top talent, innovative approaches like &lt;a title="Office &amp;amp; Corporate Game Entertainment" href="/pages/office-and-corporate-entertainment"&gt;company fun days&lt;/a&gt; can be game-changers. Fun Pro UK is poised to help you redefine your company culture, making it not just a place to work, but a space to grow, bond, and thrive. Make a booking today and find out for yourself! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Considering a unique approach to staff retention? Dive into play with Fun Pro UK. After all, a company that plays together, stays together.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Make Award Ceremonies Extra-Special: Event Entertainment Experts</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-09-20/make-award-ceremonies-extra-special-event-entertainment-experts</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-09-20/make-award-ceremonies-extra-special-event-entertainment-experts</guid><pubDate>Wed, 20 Sep 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;In the bustling world of corporate achievements, recognising milestones is not just essential&amp;mdash;it's a cause for celebration. Every award and acknowledgement is a testament to hard work, innovation, and the pursuit of excellence. But how do we ensure that these celebrations leave a lasting impression?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enter Fun Pro UK's &lt;a title="Branded Game Hire" href="/pages/branded-game-hire"&gt;bespoke branded games&lt;/a&gt;&amp;mdash;a game-changing solution that promises to amplify your &lt;a title="Company Award Ceremonies" href="/category/company-award-ceremonies"&gt;awards ceremony entertainment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Why Branding Matters at Awards Ceremonies&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Branding isn&amp;rsquo;t just about logos or colour schemes; it's about creating an identity&amp;mdash;a story that resonates with stakeholders, both internal and external. Embedding this identity into events and celebrations ensures continuity in messaging and reinforces the company's values. With Fun Pro UK's customised games, this brand identity gets a playful twist, ensuring that attendees not only remember the awards but also associate them with fun! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Our Suite of Branded Games&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are plenty of awards ceremony entertainment options for hire with us! Why not consider some of these four? &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="Virtual Pinball" href="/category/exhibition-games/77/virtual-pinball"&gt;Pinball Games&lt;/a&gt;: Merge the thrill of classic pinball action with your company's logo. It's nostalgia, excitement, and brand promotion&amp;mdash;all in one package.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="CASINO TABLE HIRE" href="/category/pub-games/16/casino-table-hire"&gt;Mobile Casino&lt;/a&gt;: Envision roulette, blackjack, or poker tables, each tailored with your logo, for a sophisticated touch that radiates a sense of achievement and celebration.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="Arcade Games " href="/category/arcade-games"&gt;Arcade Games&lt;/a&gt;: Transport attendees back in time with iconic games like Pac-Man and Space Invaders! Who could resist the chance to show off their retro arcade skills? &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;Photo Booths&lt;/a&gt;: Our range, including the enchanting Magic Mirror booths, captures the heart of the ceremony. You could even have your logo on the print-outs! &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the corporate world evolving rapidly, it&amp;rsquo;s essential to stay ahead of the curve, even in celebrations. At Fun Pro UK, we&amp;rsquo;re dedicated to blending entertainment with brand identity. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Make a booking online today, or if you need more information or advice, please feel free to &lt;a title="Contact Fun Pro UK" href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;contact us&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Make Autumn Fairs &amp; Exhibitions Fun with Branded Games</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-08-31/make-autumn-fairs-and-exhibitions-fun-with-branded-games</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-08-31/make-autumn-fairs-and-exhibitions-fun-with-branded-games</guid><pubDate>Thu, 31 Aug 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Autumn is a season of change, bringing not just the vibrant colours of falling leaves but also a bustling schedule of exhibitions and trade shows. As you gear up for the autumn exhibition season, we're excited to share how our range of &lt;a title="Branded Game Hire" href="/pages/branded-game-hire"&gt;branded games for hire &lt;/a&gt;can transform your stand into a captivating and engaging space that draws footfall and leaves a mark on all attendees. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the competitive landscape of exhibitions, it's essential to go beyond the ordinary to attract attention and create a buzz around your stand. This is where Fun Pro UK's branded&lt;a title="Exhibition Games " href="/category/exhibition-games"&gt; exhibition stand games&lt;/a&gt; come into play. Our trade show games immerse visitors in your brand and message, creating a lasting impact and giving you plenty of opportunities to sell services or network with prospects. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Just some of the upcoming exhibitions you might soon see Fun Pro UK's branded exhibition games at include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Autumn Fair (NEC Birmingham)&lt;/strong&gt;: At the NEC Birmingham's Autumn Fair, your stand deserves to shine. Our branded attractions, including&lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt; photo booths&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;a title="Dance Machine" href="/category/arcade-games/39/dance-machine"&gt; dance machines&lt;/a&gt;, and more, can transform your exhibition stand into an engaging hotspot that draws footfall and encourages interaction. &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Trade Fair (SEC Glasgow):&lt;/strong&gt; The Trade Fair at the SEC Glasgow presents a prime opportunity to showcase your offerings. Our range of attractions, such as branded games and interactive experiences, can make your stand a standout. With customised branding that aligns with your company's identity, you'll create a lasting impression that lingers long after the exhibition concludes.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Connected Britain (London ExCel): &lt;/strong&gt;Connected Britain at the London ExCel is a hub for innovation and networking. Ensure your stand reflects your brand's forward-thinking approach with our cutting-edge products. From branded &lt;a title="Batak Pro" href="/category/exhibition-games/43/batak-pro"&gt;Batak &lt;/a&gt;to &lt;a title="CASH GRABBER MACHINE HIRE" href="/category/exhibition-games/3/cash-grabber-machine-hire"&gt;Grab a Grand Cash Grabbers&lt;/a&gt;, we have it all. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Fun Pro UK's branded attractions are ideal for drawing crowds to your stands and keeping them there. We have all kinds of quirky branding options on everything from &lt;a title="Pix N Mix Hire" href="/category/fun-foods/42/pix-n-mix-hire"&gt;Pick and Mix stands&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a title="Prize Crane Arcade Grabber" href="/category/arcade-games/47/prize-crane-arcade-grabber"&gt;Prize Claw machines&lt;/a&gt;, so you can tailor our services to perfectly match your corporate identity. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that every season is a busy season for Fun Pro UK, and as always, it's best to book in advance to avoid disappointment! We work on a first-come first-served basis, so it's in your interests to snap up all the products you want as early as possible. Use our online booking system to get started today!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All products are of a commercial-quality, are PAT-tested when required, are subject to routine inspections, and are set up and cleaned properly to ensure they're totally safe and immaculately clean. We know how important quality is at exhibitions and corporate events, so we do our utmost to ensure our services are second-to-none. &lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>It's never too early to think about Christmas parties!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-07-28/its-never-too-early-to-think-about-christmas-parties</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-07-28/its-never-too-early-to-think-about-christmas-parties</guid><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jul 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;The warmth of summer may still surround us, but at Fun Pro UK, we're already preparing for the most magical time of the year - Christmas! While it may seem early to talk about the holiday season, we believe in getting a head start to ensure that your Christmas party is nothing short of spectacular. With our wide range of exciting&lt;a title="Christmas Game Hire " href="/category/christmas-game-hire"&gt; Christmas party games for hire&lt;/a&gt;, you can beat the December rush and secure the best entertainment for a celebration that will be talked about for years to come!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the days lead up to Christmas, our schedule fills up rapidly with bookings from enthusiastic clients eager to host holiday parties. By booking early, you can secure your preferred date and take advantage of our full selection of games, including some of our most popular festive products. Don't wait until the holiday rush begins; be proactive and get your Christmas party preparations underway with Fun Pro UK!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Huge Range of Christmas Party Entertainment&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Christmas party games are designed to bring joy and excitement to your corporate celebration. Whether you're planning an intimate office gathering or a grand festive celebration, we have the entertainment you need to make it merry and bright. Here's a glimpse of what awaits you:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="CHRISTMAS PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/christmas-game-hire/12/christmas-photo-booths"&gt;Christmas Photo Booth&lt;/a&gt;: Capture the spirit of the season with our Christmas-themed photo booth. Decked out in festive props and backdrops, it's the perfect way to create lasting memories and provide guests with cherished keepsakes from the celebration.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="Christmas Grotto Hire " href="/category/christmas-grotto-hire"&gt;Santa's Grotto&lt;/a&gt;: Add some family-friendly fun to your Christmas event with our range of Santa's Grottos for hire. Step inside and say hello to Father Christmas himself! &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="Reindeer Nosenado (Christmas Ballnado Hire )" href="/category/christmas-game-hire/65/reindeer-nosenado-christmas-ballnado-hire"&gt;Rudolph Nosenado&lt;/a&gt;: Step into a winter wonderland with our Rudolph Nosenado. This unique game puts a fun twist on the classic&lt;a title="CASH GRABBER MACHINE HIRE" href="/category/exhibition-games/3/cash-grabber-machine-hire"&gt; cash grabber&lt;/a&gt; concept, replacing money with red Rudolph noses. Guests will love the challenge of grabbing as many noses as they can; you could even give prizes to the winners. &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a title="Dance Machine" href="/category/arcade-games/39/dance-machine"&gt;Dance Machine&lt;/a&gt;: Light up the dance floor and get your guests moving with our Dance Machine! From holiday classics to contemporary hits, this game is all about letting loose and stepping in time with the beat. Show off your skills to some of your favourite Christmas pop songs! &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; This Christmas, let Fun Pro UK be your partner in creating a corporate party that truly sparkles. December can be busy for us, so book in advance so you don't miss the chance to secure your preferred date and the best selection of games. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Unleash the festive fun with Fun Pro UK, and let's make this Christmas the most memorable one yet!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Make Trade Shows Fun with Branded Exhibition Games</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-07-14/make-trade-shows-fun-with-branded-exhibition-games</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-07-14/make-trade-shows-fun-with-branded-exhibition-games</guid><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jul 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Trade shows are a dynamic platform for businesses to connect with potential clients, showcase their products and services, and try to stick in people's minds. In this competitive landscape, standing out at bustling trade shows is key to drawing crowds and capturing attention. At Fun Pro UK, we're here to help you find success at trade shows with our range of &lt;a title="Branded Game Hire" href="/pages/branded-game-hire"&gt;branded games&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
These &lt;a title="Exhibition Games " href="/category/exhibition-games"&gt;exhibition games&lt;/a&gt; offer a powerful solution to increase footfall, engage your target audience, and amplify brand recognition. Check out some popular options below!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Spark excitement and create a whirlwind of fun with our &lt;a title="CASH GRABBER MACHINE HIRE" href="/category/exhibition-games/3/cash-grabber-machine-hire"&gt;Grab a Grand Cash Cube&lt;/a&gt;. As visitors step inside and attempt to grab swirling cash, the energy in the room becomes electric. With your logo emblazoned on the cube, this game generates buzz around your stand and entices attendees to stop and interact.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Challenge attendees' reflexes and coordination with our thrilling &lt;a title="Batak Lite" href="/category/exhibition-games/61/batak-lite"&gt;Batak Lite&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a title="Batak Pro" href="/category/exhibition-games/43/batak-pro"&gt;Batak Pro&lt;/a&gt; game. This fast-paced and addictive game can be branded with your company logo, attracting attention and encouraging passersby to test their skills in the company of your branding. &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Create an inviting and interactive atmosphere with our branded &lt;a title="FOOTBALL TABLES" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/27/football-tables"&gt;Table Football game&lt;/a&gt;. A timeless favourite, this game brings people together for friendly competition and fosters a relaxed and engaging environment. With your branding prominently displayed on the table, you enhance brand recognition and initiate conversations that can lead to valuable connections.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Ignite curiosity and showcase your brand's ingenuity with our &lt;a title="Crack The Code safe cracker" href="/category/exhibition-games/37/crack-the-code-safe-cracker"&gt;Crack the Code game&lt;/a&gt;. Attendees are challenged to crack the secret code, driving engagement and creating a buzz around your stand. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With Fun Pro UK's branded games, you have the power to unleash success at trade shows. These interactive attractions not only attract attention but also create memorable experiences that set you apart from your competitors. The combination of excitement, friendly competition, and brand exposure guarantees increased footfall, engagement, and the opportunity to generate valuable leads.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our experienced team is ready to help you choose the perfect branded games for your trade show objectives. We handle everything from setup to dismantling, allowing you to focus on connecting with attendees and showcasing your offerings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Don't miss out on the chance to make a lasting impact at your next trade show. Speak with our team to discuss your requirements and let us help you unlock the potential for success with our range of branded games - just visit our &lt;a title="Contact Fun Pro UK" href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;contact page&lt;/a&gt; to see how to tell us about what you need. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Remember, when it comes to trade shows, standing out is essential. Let Fun Pro UK be your partner in creating a show-stopping experience that leaves a lasting impression on attendees and sets your brand apart from the competition.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Showcasing at the NEC? We're local branded exhibition stand game experts!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-05-11/showcasing-at-the-nec-were-local-branded-exhibition-stand-game-experts</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-05-11/showcasing-at-the-nec-were-local-branded-exhibition-stand-game-experts</guid><pubDate>Thu, 11 May 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Are you ready to take your exhibition presence to the next level? Based in Birmingham and the West Midlands, we at Fun Pro UK are your go-to destination for &lt;a title="NEC Birmingham" href="/pages/nec-birmingham"&gt;exhibition stand game hire at the NEC Birmingham&lt;/a&gt;! With our range of branded games and top-notch services, we're here to inject a dose of excitement and make your exhibition stand truly unforgettable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a local company for&lt;a title="NEC Event Hire" href="/pages/nec-event-hire"&gt; NEC event hire&lt;/a&gt;, we've had the pleasure of working with countless professionals just like you. We understand the importance of making a lasting impression on your audience, and that's why we've curated an exceptional collection of &lt;a title="Exhibition Games " href="/category/exhibition-games"&gt;exhibition games&lt;/a&gt; that are sure to turn heads and draw crowds.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Brace yourself for an immersive and entertaining experience as we introduce you to some of our star attractions for &lt;a title="Branded Game Hire" href="/pages/branded-game-hire"&gt;branded game hire&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Branded Wheel of Fortune&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Step right up and give our branded &lt;a title="Prize Wheel" href="/category/prize-games/49/prize-wheel"&gt;Prize Wheel&lt;/a&gt; a spin! We recently had the pleasure of showcasing this game at the NEC Birmingham, with bespoke branding and prizes tailored specifically to the event, the Prize Wheel became an instant hit. It's not just about winning prizes; it's about creating a buzz, generating excitement, and getting visitors flocking to your exhibition stand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Ballnado&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prepare for a whirlwind of fun with our &lt;a title="Ballnado Grabber" href="/category/exhibition-games/36/ballnado-grabber"&gt;Ballnado game&lt;/a&gt;! While the photo might reveal a slight mishap (we promise it won't happen at your event!), rest assured that we prioritize safety and ensure that everything is securely installed. Ballnado offers a unique and interactive way to captivate your audience, leaving a lasting impression as they immerse themselves in the game's excitement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Prize Crane Claw Machine&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Remember the thrill of trying to grab a prize from a claw machine? Well, imagine that thrill with your own branding! Our branded &lt;a title="Prize Crane Arcade Grabber" href="/category/arcade-games/47/prize-crane-arcade-grabber"&gt;Prize Crane&lt;/a&gt; is a guaranteed crowd-pleaser. As participants try their luck, your brand takes centre stage, amplifying your visibility and leaving a lasting impression on attendees. This &lt;a title="Arcade Games " href="/category/arcade-games"&gt;arcade game&lt;/a&gt; is an opportunity to create a playful connection with your target audience while promoting your products or services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Batak Lite Speed Reaction Game&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you're looking for a game that gets hearts racing and reflexes sharpened, look no further than the &lt;a title="Batak Lite" href="/category/exhibition-games/61/batak-lite"&gt;Batak Lite Speed Reaction Game&lt;/a&gt;. With a bespoke branded backboard showcasing your design, this game becomes a powerful tool for promoting your brand while delivering a thrilling experience. Leave visitors in awe of your brand's agility!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our game lineup doesn't stop there. The range of products we have seems almost endless! You'll find something that speaks to your brand and attracts your target audience with us. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We pride ourselves on our close collaboration with stand builders at the NEC. We seamlessly integrate our games into your exhibition space, ensuring a smooth and hassle-free experience for you and your team. Our mission is to provide you with engaging, branded games that amplify your presence, spark conversations, and create memorable moments for your audience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So, if you're ready to elevate your exhibition experience to new heights, let Fun Pro UK be your guide. Get in touch with us today, and let's make your next exhibition a resounding success!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Stay tuned for more exciting updates, industry insights, and game spotlights in the world of exhibition hire. Together, let's redefine what it means to stand out at the NEC!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Boost Your Staff's Wellbeing with Fun Pro UK's Entertainment Hire</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-04-25/boost-your-staffs-wellbeing-with-fun-pro-uks-entertainment-hire</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-04-25/boost-your-staffs-wellbeing-with-fun-pro-uks-entertainment-hire</guid><pubDate>Tue, 25 Apr 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;As companies across the UK focus more on employee wellbeing, there's an increasing trend for businesses to &lt;a title="Office &amp;amp; Corporate Game Entertainment" href="/pages/office-and-corporate-entertainment"&gt;hire office entertainment equipment&lt;/a&gt; to support staff health and happiness. With Fun Pro UK, it's easier than ever for businesses to access a range of equipment designed to improve wellbeing in the workplace.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Employee wellbeing is essential for the smooth running of any organisation. Happy employees mean lower staff turnover, higher productivity, and more motivated workers. We have plenty of cool ideas that could help you boost worker satisfaction and keep your business flowing as it should. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Sports and Exercise Equipment&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Regular exercise is essential for physical and mental health. By hiring sports exercise equipment such as &lt;a title="Batak Pro" href="/category/exhibition-games/43/batak-pro"&gt;Batak Lite&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="Batak Pro" href="/category/exhibition-games/43/batak-pro"&gt;Batak Pro&lt;/a&gt; or even something as simple as &lt;a title="Air Hockey Table Hire" href="/category/exhibition-games/60/air-hockey-table-hire"&gt;Air Hockey&lt;/a&gt;, businesses can encourage employees to take a break and get moving during the workday. Not only does this improve physical health, but it can also boosts people's mood and productivity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Games and Entertainment&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;Corporate entertainment equipment and games&lt;/a&gt; can have a significant impact on employee wellbeing. We have many options such as &lt;a title="FOOTBALL TABLES" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/27/football-tables"&gt;table football&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="Air Hockey Table Hire" href="/category/exhibition-games/60/air-hockey-table-hire"&gt;arcade claw grabbers&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="RETRO ARCADE GAMES" href="/category/arcade-games/4/retro-arcade-games"&gt;retro arcade games&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a title="Racing Car Simulators" href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;Racing Car Simulators&lt;/a&gt; that can provide a much-needed break from work, reducing stress levels and helping employee morale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Outdoor Equipment&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Getting outside and enjoying fresh air is vital for physical and mental health. By hiring equipment such as &lt;a title="LARGE BOUNCY CASTLES" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/23/large-bouncy-castles"&gt;adult bouncy castles&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a title="Dash &amp;amp; Grab / Hungry Hippo Inflatable Game" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/32/dash-and-grab-hungry-hippo-inflatable-game"&gt;human hungry hippos&lt;/a&gt;, businesses can draw their staff into the great outdoors to enjoy themselves. &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
By hiring equipment from Fun Pro UK, companies from London, Manchester, Birmingham, Leeds and throughout the country can show employees that they care about their wellbeing. We make hiring office entertainment equipment easy, with nationwide delivery and a wide range of products available. Just look through our website and make a booking online! &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;em&gt;At Fun Pro UK, we're committed to helping businesses promote employee wellbeing. &lt;a title="Contact Fun Pro UK" href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;Speak with us today&lt;/a&gt; to find out more about our range of equipment and how it can benefit your business. With our expert help, you can support employee wellbeing and enjoy a happier, more motivated workforce.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Happy Easter! Prepare for Summertime Fun!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-04-06/happy-easter-prepare-for-summertime-fun</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-04-06/happy-easter-prepare-for-summertime-fun</guid><pubDate>Thu, 06 Apr 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;At Fun Pro UK, we want to wish everyone a very happy Easter! Whether you're celebrating with family, friends, or just enjoying some time off work, we hope you have a fun and festive holiday. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As we head towards the warmer months, we're excited to offer a range of party equipment and games for hire that are perfect for making the most of the sunshine. We have a spectacular array of products on offer for you, and we're here to help you make your next event one to remember. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So let's all hop into the summer with joy and positivity, and celebrate the season in style!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Summertime Party Fun&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/img-20220617-wa0004.jpg" style="width: 150px; height: 113px; float: left; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;Summer is fast approaching and with it comes the promise of warm days, long evenings and fun in the sun at all kinds of&lt;a title="Summer Entertainment" href="/pages/summer-entertainment"&gt; summer events&lt;/a&gt;. Whether you're planning a family BBQ, a birthday party, a garden soiree, a &lt;a title="Weddings" href="/category/weddings"&gt;wedding&lt;/a&gt;, a &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;corporate event &lt;/a&gt;or any other special summertime celebration, Fun Pro UK has everything you need to make it a summer to remember. We are the go-to place for all your entertainment needs, with a wide range of fun products available for hire that will get everyone in the party mood.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Some of of our most popular products during the summertime are our inflatable slides. Our &lt;a title="SUPER SLIDES" href="/category/fun-days/26/super-slides"&gt;Super Slides&lt;/a&gt; are a huge hit with both kids and adults alike, with some featuring double alleys for some friendly competition. You could raise the heat even further with our &lt;a title="GLADIATOR DUEL" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/22/gladiator-duel"&gt;Gladiator Duel!&lt;/a&gt;, or get everyone involved with our &lt;a title="HUMAN TABLE FOOTBALL" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/19/human-table-football"&gt;Human Table Football&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you're not looking for high-octane fun and would prefer something a little more relaxed, don't fret. We have a whole range of Giant Garden Games that are perfect for even the smallest of gardens. From&lt;a title="Giant Jenga Hire" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/44/giant-jenga-hire"&gt; Giant Garden Jenga &lt;/a&gt;to &lt;a title="Giant Connect 4 Game Hire" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/45/giant-connect-4-game-hire"&gt;Giant Connect Four&lt;/a&gt;, you'll have something to entertain young and old with Fun Pro UK. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And what better time to enjoy a drink from our slush machine than while outdoors at a summertime event? People will be queuing for their turn!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/20220609-174158.jpg" style="width: 450px; height: 234px; vertical-align: middle;" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
But it's not just our products that are fantastic - our service is too. We pride ourselves on our punctuality and reliability, delivering our premium quality products right to your doorstep no matter where you are in the UK. And with our commercial grade equipment, you can be sure that everything we stock is built to last, making it perfect for those warm summer afternoons of fun and games.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Book your summer party entertainment today through our website and get ready for a summer to remember. And if you need any assistance, don't hesitate to &lt;a title="Contact Fun Pro UK" href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk"&gt;contact us &lt;/a&gt;- we're always here to help.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Awesome Event Ideas from Fun Pro UK</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-03-20/awesome-event-ideas-from-fun-pro-uk</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-03-20/awesome-event-ideas-from-fun-pro-uk</guid><pubDate>Mon, 20 Mar 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Are you planning an event but don't know where to start? Look no further than Fun Pro UK! We offer an extensive range of &lt;a title="Event Type" href="/pages/event-type"&gt;event ideas&lt;/a&gt; to help you create an unforgettable experience for your guests. Our packages are tailored to suit a variety of events, from corporate exhibitions to school fun days, charity fundraising events, evening events, summer parties and everything else.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Event Ideas for All Occasions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;a title="Exhibition Games " href="/category/exhibition-games"&gt;Exhibitions &lt;/a&gt;are a fantastic way to showcase your products or services, and we can help you make a lasting impression with branded games and attention-grabbing stalls such as our&lt;a title="Prize Wheel" href="/category/prize-games/49/prize-wheel"&gt; Prize Wheel&lt;/a&gt;. Our team of event planners are loaded with&lt;a title="Exhibition Game Hire" href="/pages/exhibition-game-hire"&gt; exhibition entertainment ideas&lt;/a&gt;, and can work with you to create a professional platform to showcase your brand and attract a targeted audience.&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Whack%20a%20mole/37e0bbea736ba19a7e6043fe17d3f2df.jpeg" style="width: 250px; height: 188px; float: right; margin-left: 5px;" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
If you're planning a &lt;a title="School Fun Day Entertainment Hire" href="/pages/school-fun-day-entertainment-hire"&gt;school fun day&lt;/a&gt;, keep students entertained with a range of fun and interactive activities. Our packages include &lt;a title="Bungee Run" href="/category/fun-days/33/bungee-run"&gt;bungee runs&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="GLADIATOR DUEL" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/22/gladiator-duel"&gt;gladiator duels&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt; photo booths&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="Arcade Games " href="/category/arcade-games"&gt;arcade games&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;a title="Fun Foods " href="/category/fun-foods"&gt; fun food machines&lt;/a&gt;, and a whole lot more. We'll work with you to create a package that's tailored to your school's needs and budget, ensuring that your students have a memorable experience.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
For an elegant &lt;a title="Evening Entertainment" href="/pages/evening-entertainment"&gt;evening event&lt;/a&gt;, our team of professionals can help you create a sophisticated and glamorous experience that your guests will never forget. Whether it's guests at a &lt;a title="Fundraising Event ideas" href="/pages/fundraising-event-ideas"&gt;charity fundraiser&lt;/a&gt; or colleagues at a &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;corporate party&lt;/a&gt;, you're certain to find some fun and engaging activities that will keep your guests partying through the night with us. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/20220324-125141.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 136px; float: left; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;And with summer just around the corner, it's time to start planning your next &lt;a title="Summer Entertainment" href="/pages/summer-entertainment"&gt;summer party&lt;/a&gt;. Our summer party packages include a range of activities that will make the long summer holidays fly by. You'll certainly hold a summertime soiree that hits the right spots with our &lt;a title="SUPER SLIDES" href="/category/fun-days/26/super-slides"&gt;inflatable slides&lt;/a&gt; and garden games such as &lt;a title="Giant Jenga Hire" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/44/giant-jenga-hire"&gt;Giant Jenga&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;If you're planning a corporate exhibition, a school fun day, a charity fundraising event, an evening event, or a summer party, Fun Pro UK has got you covered with an extensive range of event ideas. Contact us today to learn more about our packages and start planning an unforgettable experience for your guests!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Party Hire Experts: Looking forwards to March Events</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-03-01/party-hire-experts-looking-forwards-to-march-events</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2023-03-01/party-hire-experts-looking-forwards-to-march-events</guid><pubDate>Wed, 01 Mar 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;We're thrilled to share some exciting updates about our event supply services and game hire options as we kick off the month of March.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Fun Pro UK, we specialise in providing game hire services for a variety of events, such as exhibitions, trade shows, and conferences. With our bespoke &lt;a title="Branded Game Hire" href="/pages/branded-game-hire"&gt;branded game hire&lt;/a&gt; options, we can personalise the games to include branding and enhance brand activation, footfall, engagement, attraction, and sales.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our games are a huge success at events, and we've received many compliments on our diverse range of options. Our selection includes&lt;a title="Batak Pro" href="/category/exhibition-games/43/batak-pro"&gt; Batak Pro&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="Batak Lite" href="/category/exhibition-games/61/batak-lite"&gt;Batak Lite&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="Crack The Code safe cracker" href="/category/exhibition-games/37/crack-the-code-safe-cracker"&gt;Crack the Code&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="Prize Crane Arcade Grabber" href="/category/arcade-games/47/prize-crane-arcade-grabber"&gt;Prize Crane/Claw Machine&lt;/a&gt;, and more. We've also included some photos of these games in action at recent exhibitions for you to see.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/batak23.jpg" alt="Batak Hire" style="width: 300px; height: 315px;" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We're proud to offer our services throughout the UK, ensuring that every event we're a part of is a success. Whether you're planning a small event or a large-scale exhibition, we've got you covered! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/crackcode.jpg" alt="Crack the Code Hire" title="Crack the Code Game" style="width: 300px; height: 298px; vertical-align: middle;" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here are some upcoming events to look forward to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;St David's Day - today is Saint David's Day! For parties today or this weekend, Fun Pro UK is the team you can always trust. &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;St Patrick's Day - March 17th is Saint Patrick's Day! There'll be plenty of wild events taking place throughout the UK and Ireland, as well as internationally. Make sure fun is a part of your upcoming events! &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;International Women's Day - while there are plenty of big celebrations and parties taking place on March 8th, you can also enjoy the Fun Pro UK service at conferences, awards shows, and high-class corporate events. &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;First Day of Spring - March 20th marks the first day of Spring. Put your winter coats away and come out to play with Fun Pro UK!&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/20211128-122518.jpg" alt="Air Hockey Table Hire" title="Event Hire - Air Hockey Table" style="width: 300px; height: 136px;" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Your Event Hire Experts&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Fun Pro UK, we take pride in providing the best event hire services throughout the UK. We have been in the business for many years and have established ourselves as a trusted partner for all occasions. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One of the key reasons to choose Fun Pro UK for your event hire needs is our diverse range of game hire options. We understand that every event is unique and requires different types of entertainment, so we make sure we offer everything you could possibly need! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are committed to providing exceptional service to our clients. We believe that every event is special and deserves the utmost attention to detail. Our experienced team works closely with our clients to understand their requirements and provide tailored solutions that fit their specific needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Fun Pro UK, we also understand the importance of reliability and professionalism. That's why we always arrive on time, set up quickly and efficiently, and provide a service that puts you first.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Book online today! Just look through our website to see more. &lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Happy 40th to the Boss!!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2022-03-25/happy-40th-to-the-boss</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2022-03-25/happy-40th-to-the-boss</guid><pubDate>Fri, 25 Mar 2022 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Happy 40th to the Boss!!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When we received a last minute call asking how we can help with a 40th birthday celebration at a work place in Nuneaton, Warwickshire yesterday we quickly put our thinking caps on!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It was all a big surprise, the staff were arranging a celebration for the boss at their work place.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;How exciting! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Fun Pro Team jumped into action thinking what we had available at such short notice and which game from the huge variety of fun games we stock, would be best for everyone to enjoy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team didn't take long before they came up with the ultimate fantastic game,... Bully!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bully as he is lovingly known is Fun Pro's friendly &lt;a title="Rodeo Bull" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/46/rodeo-bull"&gt;rodeo bull&lt;/a&gt;. He loves to come out for parties and events, as long as he has been fed and watered by the team he will perform for the crowd with his twists and turns ensuring not many people stay on his back for long!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When we came up with the idea for the party our clients were in awe as they were struggling to think of a special game they could hire for their do!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Fun Pro delivery team set Bully up in pride of place, he was ready for the festivities to begin! The birthday boy was the first contestant to see how long he could hang on - all on his 40th birthday too! Bully was in a good mood that day, the twisting and turning began, the crowd gathered to see how long their boss could possibly hang on for.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; As the seconds went by it was all looking so good, maybe Bully decided to have the last laugh with the birthday boy? Before we knew it Bully was riding solo, we could hear a little tune with the lyrics ' I'm gonna take my horse to the old town road, I'm gonna ride til i can't no more!' Maybe we have a singing bull as well??&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The laughter subsided and the boss did a great job but i don't think he will become a cowboy anytime soon!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Each staff member had a go at keeping Bully under control, it was a great birthday celebration that all staff members took part in and loved every minute especially the boss! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Happy 40th Birthday from the Fun Pro Team!!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/20220324-125141.jpg" style="width: 1000px; height: 453px;" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>January doesn't have to be Blue!!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2022-01-04/january-doesnt-have-to-be-blue</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2022-01-04/january-doesnt-have-to-be-blue</guid><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jan 2022 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 18px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #00b0f0;"&gt;January doesn't have to be Blue!!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;December is always a very busy month for everyone, before we know it we are wrapping up the last present, licking the envelope and hoping it's not too late to catch the postman in time for the big day! It is hard to arrange a date that everyone can make and enjoy for parties.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;If you didn't get round to arranging that all important staff Christmas Party then not to worry - why not arrange a January bash? &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Here are Fun Pro's top reasons why it&amp;rsquo;s great to hold a staff &lt;a title="party games hire" href="/pages/party-games-hire"&gt;Christmas Party&lt;/a&gt; in January!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;With the cold, dark winter weather and the festivities of Christmas over for another year January is known for 'January Blues!' But it doesn't have to be!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Why not bring celebration and cheer to the month by holding your festive office party. There are so many events for people to attend in December that your staff will be glad of a party or two to attend in January!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 18px;"&gt; &lt;strong&gt;CELEBRATE YOUR TEAM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;January is a great time to gather your team together and ensure they feel valued for all the hard work they completed in the run up to Christmas. Everyone is so busy in the work place that sometimes your team miss the opportunity to develop friendships and relationships. Throwing a party away from the work place will allow your staff to be themselves - let their hair down and enjoy each others company. Use the event as a way to motivate your team for the new challenges this year that lie ahead. A little bit of team spirit goes a long way!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 18px;"&gt; &lt;strong&gt;SAVE THE DATE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Diaries and calendars won't be quite so manic during January. Take this opportunity to save the date and arrange when to have your staff office party. The turn out should be high as you will not be competing with other festive events such as School Plays, Christmas Shopping, Carol singing etc that your guests have already committed to attend.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 18px;"&gt; &lt;strong&gt;NO TINSEL OR TURKEY &lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/img-20211217-wa0004.jpg" style="width: 250px; height: 334px; float: right; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Fed up of tinsel and turkey? This is a fabulous reason to organise your Office Party in the new year, nobody will want another turkey dinner! Break free from the Christmas theming and celebrate in style. Why not create a themed evening? A James Bond themed event is very popular with a&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt; photobooth&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;casino tables&lt;/strong&gt;. Maybe a retro game themed evening with &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a title="Arcade Games " href="/category/arcade-games"&gt;Arcade Machines&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Football Tables&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Basketball games&lt;/strong&gt; to keep your guests entertained. There will not be a Christmas Tree or cracker insight!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;So, go on - what are you waiting for? Get that date in the diary and arrange your Christmas Office Party in January, it will be the best party ever!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>FUN PRO UK AND COVID-19</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2020-03-16/fun-pro-uk-and-covid-19</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2020-03-16/fun-pro-uk-and-covid-19</guid><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2020 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;div&gt;Fun Pro Uk and COVID-19&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We are continuing to work hard with our clients and venues to support everyone in this uncertain time that we are all experiencing.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Our main aim here at Fun Pro UK is always the health and safety of our clients.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We are currently receiving up to date advice from the UK Government and will be guided by the advice issued.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We understand that this is a difficult time in our industry but are working to re-schedule your events for the future.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We are here to support all of our clients just as we have been before and will continue to do so from our homes.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our office is closed for now but will be back with the FUN soon!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stay in touch&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Call our team on : 02476 629197&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email: &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/clear-back-ground-logo.png" alt="Fun Pro UK" style="width: 150px; height: 188px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Why Should Your Company Consider Hosting Staff Events?</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2020-03-04/why-should-your-company-consider-hosting-staff-events</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2020-03-04/why-should-your-company-consider-hosting-staff-events</guid><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2020 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 24px;"&gt;Why Should Your Company Consider Hosting Staff Events?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;Whether you are considering an annual award ceremony, a dinner or a summer party, there are far greater benefits than just getting your team to let their hair down&lt;strong&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt;Everyone loves a good party, right? Well hosting events for your business could be bringing your company benefits that you may not be aware of, including validating your employees, promoting creativity and boosting productivity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 24px;"&gt;Validating your Employees&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 24px;"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Hungry%20Hippos/20190607-142841.jpg" alt="Human football" style="width: 250px; height: 188px; float: right; margin-left: 5px;" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Having an &lt;a title="Company Award Ceremonies" href="/category/company-award-ceremonies"&gt;award ceremony&lt;/a&gt; is a great way of showing your appreciation to staff,by rewarding performance or company culture and values. These awards will make an employee feel valued, important and like they are having an impact on the business. Which overall will do wonders for the productivity when they are back in the office.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If your business has just brought in a big deal or had a great quarter, why not celebrate it? Bring in the client for employees to meet, as everyone loves to be acknowledged for their work. Celebrating the success within a workplace builds the company culture, which in the long term will bring in improved talent!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Overall, everyone wants to feel appreciated for what they bring to the table, so don&amp;rsquo;t forget to celebrate this by hosting a celebration for your team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 24px;"&gt;Promotes Creativity within your Team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Taking your staff out of their usual environment can often help them think differently and foster collaboration to solve problems This is particularly the case during team building events but can also be done during the breakout sessions at &lt;a title="Conference Game Hire" href="/pages/conference-game-hire"&gt;conferences&lt;/a&gt; and long meetings. Collaborating with those outside their usual departments can also help individuals produce fresh new ideas and think outside the box. This is extremely helpful when they return to the office, as they may begin thinking in a new way to solve issues.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Having a company event will give your team the chance to step away from the daily drive for results allow their creative side to shine. Without the daily pressure you might discover the hidden creative potential of some of your team resulting in huge benefits to your business. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 24px;"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/teamwork-transparent-background-8.png" alt="Team Work" style="width: 200px; height: 165px; float: right; margin-left: 5px;" /&gt;Boosting Company Morale&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Celebrating successes has proven to be beneficial in creating happy and engaged employees who feel part of the organisation rather than a cog in the corporate machine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Almost every job will have some level of stress with deadlines,targets and customer demands, but hosting a staff-based event will give everyone the chance to take a step back and relax with those they work so closely with. Having an event or celebration after a big project or a busy season will give your team that chance to recharge and improve the well-being for everyone involved.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When morale is high, teams are naturally more motivated and productivity goes through the roof. So, give your teams an event to motivate them to work hard and succeed then reward that with a celebration!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>All work, no play? We really need to talk about that!!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2020-01-20/all-work-no-play-we-really-need-to-talk-about-that</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2020-01-20/all-work-no-play-we-really-need-to-talk-about-that</guid><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2020 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 28px;"&gt;All work, no play? We really need to talk about that!!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px;"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Fundays/20180616-152805.jpg" alt="Fun days" style="width: 200px; height: 151px; float: right; margin-left: 5px;" /&gt;Show your staff how to party this summer with inflatables and interactive games for all ages.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why host a family &lt;a title="Fun Days" href="/category/fun-days"&gt;fun day&lt;/a&gt; with a single bouncy castle and a small BBQ, when Fun Pro UK can work with you to make the best use of your space and show your team and their families what a real summer party is! With a wide range of inflatables from both adults and children&amp;rsquo;s bouncy castles to inflatable assault course and tv classics such as Total Wipe Out, we have everything you need this summer! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Why not host your own Company Carnival!&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px;"&gt;Slide to the fun&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These huge, colourful inflatables stand head and shoulders above everything else and draw the crowds in from far and wide. Making an exciting centre piece that everyone will want to have a go and they can! All our super slides are built for both children and adults, so no one is left out of the fun! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px;"&gt;&lt;a title="PLUCK A DUCK RACING" href="/category/arcade-games/8/pluck-a-duck-racing"&gt;Pluck that Duck&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/duck%20game/unadjustednonraw-thumb-9d21-768x1024.jpg" alt="Pluck the duck hire" style="width: 125px; height: 167px; float: left; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;Have you got what it takes? The concentration and nerves of steel to go head to head to free all five ducks, or race against the clock to be the fastest duck-freer at your company! This very silly but highly addictive interactive game really puts your skills to the test, as an adaption of the classic operation, as you use an electromagnet on the pole to free all the ducks. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All getting a bit warm, well cool down with some ice cream delivered by tricycle!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s better than having fresh ice cream served at your event? With 40 flavours to pick from, you will have a hard time narrowing it down! We can even brand the tricycle to your company&amp;rsquo;s colours and logo to make it fit perfectly into your company carnival.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px;"&gt;Get your team jumping and diving&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;a title="TOTAL WIPE OUT" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/20/total-wipe-out"&gt;Total Wipeout&lt;/a&gt; game will get everyone involved and laughing as six opponents battle it out to be crowned the Total Wipeout King or Queen! Don&amp;rsquo;t worry about being dislodged as you are guaranteed a soft landing with the squishy inflatable floor. We are sure that this inflatable hire will be busy all day at your event, as it is a hit with both adventurous adults and fearless children! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px;"&gt;Make the most of your Summer Family Fun Day!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whether you are just looking for a single inflatable or want to push the boat out with a special package deal, the experts at Fun Pro UK are on hand to help you make the most of this year&amp;rsquo;s &lt;a title="Fun Days" href="/category/fun-days"&gt;summer family fun day&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NtWF3ajxGYo?autoplay=0" width="400" height="300" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contact us on &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email: &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk" target="_blank"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tel: 02476 629 197&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Conference Entertainment - Keep your guests entertained this year!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2020-01-07/conference-entertainment-keep-your-guests-entertained-this-year</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2020-01-07/conference-entertainment-keep-your-guests-entertained-this-year</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2020 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2&gt; Conference Entertainment&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px;"&gt;Keep your guests entertained this year!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Enhance your corporate conference and make it one to remember!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Hire some interactive entertainment to keep everyone entertained throughout the day.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Corporate conferences can get a bad reputation for being boring.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Well, let us help you change that! Fun Pro UK offer an amazing range of corporate interactive entertainment that will take your conference to the next level. With entertainment of all sizes, we are bound to find the perfect piece for you and your venue.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px;"&gt;Compact and highly portable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Stike%20a%20light/20190619-160019.jpg" alt="Lights out reaction game hire" style="width: 250px; height: 188px; float: right; margin-left: 5px;" /&gt;Our strike a light game is the perfect moveable piece of event entertainment that will give your delegates the opportunity to get moving and test their reflexes, making break time far more entertaining! This electronic reaction game gives two opponents the chance to battle head to head across the table, tapping the lights as they show. The large digital scoreboard also allows all those watching to see who&amp;rsquo;s winning and cheer the players on. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Being only 1.5m by 1m this game is perfect for all venues and can be set up almost anywhere from your break room, the side of the canteen or in the reception once your conference has started. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px;"&gt;Twin hoops for head to head fun&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Put your guests slam-dunk skills to the test with Fun Pro UK&amp;rsquo;s classic arcade style electronic&lt;a title="ELECTRONIC BASKET BALL HIRE" href="/category/arcade-games/6/electronic-basket-ball-hire"&gt; basketball game&lt;/a&gt;. Having two hoops allows challengers to play head to head to be crowned king or queen of the hoops! This self-contained game creates an instant, pop up court in any location in your venue, with the side netting and printed canvas ball catcher there to contain the fun. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px;"&gt;The prize is up to you!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Our &lt;a title="CASH GRABBER MACHINE HIRE" href="/category/exhibition-games/3/cash-grabber-machine-hire"&gt;Grab A Grand machine&lt;/a&gt; is a definite favourite with all event attendees. Whether you fill it with tokens or actual cash, there is no better thrill than trying to grab and snatch as much as you can, while the clock ticks down. This is a huge crowd pleaser wherever you place it within your conference, with guests being drawn towards the fun!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px;"&gt;Build the competition&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Why not get your delegates to battle throughout the conference, with the top scores being placed on the leader board. Each guest can see who&amp;rsquo;s winning, allowing them to get more competitive and try again and again to win! Why not make it worthwhile by announcing a prize at the start of the day for the winner of each game when the conference finishes. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Inspired to bring entertainment into your next conference? Contact our expert team at &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Email: &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk" target="_blank"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px;"&gt;Tel: 02476 629 197&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>It's not too late!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-12-01/its-not-too-late</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-12-01/its-not-too-late</guid><pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2 style="text-align: center';"&gt;There's still time to book your Christmas party fun!&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Well it's officially December and the countdown to Christmas can start in earnest. It's now acceptable to put up your Christmas decorations and tree, start playing Christmas carols and order the all-important turkey. The Christmas party season is also in full swing with work parties, and gatherings with family and friends.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
If you've suddenly realised that you haven't organised the Christmas party fun, the good news is that you're not too late. At Fun Pro we still have some availability on selected dates for our Christmas Grotto's, Christmas photo booths and interactive games.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px';"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Dance%20Machine/dance-1.jpg" alt="Christmas Dance Machine Hire" style="width: 150px' height: 200px' float: right' margin-right: 5px';"&gt;Interactive games&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;If you're looking for something a little more active for your Christmas party, then one, or a few, of our interactive games can really add some excitement. Our new &lt;a title="Dance Machine" href="/category/arcade-games/39/dance-machine"&gt;Dance Machine&lt;/a&gt;, which sees players trying to keep up with the dance moves on the screen, will have everyone up and dancing, and is just as fun for spectators as those busting out the moves. While our Twin Racing Car and &lt;a title="VR Race Car Simulator" href="/category/arcade-games/38/vr-race-car-simulator"&gt;VR Race Car Simulators&lt;/a&gt; will unearth the rev heads at the party and bring out a bit of healthy competition. We also have a Grab A Grand machine and the Crack the Code Safe Cracker game, which can be a great way to reward staff with some bonus Christmas presents.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px';"&gt;Christmas Photo booths with props&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Photo%20Booth/20171214-173433.jpg" alt="Christmas Photo Booth Hire" style="width: 120px' height: 92px' float: left' margin-right: 5px';"&gt;Everyone loves a &lt;a title="CHRISTMAS PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/christmas-game-hire/12/christmas-photo-booths"&gt;Photo Booth&lt;/a&gt; and our Winter themed booths are a fantastic way of capturing your party guest's festive fun. Party goers will love diving into the festive props box and posing with their friends &amp;amp; colleagues to celebrate the silly season. Our Magic Selfie Mirror also captures those fun festive photos and comes with a few cheeky compliments from the Mirror.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px';"&gt;Christmas Grottos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Christmas%20Grotto/20171222-105153.jpg" alt="Christmas Grotto Hire " style="width: 190px' height: 145px' float: right' margin-left: 5px';"&gt;Nothing says Christmas more than a &lt;a title="Christmas Grotto Hire " href="/category/christmas-grotto-hire"&gt;Christmas Grotto&lt;/a&gt;. Our inflatable Grottos are the perfect place for children and adults alike to visit Santa Claus and ask for their Christmas wish. They really do look festive with snow on the roof and lights in the window and they even come with a white picket fence and a snowman in the garden.
&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
Make your Christmas party one to remember by adding some fun activities to help your guests get in the festive spirit and make magical Christmas memories.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;&lt;br&gt;
GET IN TOUCH NOW:&lt;br&gt;
Email: &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Tel: 02476 629197&lt;br&gt;
Mob: 07769979676&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Christmas Fun!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-11-05/christmas-fun</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-11-05/christmas-fun</guid><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 26px';"&gt;It's that time of year again!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;The elves are busy making presents. The reindeers are in training. And the team at Fun Pro UK are busy spreading Christmas cheer up and down the country with interactive entertainment! &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Who doesn't love Christmas? Here at Fun Pro UK, it is our favourite time of year! And we are all in full swing with our fluffy jumpers and bobbly hats. But most importantly we are delivering exceptional Christmas spirit to many events up and down the country as we countdown to the special day. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px';"&gt;Are you looking for some extra Christmas cheer for your event?&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Photo%20Booth/20171214-173433.jpg" alt="Christmas photo booth" style="width: 250px' height: 188px' float: right';" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;We all know a photo booth is a must have at an employee event. So why not hire one of our&lt;a title="Christmas Photo Booth Hire" href="/pages/christmas-photo-booth-corporate-event-hire"&gt; Christmas photo booths &lt;/a&gt;for your Christmas party or seasonal sales promotion? Whether it is our snowy forest scene or our rustic Santa's cabin. These festive booths are just what any seasonal event needs to bring the setting to life. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Not only is the booth festively designed, we will throw in our fantastic festive prop box! Fit for all events with reindeer ears, funtastic glasses and even Christmas tree hats! These props are guaranteed to bring joy to all those at your festive event! &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px';"&gt;Nothing says Christmas like Santa's Grotto!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Invite your guests into your Christmas event in style, by meeting the man himself, Father Christmas, sitting inside his very own snow covered grotto! &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Fun Pro UK's &lt;a title="Christmas Grotto Hire " href="/category/christmas-grotto-hire"&gt;Christmas grottos&lt;/a&gt; are absolutely perfect for a whole range of seasonal events from university/school Christmas parties, shopping centres, Christmas themed staff parties and seasonal sales promotions. Our authentic snow covered log cabin is ideal for those who are young, and those young at heart!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px';"&gt;Want something unique for your event?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 20px';"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Dance%20Machine/dance-1.jpg" alt="Dance Machine" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-bottom: 5px;" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Our all singing and dancing &lt;a title="Dance Machine" href="/category/arcade-games/39/dance-machine"&gt;dance machine&lt;/a&gt; is the perfect entertainment item to get your guests active at your Christmas party! Why not put your dancing shoes on and get down on the floor showing off your moves! Your guests will be intrigued when they see those shapes being thrown around and will not be able to stop themselves joining in the fun!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Our Top 4 Games for your Christmas Party</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-10-03/our-top-4-games-for-your-christmas-party</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-10-03/our-top-4-games-for-your-christmas-party</guid><pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #00b0f0';"&gt;Christmas&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color: #ff0000';"&gt;Fun &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #00b0f0';"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color: #ff0000';"&gt;Games&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Christmas our favourite times of the year with the excitement and fun that goes into planning for your Christmas event, the #TeamFunPro have everything you need to make sure you have the best games for your event. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Colin says, it's never too early for a mince pie! although, it is a bit too early for Colin to get his Christmas jumper out!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Have you thought about when to hold your Christmas party? &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Have you been tasked with organising the office Christmas party this year? Your colleagues probably won't want the same as last year, and it's never too early to choose a date for your Christmas event, venues get booked up so quickly. Tis the season to be jolly, bringing everyone together for that very special Christmas party, with an evening full of roast turkey, Christmas pudding and don't forget the Christmas crackers! &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;After deciding your venue and date, then give the team at Fun Pro UK a call, and we'll be happy to add the icing to the cake with a variety of indoor games to hire for the evening.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Christmas Grotto&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Christmas is all about making memories, let's hope you've been good throughout the year as Santa brings his presents.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Why not&lt;/span&gt; try our &lt;a title="Christmas Grotto Hire " href="/category/christmas-grotto-hire"&gt;Christmas Grotto&lt;/a&gt;, you can ge&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;t the boss to dress up as Santa and handout the secret Santa gifts inside the grotto! The Christmas Grotto can also come with Santa's throne to add that extra bit of excitement, as you can take pictures on the throne with Santa.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Escape to the North pole &amp;amp; dash inside the Photo Booth Cabin!&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Photo%20Booth/20171214-173433.jpg" alt="Christmas Photo Booth" style="width: 1000px; height: 750px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px;"&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;What better way to start the festive season than to escape to the North Pole with our unique winter themed&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;photo booths&lt;/a&gt;! Dig into the festive props box and find your favourite fancy dress for a group photo with your coll&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;eagues, as you laugh, smile, and create Christmas memories. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 22px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who will be Santa's fastest reindeer? Virtual Reality Racing Car Simulator&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Race%20Cars/2-3.jpg" alt="Race car sims" style="width: 1000px; height: 599px; margin-bottom: 5px;"&gt;Experience this incredible all new &lt;a title="VR Race Car Simulator" href="/category/arcade-games/38/vr-race-car-simulator"&gt;Virtual Reality Racing Car Simulator&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="/category/corporate-entertainment/38/vr-race-car-simulator" title="VR Race Car Simulator"&gt;&lt;/a&gt; like no other! &lt;/span&gt;Put your driving skills to the test with a choice of tracks whilst sitting in a specially formulated racing seat. If you feel the need for speed, why not step it up a gear with our all new VR game. You will have your fans cheering you to the finish line as they watch your moves on the monitor!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Get Your Christmas Groove on!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;We don't want to make a song and dance out of it, but th&lt;/span&gt;e &lt;a title="Dance Machine" href="/category/arcade-games/39/dance-machine"&gt;Dance Machine Twin Player game&lt;/a&gt; is great fun and will guarantee to get everyone dancing, both adult and children alike. This highly visual interac&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;tive game is also fantastic for spectators to watch the players bust out their best dance moves!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;We want to make your Christmas as magical as possible, and even though we can't make it snow, with our fun festive games you can be sure that your event is full of festive fun!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;GET IN TOUCH NOW: &lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email: &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tel: 02476 629197&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mob: 07769979676&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>How Do You Celebrate Christmas At Work?</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-09-10/how-do-you-celebrate-christmas-at-work</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-09-10/how-do-you-celebrate-christmas-at-work</guid><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2&gt;How Do You Celebrate Christmas at Work?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;You snow the drill!🎄&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Christmas - The most wonderful time of the year &amp;amp; as the famous song goes is only 4 months away!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here at the Fun Pro UK office, it is most definitely our favourite time of the year, and yes, we know it is still summer, but we are already checking over all our Christmas entertainment equipment in readiness for the coming season. Colin is not quite ready yet to swap his summer shorts for his Christmas jumpers and socks but as soon as the children are back to school, we know companies will be busy with their Christmas plans.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Christmas is a superb time to get out the fluffy jumpers, drink mulled wine and enjoy the festive spirit. Within the corporate environment, it is a chance to decorate the office and treat your staff to a whole range of festive events from private Christmas parties to Christmas light switch on events. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Did you know 11 million employees will attend their company's Christmas party this year! That's a lot of venues, entertainment and catering needed and being booked up fast. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;It's snow joke, we have Christmas Photo Booths too! &lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Photo%20Booth/20171214-173433.jpg" style="width: 300px' height: 226px' float: right' margin-right: 5px';" alt="Christmas Booth"&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We all know how entertaining taking funny photos with friends is and with our &lt;a title="Christmas Photo Booth Hire" href="/pages/christmas-photo-booth-corporate-event-hire"&gt;Christmas Photo Booths&lt;/a&gt;, we have made it especially easy with the addition of our amazing exclusive &amp;amp; Festive Prop Box. This box contains all you need to have a joyful laugh from our funtastic glasses to Christmas Tree hats and reindeer ears. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But wait &amp;amp; there's myrrh! Why just use Christmas props, when you can hire our Deluxe Christmas Booths? We have two festive styles to choose from, a snowy forest or Santa's wooden cabin. Why not hire one of these brilliant designs to get your guests feeling extra Christmassy. Whether you are hosting a private Christmas party or having a seasonal sales promotion. A photo booth will be the perfect opportunity for all your guests to remember the brilliant festive memories you helped create!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Let's take an Elfie! &lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our booths fit perfectly in your head office reception or staff social club and can be delivered and manned anywhere within the UK. If you don't feel you have the space for a photo booth, Fun Pro UK are delighted to be able to offer our Social Media Pods. This clever and compact piece of technology will fit almost anywhere and contains everything you need to take unlimited photos and instantly upload them to your social media. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Want to keep it festive? We are happy to provide our Christmas Prop box with this hire too. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;A round of Santa-plause! &lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Back to serve another season, our fabulously designed inflatable &lt;a title="Christmas Grotto Hire " href="/category/christmas-grotto-hire"&gt;Christmas Grottos&lt;/a&gt; are already being booked up to deliver an exceptional Christmas atmosphere for events up and down the UK. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Each of our grottos is beautifully designed with snow on the roof and can bring your venue to life with elves, Christmas trees, snowmen and even reindeer. Obviously, not forgetting the real Father Christmas who sits inside the delicately lit grotto. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Dance%20Machine/dance-1.jpg" alt="Dance Machine" style="width: 185px' height: 247px' float: left' margin-right: 5px';"&gt;Dream big, sparkle more, shine bright&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Keep your guests entertained all night with a full range of interactive entertainment. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why not consider having a social media pod or photo booth alongside hiring our gorgeous grotto, allowing all your guests to capture their Christmas memories to help them remember this special time of the year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alternatively, make your event into a Christmas games night and consider hiring a variety of interactive games to let your guests let their hair down. Why not try our &lt;a title="Racing Car Simulators" href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;Race Car Simulators&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="ELECTRONIC BASKET BALL HIRE" href="/category/arcade-games/6/electronic-basket-ball-hire"&gt;Electronic Basketball hire&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a title="RETRO ARCADE GAMES" href="/category/arcade-games/4/retro-arcade-games"&gt;Retro Arcade games&lt;/a&gt; or our brand new &lt;a title="Crack The Code safe cracker" href="/category/exhibition-games/37/crack-the-code-safe-cracker"&gt;Crack the Safe&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Don't get your tinsel in a tangle whilst dancing on our all new &lt;a title="Dance Machine" href="/category/arcade-games/39/dance-machine"&gt;Dance Machine&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a whole team of event experts who are on hand to help you with every stage of planning your festive corporate event. Just give our team a call on 02476 629 197 or email us at &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt; to find out how we can bring that extra bit of Christmas magic to your event this year! &lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>All You Need to Plan For Your Award Ceremonies</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-08-06/all-you-need-to-plan-for-your-award-ceremonies</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-08-06/all-you-need-to-plan-for-your-award-ceremonies</guid><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2&gt;Getting your employees engaged at award ceremonies!&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Why wait until the year draws to a close to award your staff? Why not host your annual employee award ceremony during summer to show your continued appreciation for their hard work. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;A great way of entertaining your staff and guests is with a ran&lt;/span&gt;ge of &lt;a title="Interactive Game Hire " href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;But I hear you say that there are so many options. Not to worry, as here at Fun Pro UK we have put together a comprehensive guide to the best &lt;a title="Company Award Ceremonies" href="/category/company-award-ceremonies"&gt;award ceremony entertainment.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Memories to last a lifetime!&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Photo%20Booth/img-20190709-wa0000.jpg" style="width: 200px' height: 150px' float: right' margin-left: 5px';" /&gt; &lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;You could employ a photographer, right? Why not get your staff involved using a variety of fun and seasonal props within a &lt;a href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors#BodyContent"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;photo booth&lt;/a&gt;? &lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Your attendees can couple up or go in a group and take photos inside a range of high-quality photo booths. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;With unlimited visits, your guests can take as many photos as they want with 2 prints from each visit to have a fun memory from your event. Whether you are looking for a traditional Green Screen Photo Booth or a Bespoke booth, Fun Pro UK can ensure it fits perfectly into your event.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Play the night away!&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Why host a traditional Awards Night when you can theme it? Fun Pro UK can help bring your award night to life with a real sense of style and sophistication with a genuine casino table. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Hire a table that is exactly like those you would find in the finest casinos in Las Vegas, boosting the authentic atmosphere and giving a thrill to all your guests. The whirr of the roulette wheel, the rattle of the ball, the click of the chips- it will all just add to the ambience. Why not go full-on and provide cocktails and have a black-tie dress code to bring the James Bond theme to your award night!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Bring energy to your evening! &lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;If you have ever wanted to be a jockey or to find out who is the most competitive employees within your business! This is the perfect entertainment game for your event! &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Our amazing &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire/29/gold-cup-horse-racing#BodyContent"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a title="GOLD CUP HORSE RACING" href="/category/arcade-games/29/gold-cup-horse-racing"&gt;Gold Cup Horse Racing Game&lt;/a&gt; is bril&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;liant for getting your employees engaged, along with entertaining those who watch and flock around as each short race takes place! Four players can race at each time by selecting their racer and galloping to victory. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Award nights are about celebrating your company's and employees' achievements. So why not pair this product with our &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a title="LEADER BOARD" href="/category/interactive-game-hire/30/leader-board"&gt;leader board&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt; to find the fastest jockey at your event or keep it to the winner of each race!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Drive to victory!&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Race%20Cars/20190702-115236.jpg" style="width: 200px' height: 151px' float: left' margin-right: 5px';" /&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Are your employees' still competitive but far greater petrol heads? Then let them put the pedal to the medal and tear up the track with Fun Pro UK's awesome &lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire/5/twin-racing-car-simulators#BodyContent"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a title="Racing Car Simulators" href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;Race Car Simulators.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;We have two realistic racing simulators which come complete with contoured racing seats, smart steering wheel and authentic pedals and have LED screens to give the best display of the circuit or track you are racing on! &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;But wait! Fun Pro UK is now introducing two more brand new &lt;a title="VR Race Car Simulator" href="/category/arcade-games/38/vr-race-car-simulator"&gt;racing simulators which come with VR technology&lt;/a&gt; to make the experience of racing against your colleagues to the chequered flag even more realistic!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;#CompanyAwardNight!&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;As the modern world keeps developing, many employees spend their spare time on their phones using social media. Why not bring in this advancement to your event! &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Fun Pro UK'&lt;/span&gt;s Hashtag Printer is perfect for your &lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;company and employees to capture all the best moments! The idea is simple, instead of phones being passed around to take photos, we create a dedicated event hashtag! The print station will then search the internet for all the images using this hashtag, allowing your guests to then print off any photos taken instantly at your event! &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;This&lt;a title="Interactive Game Hire " href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt; interactive event entertainment &lt;/a&gt;is perfect for any business to harness the power of user-generated content on social media. It's free publicity as your employees will need to post their photos of the night using your bespoke hashtag before they can print, creating a digital buzz for your business, great fun for your guests.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt; If you would like to know more about how the team at Fun Pro UK can help you with your award ceremonies, then call us on 0247 7220 701.&lt;/span&gt;</description></item><item><title>Where's Colin??</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-07-10/wheres-colin</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-07-10/wheres-colin</guid><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2&gt;Summer Event Fun&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Where's Colin and the Fun Pro UK Team this week?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Over the last two weeks the Fun Pro team and Colin have been busy travelling from one end of the country to the other (and back again!) there was some serious mileage recorded!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Heading for London &lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/Stike%20a%20light/20190619-160019.jpg" alt="Lights Out" style="width: 250px' height: 188px' float: right' margin-left: 5px';" /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Last Monday saw the Fun Pro team travel to the Excel Centre in London to deliver our Strike a Light - Lights Out game for a corporate client. The game was set up on their exhibition stand for visitors to play as they were passing by. The game was a real winner - everyone loves to compete against a friend or colleague and the Strike a Light' does exactly that! Our electronic game attracted great footfall for our client, helping gain potential new customers for their business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Before we knew it those few days at the Excel were over and it was time to return to the Big Smoke once again to staff the game for a few hours and then collect the interactive game and head back home!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manchester here we come!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Just so the team didn't think the heat was off, last Friday Colin and the crew set off to Manchester. This was a very early start to beat the traffic and arrive at The Trafford Centre in good time to get set up. A very popular department store was having a staff appreciation day, it's great to see companies recognising the hard work of their staff don't you think.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The staff at Selfridges, Manchester, were given the opportunity by their managers to have a go on our &lt;a title="CASH GRABBER MACHINE HIRE" href="/category/exhibition-games/3/cash-grabber-machine-hire"&gt;Grab a Grand&lt;/a&gt; game. We had been asked by the store if we could brand our game, we were delighted to assist with, this is something Fun Pro UK does in house. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Branding is important &lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/blog.jpg" alt="Grab a Grand " style="width: 250px' height: 334px' float: right' margin-left: 6px';" /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Branding a game with your company name and logo is an effective way to showcase your company and ensure it is recognised by your target market. Brand activation ensures that your name stands out, everyone sees a name and is more likely to remember the visual graphics of an item. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Did you know that humans are more likely to remember an image they have seen? Which means if your brand is at the front of their minds, people will talk about it and share their great memories with friends, colleagues and family. The result is great marketing for your company everyone will get to hear about you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Once the Fun Pro team were all set up, the game was good to go. It was fun to see the staff members excitement as they tried to grab as many coloured foils as possible, in the shortest amount of time as they blew all around the capsule- there was quite a queue forming with everyone wanting to have turn! Lots of fun was had by everyone at the department store and the day flew by. We can't wait to return for their next staff fun day!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#eventprofs #teamfunpro #StrikeaLight #funday #staffparty&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Top 5 Most Popular Interactive Outdoor Games For Corporates</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-06-05/top-5-most-popular-interactive-outdoor-games-for-corporates</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-06-05/top-5-most-popular-interactive-outdoor-games-for-corporates</guid><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2 style="text-align: center';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline';"&gt;Top 5 Most Popular Interactive Outdoor Games for Corporates&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline';"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/team-work.png" alt="Team work" style="width: 250px' height: 132px' float: right' margin-bottom: 0px';"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Are you sat there wondering how to keep your employees motivated and increase employee retention? Well, look no further, as this guide will go through the top 5 most popular team building games for &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;corporate entertainment hire&lt;/a&gt;, just the thing to engage your staff and say thank you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 24px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Human Table Football&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/human-football.jpg" alt="Human Football" style="width: 450px' height: 227px' float: left' margin-left: 0px' margin-right: 4px';"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;This giant inflatable version of the popular pub game is perfect to stimulate and engage employees to work as part of a team in a hilarious game of football. The players are enclosed in an inflatable pitch and must work in teams of 5 to kick the ball across into the opposite goal.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;However, it is not as easy as it sounds as players can only move side by side as a team, so a great deal of communication and coordination is needed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;To find out more about this fun game click here: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration-line: underline' font-size: 16px';"&gt;&lt;a title="HUMAN TABLE FOOTBALL" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/19/human-table-football"&gt;Human table football&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 24px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Hungry Hippos &lt;img src="/userfiles/file/20190525-144446-023.jpg" alt="Hungry Hippo" style="width: 400px' height: 303px' float: right';"&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Hungry Hippos is one of our best sellers in outdoor games and has evolved from the classic Hungry Hippos board game we all know and love. It's ideal for your staff to challenge themselves both as individuals and to show how they work in a team. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;This 4-player game will find each player connected to a bungee belt, they must run towards the pool of balls, and battle to collect the balls in their bags whilst the belt tries to pull the players back in a race against each other.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Don't miss out on the chance to book our latest game by clicking here: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration-line: underline' font-size: 16px';"&gt;&lt;a title="Dash &amp;amp; Grab / Hungry Hippo Inflatable Game" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/32/dash-and-grab-hungry-hippo-inflatable-game"&gt;Hungry Hippos Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: x-large';"&gt;3. Bungee Run&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/bungee-run.jpg" alt="Bungee Run" style="float: left' margin-right: 4px' margin-left: 0px' width: 250px' height: 250px';"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Test your strength and stamina with the Bungee Run! In this fast and furious game, two players are attached to the bungee cord and position themselves on the inflatable brightly coloured lanes, where they run as fast as possible to the other end and place their Velcro marker before their opponent does. But be aware as soon as you relax the bungee cord will then drag you back to the start.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;The aim of the game is the fastest and strongest individual will place their marker the furthest.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Do you want to be the next ultimate Bungee run champion? Click here for more information &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline' font-size: 16px';"&gt;&lt;a title="Bungee Run" href="/category/fun-days/33/bungee-run"&gt;Bungee Run Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 24px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
4. Total Wipe Out&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/total-wipe-out.jpg" alt="Total Wipeout" style="width: 450px' height: 219px' float: right' margin-left: 4px' margin-right: 0px';"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Looking for a team activity game that will test the nerve, strength and timing of your employees working as part of a team? Well, this is the game for you! As seen on popular TV programmes such as Total Wipeout. In this game everyone will need to communicate effectively and concentrate on the challenge ahead.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;As the revolving arms swing past, the aim of the game is to avoid being knocked from their podium and be the last man standing, it requires the commitment of all team members and effective communication to allow the team to succeed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Get your employees together, and become the dream team for the Total Wipeout challenge click here: &lt;span style="text-decoration: underline';"&gt;&lt;a title="TOTAL WIPE OUT" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/20/total-wipe-out"&gt;Total Wipe Out &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 24px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5: Assault Course Game&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;This game will keep your employees on their feet or not! as they bounce and slide their way through our inflatable assault course. Let them have fun and enjoy the outdoors by trying the assault course, that is packed full of small challenges inside. We have two for you to choose from the Extreme Assault course and the dazzling Dragon Run, there is no better way to bring out the big kids and see who the ultimate Indiana Jones or Lara Croft is!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Employees can be split into teams, for example, one department against another to see which team can last and lead their team to victory. This is a popular assault course that will bring entertainment and a sense of togetherness for the employees, also a way to build confidence and morale amongst colleagues.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center';"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/assault-course.jpg" alt="Assault Courses" style="width: 650px' height: 488px' vertical-align: middle' margin-right: 4px' margin-left: 4px';"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;What are you waiting for! Find out more by clicking here: &lt;span style="text-decoration: underline';"&gt;&lt;a title="INFLATABLE ASSAULT COURSES" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/21/inflatable-assault-courses"&gt;Assault course game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;We have given you our Top 5 most popular hired outdoor games that we feel will enhance your company fun day, getting your team out of the office and off the factory floor.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;If you would like to find out more about how &lt;a title="Fun Days" href="/category/fun-days"&gt;corporate fun days&lt;/a&gt; can be fun, please &lt;a href="/news/2019-03-18/corporate-fun-days-can-be-fun"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a title="News" href="/news"&gt;click here to read our blog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Book with FUN PRO UK, with leading customer service experience and being rest assured that the products offered are of the highest quality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;To find out more please contact the team at FUN PRO UK &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Tel: 02476 629 197&lt;br&gt;
07769 979 676&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Email:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>AWARDS DESERVE SELFIES!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-05-15/awards-deserve-selfies</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-05-15/awards-deserve-selfies</guid><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 22px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AWARDS DESERVE SELFIES!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;With award season for many of our Corporate Clients well under way at a variety of locations up and down the U.K, we were excited to be able to supply yet another fab &lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;Green Screen Dream Machine Photobooth &lt;/a&gt; for a large company who deliver caring packages to their clients up and down the country.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 22px';"&gt;AWARDS &amp;amp; SELFIES!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;The Managers attended their company conference during the day at a hotel venue on the outskirts of Rugby, Warwickshire. This was a formal day with colleagues, followed by dinner and an awards ceremony for everyone who works there. When the evening entertainment arrived the party animals came a live!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;The Green Screen Dream Machine Photobooth was set up and ready to get the party started for 7.30pm. This gave everyone a chance to put their party frocks on and practice their best cheesy grin! Our prop box was over flowing with colourful glasses, hand held signs and silly hats. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;It was great to see everyone grabbing their friends and entering the booth to choose a background for their selfie - whether you wanted a dinosaur selfie or to be a subject on 'Our Most Wanted' caption. The booth was inundated as always with guys and girls enjoying their evening. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 22px';"&gt;STAFF APPRECIATION&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Holding an &lt;a title="Company Award Ceremonies" href="/category/company-award-ceremonies"&gt;awards ceremony&lt;/a&gt; is a great way to celebrate the hard work that your staff do from day to day. They often feel that they don't get noticed or recognised. By holding an awards ceremony this will make them feel appreciated by the company and will boost staff morale.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 22px';"&gt;HAVE FUN &amp;amp; SOCIALISE WITH YOUR TEAM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;If you are holding a company conference, why not hire some fun entertaining games for the evening after a formal dinner. This will ensure all the guests relax, have fun and socialise with the&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;ir teams. There is nothing better than building great working relationships whilst having fun!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 22px';"&gt;LET US HELP YOU!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Are you arranging a conference or awards ceremony and aren't sure what you could hire for evening entertainment? Contact our team today, we have a huge variety of social media selfie pods, booths along with table top games for everyone to enjoy. All of our products can also be branded in house with your company logo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>How To Attract More Foot Fall To Your Trade Show Stand</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-04-09/how-to-attract-more-foot-fall-to-your-trade-show-stand</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-04-09/how-to-attract-more-foot-fall-to-your-trade-show-stand</guid><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2&gt;How To Attract More Foot Fall To Your Trade Show Stand&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Arranging a new product launch in a car showroom or trade stand entertainment for an expo? Hiring interactive games will increase footfall &amp;amp; attract new clients for your business.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Walking around a busy Trade Show or Expo with a sea of stands trying to grab your attention isn't much fun, is it? It can be even worse if the exhibitors are staring at their phones and not engaging with passing potential clients. We know as we have been to many ourselves! Here are a few tips to remember when planning your stand:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;span style="font-size: 22px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Planning Your Stand&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;A worthy Trade Show Stand will have been planned and thought about well before the day. You need to think about:&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/busy-expo.jpg" alt="busy expo stand" style="float: right' margin-right: 6px';"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;How you can tell your story about your brand&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Ensure your name can be clearly seen&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Make your visitors feel at home - be welcoming and friendly&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Offer a memorable experience linked to your business&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 22px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Not Stand Out from The Norm?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Instead of being like everyone else who does a competition to win a bottle of Champagne or gives away cans of pop, make your exhibition stand unique and you are sure to stand out from your competitors. By standing out from the crowd you will attract more footfall to your business and will have the opportunity to engage with more clients. Ultimately this will mean positive leads made on the day and once you follow up after the event it will earn you more revenue.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 22px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Engagement Can Be Fun!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;You need your&lt;a title="Exhibition Games " href="/category/exhibition-games"&gt; Exhibition Stand&lt;/a&gt; entertainment to be engaging. Human beings are visual creatures - meaning if we like the look of something then we will want to know more about it. If a potential client sees something on your stand that they can resonate with they are more likely to stop by and speak with you for a few moments instead of walking on to your competitor next door.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Why not place a game on your stand that will catch the eyes of the attendees? By getting engagement and interaction with your new lead you are half way there - if they can have fun whilst at your expo stand then it will make your job of capturing that deal even easier. Competitions are a great way to obtain details but again you want a competition with a difference.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 22px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fun Pro UK Can Help You&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Our huge variety of exhibition games to hire include table top games. These are ideal to have on Expo stands or at a Trade Shows. We can cater for all kinds of theme. Maybe you are attending a medical conference - our table top &lt;a title="TOP DOC OPERATION GAME" href="/category/arcade-games/7/top-doc-operation-game"&gt;Tap a Doc&lt;/a&gt; game (for those who remember the Operation game when you were kids this is it!) is a fun way of engaging new clients. These table top games will fit neatly on your stand and guarantee to draw an eager crowd.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;If you want to test a skill, then our &lt;a title="GIANT BUZZ WIRE" href="/category/interactive-game-hire/9/giant-buzz-wire"&gt;Giant Buzz Wire&lt;/a&gt; is great to see if your audience has a steady hand!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;If you are thinking of a game that will ensure you interaction with your contestants which can offer a truly memorable experience where the winner could receive a prize, then our &lt;a title="CASH GRABBER MACHINE HIRE" href="/category/exhibition-games/3/cash-grabber-machine-hire"&gt;Grab A Grand &lt;/a&gt;is a real head turner. This game has been hired many times for exhibition entertainment and was a regular feature on The Crystal Maze TV show. The contestant steps into a clear pod, the fans turn on and the wind blows paper money or soft balls around the pod. The contestant then gathers as many notes/balls as possible with in the time allowed. The winner at the end of the show could then be issued with a prize. This is a fun way of engaging potential new clients for your business.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/whatsapp-image-2019-04-09-at-134801.jpeg" alt="Racing Car Simulator" style="width: 350px' height: 197px' float: left' margin-right: 5px';"&gt;Maybe you are planning a product launch - our &lt;a title="Racing Car Simulators" href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;Racing Car Simulators&lt;/a&gt; for a new car launch is a fabulous way to make this type of event unique to other showrooms in your area. Our Racing Cars are hired as a pair where the drivers can choose their vehicle colour, make and style. Once the games are ready and the track has been chosen the flags are waved and it's time to see who can go the fasted around the track. Our leader board can also be hired where times can be recorded to see who the fasted racing driver was - again a prize from your business could then be given making this a real memorable experience that your opponents will not have done.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 22px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ensure Your Brand is Noticed!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;It is all well and good having a stand at an expo with your products but you want your new clients to remember who you are. There will be many stands at your show who are marketing the same type of business as you. We can help ensure your brand will be noticed - let us print your company name onto one of our games or photobooths. This will automatically ensure your company stands out from the crowd. Having your company name or logo on a game hired from Fun Pro UK will help your potential client remember who you were and retain an image of your brand.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Everyone is so busy these days and has so much information thrown at them within such a short space of time it is all too easy to visualise a product but within minutes become side tracked and forget all about it. By branding a game on your stand this will guarantee you will be remembered and your new clients will know exactly who caught their eye at the expo they attended making it easier for them to contact you for future business.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;Whether it is trade stand entertainment, exhibition games to hire or items for a product launch to ensure you are noticed at your event' we can help. Why not drop our team a line today a&lt;/span&gt;t &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 16px';"&gt;with your brief and we will put together a few ideas to make your pitch profitable?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Corporate Fun Days Can Be Fun!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-03-18/corporate-fun-days-can-be-fun</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-03-18/corporate-fun-days-can-be-fun</guid><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Do you appreciate your staff?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Do your staff work hard to make your business complete and successful? Then why not arrange a &lt;a title="Fun Days" href="/category/fun-days"&gt;Corporate Fun day?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Inviting staff members to a fun day away from the office is a great idea, but inviting their families along to take part in a family fun day would make your employees feel valued, allow them to have fun and also spend quality time making memories with their loved ones.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;In return your staff would feel a sense of loyalty to the company they work for, it would improve colleague relationships and motivate your team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 32px';"&gt;Let Fun Pro UK help you!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/fundays.png" alt="Inflatable Fun days" style="width: 150px' height: 150px' float: right' margin-left: 10px';" /&gt;Our fun experts at Fun Pro HQ have years of experience in planning corporate family fun events. We love arranging fun days and get excited when a new challenge comes along. If you are wondering where on earth to begin with planning your event then give the team a call in the office or drop them a line. Our friendly funtastic experts will be waiting to speak with you to see how they can help you make your next event a huge success!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 32px';"&gt;Something For Everyone.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Wondering what to do first when arranging your family fun day? Don't panic, we have a few tips to get everything covered!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Date &lt;/strong&gt;- What date are you thinking of for your event? - Is it the same date as last year? - Check there aren't any major events happening near by or a sporting event that people will attend rather than your fun day.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Venue&lt;/strong&gt; - Has your chosen venue got enough space for your entertainment and amount of guests you are expecting? Is there a large car park? Is access easy for pushchairs/wheelchairs etc? Is there access to power for inflatables? Do you have a grass area for your entertainment/ marquees. Remember inflatable fun needs a grass base to secure the equipment on safely! Are there toilet facilities? Maybe an indoor hall is required as well as outside?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. What time&lt;/strong&gt; will your event run from and too? - Your team will need time to set up in the morning. Early afternoon is a good start time for families to be out and about, running through to early evening.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Who is your audience?&lt;/strong&gt; - What age range are you catering for. Fun Pro UK can supply entertainment for small children, teens and adults.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. Budget.&lt;/strong&gt; What is your budget? Do you have anyone sponsoring your event? Fun Pro UK can work on quotes to fit in with your budget.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;We have games to hire and inflatable fun that will tick all of your boxes! We have fun inflatables that will suite toddlers, teens and grandparents alike.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Fun Pro UK has themed bouncy castles to hire for younger children as well as soft play which is ideal when entertaining toddlers and small children alike. The brightly coloured castles make great fun to bounce as high as you can with your friends!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Older children and teens usually enjoy a bit more of a thrill! Here our super slides and assault courses play a huge part in family fun days. Everyone has a great time on these pieces of equipment and always come back for another turn. See how fast you can go down our super slides or time yourselves as you encounter the many obstacles waiting for you on the mega assault courses&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;&lt;img src="/userfiles/file/FunPro/ultimate-wipeout-462.jpg" alt="Total wipe Out" style="width: 250px' height: 141px' float: left' border-width: 0px' border-style: solid' margin-right: 10px' margin-left: 0px';" /&gt;We also offer games to hire too. The &lt;a title="Racing Car Simulators" href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;racing car simulators&lt;/a&gt; are a big hit with teens and adults . Take your seat, choose your car and terrain then buckle up before you take the road as fast as you can around the track to beat your opponents. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;If it is a team game to hire we have some equipment that will knock your socks off! &lt;a title="HUMAN TABLE FOOTBALL" href="/category/corporate-entertainment/19/human-table-football"&gt;Our Human Football Game, &lt;/a&gt;Total Wipe Out or Hungry Hippos life sized game are all fabulous for your work colleagues to come together as a team and have fun whilst taking part in the challenge to be the winner!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 32px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We all love Ice Cream!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px' color: #000000';"&gt;Our boss Colin at Fun Pro must be the biggest ice cream lover around! His favourite flavour is Cornish Vanilla! Wonder why? Maybe its cos he's from Cornwall. We can provide gorgeous vintage ice cream trikes with dedicated staff for your event who will serve the fun day guests with either cones or cups in a variety of flavours with toppings and not forgetting the all important sauce! After all, you have to have an ice cream at a fun day!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 32px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are the professionals of Fun&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Here at Fun Pro UK you can be rest assured that we are professionals providing safe and insured fun games to hire. We are suppliers to the industry therefore own all of our equipment. The team deliver a 1st class service to give each client the best service possible meeting the brief given by you, the client each and every time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;If you are planning a corporate fun day which requires fantastic value, excellent entertainment and outstanding results for your business then Fun Pro UK are the company to contact.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Call us on 📞02476 629197 to discuss how Fun Pro UK can help your Family Fun Day be the best ever.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>The benefits of exhibiting at trade shows &amp; exhibitions</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-03-01/the-benefits-of-exhibiting-at-trade-shows-and-exhibitions</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-03-01/the-benefits-of-exhibiting-at-trade-shows-and-exhibitions</guid><pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Have you been thinking about exhibiting at a trade show or exhibition but are not sure if it's worth your while? We've had a stand at numerous different expos over the years, from business exhibitions to wedding shows and have found they have many benefits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Trade shows and exhibitions help to raise the awareness of your business in your industry, the surrounding area and with potential customers. In many cases this is not just limited to attendees of the show either as some packages also include a listing on the organisers website and mentions on their social media.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They are also great for meeting people in person which helps in building stronger business relationships. A phone will only get you so far these days. Meeting and being able to chat with someone in person, helps you to build rapport and allows you to explain more easily how your products or services could help them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We've found &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Birmingham" href="/pages/corporate-event-hire-birmingham"&gt;trade shows and exhibitions&lt;/a&gt; are also great networking opportunities. You can meet not only potential customers, but also suppliers as well as businesses with whom you could work in partnership with or collaborate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have a new product or service coming out, exhibitions and trade shows can be a great place to launch them, as you have a ready made audience. This is especially useful if your product is innovative, as it allows you to talk about the product or service in person.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Finally, expos and trade shows are a great place to build your marketing database and generate qualified sales leads. You can ask people for their business card while you're chatting to them or, as many exhibitors do, obtain business cards as part of a competition. If you do collect business cards as part of a competition remember to be very clear on how you will use their information to ensure GDPR compliance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you do decide that you'd like to book at stand at a trade show or exhibition, one of the keys to success is ensuring that the people attending the exhibition or show are your target audience. Before booking do some research on the company running the event and who they are looking to attract to the show or exhibition. You don't want to waste time or money going to a show if your target market is not there.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Trade shows and exhibitions can be pricey compared to other forms of marketing, which is why if you're going to invest in this, you need to make sure you stand out from the crowd. At Fun Pro UK we can help you do this with our range of fun and interactive games. From our table top games such as '&lt;a title="TOP DOC OPERATION GAME" href="/category/arcade-games/7/top-doc-operation-game"&gt;Top Doc operation&lt;/a&gt;' and '&lt;a title="PLUCK A DUCK RACING" href="/category/arcade-games/8/pluck-a-duck-racing"&gt;Pluck a Duck Racing&lt;/a&gt;', to our larger '&lt;a title="GIANT BUZZ WIRE" href="/category/interactive-game-hire/9/giant-buzz-wire"&gt;Giant Buzz Wire&lt;/a&gt;' or our '&lt;a title="CASH GRABBER MACHINE HIRE" href="/category/exhibition-games/3/cash-grabber-machine-hire"&gt;Grab a Grand&lt;/a&gt;', we have something for any size exhibition stand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information or to chat to us about how we can make your exhibition or trade show stand out and draw a crowd, check out our website https://www.funprouk.co.uk or call 02476 629 197 or 07769 979 676.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Tips for running a Successful Team Building Day</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-02-15/tips-for-running-a-successful-team-building-day</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-02-15/tips-for-running-a-successful-team-building-day</guid><pubDate>Fri, 15 Feb 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Team building days are a great way to bring your team together, improve communication, improve productivity and build trust. But organising and running a successful team building day is no easy task.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To ensure your day achieves all the goals you've set, we've put together our tips for running a successful &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;team building event.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Take it offsite. It helps people to distance themselves from the work environment and switch off mentally from their daily tasks. It can give your team the space to bond without the pressure of work. A fresh environment can also shed new light on problems and get the creative juices flowing.
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Set clear expectations. It's important to ensure everyone knows the purpose of the day and your expectations. We also recommend letting your team know a bit about what's involved in the day. For example, if there is physical activity, it's best to give people warning.
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Don't try to pack too much into your team building event. We understand that getting your whole team offsite for the day is tricky and you want to make the most of it, but you can't achieve everything. Be realistic about what you can achieve in the timeframe.
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Allow time between each activity for discussion. Talk about what people learnt in the activity and then how it could be applied back in the workplace.
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Have some fun. When planning activities for your team building day, remember to make it fun. This can be done through the activities themselves or in the breaks. For your day to be successful and for people to take the lessons onboard, people need to have enjoyed themselves.
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Schedule time for follow-up after the team building day. To ensure your event has the biggest impact make sure you schedule in time to follow-up when you're back in the office.This can often be done in a team meeting and ensures you are implementing the learnings you gained from the day.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Team building days can be a lot of fun and a fabulous way to build cohesive teams. At Fun Pro UK we can help to make your day a success with our large range of &lt;a title="Interactive Game Hire " href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; and inflatables. Contact us at email: &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt; or give us a call on Tel: 02476629197.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>7 ways to show your staff some love!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-01-30/7-ways-to-show-your-staff-some-love</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-01-30/7-ways-to-show-your-staff-some-love</guid><pubDate>Wed, 30 Jan 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;February is known as the month of love, with February 14&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt;, Valentine's day, seen as a chance to show your partner how much you love them. The greeting card companies do a roaring trade, the florists sell huge numbers of flowers, and restaurants are all booked up by couples celebrating their relationship.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Many of us however, spend more time at work than we do with our partners. What are you doing as a company to show your employees some love? We think February, well any time of the year really, is a great time to show some love to your employees for their commitment and hard work. There are hundreds of ways that you can show your staff how much you appreciate them but here are a few of our favourites:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Thank you notes, cards and little gifts of appreciation. It doesn't have to cost a lot but the impact that it will have on your staff in terms of morale can be huge.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Free food. Throw a morning or afternoon tea with cakes, or perhaps order in some pizza for lunch. Gatherings like these can help bring the office together and make your staff feel appreciated.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Celebrating employee personal life events such as birthdays, weddings &amp;amp; new babies. Buy a cake, throw a small party, buy a card and gift. Often this is done by other staff and not management. It shows your staff that you see them as people and not just employees.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Upgrading the break out room. Staff need a space where they can get away from it all, switch off and just chill. Does your breakout room do this, or could you be doing more? Ask your staff what they'd like to see in the breakout room? You could add books, a gaming console, or hire a game such as our lights out game.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Giving out awards. Recognise staff, team and department achievements with certificates, trophies and awards. If you have the funds you can also have an awards night where everyone has the chance to dress up and feel special.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Team building activities. Invest in your staff with an offsite morning, afternoon or whole day team building. Not only will it boost morale, but it will also produce more cohesive and productive teams. You could run it through your training department if you have one or you could bring in an external company to help. &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Host a &lt;a title="Christmas Game Hire " href="/category/christmas-game-hire"&gt;company event to celebrate Christmas&lt;/a&gt;, end of financial year or just to say thank you. This can be a small or big event depending on your budget. Go out for dinner at a restaurant, go paint balling or hire a conference room at a swish hotel with a photo booth to capture the fun. The list is endless.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contact us today to arrange your next event. Email: &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt; or give us a call on Tel: 02476629197&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Photo booths are not just for fun!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-01-18/photo-booths-are-not-just-for-fun</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-01-18/photo-booths-are-not-just-for-fun</guid><pubDate>Fri, 18 Jan 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;Photo booths and Magic Mirrors&lt;/a&gt; add a lot of fun to an event. From Christmas parties to awards ceremonies, and from birthday parties to weddings, party guests love hopping into a photo booth to capture a happy group shot or seeing who can put on the funniest face. When it comes to &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;magic mirrors&lt;/a&gt;, attendees love donning the array of crazy hats, goofy glasses and holding up silly signs to get fun photos.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But your guests having fun is just one of the benefits of hiring a photo booth or magic mirror for your event. Photos from events not only provide immediate enjoyment, they also trigger future enjoyment. There's nothing like looking at old photos and reliving happy times. Photos of family holidays, birthday celebrations, even class photos from school can evoke wonderful memories.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Photos also facilitate memory. As we get older, it becomes more difficult to remember every event or occasion and all the details from those events. Photos can remind us of things we may have forgotten, again allowing us to relive happy memories. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;From a business perspective, an investment in a &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;photo booth&lt;/a&gt; or magic mirror at a company event is also a great way to reward and recognise employees for all their hard work. When companies put on fun entertainment at employee events, staff feel valued and appreciated. When staff feel valued and appreciated, they are likely to be happier and more productive employees. In turn, this can reduce staff sick leave and increase retention.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Photo booths and Magic Mirrors also add more than just fun at promotional events. At exhibitions and trade shows, they can draw crowds to your stand and give you an opportunity you may not have had, to increase awareness and sales of your products and services. Take-away photos branded with your logo further fosters this relationship by increasing brand retention and opening the door for future sales.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So, as you can see photo booths and magic mirrors are more than just fun. They add value to us as individuals as well as companies. Talk to us about how we can help you enjoy the benefits of photo booths or magic mirrors at your next event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Call: 02476 629197&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email: &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Get organised!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-01-04/get-organised</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2019-01-04/get-organised</guid><pubDate>Fri, 04 Jan 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2&gt;New Year's resolution: Time to get organised!&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you one of the thousands of people who set a new year's resolution each year, only to see it fail within a month or two of starting? Yep, we've been there too! We've promised to eat healthier, exercise and spend more time with family to name a few. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Is your new year's resolution this year to get organised? This is a big one for many people and can help you to achieve many of your other goals. Here are some great tips on how to get more organised this year and finally see your resolution through. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One of the keys to getting more organised is to start small. Rather than try and organise all aspects of your life in one go, start with one area, work on this until you're happy and then move on to the next area. Don't forget to revisit it regularly to make sure you stay on track.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Get yourself a calendar or diary (paper or electronic) and commit to use it daily for recording all your activities. Having everything in one place makes it so much easier to manage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Set some realistic and manageable goals. We're not saying don't aim high, your goals should stretch you, but make sure they are not unrealistic and can be achieved given everything else on your plate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Next, you need to set up daily, weekly and monthly routines to help you achieve your goal and stay on track. What can you do before you go to bed to get ready for the next day? What can you do in the morning to get focused on what you need to achieve that day? Are there weekly and monthly routines, such as a weekly meal planning or monthly budgeting that will help you reach your goals?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sometimes you need to acknowledge that you can't do it all on your own. It is not a sign of weakness to get support. Enlist the help of family, friends or experts in an area to achieve your resolution. Your family can play a part in the running of the household. External parties such Virtual Assistants can help with a variety of tasks. If you've got a big event coming up give us a call to see how we can help.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Don't forget to check in regularly to see how you're going. If you need to make changes to stay on track, do it. Also remember to acknowledge your successes. If you've stayed focused and achieved some of your goals, give yourself a huge pat on the back, you deserve it! &lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Thank you!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-12-19/thank-you</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-12-19/thank-you</guid><pubDate>Wed, 19 Dec 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;It has been a busy year here at Fun Pro UK with a huge increase in business, taking on new staff members and moving to a larger premise. But none of this would have been possible without our new and existing clients. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have been all across the UK delivering exceptional &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;corporate entertainment&lt;/a&gt; from London to Nottingham. Working on a huge array of events including award shows and &lt;a title="Christmas Game Hire " href="/category/christmas-game-hire"&gt;Christmas parties&lt;/a&gt; to pre-match fan villages at Wasps to conferences, exhibitions and weddings. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But everyone here at Fun Pro UK wants to thank each and every client for their business over the last year, allowing us to be what we are today! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are all looking forward to what the new year will bring! But in the meantime, we wish everyone a very merry Christmas and a happy New Year!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Did you know we have moved!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-12-12/did-you-know-we-have-moved</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-12-12/did-you-know-we-have-moved</guid><pubDate>Wed, 12 Dec 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Did you hear that we recently moved premises? Why, I hear you ask.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here are at Fun Pro UK we have seen a major increase in the number of corporate clients hiring our &lt;a title="Interactive Game Hire " href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games &lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;photo booths&lt;/a&gt;. For a whole variety of events from &lt;a title="Company Award Ceremonies" href="/category/company-award-ceremonies"&gt;award ceremonies&lt;/a&gt;, family fun days and sales conferences, all across the UK.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By moving to a new larger site, we are able to offer a wider variety of products to keep your guests entertained during the day and at evening events. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team all worked hard moving the office and &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;corporate entertainment&lt;/a&gt; equipment into our vans to transport off to our new site. Colin even got the hang of driving our forklift around our warehouse! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The move has been stressful for the whole team, while still delivering our high-quality entertainment to a range of Christmas parties, outdoor events and award ceremonies. But the aim of moving now will mean everything will be ready to kick off 2019 in style and deliver an even more exceptional service for our ever-growing list of corporate clients! &lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Why hire corporate entertainment with Fun Pro UK?</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-12-05/why-hire-corporate-entertainment-with-fun-pro-uk</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-12-05/why-hire-corporate-entertainment-with-fun-pro-uk</guid><pubDate>Wed, 05 Dec 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 18px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are the benefits of incorporating interactive games and entertainment into your company's events and work place?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Ensuring your employees have sufficient down time is becoming an ever-increasing issue with the drastic changes in technology over the last few decades. Where staff used to work 9 - 5, they are now connected to work emails and phone calls 24/7 with company mobile phones and laptops. This is putting increased pressure on employees and reducing the time they spend switched off from thoughts about work. This can impact your business in a variety of ways from increased employee absence and stress related issues to reduced productivity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Ensuring the well-being and mental health of all employees is a relatively new concept. However, it was found in a recent Absence Management Survey by the Chartered Institute of Personnel Development (CIPD) that the average employee takes 6.3 working days off each year due to sickness. This costs an astounding &amp;pound;522 per employee per year in lost hours, reduced output and other staff trying to compensate. A potential way of maintaining the well-being of your staff is by rewarding them with staff incentives such as team building days. Engagement with other members of staff enables connections to be built and can act as a stress relief, as well as allowing your staff the chance to get some fresh air in a different environment to their usual office.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;When employees are happy and satisfied within their teams, a study found that they are 20% more productive. When multiplied up for all employees within a business, that's a lot more productiveness! Have you considered placing entertainment in your office over a lunch break? Why not &lt;a title="ELECTRONIC BASKET BALL HIRE" href="/category/arcade-games/6/electronic-basket-ball-hire"&gt;hire our electric basketball hoops&lt;/a&gt; to let your staff take a decent break away from their desks and have fun getting competitive?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Have you heard of your employees not wanting to be sent to another boring sales conference where you end up sitting in the same room all day? When incorporating &lt;a title="Interactive Game Hire " href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; into the schedule, delegates get the chance to move about, helping to keep them stay alert and motivated to listen to each talk. Not only does it help to build new connections with those they interact with, it also inspires them to continue learning about their industry and those working within it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Company training can be extremely useful, but if your employees are disengaged, they are unlikely to take away any benefits. If you think back to being at school, if the teacher incorporated games into a lesson, you paid far more attention than if you just had to complete a worksheet. It can work the same way with corporate training. Staff feel rewarded, pleased, surprised and a sense of accomplishment when they play games. So why not consider hiring our range of giant board games to place within your training, to get your staff more involved. When they are paying more attention to their learning, they will take more away, even if they aren't realising it, and this can improve both their own work, as well as those around them.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Hosting a staff event, whether in the form of an awards night, family fun day or team building day, can boost the morale of your employees and makes them feel valued. When employees feel like their company values them and their work, they are far more likely to want to stay in the business. This results in increased staff retention, which we all know is a good thing all round for consistency and productivity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Ensuring the overall health, well-being and happiness of your employees doesn't have to be hugely expensive. You can host large award ceremonies to congratulate staff who are succeeding within the business and industry, but you can also hire corporate entertainment to capture your staff's imagination on a smaller scale. By placing an interactive game or photo booth within the canteen area at lunch time or by getting delegates at a conference moving on a break with a racing simulator or playing a childhood game, the benefits can be just as great! Rewarding staff with entertainment within the work place as well as at events, it can delivery significant benefits to your business, with you seeing a long term return on your investment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why hire your entertainment from Fun Pro UK?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;If you're wanting to create the feel-good factor at your next event or generate a wow from all your guests, then you need top quality, fully integrated corporate entertainment. But why waste your time getting half a job from other companies, when the dedicated team at Fun Pro UK will take you and your event as our primary concern.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;Our growing team keeps our values at heart, ensuring the professional delivery and installation of all our corporate entertainment. We ensure each guest has an unforgettable experience, while playing with our huge variety of interactive games or taking fun photographs in our range of traditional or unique &lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;photo booths&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 14px';"&gt;To find out more Email &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt; or Call our office on 02476 629197&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Award ceremony London</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-12-03/award-ceremony-london</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-12-03/award-ceremony-london</guid><pubDate>Mon, 03 Dec 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;div original_font_attr="-1"&gt;Thursday saw team Fun Pro UK bring the fun to an awards party for a large corporate company based near London.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div original_font_attr="-1"&gt;The brief was to supply a &lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;green screen photo booth&lt;/a&gt; - with the company logo to be printed on each selfie&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div original_font_attr="-1"&gt; - to be delivered and set up by 6pm&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div original_font_attr="-1"&gt; - ready for the party fun to begin at 8.30 until 1am. &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div original_font_attr="-1"&gt;The venue - a luxurious hotel and golf club in Watford, London. The client a large aviation firm.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div original_font_attr="-1"&gt;The team travelled from Coventry to London with time to spare. Unloading the van and building the booth was done in record time once again, so there was even time to take a break!&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div original_font_attr="-1"&gt;Once the awards had been issued, the speeches made, it was time to party! Before we could say 'awards ceremony' the queue to have a selfie in the Fun Pro photo booth was getting lengthy, full of happy work colleagues and friends enjoying their evening event. With the after party now in full swing every guest was rocking the selfies with our over flowing prop box.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div original_font_attr="-1"&gt;It was an amazing night with our photo booth capturing fabulous memories of the &lt;a title="Company Award Ceremonies" href="/category/company-award-ceremonies"&gt;awards party&lt;/a&gt;. We can't wait to return to London again soon for more corporate events.&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Christmas parties are go!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-11-30/christmas-parties-are-go</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-11-30/christmas-parties-are-go</guid><pubDate>Fri, 30 Nov 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;div original_font_attr="-1"&gt;Are you in the Christmas spirit yet? The Christmas party season has well and truly begun for Fun Pro UK. Our photo booth and selfie mirror prop boxes have been fully replenished and are overflowing with Christmas spirit, ready for the dozens of corporate and private events booked from Coventry to London.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div original_font_attr="-1"&gt;From funtastic glasses to Christmas turkey hats and reindeer ears there is not a prop that will not look great in your photo. Whether it is a work event of a private do we can guarantee your friends will look back on the prints with a smile and great memories of having a selfie in our &lt;a title="Christmas Photo Booth Hire" href="/pages/christmas-photo-booth-corporate-event-hire"&gt;Christmas themed photo booths&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div original_font_attr="-1"&gt;Whatever time of year each green screen photo booth and &lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;magic selfie mirror&lt;/a&gt; we hire is delivered with an over flowing prop box of fun - ensuring that your guests can dress up for the occasion!&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div original_font_attr="-1"&gt;Why not hire our Santa's cabin themed photo booth for your Christmas event. The outer images on the cabin really make your venue come to life and add the magical ambience your guests will adore.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div original_font_attr="-1"&gt;What are you waiting for? book your Christmas party photo booth or selfie mirror for your December event today!&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Award ceremony season is fast approaching!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-11-28/award-ceremony-season-is-fast-approaching</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-11-28/award-ceremony-season-is-fast-approaching</guid><pubDate>Wed, 28 Nov 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;As the year starts to draw to a close, companies are preparing their annual &lt;a title="Company Award Ceremonies" href="/category/company-award-ceremonies"&gt;employee award ceremony&lt;/a&gt; to show their continued appreciation for their staff's hard work over the last year. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A great way of entertaining your guests is with a range of interactive games. But the perfect way to ensure they remember their unforgettable experience and the joy of the event is to have photographs taken.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You could employ a photographer right? But why not get your staff involved with a variety of fun and seasonal props. Your attendees can couple up or go in group and take photos inside a range of high-quality photo booths. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With unlimited visits your guests can take as many photos as they desire with 2 prints from each visit to have a tangible item from your event. Whether you are looking for a traditional &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;Green Screen Photo Booth&lt;/a&gt; or a &lt;a title="Bespoke Photo Booth Hire" href="/category/branded-exhibition-games/24/bespoke-photo-booth-hire"&gt;Bespoke photo booth&lt;/a&gt;, Fun Pro UK can ensure it fits perfectly into your event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our bespoke designed photo booths are an effective way of promoting your business and are created with by our expert team incorporating your company colours, logo and slogans. These booths are bound to make a massive impact at any event and is ideal to put on your social media. Once you have designed a skin with us, we store it safely in our warehouse until your next event!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have worked with a huge array of companies to deliver exceptional award ceremonies including Amazon, &lt;a title="Putting KPMG in the Picture" href="/pages/putting-kpmg-in-the-picture"&gt;KPMG&lt;/a&gt; and Virgin Trains. So why not get in contact with us today to see how we can make your next award show unforgettable!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/photo-booth-1.jpeg" style="width: 250px' height: 188px' border: 1px solid #000000';" /&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/queues.jpeg" style="width: 250px' height: 188px' border: 1px solid #000000';" /&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/photo-booth-4.jpeg" style="width: 250px' height: 188px' border: 1px solid #000000';" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Continually Working to Deliver a Quality Service!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-11-21/continually-working-to-deliver-a-quality-service</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-11-21/continually-working-to-deliver-a-quality-service</guid><pubDate>Wed, 21 Nov 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;It has been a busy week within the Fun Pro UK office with brainstorming sessions on how to continue to deliver our top-quality service to our new and long-standing customers. Even Demi (the Fun Pro UK dog) has been getting involved with our meetings! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a business we are constantly wanting to evolve to ensure we are meeting the needs of our customers and a great way of doing this is through gaining feedback. So, we have set our marketing team the challenge of creating a new feedback system, to gather all our customers' thoughts on the service we currently deliver and the areas where we could develop and improve. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So the next time you &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;hire corporate entertainment&lt;/a&gt; through us, please look out for and complete our new and improved feedback survey.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Ho Ho Ho it's Christmas!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-11-07/ho-ho-ho-its-christmas</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-11-07/ho-ho-ho-its-christmas</guid><pubDate>Wed, 07 Nov 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;There's nothing like the festive season to boost everyone's spirits and have a reason to get a bit merry. But why not make this year extra special for your clients and employees with one or other of our two fabulously designed &lt;a title="Christmas Grotto Hire " href="/category/christmas-grotto-hire"&gt;inflatable Christmas Grotto!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Each grotto is beautifully designed with snow on the roof and can bring your venue to life with elves, Christmas trees, snowmen and even reindeer. Obviously, not forgetting the real Father Christmas who sits inside the delicately lit grotto!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Our Christmas grotto is perfect for the young and those who are young at heart, fitting into staff Christmas parties, award shows or even a family open day at your business. It is the ideal way to show your company's appreciation for those involved with your business and is certain to draw the crowds to a seasonal sale at your store.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Why not make it the full package? Combine one of our gorgeous grottoes with a &lt;a title="Christmas Photo Booth Hire" href="/pages/christmas-photo-booth-corporate-event-hire"&gt;seasonal Photo Booth&lt;/a&gt; or our Social Media Pod - allowing your guests to capture their Christmas memories. They may even get a snap with Father Christmas himself!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;There are still a few spaces available to hire out our Christmas Grottoes this festive season. So, give us a call today to check availability and bring the party to life at your Christmas event!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;img alt="" style="border: 1px solid #000000' border-image: none' width: 250px' height: 188px';" src="/userfiles/elves.jpg" /&gt;&lt;img alt="" style="border: 1px solid #000000' border-image: none' width: 250px' height: 188px';" src="/userfiles/grotto-1.jpg" /&gt;&lt;img alt="" style="border: 1px solid #000000' border-image: none' width: 250px' height: 188px';" src="/userfiles/grotto-inside.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;</description></item><item><title>Mirror, Mirror out at Wasps, where will I go next?</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-10-31/mirror-mirror-out-at-wasps-where-will-i-go-next</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-10-31/mirror-mirror-out-at-wasps-where-will-i-go-next</guid><pubDate>Wed, 31 Oct 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;We recently visited a long-standing client of ours to deliver our &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Mirror&lt;/a&gt; to their hospitality area, pre-Wasps match. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A Magic Mirror was a perfect fit for their pre-match event, as it allowed their season members the chance to get creative with a range of props and strike a pose. Each guest was able to get a hard copy of their photograph, giving them something tangible to take away from the event. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For the company themselves, it is a great piece of marketing as you can brand each print to have a company logo or message, making the prints unique to your event!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This unusual photo machine will really stand out and make your audience smile! Perfect for a huge variety of events from &lt;a title="Company Award Ceremonies" href="/category/company-award-ceremonies"&gt;award ceremonies,&lt;/a&gt; exhibitions to draw in the crowds or event a product launch! Making every event memorable for your attendees. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Magic Mirror being more compact than a traditional photo booth means it can fit into smaller areas for instance at trade shows but will give a big impact to guests! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But don't forget the mirror also gives cheeky compliments too!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So give one of our team a call today to check the availability of our Magic Mirror for your next event!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Gallop to victory!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-10-24/gallop-to-victory</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-10-24/gallop-to-victory</guid><pubDate>Wed, 24 Oct 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Looking for something different to entertain your guests with? Or planning a Race Night event? &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Well Fun Pro UK's &lt;a title="GOLD CUP HORSE RACING" href="/category/arcade-games/29/gold-cup-horse-racing"&gt;Gold Cup Horse Racing Hire &lt;/a&gt;will be perfect. Complete with four horses all saddled up and ready to race. All you need to do is pick your racer - will it be green like the grass your race on, blue like the sky, red like your determination or yellow for the beaming smile you'll give when you win?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pick up your horse and gallop your way to victory by holding the handles. The faster you gallop, the quicker you'll be crowned the ultimate jockey. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This interactive game works at a huge range of events from team building days, award nights or at exhibitions, helping to increase your footfall. This game isn't just fun for those playing, it is entertaining for those watching and people will flock around to see the racing go underway. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why not pair this product with our leader board to find the fastest jockey at your event or keep it to the winner of each race!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whatever event you host, the Gold Cup Horse Racing Hire will go down a treat with all your guests!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So call us today on 02476 629197 to discuss how we can add a buzz to your next event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;</description></item><item><title>Top things to think about when planning a corporate event</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-10-17/top-things-to-think-about-when-planning-a-corporate-event</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-10-17/top-things-to-think-about-when-planning-a-corporate-event</guid><pubDate>Wed, 17 Oct 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;div&gt;When it comes to planning a &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;corporate event&lt;/a&gt; there is lots to think about from the venue to the theme, sending out invitations to staffing. But don't worry as we have put together a list of the important things to remember when planning an event.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What is the purpose of the event?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;It is easy to get carried away when planning an event from thinking about things such as the aesthetics of the event, but ensuring that you stick to the purpose of the event is critical for its success. A simple way of doing this is to set out aims/objectives for the event before you start, whether it is a product launch that you wish to share with your customers or an awards ceremony to reward your employees. Without having structured aims your event is likely to be costly without huge effectiveness.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How to ensure your guests hear about your event?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Different groups of people will respond better to different forms of media when getting the information out about your event. Many more people are using social media and emails to receive invitations to events than ever before. But this might not be the correct communication method for all events and audiences. So it is important for any event organiser to analyse the target audience for their event to ensure the time and money put into marketing your event to attendees is effective. &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How do you keep your attendees engaged?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Depending on the type of event you are organising and the objectives you've set, you will change the entertainment you provide. &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;For a conference you may want to consider a high-profile speaker in the topic of the conference. &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;If you venue has special features such as being a sports ground, why not offer the chance of a tour.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Alternatively, get your audience engaging online through a discussion on Facebook or show your audience's tweets on a big screen. &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Although whatever event you are hosting, interactive games will always go down a treat! Fun Pro UK can provide a huge variety of interactive games from &lt;a title="Racing Car Simulators" href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;Race Car Simulators&lt;/a&gt; to giant table top games to Strike a Light Challenge, which are all guaranteed to add that extra level of excitement to your event. &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Alternatively, you could engage your audience using &lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;Photo Booths or Magic Mirrors&lt;/a&gt; which produce hard copies of all photographs and in some cases can be connected instantly to social media using your event's unique hash tag. &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Have you considered all the areas of logistics?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Although these may seem like small problems to solve, if you don't tackle them correctly they could become a much larger issue during or after your event. For instance, the flow of traffic and parking contributes to the safety of all your attendees. Alongside having enough and well-trained staff who are prepared for any situation. Other areas of logistics that organisers should consider (but not limited to): signage, food, sponsorship, facilities, set up/build plan and audio-visual elements.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Do you need a de&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;brief&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Debriefs are so important to ensure that you managed to hit the aims you set before the event. It is a great chance to analyse what worked well within your event, anywhere from d&amp;eacute;'cor or location of the venue. But it is also critical in giving all those involved with organising the event the chance to discuss what they felt didn't go to plan such as traffic flow to the event schedule.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;However you organise your event, Fun Pro UK are specialists in event planning and corporate entertainment and will be happy to help with any enquiries. So just pick up the phone and give our team a call today! &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Energetic Electronic Basket Ball Hire!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-10-11/energetic-electronic-basket-ball-hire</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-10-11/energetic-electronic-basket-ball-hire</guid><pubDate>Thu, 11 Oct 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Looking for something different to entertain your guests at your upcoming event? &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why not consider our heart pounding &lt;a title="ELECTRONIC BASKET BALL HIRE" href="/category/arcade-games/6/electronic-basket-ball-hire"&gt;Basketball Game Hire&lt;/a&gt; to put your attendees head to head and a chance to show off their skills. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With two hoops you can challenge each other head to head or organise a knockout competition. Perfect for a staff party or delegates on a break in conference. Or why not incorporate it within a team building day or family fun day. Ideal for both adults and children, everyone is able to get involved.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Being a self-contained game, it can be popped-up almost anywhere from the reception area of a conference to the back of an annual awards ceremony. Having side netting and a printed canvas ball catcher, allows all the entertainment to be captured! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="/category/interactive-game-hire/6/electronic-basket-ball-hire#BodyContent"&gt;Check out our 5 star reviews on this product! &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No matter the event or no matter where it is, Fun Pro UK will do their absolute best to ensure your guests are fully entertained! So give us a call today on 02476 629197.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Importance of Photo Booths!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-10-03/importance-of-photo-booths</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-10-03/importance-of-photo-booths</guid><pubDate>Wed, 03 Oct 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Recently we joined many of &lt;a title="Putting KPMG in the Picture" href="/pages/putting-kpmg-in-the-picture"&gt;KPMG's staff in Birmingham for their annual awards night&lt;/a&gt;. We attended with two of our most popular &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;Green Screen Photo Booths.&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For a company hosting an awards night is incredibly important in showing your staff that you value their continual hard work throughout the year. But as we all know there are lulls in these types of events when acts are changing over on stage or between courses. So why not put some &lt;a title="Interactive Game Hire " href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; or a few &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;photo booths&lt;/a&gt; into your next event to keep your staff entertained.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Photo Booths at KPMG's&lt;a title="Company Award Ceremonies" href="/category/company-award-ceremonies"&gt; award night&lt;/a&gt; went down a storm with continual queues through the whole time we attended. The massive benefit of photo booths are that your guests get a tangible item from your event. Meaning they are able to take away the memories of the night. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With a variety of props, all guests can find the perfect item to pose with. Allowing everyone the chance to let their hair down and enjoy a night off with colleagues. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why not contact one of our friendly team on 02476629197 or Email &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt; today to discuss how we can keep your guests entertained! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br&gt;</description></item><item><title>Are we connected?</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-09-26/are-we-connected</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-09-26/are-we-connected</guid><pubDate>Wed, 26 Sep 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Are we connected? Have you seen all our social media?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have very active Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn and Instagram pages, where you can see a whole range of information about Fun Pro UK.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We post about events we have attended and been hired at, insights into the industry and most importantly our products and services that will give the wow factor to your next event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why not follow, like and connect with us now to find out more about Fun Pro UK.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.facebook.com/funprouk/"&gt;&lt;img alt="" style="width: 80px' height: 80px';" src="/userfiles/Social%20media%20logos/facebook.png" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://twitter.com/funprouk"&gt;&lt;img alt="" style="width: 80px' height: 80px';" src="/userfiles/Social%20media%20logos/twitter.png" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://www.instagram.com/funprouk/"&gt;&lt;img alt="" style="width: 80px' height: 80px';" src="/userfiles/Social%20media%20logos/instagram.png" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/liz-parker-90a194134/"&gt;&lt;img alt="" style="width: 80px' height: 80px';" src="/userfiles/Social%20media%20logos/linkedin.png" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="/pages/contact-fun-pro-uk#BodyContent"&gt;&lt;img alt="" style="width: 80px' height: 80px';" src="/userfiles/Social%20media%20logos/email.png" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;</description></item><item><title>How to make your Christmas event stand out from the rest</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-09-19/how-to-make-your-christmas-event-stand-out-from-the-rest</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-09-19/how-to-make-your-christmas-event-stand-out-from-the-rest</guid><pubDate>Wed, 19 Sep 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Fun Pro UK are &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;corporate entertainment&lt;/a&gt; specialists who work alongside each client to make their brand and event stand out. We have helped many clients with their Christmas parties, including MIB, Suzuki and Rant and Rave. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here are some of our favourite &lt;a title="Christmas Game Hire " href="/category/christmas-game-hire"&gt;Christmas party themes&lt;/a&gt; to treat your staff this December. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Change up the traditional Christmas party and make it a Black-Tie affair. Hire our casino table to add that next level of sophistication and our James Bond themed Photo Booth, to give all your guests the chance to make home a memento. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alternatively, bring back summer with your very own carnival. Let your employees travel back to their childhood and play the games they once did at the fair. We have a wide range of carnival games including luck A Duck, Giant Buzz Wire, Gold Cup Horse Racing and even a Retro Arcade Machine. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;However, if you want to stick to the traditional Winter Wonderland theme, we have lots of products to make your event magical and unforgettable. Try out our magnificent &lt;a title="Christmas Grotto Hire " href="/category/christmas-grotto-hire"&gt;Santa's grotto&lt;/a&gt; to enhance the whole atmosphere of the event. This comes beautifully decorated with a white picket fence, snow covered trees and even a snowman or reindeer. Our seasonal selection also includes festive themed Photo Booths, and even adult sized bouncy castles to really add bounce to your company party. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you haven't had the chance to organise an awards night during the year, the Christmas party is a great chance to show your appreciation and recognise the hard work and determination of your team. Whether you want to have an Oscar style event or keep it traditional with a festive celebration, you will reap the rewards the following year with the continued happiness on your employees. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Can't decide what theme to go for? Why not get your departments voting for what party they want. Or call one of the friendly team here at Fun Pro UK (02476 629197), who can talk you through all the options to create the best Christmas party yet! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;</description></item><item><title>The importance of throwing the company Christmas party</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-09-12/the-importance-of-throwing-the-company-christmas-party</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-09-12/the-importance-of-throwing-the-company-christmas-party</guid><pubDate>Wed, 12 Sep 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;We know it is only September and you don't really want to be thinking about the company Christmas party yet. But you need to get to it early to secure yourselves the best corporate entertainment available. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here at Fun Pro UK we understand the importance of throwing a &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;company Christmas party&lt;/a&gt;. Check out our top reasons for why you should host a staff party this Christmas. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Shows the company's appreciation for their staff's hard work over the last year, which often leads to teams feeling more motivated and therefore increasing achievement for the following year. &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Helps to boosts morale and strengthens communication and teamwork within departments.&lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Helps staff retention as they have good memories of the company to look back on. &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;However, we recognise that not all companies have huge pots of money to host a &lt;a title="Christmas Game Hire " href="/category/christmas-game-hire"&gt;Christmas event&lt;/a&gt;. So why not think about having a party during a lunch time within the office. This way more people may be able to attend rather than an evening event, and you would still see the benefits of rewarding your staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alternatively, you could push back the party until January when more staff may be free as everyone knows December is a very busy month. This could also give your staff something to look forward to in the new year, to wipe away those post-Christmas blues. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check out our blog next week for more ideas for your Christmas party and &lt;a title="Christmas Grotto Hire " href="/category/christmas-grotto-hire"&gt;products&lt;/a&gt; that Fun Pro UK can offer to make it extra special. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;</description></item><item><title>SAS guests head for the chequered flag!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-08-29/sas-guests-head-for-the-chequered-flag</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-08-29/sas-guests-head-for-the-chequered-flag</guid><pubDate>Wed, 29 Aug 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Fun Pro UK were recently hired to provide &lt;a title="Racing Car Simulators" href="/category/arcade-games/5/racing-car-simulators"&gt;Race Car Simulators&lt;/a&gt; to an event close to our base in Coventry. This was for a large car parts company that wanted to put on a promotional event to thank all their customers for their continual support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This was an exciting event for us as we were invited to put our simulators head to head and the event guests could race against each other to become the top of the leader board. This became very competitive as the night went on, with the top three drivers winning prizes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Comments received on the night included how realistic the graphics were and how much fun contoured racing seat, smart steering wheel that moves with the driving on screen and authentic pedals made for a genuine racing experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It was a great experience for Fun Pro UK to be involved with such an original event idea. However, our Race Car Simulators are perfect for car dealerships, car parts companies and manufacturers, and would fit into a range of events from car launches to fun days, trade shows to car related sales promotions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested in hiring out Race Car Simulators, please call one of our team on 07769 979 676 or email us at &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="" style="border: 2px solid #000000' width: 334px' height: 250px';" src="/userfiles/race-car-simulator-3.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="" style="border: 2px solid #000000' width: 428px' height: 250px';" src="/userfiles/race-car-simulator-4.jpg"&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description></item><item><title>Benefits of Team Building Days</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-08-22/benefits-of-team-building-days</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-08-22/benefits-of-team-building-days</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Aug 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;In every corporate business there is a variety of people interacting with one another on daily tasks and projects. The effectiveness of this communication will determine the success of the business. If colleagues can learn to work together through activities outside their usual tasks, there can be a better working relationship delivering cohesive results across departments. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are a range of team building activities from problem solving to skills bases activities, to communicating with ice breakers. All contributing to the benefits of team building sessions. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our top five benefits to these activities are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1) Keeps employees motivated &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-left: 40px';"&gt; Employees will take note that the business is taking an interest in their success and developing their skills. This is likely to be reciprocated by the employee as they will invest themselves in the business, through taking pride in their work and aiming to achieve company goals. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2) Improving communication &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-left: 40px';"&gt;&lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;Team building activities&lt;/a&gt; allow for clearer communication and co-operation between staff, which can develop into smoother relations between employees and success in projects. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3) Improved productivity &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-left: 40px';"&gt;A range of team building activities will allow staff to see the skills of their colleagues and their approaches to problems. This knowledge is then transferred into the workplace, allowing individuals to benefit from each other's abilities within their work. Often allowing work to be completed in a more effective manner. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4) Developing problem solving skills &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-left: 40px';"&gt;Lots of team building activities involves a group to solve a problem, under less pressure then they may feel within their office environment. This often results in employees reaching the solution, despite hurdles, and feeling more confident with their abilities. This new skill can be transferred back into the workplace. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5) Builds trust&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-left: 40px';"&gt;These activities will enable employees to learn about each other through their interactions, allowing them to trust each other within and out of the corporate environment. A team without a level of trust in each other, simply won't function and won't achieve the company's goals. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are both benefits to the individual and the company from undertaking team building activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;</description></item><item><title>Tis’ the season to organise your Christmas party!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-06-27/tis-the-season-to-organise-your-christmas-party</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-06-27/tis-the-season-to-organise-your-christmas-party</guid><pubDate>Wed, 27 Jun 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;With all this lovely Summer weather it's hard to start thinking about organising the work Christmas do. We get it, you're thinking about relaxing on your summer holiday and will sort it out when you get back. There's only one problem with this strategy, other companies are organising theirs now and if you don't get started, you'll find you've missed the boat when it comes to venue and entertainment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To help get you started we've put together a quick guide on things to consider now, to ensure your &lt;a title="Christmas Game Hire " href="/category/christmas-game-hire"&gt;Christmas event&lt;/a&gt; is memorable and hopefully, stress free.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Set the date for your event. If possible have a few dates in mind which can be narrowed down to one based on the availability of your venue.
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Find out your budget. Everything you do will depend on this!
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;If your event is going to be large, consider putting together a committee to help you with planning and organising.
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Decide on a venue &amp;amp; book it. Take into consideration your budget, how many people will be coming and the atmosphere you are trying to create.
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Decide on a theme. Themes can add a little extra something to an event. There are hundreds to choose from so consider your party goers and what they might like.
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Consider what entertainment you will have on the day or night? Will you have a band, DJ or background music? Will you have other forms of entertainment such as a magician, photo booth or interactive games. These too need to be booked early to ensure you don't miss out.
 &lt;/li&gt;
 &lt;li&gt;Agree on the type of food you will be serving at your event. Will it be a sit-down dinner, buffet or finger food? If your venue has its own caterers, then there's less to do but if you need outside catering, you need to get organising.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So, if you've been given the task of organising this year's Christmas party, set aside a few hours in the next few weeks to start planning the event. You can then head off on holiday knowing you have the Christmas party in hand and there will be minimal work needed when you get back.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>5 tips for running a successful event!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-06-10/5-tips-for-running-a-successful-event</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-06-10/5-tips-for-running-a-successful-event</guid><pubDate>Sun, 10 Jun 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>Successful events don't happen by accident. They take a lot of time, hard work and planning. Here are our tips to help you create a successful event that not only runs smoothly but is also stress free.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
1. Planning. Begin planning as soon as you can. Make a plan of all the elements that need to be considered to make your event a success. Venues, caterers and entertainment all book up early. If your event is reasonably small and simple, a month or two should be enough lead time. If your event is larger, you should begin planning 6-12 months ahead of time. &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
2. Delegation. You can't do it all! Assemble a trusted team to support you and share out the tasks. Breaking the tasks into sections can often help here. Put someone in charge of areas such as entertainment, catering and logistics. &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
3. Communication. Keep the lines of communication going between yourself, your team and your suppliers. The more communication there is between you leading up to the event the less likely there is to be a problem on the day. &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
4. Marketing, marketing, marketing. You may have organised the best event but if nobody comes your efforts have been wasted. Spend time thinking and planning the best ways to promote your event to potential attendees. Consider a range of marketing options from social media, emails, flyers and networking.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
5. Create a plan for the day of the event. To ensure your event goes smoothly on the day, create an event day plan or running sheet. If possible, go through the plan with all those involved to ensure everyone is on the same page. If possible do a run through the night before or on the morning of the event to highlight any potential problems.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
We hope you've found these tips useful and that your event is a huge success!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Adding A Little Magic At The Botanical Gardens</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-05-29/adding-a-little-magic-at-the-botanical-gardens</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-05-29/adding-a-little-magic-at-the-botanical-gardens</guid><pubDate>Tue, 29 May 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Last week we were approached by an agency from London to supply entertainment for a corporate conference. The conference was being held at the beautiful Birmingham Botanical Gardens for the management of a well-known train operator. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The brief was simple, supply something that would entertain and add a fun element to the event as well as create wonderful memories. We supplied one of our &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;magic selfie mirrors&lt;/a&gt; for the afternoon and it went down a treat.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our magic selfie mirror is an original and unusual photo machine that not only takes great pictures of guests, but also pays them a cheeky compliment too, with messages written on the mirror and spoken. The mirror comes with lots of fun photo props including hats, feather boas and novelty glasses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Magic mirror has the option of adding a company logo or message to every print. The company holding this conference wanted to reinforce the message being delivered on the day, so each image was personalised with the motto &amp;amp;lsquo'Screw Average, create amazing'. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The attendees had a wonderful time dressing up and interacting with the mirror and now have a lasting memento of the conference and what their company is trying to achieve.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As well as magic selfie mirrors, Fun Pro UK also hire &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;photo booths&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a title="Interactive Game Hire " href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; for all manner of corporate events including expos, company parties and &lt;a title="Company Award Ceremonies" href="/category/company-award-ceremonies"&gt;award nights&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Congratulations Mr and Mrs Moore</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-04-09/congratulations-mr-and-mrs-moore</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-04-09/congratulations-mr-and-mrs-moore</guid><pubDate>Mon, 09 Apr 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;div&gt;On Saturday we spent a fabulous evening at the Citrus Hotel near &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Coventry" href="/pages/corporate-event-hire-coventry"&gt;Coventry&lt;/a&gt; helping this wonderful couple to celebrate their wedding day .&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;The evening party began at 7pm , our green screen dream machine photo booth was all ready to keep the guests entertained with our staff on hand to ensure each guest had a great time taking selfies all night long. We heard that the bride loved VW camper vans so this is what the couple chose for the outer skin of their booth which went amazingly well with their theme.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;It wasn't long until the booth became very busy and a crowd formed to see what all the fun was about! It was a gorgeous setting, for a gorgeous day. &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Congratulations to Mrs and Mrs Moore, we wish you a long and happy future together. Perfect Snap would also like to say thanks for hiring one of our &lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;photo booths&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center';"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/file/img-20180408-wa0005-resized-20180409-112103658.jpg" longdesc="VW Camper Van Photo booth" style="width: 250px' height: 334px';" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Corporate team building!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-02-09/corporate-team-building</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-02-09/corporate-team-building</guid><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p style="text-align: center';"&gt;Our team have had a busy week. One of our events was a team building conference day at a new venue for us in the centre of &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Coventry" href="/pages/corporate-event-hire-coventry"&gt;Coventry&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
We spent a wonderful day at The Welcome Centre. The staff there were so helpful and looked after us all day (we were kept topped up with coffee and a delicious lunch).&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Fortunately we were able to access the venue and set up our equipment the day before which meant we were all ready to go as the staff arrived on coaches for breakfast before the conference began!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Our &lt;a title="RETRO ARCADE GAMES" href="/category/arcade-games/4/retro-arcade-games"&gt;retro arcade game&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;magic selfie mirror&lt;/a&gt; were placed outside the main conference room. As soon as staff came out for their mid morning coffee they were immediately drawn to exploring the fun entertainment the company had hired.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Mean while down stairs in another gaming corner our &lt;a title="GIANT BUZZ WIRE" href="/category/interactive-game-hire/9/giant-buzz-wire"&gt;beat the Buzz&lt;/a&gt; and Strike a light game were on fire! No, we don't mean literally.. the guys and girls were super hot on these games trying to beat their opponents. We sure had a laugh and this was only at morning coffee!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Lunch time came around pretty quick and so did the crowds! Everyone wanted a go on the games, the beat the bleep was very popular with friends competing head to head to see who could get the best score, while our selfie mirror was raising the roof with its cheeky comments printing off team selfies!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Even the popular tribal dancers had a go on the buzz wire and posed for a great picture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center';"&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The staff had a wonderful time at their conference and Fun Pro UK once again provided our team building games for their amusements.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Beat the Bleep!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-02-06/beat-the-bleep</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-02-06/beat-the-bleep</guid><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt; One of our &lt;a title="Interactive Game Hire " href="/category/interactive-game-hire"&gt;interactive games&lt;/a&gt; which is all set up ready for a &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Coventry" href="/pages/corporate-event-hire-coventry"&gt;corporate event in Coventry&lt;/a&gt; tomorrow .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; The &lt;a title="GIANT BUZZ WIRE" href="/category/interactive-game-hire/9/giant-buzz-wire"&gt;Mega Buzz Wire game&lt;/a&gt; is a real popular choice of entertainment for corporate events. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This battery operated stand alone game is a one player challenge where you have to take the hand held wand through the magical electronic maze without touching it and avoid the bleep!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It's a real race against time and builds the excitement to see who can finish first! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can't wait to see the staff at their team building and conference enjoying this game tomorrow.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Saturday night Selfies at Milton Keynes!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-01-30/saturday-night-selfies-at-milton-keynes</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-01-30/saturday-night-selfies-at-milton-keynes</guid><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;div&gt;Our all singing and dancing Magic Selfie Mirror was out at a great corporate event on Saturday night with our friends in &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Milton Keynes" href="/pages/milton-keynes-corporate-event-hire"&gt;Milton Keynes.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;With our funny prop box on hand for everyone to choose hats, comedy glasses and hilarious signs it wasn't long before there was a real crowd. Donkey, Shrek's talking buddy was the voice over - he was working the crowd with his cheeky ass comments!&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;As more guests began to arrive the queue for the mirror began to grow. Groups of friends gathered ready to strike their pose for an outstanding selfie!&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;The&lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt; Magic Selfie Mirror&lt;/a&gt; from Fun Pro UK is a real source of fun &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;entertainment for corporate events&lt;/a&gt;. Whether it be an awards night or special celebration there is nothing like an instant print of you and your mates having fun to stick on the fridge as a memory of a fab night out!&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We would like to thank the guys and girls at Milton Keynes for hiring our services for your event. We are looking forward to working with you again next month!&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are arranging an event and you want the entertainment to be fun with great instant memories then contact us to see how we can help you! Remember, everyone loves a selfie!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Ansty Hall this Sunday!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-01-02/ansty-hall-this-sunday</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2018-01-02/ansty-hall-this-sunday</guid><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2018 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;We are getting excited at Perfect Snap HQ. This Sunday, 7th January at 1200 will be the first &lt;a title="Weddings" href="/category/weddings"&gt;wedding &lt;/a&gt;fayre of 2018!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Green Screen Dream Machine 3D Photo booth ,&lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt; Magic Selfie Mirror&lt;/a&gt; and Social Media Pod will all be on display for you to strike your pose and have your very own selfie taken there and then. Our hi-tech digital booths really are the talk of the town when it comes to your wedding entertainment. You and your guests will be amazed at the fun selfies they walk away with - it is an experience you will never forget!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The talking Magic Mirror will be in full swing - listen out for Donkey's cheeky comments as you stop by for a photo - nobody can resist a selfie with him!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If Social Media is your thing then this will be right up your street - our all new singing and dancing social media pod will be on display for you to instantly share that fantastic selfie to facebook and instagram tagging yourselves right at the fair for all of your friends to see!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ansty Hall Hotel is situated in the pretty little village of Ansty near Coventry is a wonderful venue with outstanding grounds for photographs on your special day. The Orangery room and the main hotel will be packed with many exhibitors to help you plan for your big event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fun Pro UK are regular guests at this hotel and can't wait to be back on Sunday. We really do hope to see you there. So, bring your best smile and come to say Hello!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Is it Christmas already</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-12-22/is-it-christmas-already</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-12-22/is-it-christmas-already</guid><pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Is It &lt;a title="Christmas Game Hire " href="/category/christmas-game-hire"&gt;Christmas&lt;/a&gt; already?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can't believe that Christmas really is around the corner now. We've been so busy helping to celebrate at wonderful parties, it's really crept up on us!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We've had a very busy 2017 and have recently taken delivery of some wonderful new products for you to hire, ensuring any event you host will be fun and entertaining.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This year we've seen our &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Selfie Mirrors&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;Green Screen Photo Booths&lt;/a&gt; become even more popular. Hiring these at private parties and corporate functions have bought great fun and laughter. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Everyone loves a selfie, right?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Perfect Snap have also taken delivery of a few new products this year. Our Social Media Pod has been a real hit for those wanting to engage and attract new clients on exhibition stands, conferences and meetings. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This stand-alone pod can be branded with your company logo and lets your clients, customers or guests takes their selfie and then instantly share it to social media! They can also email then to their personal email. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With this great new product and sharing capability, your guests and clients will always remember your event. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our interactive games have been a huge hit too. The 'Beat the Bleep' competitive speed game where you play head to head with your opponent hitting the flashing buttons to beat the clock, was very popular at an event last week. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As was our huge buzz wire game and not forgetting our 1980's retro arcade game which has definitely brought back childhood memories of Pacman and Space Invaders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We'd like to take this little opportunity to thank you for being a customer of Perfect Snap this year. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can't wait to see you all again in 2018.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Merry Christmas and a happy New Year! &lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Christmas Parties with the NEC</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-12-01/christmas-parties-with-the-nec</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-12-01/christmas-parties-with-the-nec</guid><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Last night saw Team Perfect Snap returning to the NEC in &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Birmingham" href="/pages/corporate-event-hire-birmingham"&gt;Birmingham &lt;/a&gt;to help celebrate Christmas with them just as we did last year!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This year, the theme was ' New York New York' for their Christmas Party. Our&lt;a title="Christmas Photo Booth Hire" href="/pages/christmas-photo-booth-corporate-event-hire"&gt; Selfie Mirror and Christmas prop box &lt;/a&gt; were hired to entertain the party goers!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our designers had already made a framed overlay with the companies chosen wording which looked fab on the instant photos. We were also able to design a custom screen over lay on the front of our mirror to accompany the New York theme.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team were happy to assist by setting up earlier in the day, way ahead of the start of the function to allow the finishing touches at the venue to be completed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/nec1.png" style="width: 300px' height: 226px' float: right';" /&gt;Once the guests had arrived for a drinks reception, the entertainment began. Our talking&lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt; Magic Selfie Mirror&lt;/a&gt; sprang to life and the Christmas party was in full swing. Everyone grabbed their friends and gathered around the props deciding which hat would look best for their photo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div data-imgsrc="https://media.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/AAIABADGAAgAAQAAAAAAAAyLAAAAJGM2YjczNjc4LTc0NzQtNDllZi1iOWVkLTY0NjJhOWQ2N2VkNw.png"&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Selfie Mirror proved very popular as always and everyone loved their instant photos that are printed as a souvenir of their evening . We had a great time meeting guests that had remembered us from last year too. Perfect Snap can't wait til next year!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Christmas Parties are Go!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-11-19/christmas-parties-are-go</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-11-19/christmas-parties-are-go</guid><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Last night saw our friends from Gefco celebrate in style with a Perfect Snap &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Selfie Mirror&lt;/a&gt; at their company&lt;a title="Christmas Game Hire " href="/category/christmas-game-hire"&gt; Christmas Party&lt;/a&gt;. We had been asked to customise the prints with their company slogan which was designed by our in house team.These looked fab on the instant selfies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Slate, at Lakeside Village Coventry was the venue of choice for the &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;corporate event.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The event began at 9pm, our team as always were flexible and arranged to attend and set up before the guests arrived.This always works so well and allows our event team to be in,set up and out as quickly as possible This gave the staff an instant surprise as they began to arrive and made the atmosphere great for the night ahead.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The event incorporated the annual staff awards ceremony which was followed by a celebratory meal. Once the formal bits and pieces were over then it was time to party!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our friends here really knew how to have a great time, the Selfie Mirror along with our over flowing box of props were busy all night long with groups of friends taking photos and then coming back for more!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Everyone had an instant print to take home as a fab souvenir. A great night was had by all as you can see from the photos.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Christmas in October!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-10-22/christmas-in-october</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-10-22/christmas-in-october</guid><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Christmas in October!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Wow! The Perfect Snap Team can't believe it, it's Christmas in October!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The past few weeks we have been out and about at several early Christmas parties along with corporate awards nights in &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Birmingham" href="/pages/corporate-event-hire-birmingham"&gt;Birmingham, West Midlands &lt;/a&gt;and &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Leicester" href="/pages/leicester-corporate-event-hire"&gt;Leicester &lt;/a&gt;- not forgetting our home town of &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Coventry" href="/pages/corporate-event-hire-coventry"&gt;Coventry&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our stunning &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Selfie Mirror&lt;/a&gt; was the main attraction at a venue in Leicester. This was an office party where the staff were busy dancing the night away and making great use of our prop box in front of the camera.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;During the same week the Magic Selfie Mirror also made a guest appearance for the Stone Water Company awards ceremony at a central hotel in the City of Birmingham. A huge event where our mirror was a great source of entertainment for the guests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;Green Screen Dream Machine Photo booth&lt;/a&gt; with the sleek black outer skin was also set up and ready for a &lt;a title="Corporate Entertainment " href="/category/corporate-entertainment"&gt;corporate Christmas Party.&lt;/a&gt; This event was themed for super heroes! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center';"&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://bouncycastlenetwork-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/f_auto/thumbs/aHR0cDovL2Z1bnByb3VrLmJvdW5jeWNhc3RsZW5ldHdvcmsuY29tL3RodW1icy5hc2h4P2NzPTIwMCZpbWc9Y2hyaXN0bWFzLWluLW9jdG9iZXIuanBn" style="border: 2px solid #d99694' width: 400px' height: 300px';"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The guests looked so cool dressed in their costumes and really got into the party mood along with their boss. The instant prints from the booth went down a storm, check them out!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you haven't booked your Photo booth or Selfie Mirror for your Christmas Party yet- don't panic we do have a few more dates in the diary! There is still time, so drop us a line!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email: &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Wedding Fair at Ettington Park</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-10-17/wedding-fair-at-ettington-park</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-10-17/wedding-fair-at-ettington-park</guid><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;On Sunday we attended a very busy &lt;a title="Weddings" href="/category/weddings"&gt;wedding &lt;/a&gt;fair at Ettington Park Hotel in Stratford Upon Avon. The hotel is on the far side of Stratford, approximately 6 miles from the town and is situated in stunning countryside with the River Stour running through the estate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
The mansion is a truly tremendous sight as you travel up the sweeping drive to the main entrance. Once we arrived it was all hands on deck to unload the Perfect Snap van which was packed full of our state of the art &lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;photo booths, selfie mirrors&lt;/a&gt; and of course not forgetting our brand new social media booth!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
So, it was a bit of a race against the clock before the show began and the first guests came through the entrance but working together as the Perfect Snap Team always do we made it!! We even had time for a coffee or two and a quick natter to the other companies who were there.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Our stand quickly became very busy - which we love!It is great to meet so many new people, we love to chat to the brides to be and find out a little more detail about their special day they are planning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
The green screen dream machine was feeling the vintage theme of the wedding show - demonstrating the gorgeous vintage outer skin of the booth - this proved very popular and everyone who tried our booth adored the choice it gave for photo themes and green screen backgrounds along with the high quality instant selfies it printed to take away!&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect Snap's &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Selfie Mirror&lt;/a&gt; was another popular attraction on our stand. You cant get away from Donkey talking right at ya!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Our new baby also drew a crowd - the new kid on the block, our Social Media Booth was a real popular addition. The selfies were taken and then socially shared by the guests on email, facebook and twitter. They were really spreading the word amongst social media!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
If you missed our stand on Sunday there is no need to worry - you can catch Donkey and the rest of the Perfect Snap Team again this Sunday at The Heart of England hotel and conference centre in Meriden - we would love to see you!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Sunday's Wedding Fair</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-09-12/sundays-wedding-fair</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-09-12/sundays-wedding-fair</guid><pubDate>Tue, 12 Sep 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;It was lovely to see so many people at the wedding fair on Sunday which was held at Ansty Hall Hotel in &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Coventry" href="/pages/corporate-event-hire-coventry"&gt;Coventry&lt;/a&gt; by Perfect Brides.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is a popular venue for us as we attend there often. Although we are normally in the Orangery Room at the hotel, this time we were in the Drawing Room which is actually in the main building. The building has so many features and we adore the huge grounds which are stunning for your photos on your wedding day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We had our vintage theme &lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;green screen dream machine photo booth along with our magic selfie mirror&lt;/a&gt; on show. This went down a storm with so many visitors on the day. Everyone we spoke to was delighted with our green screen booth and loved having their own selfie taken . We had lots of comments about how clear and bright the photo quality was not to mention all of our spectacular 3D effects you can choose to be on each photo. Eddie our voice over from our selfie mirror was on top form making his usual flattering comments to the guests - again another outstanding quality helping to make ever lasting memories!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you didn't get chance to see us at the show then don't worry we are guests at quite a few wedding fairs coming up - just check our Facebook page for venues and dates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Perfect Snap &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;photobooth&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;magic selfie mirror hire&lt;/a&gt; are holding the show offer all week, so if you didn't book with us for your wedding on the day then give us a call or drop us a line, we can't wait to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To book one of our perfect Booths please call 02476629197 or Email: &lt;a href="mailto:info@funprouk.co.uk"&gt;info@funprouk.co.uk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Weekend of 29th July 2017</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-07-31/weekend-of-29th-july-2017</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-07-31/weekend-of-29th-july-2017</guid><pubDate>Mon, 31 Jul 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>Wow! I can't tell you what a busy weekend we have had here at Perfect Snap. We seem to have been all over the place! On Friday we were at a beautiful wedding with a &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;green screen photo booth&lt;/a&gt; and our spectacular LOVE letters at Ardencote Manor, Warwickshire. This was a gorgeous venue where the guests were really in the mood to party! Our LOVE letters made a fabulous back drop shining brightly in the background. A 'lovely' effect!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Saturday saw us at a few venues in and around Warwickshire and &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Birmingham" href="/pages/corporate-event-hire-birmingham"&gt;Birmingham&lt;/a&gt; not forgetting Evesham too!. The first of our photo booths went to a wedding reception at Jephson Gardens, Leamington Spa, Warwickshire. Our green screen dream machine photo booth and the vintage retro themed outer skin was chosen by the bride for the entertainment during the evening reception. This looked amazing at the venue which over looks the park.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Our popular team member Ross was out with a Magic Selfie Mirror at the extravagant venue of Aston Villa Football Club, Birmingham. The guests had a great time at the wedding reception using our Mirror to have a selfie or two! It was a wonderful outlook onto the pitch from the room the special couple had &lt;a title="Weddings" href="/category/weddings"&gt;hired for wedding entertainment&lt;/a&gt;. Ross even managed to have a cheeky selfie himself with the football pitch behind him.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Warwickshire Golf Club, Warwickshire held yet another wedding reception last night where one of our Magic Selfie Mirrors took centre stage for the evening entertainment. The guests were very busy using our great prop box for their photographs and then sticking their selfies into the guest book we provided - it looked amazing, lots of pictures for the bride and groom to look back on of their special day.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Another green screen photo booth with the silver chesterfield outer skin arrived at Badsey Cricket Club near &lt;a title="Delivery Areas" href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;Evesham&lt;/a&gt; for an evening wedding reception. Again this went down a storm! Everyone adores our photo booths, they are fun and provide great entertainment and also gives the guests a memory of an instant print photo to take away with them. The props were out all ready for the guests to use as they waited to enter the booth. &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect Snap were busy that is for sure! - That is how we like it,!&lt;br /&gt;
We would like to take this opportunity to say a massive 'Congratulations' to all of the happy couples we have had the honour in meeting this weekend and thank you for using Perfect Snap.</description></item><item><title>Saturday 17th June</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-06-18/saturday-17th-june</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-06-18/saturday-17th-june</guid><pubDate>Sun, 18 Jun 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>Team Perfect Snap had a really busy evening yesterday, as did the people of Coventry City! There were lots of events happening in Coventry and we were invited to bring our &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;Photobooths&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Mirrors&lt;/a&gt; to a few!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
One of our Green Screen Dream Machine Photobooths were in attendance at a wonderful &lt;a title="Weddings" href="/category/weddings"&gt;wedding &lt;/a&gt;at one of my favourite locations - Coombe Abbey Hotel on the outskirts of Coventry. This is an absolutely gorgeous venue, the long drive up towards the hotel where you can see the elegant building before you with the park surrounding the themed hotel.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
We were able to set the photobooth up during the afternoon and the booth began at 7pm. As the evening guests began to arrive, friends and family were gathering around the booth, it creates a real party atmosphere!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Everyone wanted to have a selfie! we had a really busy night, it was a really great night!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Another Photobooth was in use at an Asian Wedding at the Allesley Hotel. This hotel again is a wonderful venue for a wedding and is situated right on the other side of &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Coventry" href="/pages/corporate-event-hire-coventry"&gt;Coventry&lt;/a&gt;. Once again, Team Perfect Snap was all set up and ready for the evening reception to begin at 7pm. There were lots of guests here at Allesley. We set all of our favourite props out ready to use and the guests didn't waste any time in choosing them for their selfies. Everyone loves a Selfie! The night flew by, guests came back again and again taking pictures using loads of different themed backgrounds from our new V3 Green Screen Dream Machine Photobooth - it really is unlike any other booth!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect Snap also helped entertain the guests at a Birthday Party at a pub in Kerseley, Coventry. This was for a special young lady's 60th! The Magic Mirror was a really winner with the guests at the pub. The Donkey voice over wowed the crowd with his cheeky comments and gave the guests a real laugh! Our Magic Mirror was in use all night - it really was a party to remember.</description></item><item><title>Hogarth's party</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-05-19/hogarths-party</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-05-19/hogarths-party</guid><pubDate>Fri, 19 May 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p original_font_attr="-1"&gt;On Friday we were in attendance at the marvellous venue Hogarths Hotel, &lt;a title="Delivery Areas" href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;Solihull&lt;/a&gt;. We are becoming part of the furniture here! It really is a fantastic place in a wonderful location. This time we were helping to celebrate a private party with our Magnificent &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Selfie Mirror&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p original_font_attr="-1"&gt;It was a very busy evening, once the mirror had been set up and Donkey was shouting to the guys and girls in his complimentary manner' all of the guests couldn't wait to 'strike a pose' using our over flowing prop box which had hats, glasses, inflatable guitars along with some comical signs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p original_font_attr="-1"&gt;The evening flew by as many friends came back for more photos!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p original_font_attr="-1"&gt;Thank you for letting us attend your party, we look forward to seeing you all again in the future.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Woodside Weddings</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-05-08/woodside-weddings</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-05-08/woodside-weddings</guid><pubDate>Mon, 08 May 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>Once again the guests who were in attendance at David &amp;amp; Michael's &lt;a title="Weddings" href="/category/weddings"&gt;wedding&lt;/a&gt; made full use of our ever popular &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;green screen dream machine photo booth&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
The booth was used to the max as you can see by some of the great photos that were taken for the evening reception at one of our favourite venues, Woodside Hotel in Warwickshire.&lt;br /&gt;
Team Alistair had a laugh with the guests and even got to appear in a few snaps himself!!&lt;br /&gt;
We would like to say a big congratulations to the happy couple and thank you for using Perfect Snap for such a wonderful wedding.</description></item><item><title>Magic mirror booth, Coombe Abbey</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-04-18/magic-mirror-booth-coombe-abbey</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-04-18/magic-mirror-booth-coombe-abbey</guid><pubDate>Tue, 18 Apr 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>On Saturday evening we attended the exclusive venue of Coombe Abbey Hotel in &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Coventry" href="/pages/corporate-event-hire-coventry"&gt;Coventry&lt;/a&gt; with our marvellous Magic Mirror Selfie Booth.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Our &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Mirror photo booth&lt;/a&gt; was a great feature to add to the evening entertainment for the wedding of Mr &amp;amp; Mrs Birch.&lt;br /&gt;
Team Perfect Snap set the equipment up in the bar area at the back of the hotel ready for the guests arriving for 7.30pm.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The wedding was a fabulous event, all of the guests were in the party mood and used our prop box to the max! The selfies with our mirror were great, all the guests came back for more!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
We would like to thank the newly weds for booking with Perfect Snap and would like to take this opportunity to wish Mr &amp;amp; Mrs Birch a very happy future together.</description></item><item><title>Whittlebury Park</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-04-10/whittlebury-park</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-04-10/whittlebury-park</guid><pubDate>Mon, 10 Apr 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>On Saturday evening we were in attendance at the &lt;a title="Weddings" href="/category/weddings"&gt;wedding reception&lt;/a&gt; of William and Jaimie. The bride looked stunning as did her maids.&lt;br /&gt;
It was the first time we had attended the venue of Whittlebury Park in &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Nottingham" href="/pages/nottingham-corporate-event-hire"&gt;Northamptonshire&lt;/a&gt; and I really must say it was stunning!&lt;br /&gt;
The Perfect Snap team arrived in plenty of time as normal to set our &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Mirror&lt;/a&gt; and overflowing box of props up ready to begin the evening of fun entertainment! &lt;br /&gt;
We always enjoy attending wedding receptions, all the guests have &lt;br /&gt;
had such a brilliant day and once the fun begins with their friends our team get busy helping them out taking that fabulous selfie!&lt;br /&gt;
On Saturday our magic mirror was hired from 7.30-11.30pm which is a great time to start as all of the evening guests have arrived to get the party started!&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect Snap had a very busy evening with a lot of happy guests at Whittlebury Park and would like to wish the new bride and groom a very long and happy future together!&lt;br /&gt;
From the Perfect Snap Team.</description></item><item><title>Woodside Wedding Fair 2nd April 2017!!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-03-31/woodside-wedding-fair-2nd-april-2017</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-03-31/woodside-wedding-fair-2nd-april-2017</guid><pubDate>Fri, 31 Mar 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>Woodside Wedding Fair - Sunday 2nd April 2017&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
We are getting excited! Perfect Snap will be attending Woodside Hotel Wedding Fair this Sunday in Kenilworth.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Woodside Hotel is a beautiful and very popular venue which is situated on the outskirts of Kenilworth. The beautiful sweeping drive way reveals this spectacular venue, ideal for your wedding.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
If you are planning your big day why not attend - there will be lots of companies showcasing their products from photographers, dresses, stationery, cakes and of course us!! There will be fun to be had by everyone especially the bhride to be!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
We will be attending with a talking magic mirror which takes awesome selfies and our all time favourite - the magnificent green screen dream machine photo booth - this really does stand out from the crowd. If you have seen or been in a photobooth before you really need to try ours, there is nothing like it!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Of course, there will be special offers to be had for bookings placed on the day. So, come down from 11.30- 3pm and have a Sunday Selfie with the Perfect Snap Team.</description></item><item><title>Mr &amp; Mrs Bull in Northampton</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-03-14/mr-and-mrs-bull-in-northampton</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-03-14/mr-and-mrs-bull-in-northampton</guid><pubDate>Tue, 14 Mar 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>On Saturday night we helped celebrate the wonderful wedding of Mr and Mrs Bull at the &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Northampton" href="/pages/northampton-corporate-event-hire"&gt;Northamptonshire Marriott Hotel.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
The special couple had booked us last minute and we at Perfect Snap were only to happy to help out!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect Snap arrived at the venue early giving the staff time to set up ready for the evening guests to arrive.&lt;br /&gt;
The party was soon in full swing, it really didn't take the guests long to be making the most of the &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;magic mirror&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;br /&gt;
The first photo to be taken was the newly weds themselves. Mrs Bull really did look beautiful in her wedding dress. Everyone had a fab time and left some real heart felt messages with the copy of prints in the guest book that we provide.&lt;br /&gt;
The happy couple had requested that Perfect Snap design a frame for them and put their newly married name and date on the prints as a little keepsake of their wedding. We enjoy designing the frames as everyone like to have something a little different - this time it was a Disney theme!&lt;br /&gt;
Before we knew it, the evening of celebrations was drawing to a close.&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect Snap would like to take this opportunity in wishing every happiness to the newly weds - Mr &amp;amp; Mrs Bull, also to thank them for using Team Perfect Snap!</description></item><item><title>Magic Mirror 18th Feb</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-02-22/magic-mirror-18th-feb</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-02-22/magic-mirror-18th-feb</guid><pubDate>Wed, 22 Feb 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>On Saturday 18th February, the Perfect Snap team attended a new venue. We spent the evening at Blackwell Grange. A beautiful venue in Shipston On Stour which is located on the outskirts of &lt;a title="Delivery Areas" href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;Stratford Upon Avon, Warwickshire.
&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt;
Our ever popular &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Mirror Booth&lt;/a&gt; had been hired to entertain the wonderful guests. Alistair, the mirror attendant for the evening set our talking stand alone mirror up in no time! The never ending prop box was opened and as soon as Donkey's voice began wowing the guests those selfies really began to flow!&lt;br /&gt;
Everyone loved the talking selfie mirror, it really gets the party started.&lt;br /&gt;
The guests left some beautiful messages in the Perfect Snap guest book for the new bride and groom to cherish.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
We would like to wish the happy couple a wonderful future together and thank you for letting Perfect Snap share your wonderful wedding day.</description></item><item><title>Draycote wedding fair</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-02-12/draycote-wedding-fair</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-02-12/draycote-wedding-fair</guid><pubDate>Sun, 12 Feb 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Team Perfect Snap are getting excited for the Wedding Inspo Evening which we are attending this a Thursday 16th February 2027 at the &lt;a title="Delivery Areas" href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;Draycote Hotel in Rugby, Warwickshire.&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We will be there with our Green Screen Dream Machine and marvellous talking &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Selfie Mirror &lt;/a&gt; for you all to see!&lt;br /&gt;
The evening will begin at 19.30, finishing at 21.30. On arrival there will be a complementary glass of bubbly, lots of demonstrations to take part in and items to sample. &lt;br /&gt;
During the event there will be a range of companies showcasing a variety of services for your wedding day. To name but a few there will be Make My Day wedding planning services, Nanna childcare agency along with Salters of Rugby.&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect Snap will invite you to try our &lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;Photo Booth and Magic Mirror&lt;/a&gt; as we firmly believe you need to try before you buy! What better opportunity is there for the bride to be to have a selfie taken with either the mother of the bride and the bridesmaids! &lt;br /&gt;
We look forward to seeing you there!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>1st Birthday Celebrations!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-02-08/1st-birthday-celebrations</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-02-08/1st-birthday-celebrations</guid><pubDate>Wed, 08 Feb 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;div&gt;Everyone had a fantastic time at the 1st birthday party of a little girl in &lt;a title="Magic Mirror Hire Birmingham" href="/pages/magic-mirror-hire-birmingham"&gt;Birmingham&lt;/a&gt; on Sunday! There were some great memories captured! The Jewels Banqueting Suite venue looked amazing with all the table decorations and lighting. We set up our famous &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;magic mirror&lt;/a&gt; and laid out our awesome prop box ready for the party to begin. On each photograph the prints had a birthday message as a memorable keepsake. &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Upstairs, our sister company &lt;a href="http://www.bounceroosevents.co.uk"&gt;Bounceroos Events&lt;/a&gt; were also busy providing one of their unique packages. A bouncy castle, ball pool and band new soft play in a colourful 'party party' theme to amuse the younger guests.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;The party guests didn't waste any time! As soon as the guests had arrived everyone was busy taking selfies with the amazing Shrek Donkey voiceover - we had some real laughs! &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
Thank you for inviting Perfect Snap and Bounceroos Events to help you celebrate your special day.</description></item><item><title>Woodside wedding show</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-02-06/woodside-wedding-show</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-02-06/woodside-wedding-show</guid><pubDate>Mon, 06 Feb 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt; Perfect Snap attended the Wedding Fair held at the beautiful Wood house Hotel in Kenilworth.&lt;br /&gt;
We have been to this location many times, however it was our first Wedding Fair of 2017!&lt;br /&gt;
The Wood house Hotel is situated just on the outskirts of &lt;a title="Delivery Areas" href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;Kenilworth in Warwickshire&lt;/a&gt;. As you glide down the sweeping drive way visitors are able to admire the wonderful grounds that surround this outstanding venue. The most attractive building then awaits for your entrance.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Team Perfect Snap arrived bright and early in order to set up the award winning &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;Green Screen Dream Machine Photobooth&lt;/a&gt; and the famous talking Magic Selfie Mirror Booth.&lt;br /&gt;
This time we were situated in the suite which is at the rear of the hotel. A lovely bright large room where you can see everybody entering.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The doors opened at 11.30 for the fair and we soon found visitors coming in to have a Selfie!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Both our &lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;Photo booth and Magic Selfie Mirror&lt;/a&gt; really do get some attention! There were a lot of prospective brides, grooms and their lovely families investigating our talking mirror' with the voice of Donkey from one of my favourite films Shrek! Remember, 'the mirror don't lie'!!. This always brings smiles to peoples faces! Many a photo were taken with our magnificent prop box also on offer which is always full of hats, glasses, signs and inflatable fun toys.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
The Green Screen Dream Machine Photo booth also received many visitors. Guests at the Wedding Fair commented on what clear colourful pictures our booth produced and they were astounded at the amount of photo backgrounds that could be chosen. The magazine cover theme and the time machine seemed to be very popular along with the Big Eds feature!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Before we knew it, the day had flown by! We had been so busy talking to all of the lovely visitors and hearing about their wedding plans as well as taking bookings it was time to say goodbye.&lt;br /&gt;
Everyone loved our booth and talking mirror. Our January special offer of receiving 4 hours for the price of 3 was flying off the shelves, you really do like the 4 hour hire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Due to popular demand we have extended our January offer 4 hours for the price of 3 in to February!!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Kishan's 21st Birthday</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-01-30/kishans-21st-birthday</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-01-30/kishans-21st-birthday</guid><pubDate>Mon, 30 Jan 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>On Saturday night we were invited to attend the 21st birthday celebrations for Kishan! He and his family had booked one of our talking &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Selfie Mirrors&lt;/a&gt; for his big party. Everyone loves a selfie, it brings the best fun and entertainment to any event.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
We travelled to the &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Leicester" href="/pages/leicester-corporate-event-hire"&gt;Athena venue in Leicester&lt;/a&gt; for the event. This was a new venue for us but we found it easily and the set up was a smooth running operation as normal. As the guests began to arrive they were all intrigued as to what our mirror was. Magic Selfie Mirrors are a new concept in the U.K and Team Perfect Snap love to show off with our talking Donkey voice over (Shrek film lovers will know what I mean) interacting with all the party people in the room!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
It wasn't long before there were guests 'striking a pose' in front of the mirror!.&lt;br /&gt;
Choosing a prop from our bottomless prop box and gathering your best friends and family ready for your photo, there really is nothing better. Once a few photos had been snapped they are then printed in seconds and ready to be passed around to show the other guests!. There was always a queue of people waiting for their next picture.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The night was amazing, there were other gaming tables at the party and everyone had wonderful time dancing the night away.&lt;br /&gt;
Thank you for booking with Perfect Snap photo booth hire Kishan, we hope you enjoyed your special night.</description></item><item><title>Woodside Hotel Wedding fair</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-01-25/woodside-hotel-wedding-fair</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-01-25/woodside-hotel-wedding-fair</guid><pubDate>Wed, 25 Jan 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>We are starting to feel excited at TeamPerfectSnap! On Sunday 29th January we will be attending the Woodside Hotel Wedding Fair in the lovely town of Kenilworth.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
We have been guests at Woodside Hotel many times with our outstanding &lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;Photobooths and Magic Mirrors&lt;/a&gt; as has our sister company Bounceroos Events with &lt;a href="http://www.bounceroosevents.co.uk"&gt;inflatable bouncy castles&lt;/a&gt; for Wedding receptions.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect Snap adore attending wedding fairs at this venue, the grounds are stunning as is the building itself.&lt;br /&gt;
On Sunday we will be situated in the Redwood Suite which is located at the rear of the hotel.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You will find us with our famous &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;Green Screen Dream Machine Photo Booth&lt;/a&gt; and our award winning Magic Selfie Mirror. We are yet to decide whether our mirror will be talking donkey language or Austin Powers!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Come down and see us - we love to get to know our clients! The &lt;a title="Weddings" href="/category/weddings"&gt;wedding&lt;/a&gt; fair begins at 11.30am-3pm at Woodside Hotel, Glasshouse Lane, Kenilworth cv8 2al.&lt;br /&gt;
There is nothing better than taking your own selfie on a Sunday!</description></item><item><title>Look back at 2016!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-01-01/look-back-at-2016</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2017-01-01/look-back-at-2016</guid><pubDate>Sun, 01 Jan 2017 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>Wow it is 2017! Perfect Snap would like to wish all of our customers a Happy New Year. &lt;br /&gt;
We had a fabulous 2016 and were non stop meeting lots of our fantastic customers, bringing our &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;green screen dream machine photobooths&lt;/a&gt; to your weddings and birthday parties, not to mention the many &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Birmingham" href="/pages/corporate-event-hire-birmingham"&gt;corporate events&lt;/a&gt; we were invited to with our Magic Mirrors.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Our &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Selfie Mirrors&lt;/a&gt; proved to be a very popular addition this year. Whether it was the voice of Donkey from Shrek as the chosen voice over, or the brand new Austin Powers theme you really cant beat an interactive talking mirror at your event!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
We attended some beautiful venues in 2016, from The Hilton Hotels various sites in the West Midlands to The City Rooms in Leicester. The Nec Group in the heart of Birmingham to the &lt;a title="Delivery Areas" href="/pages/delivery-areas"&gt;Dunchurch Hotel in Rugby&lt;/a&gt;. Perfect Snap were also guests at a few wedding shows. We had a fabulous time at Ansty Hall Hotel, Brownsover Hall Hotel, Dunchurch Park Hotel, Woodside Hotel to name but a few&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
2016 also brought us some fabulous reviews from our clients. &lt;a title="Testimonials" href="/pages/testimonials"&gt;Five star reviews&lt;/a&gt; are really something for us to talk about! Our clients are great at giving us feedback on the wonderful service we provide, from our staff being polite, friendly and courteous from their initial contact to the professionalism and care shown on the date of the event&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
There are lots of plans for 2017 for Perfect Snap. Our diary is filling up already. We have bookings for weddings throughout the year and even into 2018! So, If you require a Photobooth or a Magic Mirror for your event in 2017 book now with Perfect Snap for an event you wont forget!</description></item><item><title>Corporate Branding on our Photobooths</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-12-21/corporate-branding-on-our-photobooths</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-12-21/corporate-branding-on-our-photobooths</guid><pubDate>Wed, 21 Dec 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;div&gt;Arranging your Corporate Event? Let Perfect Snap help with organising the function. Perfect Snap really will bring the FUN to your event.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Whether you are looking for a Photo Booth or Magic Mirror for you to have some group selfies taken, celebrate a new product launch, congratulate your colleagues at your awards ceremony or to entertain the children at a family day you can be sure that Perfect Snap can supply exactly what you are looking for.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 18px';"&gt;&lt;a title="Photo Booths &amp;amp; Magic Mirrors " href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors"&gt;Photo Booths&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Step inside one of our Green Screen Dream Machine Photo Booths and let your experience begin. With the most advanced technology you are able to choose from over 1000 themed backgrounds, layout and colour styles.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;You can even decide on colour or black and white prints.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;As you wait for your turn why not take a rummage in our never ending prop box! Our prop box is overflowing with comical hats, coloured glasses, inflatable guitars and not forgetting our funny signs to hold in that all important selfie!&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Four photo's later and out pop your prints ready for collection just as you exit the booth.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 18px';"&gt;&lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Selfie Mirror&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Searching for something a little different? Well, look no further! Our Magic Talking Selfie Mirror is a magnificent stand alone mirror, it will interact with your guests by talking to them in the popular voices of the well known character of Donkey from the award winning film Shrek or the popular voice of Austin Powers. As the mirror begins to talk, your guests choose a prop from our beloved prop box and strikes a pose to have their photo taken. Four photos are taken and then instantly printed to take away with them. &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 18px';"&gt;Customised Branding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;If you are arranging a corporate event and want to provide fun entertainment then our Photo Booth is what you are looking for!&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Our Photo Booths offer fabulous promotional opportunities and are extremely popular for all events including award ceremonies, fun days and parties.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Hire the most advanced Photo Booths or Magic Mirrors for your corporate event. Customised Branding can be added to the outer skin (additional costs apply) of any booth. This has a fabulous effect at a product launch or corporate event.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;You can even print a message on the photos that all of your guests can take away with them.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Perfect Snap has provided Photo Booth's for many corporate clients including The Nec, Dairy Crest, The Hilton Hotel to name but a few.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Perfect Snap guarantee 'to bring fun to your event'. Everyone really does love a selfie. They even have a photo with your logo and branding on to take home which will let that special memory never be forgotten.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;For further information of how we can help you arrange your corporate event drop us an email to: &lt;a href="mailto:info@perfectsnap.co.uk"&gt;info@perfectsnap.co.uk&lt;/a&gt;. A member of our team will be happy to help you&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Another great review!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-12-19/another-great-review</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-12-19/another-great-review</guid><pubDate>Mon, 19 Dec 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Another fantastic review received from one of our many happy Perfectsnap&lt;br /&gt;
customers. Check out our other reviews by visiting our &lt;a title="Testimonials" href="/pages/testimonials"&gt;testimonial page&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thank you for providing the photos so quickly. The mirror definitely went down well.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thank you to your team and also to Ricky.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Will be recommending you to friends and family!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have a great Christmas and New Year.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Party Party Party</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-12-12/party-party-party</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-12-12/party-party-party</guid><pubDate>Mon, 12 Dec 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;Wow! What a busy weekend we have had. It certainly was the weekend for partying!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;From Children's birthday parties with our wonderful Christmas themed photo booth in &lt;a title="Corporate Event Hire Bristol" href="/pages/bristol-corporate-event-hire"&gt;Warwickshire&lt;/a&gt; to an adult birthday party at The Style Bar in Rugby. It was all go for the Perfect Snap Team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We also had a few spectacular Christmas parties at Stoneleigh, not forgetting a very special December wedding which we attended at Ansty Hall Hotel, Ansty.&lt;/p&gt;
The Perfect Snap Team had a busy weekend bringing fun to everyone's event. We would like to take this opportunity to thank our customers for booking with Perfect Snap Photo booth hire.</description></item><item><title>Ansty Hall 19th November 2016</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-11-20/ansty-hall-19th-november-2016</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-11-20/ansty-hall-19th-november-2016</guid><pubDate>Sun, 20 Nov 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>Wow! What a fabulously busy night we had for Jason &amp;amp; Sophie's &lt;a title="Weddings" href="/category/weddings"&gt;wedding&lt;/a&gt; yesterday at The Ansty Hall Hotel.&lt;br /&gt;
We met this special couple at the famous wedding fair which was also at Ansty Hall this year where they saw our booth and Magic Mirror.&lt;br /&gt;
Our booth was situated in the Orangery Room for the evening reception. We had a great time as did all of the guests who used our over flowing prop box to have that all important selfie using the &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;Green Screen Dream Machine &lt;/a&gt;themed option. &lt;br /&gt;
The Green Screen is by far the best choice of entertainment for any event giving the guest a real variety of themes including: magazine covers, pop art, time machine, celebrations, 3D, big edz, around the world and lottery winner!&lt;br /&gt;
Everyone had a ball! There were some lovely messages in our guest book from the couples family and friends.&lt;br /&gt;
It was a fantastic wedding. &lt;br /&gt;
Thank You for booking with Perfect Snap and best wishes to you both for a happy future together.</description></item><item><title>CHRISTMAS PHOTO BOOTH</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-11-13/christmas-photo-booth</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-11-13/christmas-photo-booth</guid><pubDate>Sun, 13 Nov 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;div&gt;Yeah!! Look what Perfect Snap has for Christmas! &lt;br /&gt;
We are super excited to introduce our brand new &lt;a title="Christmas Photo Booth Hire" href="/pages/christmas-photo-booth-corporate-event-hire"&gt;Christmas Photo Booth&lt;/a&gt; for the party season.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="/userfiles/gimp5.png" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Let us add the finishing touch to your party night with our fabulous &lt;a title="GREEN SCREEN PHOTO BOOTHS" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/10/green-screen-photo-booths"&gt;Green Screen Dream Machine Photo Booth&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Everyone adores a &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;selfie&lt;/a&gt; to take home after an awesome night out. With our Green Screen booth your guests will have a real night to remember.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
With a fabulous Christmas prop box, super imposed backgrounds to choose for your selfie, great friends and a few drinks you have everything set to go!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
We still have a few dates left for December but we are booking up fast.&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dunchurch Park</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-11-12/dunchurch-park</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-11-12/dunchurch-park</guid><pubDate>Sat, 12 Nov 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;So excited, on the way to Dunchurch Park Hotel in the beautiful town of Rugby, Warwickshire.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
We were here at this gorgeous venue the other month for the Dunchurch Park wedding fair and am delighted to be returning to see everyone.&lt;br /&gt;
Tonight, we are here to bring fun entertainment for a wedding reception with our &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Selfie Mirror&lt;/a&gt;. Along with our hilarious prop box. I know this will be a real hit!&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Will &amp; Sam 2nd November 2016</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-11-05/will-and-sam-2nd-november-2016</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-11-05/will-and-sam-2nd-november-2016</guid><pubDate>Sat, 05 Nov 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;It certainly wasn't any normal Wednesday! Last Wednesday we provided one of our fantastic &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Selfie Mirrors&lt;/a&gt; for the wedding of Will and Sam.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The happy couple and all of their wonderful guests had travelled the long distance from Liverpool to the beautiful venue of Shustoke Farm Barns for their wedding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We arrived at the barn in the evening to set up and were ready to let the fun commence for 7.30. We were positioned upstairs in the barn which was an ideal location for guests to have lots of selfie photos taken!.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Sam and Will chose to have their name and date of their wedding printed on the pictures, which i am sure you will agree looks amazing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Perfect Snap had a very busy night here, all the guests had a ball and came back for more photos which we love to see. We were looked after at the venue to and were fed stone bake pizza - mm mmm!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Not a normal Wednesday!</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-11-01/not-a-normal-wednesday</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-11-01/not-a-normal-wednesday</guid><pubDate>Tue, 01 Nov 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 28px';"&gt;Not a normal Wednesday!!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Our team at Perfect Snap HQ are looking forward to Wednesday! Yes, Wednesday 2nd November 2016, This is no normal mid week day, it is actually a very special date for two people!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect Snap are so excited as we will be attending the wedding of Sam and Will!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
This special couple will be getting married at Shustoke Farm Barns along with all of their marvellous family and friends who will be there to join in the celebrations.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect Snap adores attending weddings! It is such a wonderful occasion . Our fabulous &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Mirror&lt;/a&gt; will be there to make their evening one to be remembered with some spectacular selfies! &lt;br /&gt;</description></item><item><title>Leicester City Rooms</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-10-20/leicester-city-rooms</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-10-20/leicester-city-rooms</guid><pubDate>Thu, 20 Oct 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>We had a wonderful time at The City Rooms in Leicester on Saturday. This was our first time at this gorgeous venue set in Leicester.&lt;br /&gt;
The &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Mirror&lt;/a&gt; was as popular as ever with all of the guests that attended the wedding of Joanne and Peter.&lt;br /&gt;
As soon as we had finished setting up there was a large queue of party animals waiting to have their picture taken!&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect snap had a fabulous evening, there is nothing better to see than everyone having such a great time.&lt;br /&gt;
We would like to take this opportunity to congratulate the happy couple and thank them for booking with Perfect Snap.</description></item><item><title>Great day had at Wootton Park</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-10-18/great-day-had-at-wootton-park</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-10-18/great-day-had-at-wootton-park</guid><pubDate>Tue, 18 Oct 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;On Sunday 17th October 2016 Perfect Snap attended the wedding fair at
Wootton Park, Henley In Arden.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
It was a stunning venue, with gorgeous open countryside views and a
lovely outside area to sit and enjoy the sunny weather we were blessed
with on the day.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Perfect Snap team didn't have time however to enjoy the sun that
day, it was all hands on deck to set up our fantastic &lt;a title="MAGIC MIRROR" href="/category/photo-booths-and-magic-mirrors/13/magic-mirror"&gt;Magic Selfie Mirror&lt;/a&gt; ready for the wedding fair.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Our stand looked amazing!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; The Mirror alone is such a head turner, as
soon as that well known voice of donkey from Shrek begins to talk it
drawers a real crowd! Lots of prospective brides and grooms came
through the doors and had their pictures taken as did the smaller
attendees!!
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Wootton Park was extremely busy, lots of people came to view the
variety of suppliers that were there showcasing their goods.
We cant wait for the next one!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Wootton Park 16th October 2016</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-10-14/wootton-park-16th-october-2016</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-10-14/wootton-park-16th-october-2016</guid><pubDate>Fri, 14 Oct 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>&lt;p&gt;We are all getting excited at Perfect Snap HQ for this Sunday! Why I hear you ask?.... Well, we are attending the magnificent venue of Wootton in Henley in Arden for their wedding fair. Perfect snap will be there showcasing the Magic Mirror.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team would love to see you, so why not come down and check out interactive talking mirror for yourselves.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;See you there!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;P.S&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Better give you the address!!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The event starts Sunday 16th October from 12pm until 4pm&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Address: Wootten Park, Wootten Wawen, Henley in Arden B956HH (sat nav use B956HH)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dunchurch Park Wedding Show</title><link>https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-10-14/dunchurch-park-wedding-show</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.funprouk.co.uk/news/2016-10-14/dunchurch-park-wedding-show</guid><pubDate>Fri, 14 Oct 2016 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><description>It was lovely to see so many prospective brides and their grooms at the Dunchurch Park Hotel wedding show on Sunday 9th October October 2016. It really is a stunning venue, a very popular location for that special day.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
I had a fabulous time meeting everyone and introducing them to our Austin Powers Magic Mirror. The mirror has brand new software that stands out from so many of the mirrors that are currently on the market. This was a big hit, especially with the Austin Powers voice over, it is a real interactive experience that guests have never seen before. Even the staff at the hotel had a quick photo!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
I was able to speak with many people whilst I was at Dunchurch Park and really explain what great entertainment the Magic Mirror offers for the evening event! &lt;br /&gt;
It is a fabulous way to capture the party atmosphere, full of smiles and laughter . The best part is having an instant print for your friends to take home as a souvenir.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Our Magic mirror is a real head turner, as soon as you hear the mirror talking everyone's wants to see what it is! If you are looking for an alternative to a photo booth and want to stand on out from the crowd then this surely is it! Worried about space? - there is no need to be, the Magic Mirror from Perfect Snap will happily tuck away under stairs, near the bar or in any corner of your venue.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The quality of our mirror and the pictures it produces are second to none. We only use DSLR auto focus cameras, sub dye printers and studio lighting not forgetting our overflowing hilarious prop box which comes with every hire, all guests can take advantage of dressing up for the camera and make some marvellous memories.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
We were very busy taking bookings for 2017 and 2018 and wish to thank everyone that booked at the show, if you didn't book on the day then drop us a line as we still have availability.</description></item></channel></rss>